\id GEN (GEN.BTU) GeneŐāse en Langue Baga Sitem 
\h D…ôk…ôcop 
\toc3 DCOP 
\toc2 D…ôk…ôcop 
\toc1 Tawureta Musa, Buk 1: D…ôk…ôcop da Doru 
\mt2 Tawureta Musa, Buk 1: 
\mt1 D…ôk…ôcop da Doru 
\imt1 Moloku ma k…ôs…Ēk…ôs buk ba Musa b…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē: D…ôk…ôcop 
\ip Buk b…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ba Musa mb…õ aŇčwe ¬ęD…ôk…ôcop¬Ľ m…Ē buk ba k…ôd…õm k…ôkur ka Kitabu ka Kanu b…Ē. C…ôHeb…ôre yati c‚Äôancic…ôs bi ¬ęD…ôk…ôcop¬Ľ. Buk mb…õ bement…ôr nde mes f…ôp m…õy…õf…õ m…Ē, nt…õ Kanu k…Ē afum Ňčanacop k…ôsump…ôr mes m…Ē. Acic…ôs Ňčay…Ē m…Ēk…Ē moloku m…õlar…ôm ma afum aŇč…õ Ňčanacic…ôs buk ba D…ôk…ôcop m…Ē, k…Ē t…õm nt…õ anacic…ôs buk bab…Ēk…Ē m…Ē. Al…Ēma Ňčanc…õm-c…õmn…õ a t…Ēl…Ēma yecic…ôs yokur yoloŇčka nde Babil…ĒŇč y…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ ka meren masar cam…ôt-tin (600) haŇč k…ôb…ôp masar k…ôcam…ôt (500) ta antakom Yesu-…õ. Al…Ēma s…Ē Ňčawos…õ k…ôlaŇč k…ôkur, a Musa ecic…ôs s…ôbuk saŇčs…õ k…ôcam…ôt: D…ôk…ôcop da Doru, K…ôwur Dacar, ALewy AloŇčn…õ, K…ôl…Ēm ka aYisrayel k…Ē Sariy…õ S…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ k…ôy…õf…õ meren wul win masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (1.400) k…ôb…ôp ka meren wul win masar maas (1.300) ta antakom Yesu-…õ. 
\ip Buk ba D…ôk…ôcop b…Ēnt…Ēmp…ôr moloku m…õt…ôks…õ mm…õ m…Ēy…Ē d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…ĒŇč m…Ē, mm…õ m…õŇčmar k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč a Yesu Krist k…ôc…ôr…õ ka m…õlp…ôs ma Kitabu ka Kanu: K…ôd…õm k…ôkur k…Ē K…ôfu m…Ē. Buk bamb…õ b…ôment…ôr nt…õ k…ôciya k…ômb…õr…õ doru m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôfaŇč ka afum k…ôs…Ēt…Ē ka w…ôyac. Tat…Ēk…Ē tement…ôr s…Ē d…Ēp…Ē da Kanu k…ôyac ka afum. Antam k…ôn…ôŇčk tat…Ēk…Ē k…ôd…ôŇčk k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē teta Yesu (D…ôk…ôcop 3.15) k…Ē Kanu k…ônd…õr…ôm k…ôs…ĒŇč Abraham k…ôpoc…õ ka afum a doru f…ôp p…ôt…Ēt (D…ôk…ôcop 12.3). 
\iot Teyer ta Moloku ma Buk Bamb…õ 
\io1 1-2, Aloku t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônalomp…ôs doru, Adama k…Ē Awa m…Ē. 
\io1 3-5, Aloku teta Adama k…Ē Awa, k…ôciya k…ôŇčan k…Ē yuruya yaŇčan. 
\io1 6-9, Aloku teta Nuha k…Ē kutup k…ôp…ĒŇč. 
\io1 10-11, As…Ēk…ôs t…Ēk…Ē t…õnacep…ôr t…õm ta Nuha k…Ē Abraham dac…Ē m…Ē, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ teta k…ôl…Ē k…ôŇčeci ka Bab…õl. 
\io1 12-50, Aloku teta Abraham, k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ, k…Ē tocop ta afum aka Yisrayel: 
\io2 12-25, Aloku teyi ta Abraham k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn Sara. 
\io2 21-28, Aloku teta Siyaka k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn Rebeka, 
\io2 35, Aloku teta defi da Siyaka. 
\io2 25-50, Aloku teta Yakuba, awut …Ēn k…Ē k…ôcep…õ k…ôŇčan KanaŇč nde Misira. 
\io2 37-50, Aloku teta Isifu wan nw…õ Yakuba …õnanaŇčkan…õ k…ôb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Isifu …õnader p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ Misira m…Ē. 
\mt1 D…ôk…ôcop da Doru 
\c 1  
\ms2 D…ôk…ôcop da Doru 
\mr 1-11 
\s1 K…Ē Kanu k…ôlomp…ôs doru k…Ē afum 
\p  
\v 1 D…ôk…ôcop, k…Ē Kanu k…ôwur…õ k…Ēm k'ant…Ēf.  
\v 2 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…õnay…Ē f…õ teyi, kubump k…ônayi k…ôba k…ôroŇč. Mba Amera Ňča Kanu Ňč…õnayi s…Ē domun k…ôroŇč Ňčocbum Ňči.  
\v 3 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku: ¬ęP…ôwaŇčk…ôra peyi!¬Ľ K…Ē p…ôwaŇčk…ôra peyi.  
\v 4 K…Ē Kanu k…ôn…ôŇčk a p…ôwaŇčk…ôra pentes…õ. K…Ē Kanu k…ôŇčgb…õy p…ôwaŇčk…ôra k…Ē kubump.  
\v 5 K…Ē Kanu k…ôwe p…ôwaŇčk…ôra ¬ęd…Ēs…Ēk¬Ľ, k…Ē k…ôwe kubump ¬ępibi.¬Ľ K…Ē d…Ēf…Ēy deyi, k…Ē b…ôtb…ôt beyi, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē. 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku s…Ē: ¬ęP…ôkuym…õ peyi, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ domun deyers…õn…õ m…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 7 K…Ē Kanu k…ôy…Ē k…Ē p…ôkuym…õ peyi k…Ē p…õŇčgb…õy domun d'ant…Ēf k…Ē dak…ôroŇč, k…Ē teyi tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 8 K…Ē Kanu k…ôwe p…ôkuym…õ mp…õ ¬ęk…Ēm.¬Ľ K…Ē d…Ēf…Ēy deyi k…Ē b…ôtb…ôt beyi, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da m…õr…ôŇč. 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku: ¬ęDomun nd…õ deyi k…Ēm tant…Ēf m…Ē, doloŇčkan…õ tofo tin, p…ôwosu peyi, powur, peyi tak…ôroŇč!¬Ľ K…Ē teyi tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 10 K…Ē Kanu k…ôwe tofo towosu ¬ęant…Ēf,¬Ľ k…Ē k…ôwe mofo mm…õ m…õla domun m…Ē ¬ęc…ôba.¬Ľ K…Ē Kanu k…ôn…ôŇčk a tentes…õ tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 11 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku s…Ē: ¬ęAnt…Ēf ŇčopoŇč pubuk, yika Ňča defet, k…Ē t…Ēk yokom ny…õ yende yockom ant…Ēf k…ôroŇč taciŇča m…Ē! Y…Ēy…Ē s…Ē defet da yi!¬Ľ K…Ē teyi tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 12 K'ant…Ēf ŇčompoŇč p…ôbuk, k…Ē yika y…Ēy…Ē defet, k…Ē t…Ēk yokom y…Ēy…Ē defet da yi. K…Ē Kanu k…ôn…ôŇčk s…Ē a tentes…õ.  
\v 13 K…Ē d…Ēf…Ēy deyi k…Ē b…ôtb…ôt beyi, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da maas. 
\p  
\v 14 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku s…Ē: ¬ęYomot…ôr-mot…ôr yeyi d…ôp…ôkuym…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ d…Ēs…Ēk d…õgb…õy…õn…õ k…Ē pibi m…Ē! K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ma t…õm\f + \fr 1:14 \ft T…õm (ta teren): m…Ēl…Ēf…õ, d…õr…ôŇč, l…õŇčk, kat…õla, k…ôt…ôn.\f*, d…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē meren.  
\v 15 Y…Ēy…Ēn…õ yomot…ôr-mot…ôr ya p…ôkuym…õ ny…õ yende y…Ēcs…ĒŇč ant…Ēf p…ôwaŇčk…ôra m…Ē!¬Ľ K…Ē teyi tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 16 K…Ē Kanu k…ôwur…õ yomot…ôr-mot…ôr m…õr…ôŇč \it k…Ē k…ônd…õt yi\it*. Pomot p…Ēp…ĒŇč p…õtas…ôrn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk, k…Ē pomot p…õf…õt p…õtas…ôrn…õ pibi. K…Ē Kanu k…ôwur…õ c…Ēs k…Ē k…ônd…õt.  
\v 17 K…Ē Kanu k…ônd…õt yomot…ôr-mot…ôr ny…õ d…ôk…Ēm y…Ēcs…ĒŇč ant…Ēf p…ôwaŇčk…ôra.  
\v 18 Pomot p…Ēp…ĒŇč p…õtas…ôrn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk, pomot p…õf…õt k…Ē c…Ēs y…õtas…ôrn…õ pibi, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôwaŇčk…ôra p…õgb…õy…õn…õ k…Ē kubump. K…Ē Kanu k…ôn…ôŇčk a tentes…õ.  
\v 19 K…Ē d…Ēf…Ēy deyi, k…Ē b…ôtb…ôt beyi, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da maŇčk…ôl…õ. 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku s…Ē: ¬ęYeŇčes…ôm ya d…ôk…ôba y…õcs…õp d…ôromun. B…õmp y…õcf…õl…ôr-f…õl…ôr k…Ēm tant…Ēf!¬Ľ  
\v 21 K…Ē Kanu k…ôwur…õ s…õm y…Ēp…ĒŇč ya d…ôromun dokom dokom, k…Ē y…õŇč…õr…ôŇč-Ňč…õr…ôŇč ya d…ôromun, k…Ē domun doncop k…ôs…õp. K…Ē Kanu k…ôwur…õ s…Ē b…õmp dokom dokom. K…Ē Kanu k…ôn…ôŇčk a tentes…õ.  
\v 22 K…Ē Kanu k…ômpoc…õ yi p…ôt…Ēt\f + \fr 1:22 \fqa K…ôpoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt\ft  = ¬ęk…ôs…ĒŇč yi baraka¬Ľ.\f*, k…Ē k…ôloku: ¬ęN…ôy…Ēn…õ akomb…ôra, n…ôla, n…ôlas domun da d…ôk…ôba, k…Ē b…õmp, y…õla ant…Ēf k…ôroŇč!¬Ľ  
\v 23 K…Ē d…Ēf…Ēy deyi k…Ē b…ôtb…ôt beyi, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôcam…ôt. 
\p  
\v 24 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku s…Ē: ¬ęAnt…Ēf Ňč…Ēy…Ē yeŇčes…ôm dokom dokom, s…õm y…Ēc…Ēl, yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ, k…Ē s…õm ya d…ôkulum, f…ôp fa yi k…Ē dokom da yi!¬Ľ K…Ē teyi tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 25 K…Ē Kanu k…ôwur…õ s…õm ya d…ôkulum dokom dokom, y…Ēc…Ēl dokom dokom k…Ē yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ f…ôp dokom dokom. K…Ē Kanu k…ôn…ôŇčk a tentes…õ.  
\v 26 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku: ¬ęAwa, palomp…ôs fum teyi tosu, w…ôwur…õn…õ kosu, nw…õ endetas…ôrn…õ lop ya d…ôk…ôba, b…õmp ya darenc, y…Ēc…Ēl k…Ē yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ ya d…ônt…Ēf f…ôp m…Ē!¬Ľ 
\q1  
\v 27 K…Ē Kanu k…ôs…õl afum 
\q1 nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčawur…õn…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn m…Ē, 
\q1 k…Ē k…ôs…õl Ňča Ňčawur…õn…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn Kanu yati. 
\q1 K…Ē k…ôs…õl Ňča w…ôrkun k…Ē w…ôran. 
\m  
\v 28 K…Ē Kanu k…ômpoc…õ Ňča p…ôt…Ēt, k…Ē k…ôloku: ¬ęN…ôy…Ēn…õ akomb…ôra, n…ôla, n…ôlas ant…Ēf, n…ôboc ant…Ēf t…õfaŇč tonu! N…ôtas…ôrn…õ lop ya d…ôk…ôba, b…õmp ny…õ y…õŇčf…õl…ôr darenc m…Ē, s…õm k…Ē yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ ya d…ônt…Ēf f…ôp.¬Ľ  
\v 29 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku: ¬ęIs…ĒŇč nu yika ny…õ y…Ēy…Ē defet dakayi m…Ē, k…Ē yokom ya t…Ēk. Y…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu yeri.  
\v 30 S…õm ya d…ônt…Ēf, b…õmp ya darenc, y…õf…õl…ôr-f…õl…ôr ya darenc, k…Ē yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ ya d…ônt…Ēf, ca f…ôp ny…õ yeŇčes…ôm m…Ē, is…ĒŇč yi d…ômn…õ yika yobuk y…Ēy…Ēn…õ yi yeri.¬Ľ K…Ē teyi s…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 31 K…Ē Kanu k…ôn…ôŇčk a mes m…Ēk…Ē …õnay…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, m…Ēt…Ēt d…ôm m…õnayi. K…Ē d…Ēf…Ēy deyi k…Ē b…ôtb…ôt beyi, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da cam…ôt-tin. 
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 D…Ēs…Ēk da cam…ôt-tin dad…Ēk…Ē, di d'anal…ôp…ôs k…Ēm k…Ē ant…Ēf, k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē yeyi yi disr…õ m…Ē.  
\v 2 Tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē yolomp…ôs ya Kanu f…ôp yelip, k'…õsak, k'eŇčes…ôm tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ta y…õb…ôc y…Ēn.  
\v 3 K…Ē Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč p…ôleli. K'elel…ôs pi, bawo d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ē Kanu k…ôsak y…õb…ôc ya k…ôlomp…ôs y…Ēk…Ē …õnayi m…Ē.  
\v 4 D…ôk…ôy…õf…õ da k…Ēm k'ant…Ēf d…Ē dad…Ēk…Ē, nt…õ awur…õ yi m…Ē. 
\s1 Dal…õ da EdeŇč 
\p Nt…õ MARIKI Kanu\f + \fr 2:4 \fq MARIKI\ft  = Tewe ta Kanu c…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęYHWH¬Ľ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ¬ęIy…Ēn…õ¬Ľ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ¬ęIndey…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ\f* owur…õ ant…Ēf k…Ē k…Ēm m…Ē,  
\v 5 ali t…Ēt…Ēk pa dal…õ pin p…õnayi f…õ ant…Ēf k…ôroŇč, ali ayika Ňča dal…õ Ňčin Ňč…õnapoŇč f…õ t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē. Bawo MARIKI Kanu …õnator…õ f…õ w…ôcaf…ôn d…ônt…Ēf, fum …õnayi f…õ s…Ē, nw…õ …õmb…ôc ant…Ēf m…Ē.  
\v 6 Mba kifir k…ôncp…õ d…ônt…Ēf, nk…õ k…ôncd…ôm…ôs ant…Ēf f…ôp m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 7 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu …õs…õl…õ fum k…ôbof ka d…ônt…Ēf. K…Ē Kanu k…ôfurup k…Ē dolol…ôm kifir ka k…ôyin…õ doru, k…Ē fum …Ēy…Ēn…õ paka peŇčes…ôm.  
\v 8 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu …Ēmb…Ēf t…Ēk yokom nde dal…õ da EdeŇč, k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k'…õmb…õrs…õ di fum nw…õ …õnas…õl m…Ē.  
\v 9 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē t…Ēk yokom y…Ēb…Ēt k…ôdi yompoŇč…ôs-poŇč…ôs f…ôp, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ k…ôt…Ēk ka k…ôyin…õ w…ôyeŇč katina nk…õ k…ônac…ôm…õ nde dal…õ dac…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôt…Ēk ka k…ôc…ôr…õn…õ p…ôt…Ēt k…Ē p…ôl…õc. 
\p  
\v 10 K…Ē k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē k…ôwur EdeŇč, nk…õ k…ôncd…ôm…ôs dal…õ m…Ē. K…Ē k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē kaŇčk…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôyer…ôn…õ dal…õ disr…õ waca maŇčk…ôl…õ.  
\v 11 K…ôca k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k'ancwe ¬ęPis…ĒŇč¬Ľ, ki k…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr at…Ēf Ňča Hawila f…ôp, nde k…õma k…ôyi m…Ē.  
\v 12 Nde amb…ôp k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs m…Ē, t…Ēk yobotu amb…Ēnc,\f + \fr 2:12 \ft  Labund…õ docuca k…ôn…ôŇčk, di d'aŇčwe ¬ęb…ôd…õliy…Ēm.¬Ľ \f* k…Ē masar m…Ēt…Ēt meyim seŇč\f + \fr 2:12 \fq Masar m…Ēt…Ēt\ft  mm…õ aŇčwe ¬ę…Ēn…ôk…ôs¬Ľ m…Ē.\f*.  
\v 13 K…ôca ka m…õr…ôŇč k'aŇčwe ¬ęKih…ĒŇč¬Ľ, ki k…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr at…Ēf Ňča Kus.\f + \fr 2:13 \ft  Dif'aŇčwe m…Ēk…Ē ¬ęEcopi¬Ľ k…Ē ¬ęSudaŇč¬Ľ. \f* 
\v 14 K'aŇčwe k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka maas ¬ęTik…ôr¬Ľ\f + \fr 2:14 \fq Tik…ôr\ft  = K…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka t…Ēf ya Asi: LaTurky, Siri, k…Ē Irak.\f*, ki k…ôcep…ôr k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ dare da Asur m…Ē. K…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka maŇčk…ôl…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ ¬ę∆źf…ôrat.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 15 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu …õl…õk fum, k'…õmb…õrs…õ k…Ē dal…õ da EdeŇč disr…õ, a p…ôcb…Ēf…ôt ca, p…ôcbum…õn…õ s…Ē di.  
\v 16 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu entiŇč-tiŇč fum: ¬ęM…ôntam k…ôdi yeri ya dal…õ dand…õ f…ôp.  
\v 17 Mba ta m…ôdi pokom pa k…ôt…Ēk ka k…ôc…ôr…õn…õ p…ôt…Ēt k…Ē p…ôl…õc de! Bawo d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ m…ôndedi pokom pa ki m…Ē, m…ôŇčfi!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 18 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu oloku: ¬ęP…ômar f…õ w…ôrkun p…ôyi sona! Indelomp…ôs w…ômar…ôs k…Ēn, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčayi m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu …õŇčk…õr…õ s…õm ya dal…õ k…Ē b…õmp ya darenc ny…õ …õnawur…õ d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē, p…ôdem…Ēm…ôn nt…õ fum ende p…ôcwe yi m…Ē. Nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ yowur…õ y…Ēn f…ôp y…Ēy…Ē mewe mm…õ fum ende p…ôcwe yi m…Ē.  
\v 20 K…Ē fum …Ēs…ĒŇč s…õm y…Ēc…Ēl f…ôp mewe, k…Ē b…õmp ya darenc k…Ē fum …Ēs…ĒŇč s…Ē s…õm ya d…ôkulum f…ôp mewe. Mba nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta fum m…Ē, …Ēs…Ēt…Ē f…õ nw…õ endetam k…ôcmar k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 21 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu …Ēs…ĒŇč w…ôrkun mere m…Ēp…ĒŇč, k'endir…õ. K…Ē Kanu k…ôwur…õ w…ôrkun k…ôb…õnt k…ôk…ôs…ôk ka d…õb…ôk…ôc. K…Ē k…ôluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē, k…Ē k…ôntam…ôs d…ônda.  
\v 22 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu olomps…õ w…ôran k…ôb…õnt k…ôk…ôs…ôk nk…õ …õnawur…õ w…ôrkun m…Ē, k'eŇčken…õ w…ôrkun w…ôran nw…õ.  
\v 23 K…Ē w…ôrkun oŇčkul…õ: ¬ęApayo!¬Ľ 
\q1 ¬ęW…ôkaw…õ, 
\q1 k…ôb…õnt ka b…õnt yem, 
\q1 t…õs…õm ta s…õm yem.¬Ľ 
\q1 W…ôkaw…õ andewe ¬ęw…ôran¬Ľ w…ôn…õnc…õn…õ ka w…ôrkun, 
\q1 bawo nn…Ē dis dem d'awur…õ k…Ē. 
\p  
\v 24 Ti t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ w…ôrkun …õŇčsak…õ kas k…Ē k…õr…õ p…ôsekt…ôrn…õ k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn m…Ē. Ňäakaf…ôl…õ Ňčay…Ēn…õ t…õs…õm tin. 
\p  
\v 25 W…ôrkun k…Ē w…ôran m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan f…ôp k…ôs…Ēk…ôr k…Ē Ňčanayi, ta ŇčaŇčlap…ôr…õn…õ-…õ. 
\s1 Kiciya k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē: W…ôrkun k…Ē w…ôran k…ôb…õl…ôs k…ôŇčan nde dal…õ da EdeŇč 
\r 3.1-24 
\c 3  
\s1 W…ôrkun k…Ē w…ôran: K…ôb…õl…ôs k…ôŇčan nde dal…õ da EdeŇč 
\p  
\v 1 Abok Ňč…õnac…ôr…õ mes Ňč…õtas s…õm ya dal…õ f…ôp ny…õ MARIKI Kanu …õnawur…õ m…Ē. K'abok Ňčeyif w…ôran: ¬ęKanu k…ôloku nu ti yati a ta n…ôdi yokom ya t…Ēk ya dal…õ dand…õ ba?¬Ľ  
\v 2 K…Ē w…ôran oloku abok: ¬ęS…ôndi yokom ya t…Ēk ya dal…õ dand…õ yati.  
\v 3 Mba k…ôt…Ēk nk…õ k…ôyi dal…õ dac…Ē m…Ē, Kanu k…ôloku: ‚ÄĻTa n…ôdi yokom ya ki, ta n…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ ŇčaŇč ki! K…Ē n…ôy…Ē ti-…õ, n…ôŇčfi.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 4 K'abok Ňčoloku w…ôran: ¬ęN…ôf…Ēfi!  
\v 5 Bawo Kanu k…ônc…ôr…õ, a d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ n…ôndi yi m…Ē, f…Ēr yonu yeŇčmep…õ, n…ôyi p…ôm…Ē Kanu nk…õ k…ônc…ôr…õ p…ôt…Ēt k…Ē p…ôl…õc m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē w…ôran …õn…ôŇčk a pokom pa k…ôt…Ēk p…Ēmb…Ēt k…ôdi, p…Ēmb…Ēt k…ôm…Ēm…ôn, p…õntam k…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôc…ôr…õ p…ôt…Ēt k…Ē p…ôl…õc. K…Ē w…ôran oŇčgbotu pokom k'endi. K'…Ēs…ĒŇč wos w…ôk…Ē Ňčanasol m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôkak…Ē s…Ē endi.  
\v 7 K…Ē Ňčamep…õ f…Ēr, k…Ē Ňčanc…ôr…õn…õ a k…ôs…Ēk…ôr k…Ē Ňčawur. K…Ē ŇčaŇčgbotu b…Ēp…ôr, k…Ē Ňčas…Ēt maŇčkara k…Ē Ňčamb…õrn…õ mi. 
\p  
\v 8 Dec d…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy, nt…õ tefef towur m…Ē, w…ôrkun k…Ē w…ôran Ňčane dim da MARIKI Kanu, nw…õ …Ēnck…Ēt…ôs m…Ē. W…ôrkun k…Ē w…ôran k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčagb…Ēpn…õ Ňčab…Ēl…õ MARIKI Kanu f…Ēr kiriŇč, t…Ēk ya dal…õ dad…Ēk…Ē dac…Ē.  
\v 9 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu ewe w…ôrkun eyif k…Ē: ¬ęDeke m…ôyi-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē w…ôrkun oloku Kanu: ¬ęDim d'in'am dal…õ disr…õ, k'ines…õ, bawo iwur k…ôs…Ēk…ôr, ti t'iŇčgb…Ēpn…õn…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 11 K…Ē MARIKI eyif k…Ē s…Ē: ¬ęAn…Ē'ment…ôr …ôm a k…ôs…Ēk…ôr k…Ē m…ôwur-…õ? Cep…Ē m…ôndi pokom pa k…ôt…Ēk k…ôŇčk…Ē inam…Ēn'am m…Ē ba?¬Ľ  
\v 12 K…Ē w…ôrkun oloku: ¬ęW…ôran nw…õ m…ôs…ĒŇč im m…Ē, nk…Ēn …Ēs…ĒŇč im pi k'ina s…Ē indi.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu eyif w…ôran: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē m…ôy…Ēn…õ tant…õ-…õ?¬Ľ 
\p K…Ē w…ôran oloku Kanu: ¬ęAbok ŇčetiŇčk…ôr im, k'indi pokom pamp…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 14 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu oloku abok: 
\b  
\q1 ¬ęBawo m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôran k…ôciya, 
\q1 k…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm k…ônder p…ôl…õc s…õm y…Ēc…Ēl, 
\q2 k…Ē s…õm ya dop f…ôp dac…Ē. 
\q1 Kor k…Ē m…ônde m…ôcliŇč…õn…õ, 
\q2 m…ôcdi k…ôbof mataka ma kiyi kam doru f…ôp. 
\q1  
\v 15 K…ôb…õr…ôs …ôm k'inder dac…Ē k…Ē w…ôran, 
\q2 k…ôy…õf…õ n…ôna haŇč awut a w…ôran 
\q1 k…ôb…ôp awut a m…ôna, abok! 
\q1 W…ôran ende p…ôcput…ôk …ôm domp, 
\q2 m…ôna abok, m…ôcŇčaŇč k…Ē d…ômn…õ atek.¬Ľ 
\b  
\p  
\v 16 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku w…ôran: 
\b  
\q1 ¬ęIndey…Ē k…ôb…õk…ôs kam k…ôccu'm. 
\q2 P…ôcuca p…Ē m…ônde m…ôckom. 
\q1 M…õfaŇč mam m…ôndek…Ē nda wos …ôm. 
\q1 Mba endetas…ôrn'am.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 17 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku w…ôrkun: 
\b  
\q1 ¬ęBawo m…ônc…ôŇčk…ôl dim da w…ôran kam, 
\q1 k…Ē m…ôndi pokom pa k…ôt…Ēk nk…õ inam…Ēn'am k…ôdi m…Ē, 
\q1 indes…ĒŇč ant…Ēf p…ôl…õc tetam: 
\q2 P…ôcuca p…Ē m…ônde m…ôcs…Ēt…ôr Ňči yeri yam 
\q2 d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk kiyi kam doru f…ôp. 
\q1  
\v 18 Yika ya d…ôkulum y…Ē m…ônde m…ôcdi. 
\q1 Mba ant…Ēf Ňčende Ňčockom am 
\q1 b…õŇčk k…Ē Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē. 
\q1  
\v 19 Kawon…õ ka tobu tam 
\q1 k…ôndes…ĒŇč'am k…ôcs…Ēm k…ôcom 
\q1 haŇč t…õm nt…õ m…ôndelukus d…ônt…Ēf 
\q1 nde m…ôy…õf…õ m…Ē. 
\q1 Bawo k…ôbof k…Ē m…ôy…Ēn…õ, 
\q1 d…ôk…ôbof m…ôndes…Ēlukus.¬Ľ 
\b  
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē w…ôrkun …Ēs…ĒŇč w…ôran k…Ēn tewe ta ¬ęHawa¬Ľ\f + \fr 3:20 \fq Hawa\ft  = ¬ęIya¬Ľ, nw…õ …Ēs…ĒŇč kiyi w…ôyeŇč\f*, bawo nk…Ēn Hawa …Ēy…Ēn…õ iya w…ôka afum a doru f…ôp. 
\p  
\v 21 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu olomps…õ Adama k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn, Hawa, yamos ya akata, k'…õmb…õr Ňča yi. 
\p  
\v 22 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu oloku: ¬ęAh! Nt…õ fum ende p…ôyi oŇč p…ôm…Ē s…ôna m…Ē, p…ôc…ôr…õ p…ôl…õc k…Ē p…ôt…Ēt, s…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ ta p…ôt…õnc k…ôca p…ôl…õk s…Ē pokom pa k…ôt…Ēk k…ôyin…õ w…ôyeŇč, p…ôdeyi oŇč doru katina.¬Ľ  
\v 23 K…Ē MARIKI Kanu owur…õn…õ Adama dal…õ da EdeŇč disr…õ, p…ôk…Ēb…ôc ant…Ēf ny…õ …õnas…õl…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 24 Nt…õ MARIKI Kanu owur…õn…õ fum dal…õ da EdeŇč m…Ē, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr m…õl…õk…õ kerub \f + \fr 3:24 \fq M…õl…õk…õ kerub\ft  = mm…õ mombum d…õb…õ da Kanu m…Ē. Kerub k…ôy…Ē dobomp da fum, dis da kusunuŇčku, k…Ē s…ôy…Ē s…Ē banca y…õf…õl…ôr…õ.\f* ntende dec d…õmp…õ dal…õ da EdeŇč, k…Ē dakma nd…õ dencfik…ôl…õ d…õcc…õs…ôŇč…õ n…õnc, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta al…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…ôt…Ēk ka k…ôyin…õ w…ôyeŇč m…Ē. 
\c 4  
\s1 Kayin k…Ē Ab…õl 
\r 4.1-26 
\p  
\v 1 K'Adama Ňčamb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn Hawa, k…Ē Hawa …õmb…õk…ôs, k'oŇčkom Kayin. K…Ē Hawa oloku: ¬ęIs…Ēt…Ē wan w…ôrkun k…ômar ka MARIKI disr…õ.¬Ľ \f + \fr 4:1 \fq Kayin\ft  = c…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęk…ômar¬Ľ \f* 
\v 2 K…Ē Hawa oŇčkom s…Ē w…ôf…õt ka Kayin nw…õ anawe Ab…õl m…Ē. 
\p K'Ab…õl ende p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôk…õk ka cir k…Ē Ňčkesiya. K…Ē Kayin …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôbifti.  
\v 3 K…Ē t…õm t…Ēl…Ēma tende t…õb…ôp, k…Ē Kayin …õl…õk yokom ya d…ônt…Ēf, k'…õŇčk…õr…õ yi MARIKI k…ôdeloŇčn…õ.  
\v 4 K'Ab…õl nk…Ēn s…Ē, …õŇčk…õr…õ MARIKI yokom y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ya y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēn k…Ē moro ma yi. K…Ē MARIKI …Ēm…Ēm…ôn…õ Ab…õl k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ēn f…Ēr y…Ēt…Ēt.  
\v 5 Mba MARIKI …õnam…Ēm…ôn…õ f…õ Kayin k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ēn f…Ēr y…Ēt…Ēt. K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Kayin, k'…õŇč…õy k…ôro.  
\v 6 K…Ē MARIKI eyif Kayin: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē p…ônt…õl…õn'am-…õ, ta ake t…Ē m…ôŇč…õy…õ k…ôro-…õ?  
\v 7 K…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēt belbel-…õ, m…ôndesel. K…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēt p…ôl…õc-…õ, kiciya k…ôy'…ôm d…ôkusuŇčka k…Ē m…õfaŇč ma ki mey'…ôm. Mba m…ôs…õp m…ôtas…ôrn…õ ki.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 8 K…Ē Kayin …Ēnc…Ēp…ôr w…õnc Ab…õl. Mba nt…õ Ňčanayi dal…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Kayin …õy…õf…ôr w…õnc Ab…õl k…ôsut…õn…õ, k'endif k…Ē. 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē MARIKI eyif Kayin: ¬ęDeke w…õnc …ôm Ab…õl eyi-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Kayin oloku: ¬ęInc…ôr…õ f…õ. Cep…Ē w…ôk…õk…ôs k…Ēn iy…Ēn…õ ba?¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē Kanu k…ôyif Kayin: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē m…ôy…Ē w…õnc …ôm-…õ? Dim da mecir ma w…õnc …ôm deyi k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ k…ôy…õf…õ d…ônt…Ēf haŇč nn…Ē iyi m…Ē.  
\v 11 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, k…ôtolan'am k'ant…Ēf Ňčender p…ôl…õc, nŇč…õ Ňč…õwani kusu k…Ē m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňči k…ômer…ôs mecir ma w…õnc …ôm m…Ē.  
\v 12 K…Ē m…ônde m…ôcb…ôc ant…Ēf-…õ, Ňč…Ēf…Ēde Ňč…Ēcs…ĒŇč …ôm p…ôbotu pa Ňči. Ti t…Ē p…ônde p…ôct…õl…õn'am m…ôccep…õ-cep…õ d…ôk…ôb…ôc.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē Kayin oloku MARIKI: ¬ęP…ôlel pa kiciya kem p…õmb…õk k…ôsar…õ.  
\v 14 M…ômb…õl…ôs im m…Ēk…Ē nn…Ē ant…Ēf Ňčam Ňčebi Ňčeyi m…Ē. P…ônamar im k…ôgb…Ēp…ôn'am, k…Ē k…ôcep…õ-cep…õ d…ônt…Ēf, k…Ē fum …õmb…ôp im d…ônda-…õ, p…ôdif im.¬Ľ  
\v 15 Mba, k…Ē MARIKI oloku k…Ē: ¬ęK…Ē fum endif Kayin-…õ, aŇčluks…õ ay…õk Ňč…Ēn cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.¬Ľ K…Ē MARIKI eŇčgbesi Kayin nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ aŇč…õ Ňčamb…ôp k…Ē m…Ē, ta Ňčasut k…Ē Ňčadif.  
\v 16 K…Ē Kayin owur f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč dal…õ da EdeŇč, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôyi at…Ēf Ňča Nodu nde dec d…õmp…õ dal…õ da EdeŇč m…Ē. 
\s1 Yuruya ya Kayin 
\p  
\v 17 K…Ē Kayin Ňčamb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn. K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …õmb…õk…ôs k'oŇčkom Henok. K…Ē Kayin owur…õ dare k'…Ēs…ĒŇč di tewe ta wan k…Ēn Henok.  
\v 18 K…Ē Henok oŇčkom Iradu, k'Iradu oŇčkom Mehuyay…õl, k…Ē Mehuyay…õl oŇčkom Metusay…õl, k…Ē Metusay…õl oŇčkom L…õm…õk. 
\p  
\v 19 K…Ē L…õm…õk …õl…õk aran m…õr…ôŇč, pacwe w…ôkin ¬ęAda,¬Ľ k…Ē w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč ¬ęCila.¬Ľ  
\v 20 K'Ada oŇčkom Yabal, nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôtem ka ak…õk y…Ēc…Ēl acep…õ-cep…õ.  
\v 21 Tewe ta w…õnc t…õnay…Ēn…õ Yubal: Nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôtem k'afer coŇčk…ôlo k'afula luk.  
\v 22 K…Ē Cila nk…Ēn s…Ē d…ômn…õ oŇčkom Tubal Kayin, nw…õ …õncgb…õc ca f…ôp ya k…Ēp…ôr k…Ē ya f…õc m…Ē. W…ôkir…õ k…Ēn ancwe Nahama.  
\v 23 K…Ē L…õm…õk oloku aran …Ēn: 
\q1 ¬ęAda k…Ē Cila n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl dim dem! 
\q1 Aran a L…õm…õk n…ôsu l…ôŇč…ôs n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl moloku mem. 
\q1 K'asut im-…õ, indif fum. 
\q1 K'ambop…ôr im-…õ, indif wanf…õt. 
\q1  
\v 24 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ padif afum cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč 
\q1 k…ôluks…õ ay…õk Ňča Kayin-…õ, 
\q1 andedif afum 77, 
\q1 a pacluks…õ ay…õk Ňča L…õm…õk.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 25 Adama k…Ē Hawa Ňčas…Ēt…Ē s…Ē wan. K…Ē Hawa ewe k…Ē ¬ęS…õt¬Ľ, ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęKanu k…ôs…ĒŇč im s…Ē w…ôl…Ēma k…ôdey…Ēn'em Ab…õl w…ôk…Ē Kayin endif m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 26 K…Ē S…õt ende p…ôkom wan pacwe k…Ē En…Ēs. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t'anacop k…ôkor-koru tewe ta MARIKI. 
\c 5  
\s1 K…ôy…õf…õ Adama haŇč Nuha 
\p  
\v 1 Buk ba dokomb…ôra da Adama b…Ē bamb…õ. D…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Kanu k…ôs…õl Adama m…Ē, k'…õs…õl k…Ē, p…ôwur…õn…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn Kanu.  
\v 2 W…ôrkun k…Ē w…ôran k'…õs…õl Ňča, k'ompoc…õ Ňča p…ôt…Ēt, k'ewe Ňča tewe ta ¬ęfum,¬Ľ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ …õncs…õl Ňča m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 3 Adama endes…Ēt…Ē meren 130, k'…Ēs…Ēt…Ē wan w…ôwur…õn…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē eyi m…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē tewe ta S…õt.  
\v 4 Nt…õ Adama oŇčkom S…õt m…Ē, k'eyi s…Ē doru meren 800, mm…õ …õnas…Ēt…Ē s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran m…Ē.  
\v 5 K…ôwon ka Adama doru k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren 930, a k'endefi. 
\p  
\v 6 S…õt …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 105, a k'endekom En…Ēs.  
\v 7 Nt…õ S…õt oŇčkom En…Ēs m…Ē, k'eyi s…Ē doru meren 807, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē.  
\v 8 K…ôwon ka S…õt doru k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren 912, k'efi. 
\p  
\v 9 En…Ēs …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 90 a p…ôdekom KenaŇč.  
\v 10 Nt…õ En…Ēs oŇčkom KenaŇč m…Ē, k'eyi s…Ē doru meren 815, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē.  
\v 11 K…ôwon ka En…Ēs doru f…ôp k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren 905, k'efi. 
\p  
\v 12 K…Ē KenaŇč …Ēs…Ēt…Ē meren 70 a k'endekom Mahalalel.  
\v 13 Nt…õ oŇčkom Mahalalel m…Ē, k…Ē KenaŇč eyi s…Ē doru meren 840, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē.  
\v 14 K…ôwon ka KenaŇč doru f…ôp k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren 910, k'efi.  
\v 15 Mahalalel …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 65 a k'endekom Y…õr…õdu.  
\v 16 Nt…õ Mahalalel oŇčkom Y…õr…õdu m…Ē, k'eyi s…Ē doru meren 830, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē.  
\v 17 K…ôwon ka Mahalalel doru f…ôp, k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren 895, k'efi.  
\v 18 Y…õr…õdu …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 162 a k'endekom Henok.  
\v 19 Nt…õ Y…õr…õdu oŇčkom Henok m…Ē, k'eyi s…Ē doru meren 800, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē.  
\v 20 K…ôwon ka Y…õr…õdu doru f…ôp k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren 962, k'efi. 
\p  
\v 21 Henok …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 65 a k'endekom Metusela.  
\v 22 Nt…õ Henok oŇčkom Metusela m…Ē, k'…Ēs…Ēt…Ē s…Ē meren 300 Ňčasol k…Ē Kanu. K'oŇčkom s…Ē awut arkun k'aran al…Ēma.  
\v 23 K…ôwon ka Henok doru f…ôp k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren 365.  
\v 24 K…Ē Henok …õnc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē da Kanu dar…ôŇč, k…Ē tende telip, bawo Kanu k…ônal…õk k…Ē p…ôyi w…ôyeŇč. 
\p  
\v 25 Metusela …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 187 a k'endekom L…õm…õk.  
\v 26 Nt…õ Metusela oŇčkom L…õm…õk m…Ē, k'…Ēs…Ēt…Ē s…Ē meren 782, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē.  
\v 27 K…ôwon ka Metusela doru k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren 969, k'efi. 
\p  
\v 28 L…õm…õk …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 182 a k'endekom wan w…ôrkun.  
\v 29 K…Ē L…õm…õk ewe wan w…ôkak…Ē ¬ęNuha.¬Ľ\f + \fr 5:29 \fq Nuha\ft  = c…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęk…ôyam…ôs-yam…ôs¬Ľ \f* K'oloku: ¬ęW…ôkaw…õ ende p…ôcyams…õ-yams…õ su, k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ ka pucuy mp…õ y…õb…ôc yocuca ny…õ waca womboc ant…Ēf ny…õ, MARIKI …õnas…ĒŇč p…ôl…õc tetosu m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 30 Nt…õ L…õm…õk oŇčkom Nuha m…Ē, k'eyi s…Ē doru meren 595. K'oŇčkom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma.  
\v 31 K…ôwon ka L…õm…õk doru f…ôp k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren 777, k'efi. 
\p  
\v 32 Nuha …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 500 a k'endekom Sem, Ham, k…Ē Yaf…õt. 
\c 6  
\s1 Kanu k…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…Ēn k…ônim ka afum doru 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ afum Ňčancop k…ôla ant…Ēf k…ôroŇč m…Ē, k'aŇčkom…ôs ayec…ôra.  
\v 2 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ Ňčan…ôŇčk a ayec…ôra aka afum Ňčantes…õ. K…Ē Ňčay…õk-y…õk aran aŇčan ayec…ôra akak…Ē dac…Ē.  
\v 3 K…Ē MARIKI oloku: ¬ęIfaŇč f…õ k…ôsak afum Ňčayin…õ kifir k…ôyin…õ doru nk…õ inas…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē, bawo fum s…õm d…ôm y…Ē. K…ôyi k…Ēn doru k…ôf…Ēde k…ôccep…ôr s…Ē meren 120.¬Ľ  
\v 4 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē c…Ērgba c…ônayi doru, nt…õ awut a Kanu\f + \fr 6:4 \fq Awut a Kanu\ft  it'…Ēy…Ēn…õ c…ôHeb…ôre c…ôkur: ¬ęAwut a Kanu¬Ľ, ¬ęawut a canu¬Ľ, ¬ęm…õl…õk…õ¬Ľ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ ¬ęafum ap…ĒŇč¬Ľ.\f* Ňčant…õf…ôrn…õ ayec…ôra aka afum, ak…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč Ňča awut m…Ē. Awut akak…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ ab…õ akur a t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē. 
\p  
\v 5 K…Ē MARIKI …õn…ôŇčk deyeŇčki b…ôk…ôc da afum d…õla doru, d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ m…õl…õc gb…ôc…ôr…ôm m…Ē afum Ňčayin…õ.  
\v 6 K…Ē MARIKI …õŇčaŇčn…õ t…õl…ôr k…ôs…õl k…Ēn fum, k'ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õŇčkaf…ôl…õ k…Ē.  
\v 7 K…Ē MARIKI oloku: ¬ęK…ônim k'inder afum aŇč…õ inas…õl m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ afum, k…ôb…ôp s…õm, k…ôk…Ē ka yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ haŇč b…õmp ya darenc, bawo iŇčaŇčn…õ t…õl…ôr k…ôs…õl k…ôŇčan.¬Ľ  
\v 8 Mba k…Ē Nuha …Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…ôŇčan…õn…õ ka MARIKI, bawo Kanu k…ônan…ôŇčk dolompu d…Ēn. 
\s1 Kanu k…ôyac Nuha 
\p  
\v 9 Tecep…ôr…õn…õ ta Nuha t…õnt…õ: Nuha, fum w…ôt…Ēt …õnayi p…ôlomp, p…ôsol k…Ē Kanu.  
\v 10 Nuha, awut maas Ňč'…õnakom: Sem, Ham k…Ē Yaf…õt. 
\p  
\v 11 Mba nn…Ē f…Ēr ya Kanu kiriŇč, afum Ňčanates…õ f…õ b…ôk…ôc. Mes m…õl…õc gb…ôc…ôr…ôm m…õnayi doru.  
\v 12 Kanu k…ônan…ôŇčk a doru d…õs…ôkp…õ, bawo afum f…ôp Ňčanagbaym…õ-gbaym…õ d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēt…Ēt.  
\v 13 Ti t'…õnas…ĒŇč…õ Kanu k…ôloku Nuha: ¬ęInc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôm…ôl…ôk yeŇčes…ôm ya doru f…ôp, bawo tes taŇčan t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē doru d…õla k…ôd…ôk…ôt…õr…õn…õ, k…ônim Ňča k'inder doru.  
\v 14 M…ôcaŇč…õ abil Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč c…ôbam ca kawe, m…ôwur…õ Ňči s…ôduk…ôl…Ē s…ôlar…ôm, m…ôsop Ňči k…Ērtal tedisr…õ k…Ē todoru.  
\v 15 Nt…õ t…Ē m…ôndecaŇč Ňči: Ňä…Ēb…Ēl cururu 300 (m…õt…ôr 137), Ňč…Ēw…Ēk…ôl cururu 50 (m…õt…ôr 23), Ňčotukm…õ cururu 30 (m…õt…ôr 14).  
\v 16 M…ôgb…ôp…ôr Ňči tadarenc, m…ôsak kururu katin (m…õt…ôr dac…Ē) k…ôy…õf…õ nde k…ôroŇč haŇč nde d…ôk…ôpom, m…ôwur…õ Ňči kumba k…ôs…ôk, m…ôdeŇč…ôr Ňči d…õk maas.  
\v 17 Bawo ina, domun d…õlar…ôm \f + \fr 6:17 \fq Domun d…õlar…ôm\ft  = ¬ęW…ôcaf…ôn indetor…õ p…ôkal doru f…ôp.¬Ľ \f* d'indesak nd…õ dendem…ôl…ôk ca f…ôp m…Ē. Mp…õ o mp…õ peŇčes…ôm doru m…Ē, pendefi.  
\v 18 K…Ē m…ôna, indesek s…Ē danapa k…Ē m…ôna, m…ôde m…ôb…õr…õ debil k…Ē w…ôran kam, awut am k'aran aŇčan!  
\v 19 M…ôde m…ôb…õrs…õn…õ s…Ē Ňči disr…õ s…õm ya doru f…ôp m…õr…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč, workun k…Ē w…õran, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôde n…ôyi doru k…Ē yi m…Ē.  
\v 20 S…õm yeŇčes…ôm ya doru f…ôp, yorkun k…Ē y…õran, y…õf…õt k…Ē y…Ēp…ĒŇč, yede y…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn'am nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ yi s…Ē yede yeyi doru m…Ē.  
\v 21 Awa, m…ôt…õn yeri f…ôp, m…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ yi nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôde n…ôcs…Ēt…Ē yedi n…ôna k…Ē yi m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 22 Ti t…Ē Nuha …õnay…Ē, …õnay…Ē mes f…ôp mm…õ Kanu k…ônaloku k…Ē m…Ē. 
\c 7  
\s1 Nuha k…ôb…õr…õ k…Ēn debil 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI k…ôloku Nuha: ¬ęM…ôb…õr…õ abil disr…õ, m…ôna k'afum am f…ôp, bawo iŇčk…Ēkc…õ a m…ôn'olomp f…Ēr yem kiriŇč d…õt…õmp dand…õ dac…Ē.  
\v 2 M…ôl…õk…õn…õ s…õm y…Ēt…Ēt cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, yorkun k…Ē y…õran, mba s…õm y…õl…õc, m…ôl…õk yi m…õr…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč: Workun k…Ē w…õran gb…ôc…ôr…ôm.  
\v 3 K…Ē b…õmp, m…ôl…õk…õn…õ yi f…ôp dac…Ē, yorkun cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē y…õran cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. Ti t'endes…ĒŇč…õ yi s…Ē yeyi doru.  
\v 4 P…ônc…ôm…õ mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, itor…õ w…ôcaf…ôn mata 40 k…Ē pibi 40 camcam. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē indef…õŇč nn…Ē doru afum aŇč…õ inas…õl m…Ē f…ôp.¬Ľ  
\v 5 Nuha …õnay…Ē m…Ēy…Ē f…ôp, mm…õ MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē m…Ē. 
\s1 Kutup k…ôp…ĒŇč 
\p  
\v 6 Nuha …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 600 a k…Ē domun dendekal ant…Ēf.  
\v 7 K'…õmb…õr…õ debil k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn, awut …Ēn k'aran aŇčan, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčayacn…õ domun nd…õ d…õnabaŇč ant…Ēf m…Ē.  
\v 8 S…õm y…Ēt…Ēt k…Ē y…õl…õc, b…õmp k…Ē s…õm y…õf…õt y…õf…õt ny…õ yeŇčliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ m…Ē f…ôp,  
\v 9 k…Ē Kanu k…ômb…õrs…õ yi abil disr…õ nde Nuha eyi m…Ē, m…õr…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč yorkun k…Ē y…õran, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônaloku ti m…Ē.  
\v 10 Nt…õ tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē domun d…õmbaŇč ant…Ēf.  
\v 11 K…ôren nk…õ Nuha …Ēs…Ēt…Ē meren 600, tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčof Ňča m…õr…ôŇč disr…õ, k…Ē domun dombunc…õ d…ôc…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē k…Ēm k…ôŇčgbit…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč.  
\v 12 K…Ē w…ôcaf…ôn oncop k…ôtuf mata 40 k…Ē pibi 40.  
\v 13 D…Ēs…Ēk dayi d…Ē Nuha …õnab…õr…õ debil k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn k'awut …Ēn, Sem, Ham, k…Ē Yaf…õt, k'aran aŇčan maas,  
\v 14 k…Ē s…õm ya dop k…Ē ya dare yin yin k…Ē s…õm y…õf…õt y…õf…õt, b…õmp k…Ē taktaka.  
\v 15 K…Ē yeŇčes…ôm (s…õm) yorkun k…Ē y…õran m…õr…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč ny…õ y…õnayi doru m…Ē, k…Ē yender nde abil Ňča Nuha Ňčeyi m…Ē.  
\v 16 K…Ē yorkun k…Ē y…õran s…õm dokom f…ôp, y…õmb…õr…õ abil disr…õ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônaloku ti Nuha m…Ē, k…Ē MARIKI k…ôŇčgb…ôt…ôr Ňča kumba. 
\p  
\v 17 K…Ē domun d…õmbaŇč ant…Ēf mata 40, nt…õ domun d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k'abil Ňčofoy.  
\v 18 Nt…õ domun d…õncp…õ m…Ē, ti t…Ē abil Ňčoncfoy.  
\v 19 K…Ē domun d…õmb…õr…õn…õ k…ôp…õ haŇč k…Ē m…Ēr…Ē meŇčeci f…ôp m…õŇčkal…õ.  
\v 20 (T…õlp…ôs oŇč k…Ē domun d…õmp…õ haŇč k…Ē dencep…ôr cururu w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt m…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč). K…Ē domun d…õmp…õ k…Ē d…õŇčkal m…Ēr…Ē meŇčeci haŇč cururu w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (m…õt…ôr cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč).  
\v 21 Ca ny…õ y…õnayi ant…Ēf k…ôroŇč, a yecŇčes…ôm m…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē yefi: B…õmp, s…õm y…Ēc…Ēl, s…õm ya dop k…Ē yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ f…ôp k…ôl…õk…õn…õ afum.  
\v 22 K…ôy…õf…õ paka mp…õ p…õnayi ant…Ēf k…ôroŇč a pecŇčes…ôm m…Ē, k…Ē pefi.  
\v 23 K…Ē Kanu k…ôf…õŇč d…ônt…Ēf paka mp…õ pencŇčes…ôm m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ fum haŇč k…ôb…ôp s…õm y…Ēp…ĒŇč, y…õf…õt y…õf…õt k…Ē b…õmp, k'enim yi doru f…ôp. M…õn…õ Nuha gb…ôc…ôr…ôm, aka k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ k…Ē s…õm ny…õ y…õnayi debil m…Ē, Ňčanafis. 
\p  
\v 24 Domun d…õnabaŇč ant…Ēf haŇč mataka 150. 
\c 8  
\s1 Domun k…ôwos…ôr 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Kanu k…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ Nuha, s…õm ya dop k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl ya dare, ny…õ y…õnayi k…Ē Nuha abil disr…õ m…Ē. K…Ē Kanu k…ôwur…õ afef doru, k…Ē domun doncop k…ôtor.  
\v 2 K…ôba ka d…ônt…Ēf k…Ē darenc c…ôm…õp…õn…õ, k…Ē w…ôcaf…ôn …õsak k…ôtuf.  
\v 3 K…Ē domun dembel…õ ant…Ēf k…ôroŇč tepic tepic. Mata 150 disr…õ, k…Ē domun d…õnc…õs…õ d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 4 Tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (17), Ňčof Ňča cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k'abil Ňč…õnd…õ t…Ēr…Ē tin ta Ararat k…ôroŇč.  
\v 5 K…Ē domun d…õnc…õs…õ haŇč Ňčof Ňča w…ôco. Tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ta Ňčof ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē m…Ēr…Ē meŇčeci moncop k…ôwur…õ s…ôbomp. 
\p  
\v 6 Tataka ta 40, k…Ē Nuha eŇčgbiti wund…õr nw…õ …õnab…õr abil m…Ē.  
\v 7 K'…õsak ab…õmp Ňča ser \f + \fr 8:7 \fq Ab…õmp Ňča ser\ft  = ¬ęab…õmp Ňča M…ônar,¬Ľ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ ¬ęk…ôwan ka as…õr.¬Ľ \f* Ňčin k…Ē Ňč…ĒŇčk…Ē. P…ôwon f…õ k…Ē Ňčoluks…ôrn…õ, p…ônamar Nuha p…ôkar domun delip k…ôwos…ôr d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 8 K…Ē Nuha …õsak s…Ē antantoriya k…ôk…Ēm…Ēm…ôn k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a domun d'ontor-…õ.  
\v 9 Mba Ňč…õnas…Ēt…Ē f…õ k…ôfo nk…õ Ňč…õntam k…ônd…õ m…Ē, bawo domun d…õnas…Ēr…ĒbaŇč ant…Ēf f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčoluks…ôrn…õ nde debil. K…Ē Nuha …õnt…õnc k…ôca k'osump…ôr Ňči, k'…õmb…õrs…õ debil.  
\v 10 K'…õŇčkar s…Ē mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k'…õsak s…Ē Ňči.  
\v 11 K'antantoriya Ňčoluks…ôrn…õ dec d…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy Ňč…õgb…ôm t…Ēb…Ēp…ôr t…õcaŇčk ta k…ôt…Ēk ka olif\f + \fr 8:11 \fq K…ôt…Ēk ka olif\ft  = Yokom ya k…ôt…Ēk kaŇčk…õ k…Ē nk…õ aŇčwur…õ moro mm…õ antam k…ôdi, pamot…õn…õ ki d…ôlamp, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ pas…Ēm pokom pa ki. \f*. K…Ē Nuha …õnc…ôr…õ katina a domun d…õnc…õs…õ.  
\v 12 K'…õŇčkar…õn…õ s…Ē haŇč tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k'…õsak s…Ē antantoriya. Mba nt…õ Ňči Ňč…ĒŇčk…Ē m…Ē, Ňč…õnalukus f…õ s…Ē nn…Ē eyi m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 13 Tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ta Ňčof Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē nŇč…õ Nuha …Ēs…Ēt…Ē meren 601, ti t…Ē domun d…õnasak ant…Ēf. K…Ē Nuha eŇčgbipi abil, k'…Ēm…Ēm…ôn doru. K'…õn…ôŇčk a domun f…ôp dowos…ôr.  
\v 14 Tataka ta w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē cam…ôt m…õr…ôŇč (27), Ňčof Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Ňčayi, ant…Ēf f…ôp Ňč…õnawos f…ôr. 
\p  
\v 15 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku Nuha:  
\v 16 ¬ęM…ôwur abil disr…õ, m…ôna k…Ē w…ôran kam, awut am k'aran aŇčan.  
\v 17 M…ôwur…õn…õ s…Ē s…õm y…õl…ôp…ôs ny…õ yeyi abil disr…õ k…Ē m…ôna m…Ē. K…Ē b…õmp dokom f…ôp, s…õm y…õf…õt k…Ē y…Ēp…ĒŇč, y…õsam doru yokom.¬Ľ  
\v 18 K…Ē Nuha owur debil nk…Ēn k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn k'awut …Ēn k'aran aŇčan.  
\v 19 K…Ē s…õm, b…õmp k…Ē yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ yowur f…ôp dokom dokom. 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē Nuha olomp…ôs tetek toloŇčn…õ MARIKI, k'…õl…õk s…õm k…Ē b…õmp yosoku dac…Ē yin yin, k'…Ēnc…Ēf…õ yi MARIKI nde tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč.  
\v 21 K…Ē MARIKI …õmbaŇč amb…Ēnc Ňča k…ôloŇčn…õ nŇč…õ Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc m…Ē, k'olokun…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc, ¬ęIf…Ēs…Ēs…ĒŇč ant…Ēf p…ôl…õc teta fum. Kance k…Ē, bawo afum m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ m…õl…õc meyi Ňča d…ôb…ôk…ôc k…ôy…õf…õ dowut daŇčan, mba if…Ēs…Ēl…ôs…ôr ca ny…õ yeŇčes…ôm doru p…ôm…Ē nt…õ int…õp ti k…ôcy…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\q1  
\v 22 ¬ęK…ôwon ka ant…Ēf doru f…ôp, 
\q1 k…ôb…Ēf k…Ē k…ôt…õl, 
\q1 p…ôwonu k…Ē p…ôcaŇčki, 
\q1 k…ôt…ôn k…Ē d…õr…ôŇč, 
\q1 d…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē pibi, 
\q1 y…Ēf…Ēdelip.¬Ľ 
\c 9  
\s1 Kanu k…ôd…õrm…õ k…Ēn Nuha 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Kanu k…ômpoc…õ Nuha p…ôt…Ēt k'awut …Ēn, k…Ē k…ôloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôy…Ēn…õ akomb…ôra, n…ôkom p…ôlar…ôm, n…ôlas ant…Ēf.  
\v 2 K…ôy…õf…õ m…Ēk…Ē, s…õm ya doru f…ôp, k…ôb…ôp b…õmp, s…õm y…õf…õt k…Ē lop, yende yecnes…õ nu. N…ôndetam k…ôcs…Ēm yi.  
\v 3 Paka o paka mp…õ peyi w…ôyeŇč p…Ēck…Ēt m…Ē, p…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu peri p…ôm…Ē nt…õ inas…ĒŇč nu yokom ya yika y…õcaŇčk k…Ē ya t…Ēk m…Ē. Is…ĒŇč nu oŇč nd…õk…ôl yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 4 Mba ta n…ôde n…ôcs…Ēm w…õs…õm nw…õ w…Ēs…Ēr…Ēy…Ē mecir ma wi m…Ē. \f + \fr 9:4 \ft  W…õs…õm nw…õ ant…Ēfay amera m…Ē. \f* 
\v 5 Indeyif nu teta mecir monu, mm…õ m…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôyi doru konu m…Ē. Indeyif s…Ē ti s…õm f…ôp ny…õ yendedif fum m…Ē. P…ôm…Ē nt…õ indeyif ti fum nw…õ endedif w…õnc m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\q1  
\v 6 ¬ęNw…õ endif fum m…Ē, 
\q1 padif s…Ē (m…ôna w…ôkayi), 
\q1 bawo Kanu k…ôlomp…ôs fum p…ôwur…õn…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn s…ôrka. 
\m  
\v 7 K…Ē n…ôna, n…ôy…Ēn…õ akomb…ôra, n…ôkom p…ôlar…ôm, n…ôsams…ôr doru.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 8 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku s…Ē Nuha k'awut …Ēn:  
\v 9 ¬ęK'ina, indesek s…Ē danapa k…Ē n…ôna, k…ôb…ôp ka yuruya yam k…Ē n…ôna n…ôncep…ôr-…õ,  
\v 10 k…Ē ca f…ôp ny…õ y…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôr nu m…Ē: B…õmp, s…õm ya dare k…Ē ya dop, ny…õ yowur debil m…Ē, k…Ē ny…õ andekom nn…Ē doru m…Ē.  
\v 11 Isek danapa k…Ē n…ôna, nt…õ t'indey…Ē: Domun d…Ēf…Ēdes…Ēdi ant…Ēf, w…ôcaf…ôn …Ēf…Ēdes…Ēyi nw…õ endel…ôs…ôr ant…Ēf m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 12 K…Ē Kanu k…ôndeŇč…ôr: ¬ęPaka pa danapa dosu p…õmp…õ mp…õ pendeyi su dac…Ē k…Ē n…ôna doru o doru, k…ôb…ôp ka ca yeŇčes…ôm.  
\v 13 Is…õk…ôn amb…ônc…ôran (asiŇčki) Ňčem nde d…ôk…ôp. In'ende k…ôcc…õm-c…õm…ôs im temer nt…õ is…ĒŇč ant…Ēf m…Ē.  
\v 14 T…õm o t…õm nt…õ w…ôcaf…ôn ende p…ôcbiy…õ, a asiŇčki Ňčowur m…Ē,  
\v 15 inc…õm-c…õmn…õ temer t…Ēk…Ē inas…ĒŇč nu k…Ē ca ny…õ yeŇčes…ôm doru m…Ē, w…ôcaf…ôn …Ēf…Ēdes…Ētuf nw…õ endes…Ēl…ôs…ôr ca ya doru f…ôp m…Ē.  
\v 16 D…ôk…ôp amb…ônc…ôran Ňč…ĒŇčk…Ēyi. K'inden…ôŇčk Ňči-…õ, indec…õm-c…õmn…õ temer ta danapa dem ta doru o doru nt…õ inal…õk k…Ē ca f…ôp ny…õ yeŇčes…ôm doru m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē Kanu k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õn…õ s…Ē moloku mam…õ Nuha: ¬ęAsiŇčki Ňčement…ôr temer nt…õ is…ĒŇč nu k…Ē ca ya doru ny…õ yeŇčes…ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Nuha k'awut …Ēn maas: Doru dofu, k…Ē kiciya k…ôfu s…Ē 
\p  
\v 18 Awut a Nuha aŇč…õ Ňčanawur debil m…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ: Sem, Ham, k…Ē Yaf…õt. Ham …Ēy…Ēn…õ papa w…ôka KanaŇč.  
\v 19 Awut a Nuha akaŇč…õ maas Ňčagb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôlas ant…Ēf. 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē Nuha …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôbifti ant…Ēf k'…Ēmb…Ēf Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn. \f + \fr 9:20 \ft  Len yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē aŇčwe ¬ęw…õn¬Ľ iy'amb…Ēf Yisrayel ny…õ yokom yayi y…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč member m…Ē. \f* 
\v 21 K…Ē Nuha omun member k'encis. K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôwur k…ôs…Ēk…ôr nde abal Ňč…Ēn disr…õ.  
\v 22 Nt…õ Ham papa w…ôka KanaŇč …õn…ôŇčk kas Nuha p…ôyi k…ôs…Ēk…ôr m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôloku ti aw…õnc aŇča m…õr…ôŇč, aŇč…õ Ňčanayi nde doru m…Ē.  
\v 23 Sem k…Ē Yaf…õt Ňčal…õk k…ôloto. M…õr…ôŇč maŇčan f…ôp, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkumpn…õ k…ôloto kaŇčk…Ē d…ôc…ôro. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē c…ôk…ômunt…ôra k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp papa k…ôŇčan p…ôyi k…ôs…Ēk…ôr. K…Ē ŇčaŇčkump k…Ē k…ôs…Ēk…ôr k…ôŇčk…Ē …õnaf…ônt…ôr…õ m…Ē. Mba nt…õ Ňčanakaf…ôli c…ôro c…ôŇčan a k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē kas k…ôŇčan c…ôk…ômunt…ôra m…Ē, Ňčanan…ôŇčk f…õ kas k…ôŇčan k…ôs…Ēk…ôr.  
\v 24 Nt…õ p…ônc…õrŇč…õ Nuha k…ôcis kaŇčk…Ē disr…õ m…Ē, k'aloku k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē p…ônayi k…Ē nt…õ …õnacis m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē wan k…Ēn w…ôlp…ôs …õnay…Ē k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 25 K…Ē Nuha oloku: 
\q1 ¬ęIntolan…õ KanaŇč p…ôl…õc! 
\q1 KanaŇč p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôcar ka acar a aw…õnc aŇča!¬Ľ  
\v 26 K…Ē Nuha oloku s…Ē: 
\q1 ¬ęIntola MARIKI, Kanu ka Sem, 
\q1 KanaŇč p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôcar k…ôŇčan! 
\q1  
\v 27 Kanu k…ôyac Yaf…õt! 
\q1 Yaf…õt p…ôyi abal Ňča Sem disr…õ, 
\q1 KanaŇč nk…Ēn p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôcar k…ôŇčan!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 28 K…Ē Nuha eyi s…Ē doru meren 350, nt…õ domun d…õlar…ôm dencep…ôr m…Ē.  
\v 29 K…ôwon ka Nuha doru f…ôp, k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren 950, a k'endefi. 
\c 10  
\ms1 Dokomb…ôra da awut a Nuha d…õnd…õ 
\s1 T…õla ta afum doru 
\p  
\v 1 Dokomb…ôra da awut a Nuha: Semy, Ham, k…Ē Yaf…õt d…õnd…õ. Awut a Nuha Ňčanakom awut, nt…õ domun d…õlar…ôm denacep…ôr m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 2 Awut a Yaf…õt Ňčanay…Ēn…õ: Kom…õr, Mak…Ēk, Maday, YawaŇč, Tubal, M…õs…õk, k…Ē Tiras.  
\v 3 Awut a Kom…õr: Askenas, Rifat, k…Ē Tokarma.  
\v 4 Awut a YawaŇč: Elisa, Tarsis, Kitim, k…Ē Dodanim.  
\v 5 Awut akak…Ē Ňčanakom afum aŇč…õ Ňčayers…õn…õ k…ônd…õ c…ôba k…ôs…ôk m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēf yaŇčan, k…Ē cusu c…ôŇčan, k…Ē cusuŇčka c…ôŇčan nde t…Ēf yaŇčan. 
\p  
\v 6 Awut a Ham Ňčanay…Ēn…õ: Kus, Misira, Put, k…Ē KanaŇč.  
\v 7 Awut a Kus: Seba, Hawila, Sabta, Rama, k…Ē Sabat…ôka. Awut a Rama: Saba k…Ē DedaŇč.  
\v 8 Kus …õnakom s…Ē Nimrod, nk…Ēn onuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ korgba doru dand…õ.  
\v 9 Nimrod …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôp…õn korgba nde f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč. Ti t…Ē alok…õn…õ: ¬ęP…ôm…Ē Nimrod, korgba k…ôp…õn nde f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 10 K'eŇčkek…ôr…õ d…õb…õ k…ôr…õsna Bab…õl, ∆źr…õk, Akad, k…Ē Kalne nde at…Ēf Ňča SiŇčhar.  
\v 11 D…ôndo at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…Ē Asur …õnawur, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr Niniwe, dare da Rehobot, Kalah,  
\v 12 k…Ē R…õs…õŇč, dare d…Ēp…ĒŇč d…Ēk…Ē d…õnayi Niniwe k…Ē Kalah dac…Ē m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē Misira …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôtem k'afum aŇč…õ: Aka Lud, aHanam, aLehab, aNaftu,  
\v 14 aPat…ôrus, aKas…ôlu (aŇč…õ aFilisti Ňčawur dac…Ē m…Ē) k'aKaftor. 
\p  
\v 15 K…Ē KanaŇč oŇčkom CidoŇč, coco c…Ēn, k…Ē Het.  
\v 16 KanaŇč …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôtem ka cusuŇčka c…ôlar…ôm: Aka Yebus, Am…Ēr, aKirkas,  
\v 17 aHewy, aHarki, aSini,  
\v 18 aka Arwad, aCemar, aHamat. Ti disr…õ k…Ē cusuŇčka ca KanaŇč c…ônde c…ôsams…ôr.  
\v 19 C…ôl…ônc…ôr ca aKanaŇč c…ônak…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ CidoŇč, Kerar k…ôs…ôk, haŇč Kasa, k…Ē k…ôca ka Sodom, k…ôca ka Komora, k…ôca ka Adma k…Ē k…ôca ka Ceboyim, haŇč Lasah.  
\v 20 Awut a Ham Ňč…Ē akak…Ē, d…ôcusuŇčka cusuŇčka, d…ôcusu cusu, d…ôt…Ēf t…Ēf. 
\p  
\v 21 K…Ē Sem w…ôbeki ka Yaf…õt, …Ēs…Ēt…Ē s…Ē awut. Sem …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôtem ka Heber k'afum …Ēn f…ôp.  
\v 22 Awut a Sem Ňčanay…Ēn…õ: Helam, Asur, Arpaksad, Lud, k'Aram.  
\v 23 Awut a Aram Ňčanay…Ēn…õ: Huc, Hul, K…õt…õr k…Ē Mas.  
\v 24 Arpaksad …õnakom S…õlah. K…Ē S…õlah oŇčkom Heb…õr.  
\v 25 K…Ē Heb…õr oŇčkom awut arkun m…õr…ôŇč. Tewe ta w…ôkin t…õnay…Ēn…õ P…õl…õk,\f + \fr 10:25 \fq P…õl…õk\ft  = c…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęk…ôyer…õn…õ¬Ľ \f* bawo t…õm t…Ēn t…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…õnayer…õn…õ. K…Ē tewe ta w…õnc t…õnay…Ēn…õ Yoktan.  
\v 26 K…Ē Yoktan oŇčkom Almodad, S…õl…õf, Hacarmaw…õt, Y…õrah,  
\v 27 Hadoram, Husal, Dikalah,  
\v 28 Hobal, Abimay…õl, Saba,  
\v 29 Ofir, Hawila, k…Ē Yobab. AkaŇč…õ f…ôp awut a Yoktan Ňčanayi.  
\v 30 K…Ē Ňčand…õ k…ôy…õf…õ ka Mesa, Sefar k…ôs…ôk, haŇč nde m…Ēr…Ē ma nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.  
\v 31 Awut a Sem Ňč…Ē akak…Ē, d…ôcusuŇčka cusuŇčka, d…ôcusu cusu, d…ôt…Ēf t…Ēf. 
\p  
\v 32 CusuŇčka ca awut a Nuha c…Ē cac…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē aŇčkom Ňča m…Ē. Afum akaŇč…õ Ňč…Ē afum Ňčawur d…ôris a k…Ē Ňčandeyers…õn…õ d…ônt…Ēf, doru f…ôp nt…õ domun d…õlar…ôm denacep…ôr m…Ē. 
\c 11  
\s1 K…ôl…Ē k…ôŇčeci ka Bab…õl 
\p  
\v 1 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē doru f…ôp kusu kin k'ancc…Ēp, pacloku, moloku min mayi.  
\v 2 K'afum Ňčande Ňčak…Ē k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk m…Ēr…Ē at…Ēf Ňča SiŇčhar, k…Ē Ňčand…õ mi dac…Ē.  
\v 3 K…Ē Ňčalok…õn…õ: ¬ęPasut birik, pac…Ēf bi!¬Ľ K…Ē birik b…Ēc…Ēf bab…Ēk…Ē b…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňča masar, k…Ē k…Ērtal k…ôy…Ēn…õ Ňča dos.  
\v 4 K…Ē Ňčaloku s…Ē: ¬ęPaŇčk…Ēn, pac…ômb…ôr dare k…Ē k…ôl…Ē nk…õ domp da ki dendek…Ē haŇč d…Ēs…Ē k…Ēm m…Ē. Nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pas…Ēt…Ē tewe m…Ē, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ su s…Ē k…ôt…Ēsams…ôr doru.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 5 K…Ē MARIKI ontor k…ôdem…Ēm…ôn dare k…Ē k…ôl…Ē nk…õ afum Ňčancc…ômb…ôr m…Ē.  
\v 6 K…Ē MARIKI oloku, ¬ęN…ôm…Ēm…ôn afum aŇč…õ! F…ôp faŇčan kusu kin k…Ē Ňčanc…Ēp. N…ôm…Ēm…ôn s…Ē nt…õ Ňčancop k…ôy…Ē m…Ē. T…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm teyi f…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčm…Ēn…õ Ňča k…ôy…Ē ka t…õfaŇč taŇčan m…Ē.  
\v 7 PaŇčk…Ēn, pator, pan…ĒŇčk…ôl-n…ĒŇčk…ôl kusu k…ôŇčan nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčanen…õn…õ s…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē MARIKI …õsams…ôr Ňča doru, k…Ē Ňčasak k…ôc…ômb…ôr dare.  
\v 9 Ti t'awen…õ di Bab…õl, bawo dif…Ē MARIKI …õnan…ĒŇčk…ôl cusu, k'…õsam…ôs…ôr afum doru. 
\s1 Tecep…ôr…õn…õ ta Sem k…Ē awut …Ēn, k…ôb…ôp ka Abram 
\p  
\v 10 Tecep…ôr…õn…õ ta Sem t…õnt…õ: Sem …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 100, a p…ôdekom Arpaksad, teren ta m…õr…ôŇč nt…õ domun d…õnasak ant…Ēf m…Ē.  
\v 11 K…ôkom ka Arpaksad, k…Ē Sem eyi s…Ē doru meren 500, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 12 Arpaksad …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 35, a p…ôdekom S…õlah.  
\v 13 K…ôkom ka S…õlah, Arpaksad …õnas…Ēt…Ē s…Ē meren 403, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 14 S…õlah …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 30, a p…ôdekom Heb…õr.  
\v 15 K…ôkom ka Heb…õr, S…õlah …õnas…Ēt…Ē s…Ē meren 403, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 16 K…Ē Heb…õr …Ēs…Ēt…Ē meren 34, a p…ôdekom P…õl…õk.  
\v 17 K…ôkom ka P…õl…õk, Heb…õr …õnas…Ēt…Ē s…Ē meren 430, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 18 P…õl…õk …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 30, a p…ôdekom Rehu.  
\v 19 K…ôkom ka Rehu, P…õl…õk …õnas…Ēt…Ē s…Ē meren 209, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 20 Rehu …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 32, a p…ôdekom Seruk.  
\v 21 K…ôkom ka Seruk, Rehu …õnas…Ēt…Ē s…Ē meren 207, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 22 Seruk …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 30, a p…ôdekom Nahor.  
\v 23 K…ôkom ka Nahor, Seruk …õnas…Ēt…Ē s…Ē meren 200, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 24 Nahor …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 29 a p…ôdekom Terah.  
\v 25 K…ôkom ka Terah, Nahor …õnas…Ēt…Ē s…Ē meren 119, mm…õ …õnakom s…Ē awut arkun k'awut aran al…Ēma m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 26 Terah …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 70, a p…ôdekom Abram, Nahor k…Ē HaraŇč. 
\s1 Tecep…ôr…õn…õ ta Terah k…Ē Abram 
\p  
\v 27 Tecep…ôr…õn…õ ta Terah t…õnt…õ: Terah okom Abram, Nahor k…Ē HaraŇč nw…õ …õnakom L…Ēt m…Ē.  
\v 28 HaraŇč, f…Ēr ya kas kiriŇč y'…õnafi, at…Ēf nŇč…õ anakom k…Ē m…Ē, nde dare da Ur nde at…Ēf Ňča Kaldi.  
\v 29 Abram k…Ē Nahor Ňčan…õnc…õ. W…ôran ka Abram ancwe Saray k…Ē w…ôran ka Nahor, Milka. Milka, wan ka HaraŇč …õnayi, ŇčapaŇčn…õ kas kin k…Ē Yiska.  
\v 30 Saray …õnakom f…õ, …õnas…Ēt…Ē f…õ wan. 
\p  
\v 31 K…Ē Terah …õl…õk wan k…Ēn Abram, k…Ē wans…Ē k…Ēn L…Ēt, wan ka HaraŇč, k'…õl…õk…õn…õ s…Ē Saray w…ôran ka Abram, k…Ē Ňčasol f…ôp faŇčan k…ôwur ka nde dare da Ur nde at…Ēf Ňča Kaldi k…ôk…Ē ka at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč. K…Ē Ňčamb…ôp at…Ēf Ňča HaraŇč k…Ē Ňčand…õ di.  
\v 32 Terah …õnawon doru meren 205, a k'endefi d…ôndo at…Ēf Ňča HaraŇč. 
\c 12  
\ms2 Tecep…ôr…õn…õ ta Abraham 
\mr 12.1-25.18 
\s1 Kanu k…ôloku ka Abram k…ôwur ka at…Ēf Ňč…Ēn 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Abram: ¬ęM…ôwur at…Ēf Ňčam, d…ôŇčkom dam, k…ôl…Ē ka papa kam, m…ôk…Ē at…Ēf nŇč…õ indement…ôr …ôm m…Ē.  
\v 2 Indes…ĒŇč'am k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka kas k'afum alar…ôm, indes…ĒŇč …ôm p…ôt…Ēt, indes…ĒŇč…õ tewe tam t…õb…õk. M…ôndetolan…õ afum al…Ēma p…ôt…Ēt.  
\v 3 Indes…ĒŇč p…ôt…Ēt aŇč…õ Ňčandetolan'am p…ôt…Ēt m…Ē. Indes…ĒŇč p…ôl…õc aŇč…õ Ňčandetolan'am p…ôl…õc m…Ē. Tetam t'indes…ĒŇč…õn…õ cusuŇčka ca doru f…ôp p…ôt…Ēt.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 4 K'Abram owur HaraŇč p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnaloku k…Ē ti m…Ē, k…Ē L…Ēt …õnc…õps…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč. T…õnat…ôŇčn…õ Abram p…ôs…Ēt…Ē meren 75.  
\v 5 K'Abram …õl…õk Saray, w…ôran k…Ēn, k…Ē L…Ēt wan ka w…ôbek'…Ēn w…ôrkun k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē Ňčanay…Ē di m…Ē, k'afum \f + \fr 12:5 \fq Afum\ft  = Ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ¬ęyeŇčes…ôm, ca yeyi w…ôyeŇč.¬Ľ \f* ak…Ē …õnas…Ēt…Ē HaraŇč m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčawur k…ôk…Ē at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč. 
\s1 Abram nde at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč, k…Ē k…ônd…õ k…Ēn Misira 
\p K…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč.  
\v 6 K'Abram …õncali at…Ēf haŇč k…ôfo nk…õ ancwe S…ôk…õm, haŇč nde tofo nt…õ AŇčkiri Ňča More Ňč…õnc…ôm…õ m…Ē. Aka KanaŇč Ňčanayi at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē. 
\p  
\v 7 K…Ē MARIKI owur…ôr Abram k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęIndes…ĒŇč at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ yuruya yam.¬Ľ K'Abram olomps…õ MARIKI mm…õ m…õnawur…ôr k…Ē m…Ē, tetek toloŇčn…õ d…ôndo.  
\v 8 K'eyekti s…Ē di saŇčka, nde …õncy…õf…õ p…ôck…Ē d…ôm…Ēr…Ē m…Ē, k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ Betel \f + \fr 12:8 \fq Betel\ft  = ¬ęk…ôl…Ē ka Kanu.¬Ľ \f* m…Ē. K'…õnc…ômb…ôr abal di, Betel beyi k…Ē nde dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, dare da Hay deyi k…Ē nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē. K'…Ēl…Ē di tetek toloŇčn…õ MARIKI, k'ontola tewe ta MARIKI. \f + \fr 12:8 \fq MARIKI\ft  = Tewe t…Ēt…Ēt ta Kanu, ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ¬ęYHWH.¬Ľ \f* 
\v 9 K'Abram …õy…õf…õ k…ôcal-cali k…ôk…Ē ka k…ôca ka N…õk…õf. 
\p  
\v 10 Dor d…õnayi d…Ēt…Ēf, k'Abram ontor Misira k…ôk…Ēcep…ôr…õn…õ t…õm, bawo dor d…õncb…õk k…ôb…õk d…ôm.  
\v 11 Nt…õ …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…ôb…õr…õ Misira m…Ē, k'oloku w…ôran k…Ēn Saray: ¬ęM…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im, inc…ôr…õ a w…ôran w…ôt…Ēt teyi m…ôy…Ēn…õ.  
\v 12 K'aka Misira Ňčandek…Ēn…ôŇčk …ôm-…õ, Ňčandek…Ēloku: ‚ÄĻW…ôran k…Ēn …Ēf…Ē!‚Äļ T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē Ňčandek…Ēdif im, Ňčasak m…ôna.  
\v 13 M…ôdek…Ē m…ôloku Ňča a w…ôkir…õ kem m…ôy…Ēn…õ. Nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčasump…ôr im belbel tetam m…Ē, tetam t'endek…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ, ta ifi-…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 14 Nt…õ Abram …õmb…õr…õ Misira m…Ē, k'aka Misira Ňčan…ôŇčk w…ôran nw…õ entes…õ p…ôcep…ôr…ôr.  
\v 15 K'ak…ôs…ôk a Firawona \f + \fr 12:15 \fq Firawona\ft  = Baf…Ē tewe ta fum t…Ē, mba tewe ta ab…õ a Misira tencyi. \f* Ňčan…ôŇčk k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčayek-yek…ôs k…Ē nda Firawona. Nt…õ t…Ē k'aŇčk…õr…õ w…ôran nw…õ nde k…ôl…Ē ka Firawona.  
\v 16 K…Ē Firawona osump…ôr Abram belbel teta Saray, k'…Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ s…õm y…õf…õt haŇč y…Ēp…ĒŇč, s…Ēfale, amar…ôs arkun k'aran k…Ē y…Ēk…Ēm…õ.  
\v 17 Mba k…Ē MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč Firawona k'afum …Ēn runc y…Ēp…ĒŇč teta Saray, w…ôran ka Abram.  
\v 18 K…Ē Firawona ewe Abram, k'eyif k…Ē: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē m…ôy…Ē em nt…õ? Ake's…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ m…ônt…Ēlok'im a w…ôran kam …Ēf…Ē m…Ē?  
\v 19 T'ake t…Ē m…ôlok…õ a w…ôkir…õ kam …Ēf…Ē-…õ? M…ôs…ĒŇč'em k…ôl…õk k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôran kem. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, w…ôran kam …õw…õ. M…ôl…õk k…Ē! M…ôk…Ē!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē Firawona oloku afum …Ēn, ¬ęN…ôsak k…Ē p…ôk…Ē nk…Ēn, k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn k…Ē ca ny…õ y…Ēy…Ēn…õ y…Ēn m…Ē f…ôp.¬Ľ 
\c 13  
\p  
\v 1 K'Abram …õmp…õrn…õ Misira k…ôk…Ē ka k…ôca ka N…õk…õf, nk…Ēn, w…ôran k…Ēn k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē …õnay…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, p…ôsol k…Ē w…ôrok k…Ēn L…Ēt. 
\s1 K…ôgb…õy…õn…õ ka Abram k…Ē L…Ēt 
\p  
\v 2 Abram …õnas…Ēt…Ē daka d…õlar…ôm, …õnala y…Ēc…Ēl, p…ôsam k…Ē k…õma.  
\v 3 K'…õy…õf…õ k…ôcal-cali k…ôy…õf…õ ka N…õk…õf haŇč Betel da …õnad…Ēf abal t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, Betel k…Ē Hay dac…Ē.  
\v 4 K…ôca nk…õ …õnanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôlomp…ôs tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu d…ônda, k'Abram oŇčkorn…õ tewe ta MARIKI. \f + \fr 13:4 \ft  M…ôm…Ēm…ôn Sora sa 12.8. \f* 
\p  
\v 5 L…Ēt nw…õ Ňčanasol m…Ē, nk…Ēn s…Ē …õnay…Ē cir, Ňčkesiya, c…ôna k…ôb…ôp c…ôbal.  
\v 6 At…Ēf Ňč…õnaf…õt…ôr Ňča k…ôyi k…ôŇčan tofo tin, bawo y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan y…õnala.  
\v 7 K…Ē k…ôc…Ēp k…ônde k…ôyi ak…õk a y…Ēc…Ēl ya Abram k'ak…õk a y…Ēc…Ēl ya L…Ēt dac…Ē. At…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē s…Ē, aKanaŇč k'aPerisi Ňčanand…õ Ňči t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 8 K'Abram oloku L…Ēt: ¬ęP…ômar f…õ ak…õk a y…Ēc…Ēl yam Ňčac…Ēp k'ak…õk a y…Ēc…Ēl yem. S…ôna s…Ē p…ômar f…õ su ti, bawo aka k…ôl…Ē kin disr…õ Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ.  
\v 9 Ant…Ēf f…ôp Ňč…Ē ŇčaŇč…õ Ňčey'…ôm f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē. K…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt-…õ, iŇčk…Ē k…ômeriya. K…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ē k…ômeriya, iŇčk…Ē k…ôt…Ēt, mba m…ôwos…õ s…ôgb…õy…õn…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 10 K…Ē L…Ēt eyekti f…Ēr k'…õn…ôŇčk aranta Ňča Yurd…õn t…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnd…ôm m…Ē (t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē ta Kanu k…ôntal…ôs…ôr Sodom k…Ē Komora-…õ), p…ônck…Ē haŇč Cohar p…ôm…Ē aranta (m…õr…õ) Ňča MARIKI, p…ôm…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Misira.  
\v 11 K…Ē L…Ēt …õl…õk dal…õ da Yurd…õn f…ôp, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē Ňčanagb…õy…õn…õ k…Ē Abram.  
\v 12 K'Abram …õnd…õ at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč, k…Ē L…Ēt …õnd…õ s…ôdare sa aranta Ňča Yurd…õn k'…Ēnd…Ēf c…ôbal c…Ēn k…ôca ka Sodom.  
\v 13 Afum a Sodom Ňčanates…õ f…õ b…ôk…ôc, Ňčancciya MARIKI. 
\p  
\v 14 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Abram, nt…õ Ňčasak…õn…õ oŇč k…Ē L…Ēt m…Ē: ¬ęM…ôyekti f…Ēr k…ôy…õf…õ d…ônda m…ôyi m…Ē, m…ôm…Ēm…ôn k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, k…ômeriya nde dec d…õmp…õ k…Ē nde d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē.  
\v 15 Bawo at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ m…ôŇčn…ôŇčk m…Ē f…ôp indes…ĒŇč …ôm Ňči k…Ē yuruya yam.  
\v 16 Indes…ĒŇč…õ yuruya yam y…õla haŇč ta antam k…ôl…Ēm Ňča-…õ, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ant…Ētam k…ôl…Ēm k…ôbof ant…Ēf k…ôroŇč m…Ē.  
\v 17 M…ôy…õf…õ m…ôk…Ēt at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ dobolu k…Ē dowokulu da Ňči, bawo indes…ĒŇč …ôm Ňči.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 18 K…Ē Abram encep…õ c…ôbal c…Ēn, k'ende p…ôd…Ēf ci nde tofo nt…õ AŇčkiri Ňča Mamre y…õnc…ôm…õ m…Ē k…ôs…ôk, ta …Ēmb…Ēl…õ Heb…ôr…ĒŇč-…õ, k'olomp…ôs di tetek toloŇčn…õ MARIKI. \f + \fr 13:18 \fq MARIKI\ft  = It…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē c…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęYHWH¬Ľ: M…ôm…Ēm…ôn Sora sa 4.26 \f* 
\c 14  
\s1 Abram, ab…õ k…Ē Melkisedek 
\p  
\v 1 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē ab…õ a t…Ēf maŇčk…ôl…õ Ňčancy…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē ab…õ a s…ôdare k…ôcam…ôt: Amraf…õl w…ôb…õ w…ôka SiŇčhar,\f + \fr 14:1 \fq SiŇčhar\ft  = Mesopotami \f* Aryok w…ôb…õ w…ôka Elasar, K…ôd…Ēr-Lahom…õr w…ôb…õ w…ôka Helam, k…Ē Tid…ôhal w…ôb…õ w…ôka Koyim,  
\v 2 t…õnat…ôŇčn…õ ab…õ akak…Ē Ňčacy…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē ab…õ a s…ôdare k…ôcam…ôt: Bera \f + \fr 14:2 \fq Bera\ft  ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęp…ôl…õc¬Ľ \f* w…ôb…õ w…ôka Sodom, Bir…ôsa \f + \fr 14:2 \fq Bir…ôsa\ft  ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õl…õc¬Ľ \f* w…ôb…õ w…ôka Komora, Sinab w…ôb…õ w…ôka Adma, Semeber w…ôb…õ w…ôka Ceboyim k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Bela mb…õ b…Ēy…Ēn…õ Cohar m…Ē.  
\v 3 Ab…õ akaŇč…õ k…ôcam…ôt f…ôp aranta Ňča Sidim dac…Ē Ňčanand…õ, nde p…ôy…Ēn…õ m…Ēk…Ē K…ôba K…ôdok…ôt m…Ē.  
\v 4 Meren w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč Ňčayi k…ôtam ka K…ôd…Ēr-Lahom…õr d…ônt…Ēf, mba teren ta w…ôco k…Ē maas k…Ē ŇčayeŇčk…ôr k…Ē s…ôbomp.  
\v 5 Teren ta w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ, K…ôd…Ēr-Lahom…õr k'ab…õ ak…Ē Ňčanab…õr…õn…õ m…Ē, Ňčasut aRefay nde dare da Asterot-Karnayim, k…Ē Ňčasut aSus nde Ham, k…Ē Ňčasut afum a Em nde Aranta Ňča Kiriyatayim.  
\v 6 K'ab…õ maŇčk…ôl…õ Ňčasut aHor ndaraŇčan, nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Sehir.\f + \fr 14:6 \fq Sehir\ft  ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē Ed…Ēm, ndena Esayu k…Ē afum …Ēn \f* K…Ē Ňčamb…õl…ôs aHor haŇč nde tofo nt…õ AŇčkiri Ňča Paran Ňč…õnc…ôm…õ m…Ē, nde t…õgb…ôr…õ k…ôs…ôk.  
\v 7 K'ab…õ akaŇč…õ maŇčk…ôl…õ Ňčaluks…ôrn…õ Ey…ôn-Mispe \f + \fr 14:7 \fq Ey…ôn-Mispe\ft  ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęabat Ňča kiti¬Ľ \f* (nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ Kad…õs m…Ē), k…Ē Ňčasut aka Amalek at…Ēf ŇčaŇčan f…ôp k…Ē Am…Ēr aŇč…õ Ňčanand…õ Hacacon-Tamar m…Ē.  
\v 8 K…Ē ab…õ a s…ôdare k…ôcam…ôt (Sodom, Komora, Adma, Ceboyim k…Ē Bela, ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē Cohar) Ňčamb…õr…õn…õ k…ôsut…õn…õ nde aranta Ňča Sidim.  
\v 9 Ak…Ē s…Ē Ňčayi: K…ôd…Ēr-Lahom…õr w…ôb…õ w…ôka Helam, Tid…ôhal w…ôb…õ w…ôka Koyim, Amraf…õl w…ôb…õ w…ôka SiŇčhar, k…Ē Aryok w…ôb…õ w…ôka Elasar. Ab…õ maŇčk…ôl…õ Ňčay…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē ab…õ k…ôcam…ôt.  
\v 10 Nt…õ Aranta Ňča Sidim Ňč…õnala c…ôl…ômp ca k…Ērtal m…Ē, k'ab…õ aŇč…õ k…ôcam…ôt dac…Ē, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Sodom k…Ē w…ôka Komora Ňčay…õks…õ k…Ē Ňčant…õmp…õn…õ ci disr…õ. K'alp…ôs aŇč…õ maas k'as…Ēdar aŇčan Ňčay…õks…õ k…Ē Ňčant…õf…ôrn…õ k…ôca ka d…ôt…Ēr…Ē.  
\v 11 K'atam a as…Ēdar a ab…õ k…ôcam…ôt Ňčaw…õt…ôs ca ya aka Sodom k…Ē Komora k…Ē yeri yaŇčan f…ôp, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē.  
\v 12 K…Ē Ňčasump…ôr s…Ē L…Ēt k…Ē daka d…Ēn, nk…Ēn L…Ēt wan ka w…ôbeki ka Abram …õnayi, (k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ kaŇčk…õ k…ônab…ôp L…Ēt nw…õ p…ôyi Sodom). 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē w…ômulp…õ d…ôk…ôwan w…ôkin ende p…ôloku ti Abram w…ôHeb…ôre, nw…õ …õnand…õ nde k…ôfo nk…õ AŇčkiri Ňča Mamre w…ôAm…Ēr Ňč…õnac…ôm…õ m…Ē. Mamre nw…õ p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…õnc ka ∆źsk…Ēl k…Ē Haner, aŇč…õ ŇčanacaŇč…ôs k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē Abram m…Ē.  
\v 14 Nt…õ Abram ene k…ôsump…ôr ka wan ka w…ôbek'…Ēn m…Ē, k'oloŇčka asol …Ēn afum 318 aŇč…õ ŇčanabaŇčs…õ, akom…õn…õ …Ēn dac…Ē m…Ē. K'…õnc…õps…õ ab…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanasump…ôr wan ka w…ôbek'…Ēn dar…ôŇč haŇč dare da Dan.  
\v 15 K'Abram eyer…ôs k…ônay (k…ôgba) k…Ēn, k…Ē Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ Ňča k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ ka pibi, nk…Ēn Abram k'amar …Ēn, k…Ē Ňčasut asump…ôr a wan ka w…ôbek'…Ēn, k…Ē Ňčamb…õl…ôs Ňča haŇč Hoba, nŇč…õ Ňčeyi Damas k…ôca k…ômeriya m…Ē.  
\v 16 K'oluks…õ ca f…ôp, k'oluks…õ s…Ē L…Ēt wan ka w…ôbek'…Ēn, aran, k'afum alp…ôs aŇč…õ. 
\p  
\v 17 Nt…õ Abram osut K…ôd…Ēr-Lahom…õr k'amar…õn…õ …Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Sodom owur k…ôdefayn…õ k…Ē nde aranta Ňča Sawe, nde p…ôy…Ēn…õ ¬ęAranta Ňča W…ôb…õ¬Ľ m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 18 Melkisedek, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Sal…õm,\f + \fr 14:18 \fq Sal…õm\ft  = ¬ęYerusal…õm¬Ľ, ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē Darsalam \f* …õŇčk…õr…õ k…ôcom k…Ē member: Melkisedek, w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôka Kanu nk…õ k…ôyi canu c…ôl…Ēma f…ôp k…ôroŇč m…Ē, …õnayi.  
\v 19 K…Ē Melkisedek ontolan…õ Abram, k'oloku: ¬ęM…ôna Abram, Kanu nk…õ k…ôyi canu c…ôl…Ēma f…ôp k…ôroŇč m…Ē, W…ôb…õ w…ôka d…ônt…Ēf k…Ē darenc, k…ôpoc'am p…ôt…Ēt.  
\v 20 Ilel…ôs Kanu nk…õ k…ôyi canu c…ôl…Ēma f…ôp k…ôroŇč m…Ē, nk…õ k…ôl…õk ay…õf…ôr…õn…õ am k…Ē k…ômb…õr …ôm d…ôwaca m…Ē!¬Ľ K…Ē Abram …Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē faril…õ fa ca y…Ēk…Ē Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē d…ôk…ôwan m…Ē f…ôp. 
\p  
\v 21 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Sodom oloku Abram: ¬ęM…ôs…ĒŇč im afum, m…ôl…õk ca yay…õ f…ôp yam.¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē Abram oluks…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka Sodom m…Ēc…Ēp: ¬ęIndot k…ôca nn…Ē MARIKI nw…õ eyi canu c…ôl…Ēma f…ôp k…ôroŇč m…Ē, nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka darenc k…Ē d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē.  
\v 23 If…Ēl…õk ali paka pin ca yam dac…Ē. Ali debeŇča k…Ē p…ôyi f…õ ti-…õ p…õp…ôt…ôr…õ pa k…Ēfta kam. Ti t…Ē m…ônt…Ētam k…ôloku: ‚ÄĻIn'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Abram k…ôy…Ē daka.‚Äļ  
\v 24 If…Ēl…õk daka o daka, m…õn…õ yeri ny…õ afum em Ňčandi m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôyer nk…õ at…õmp em ∆źsk…Ēl, Haner, k…Ē Mamre Ňčas…Ēt…Ē m…Ē, bawo p…ômar Ňčas…Ēt…Ē k…ôyer.¬Ľ 
\c 15  
\s1 MARIKI …õncaŇč…ôs kiyi k…ôŇčan tes tin k…Ē Abram 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē mencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē MARIKI owur…ôr Abram d…ômere k'oloku k…Ē nt…õ: ¬ęTa m…ônes…õ, Abram! Ina yati indey…Ēn'am aca. Indeluks'am k…ôway p…ôp…ĒŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 2 K…Ē Abram eyif Kanu: ¬ęMARIKI W…ôb…õ kem, ake m…ôndes…ĒŇč im-…õ? Intas ta iy…Ē wan-…õ, w…ôdel…õk k…õ kem …Ēy…Ēn…õ Eliyeser w…ôka Damas.¬Ľ  
\v 3 K…Ē Abram …Ēn…Ēc…ôr: ¬ęM…ôs…ĒŇč f'em awut,\f + \fr 15:3 \ft  Yuruya \f* nw…õ aŇčkom nde k…ôl…Ē kem disr…õ m…Ē, nk…Ēn endel…õk k…õ kem.¬Ľ  
\v 4 K…Ē MARIKI oloku k…Ē, ¬ęAla, baf…Ē nk…Ēn endey…Ēn…õ w…ôl…õk ka k…õ kam, mba wan kam w…ôkom nw…õ endewur …ôm d…ôris m…Ē yati.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē MARIKI owur…õn…õ Abram abal Ňč…Ēn disr…õ, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôgb…ôtn…õ k…Ēm. M…ôl…Ēm c…Ēs cac…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē m…ôntam-…õ.¬Ľ K'…Ēn…Ēc…ôr: ¬ęP…ôm…Ē c…Ēs cac…Ēk…Ē, yuruya yam af…Ēde pactam k…ôl…Ēm Ňča f…ôp.¬Ľ  
\v 6 Abram …õnagb…õk…ôr k…ôlaŇč k…Ēn MARIKI. Ti t…Ē MARIKI …õnal…Ēm…õ k…Ē fum w…ôlompu.  
\v 7 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku k…Ē: ¬ęIn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI nw…õ …õnawur'am Ur Ňča aKaldi k…ôdes…ĒŇč …ôm at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ, m…ôde m…ôl…õk Ňči k…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē Abram eyif: ¬ęMARIKI W…ôb…õ kem, c…ôke c'indetam k…ôc…ôr…õ a indes…Ēt…Ē at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ k…õ-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 9 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôk…õr'em wana weyec…ôra win, wir w…õran win, k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňčin f…ôp fayi ya meren maas maas, t…Ēpay tin k…Ē apokpoka Ňčin.¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē Abram …õŇčk…õr…õ s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē k'eŇčgber-gberi yi dac…Ē dac…Ē k'omboc…ôs yegber-gberi yay…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč y…õt…õf…ôr…õn…õ, k…Ē b…õmp, m…ôlm…ôl m'…õnaboc yi ta aŇčgberi yi-…õ.  
\v 11 K…Ē y…Ēf…ôn yontor…ôr s…õm yegber-gberi yay…Ēk…Ē, mba k'Abram …õmb…õl…ôs yi. 
\p  
\v 12 Dec dendekal…õ, k'Abram endir…ôrn…õ, k'ayekyek Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč Ňč…õŇčgb…ôp…ôrn…õ k…Ē k'enes…õ d…ômere.  
\v 13 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku Abram: ¬ęM…ôc…ôr…õ a yuruya yam yendey…Ēn…õ acik…ôra at…Ēf Ňčocuru nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēnt…Ēy…Ēn…õ ŇčaŇčan m…Ē. Ňäandek…Ēy…Ēn…õ di acar, andek…Ēt…Ēr…ôs Ňča di haŇč meren 400.  
\v 14 Mba Indet…Ēr…ôs afum aŇč…õ Ňčandec…ômb…ôr Ňča dacar m…Ē, Ňčandewur at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē k…Ē ca y…õlar…ôm.  
\v 15 K…Ē m…ôna Abram, m…ôndek…Ēb…ôp atem am p…ôforu disr…õ, \f + \fr 15:15 \ft  Ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęM…ôndefi p…ôforu disr…õ.¬Ľ \f* pawup …ôm detem dobotu disr…õ. \f + \fr 15:15 \ft  Ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęP…ôbotu pa detem dam.¬Ľ \f* 
\v 16 Yuruya yam yendeluks…ôrn…õ nn…Ē m…õn…õ t…õm ta danapa da maŇčk…ôl…õ, bawo Am…Ēr Ňčantacep…ôr…ôr f…õ kiciya k…ôŇčan a ideb…õl…ôs Ňča d…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 17 Nt…õ dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k'asum Ňč…õm…ôt (dimi dontor) k…Ē teken p…õnc…õs…ôŇč…õ, n…õnc k…Ē kinim…õ yencep…ôr yoboc ya s…õm yeyer yay…Ēk…Ē dac…Ē.  
\v 18 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ē MARIKI …õnacaŇč…ôs k…ôyi k…ôŇčan danapa k…Ē Abram. P…ôcloku Abram: ¬ęIs…ĒŇč yuruya yam k…ôy…õf…õ ka k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Misira haŇč ∆źf…ôrat, k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč:  
\v 19 Indes…ĒŇč yuruya yam at…Ēf Ňča aKeni, aKenisi, aKadmon,  
\v 20 Ňča aHewy, aPerisi, aRefay,  
\v 21 Ňča Am…Ēr, aKanaŇč, aKirkas, k…Ē aYebus.¬Ľ 
\c 16  
\s1 K…ôkom ka S…ômayila 
\p  
\v 1 Saray w…ôran k'Abram …õnakom…õ f…õ k…Ē wan. Mba …õnay…Ē w…ôcar w…ôran w…ôMisira, pacwe k…Ē Hakar.  
\v 2 K…Ē Saray oloku Abram: ¬ęM…ôn…ôŇčk, MARIKI …õyams…ôr im k…ôs…Ēt…Ē ka wan. M…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôcar kem, t…Ēl…Ēma intam k…ôs…Ēt…ôr k…Ē wan w…ôrkun.¬Ľ K…Ē Abram …õnc…ôŇčk…ôl dim da Saray.  
\v 3 Awa, k…Ē Saray w…ôran ka Abram …õl…õk w…ôcar k…Ēn w…ôMisira, Hakar, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē wos Abram p…ôy…Ē k…Ē w…ôran. T…õnat…ôŇčn…õ k…ônd…õ ka Abram at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč k…ôs…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco.  
\v 4 K…Ē Abram Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē Hakar, k…Ē Hakar …õmb…õk…ôs. Nt…õ …õnc…ôr…õ a …õmb…õk…ôs m…Ē, Hakar …Ēm…Ēm…ôn…õ f…õ s…Ē Saray f…Ēr y…Ēt…Ēt.  
\v 5 K…Ē Saray oloku Abram: ¬ęM…ôn'endesar…õ p…ôcuy pa m…Ēl…Ēm…ôs mm…õ …Ēl…Ēm…ôs im m…Ē! Ina yati, in'…õl…õk w…ôcar kem k'imb…õr …ôm k…Ē d…ôwaca, mba nt…õ …õn…ôŇčkn…õ oŇč p…ôb…õk…ôs m…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôf…ôr-f…ôr…ôs im. Mba MARIKI omboc su kiti dac…Ē (k…ôyi su dac…Ē), ina k…Ē m…ôna!¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē Abram oluks…õ Saray moloku: ¬ęW…ôcar kam ey'…ôm d…ôwaca. M…ôy…Ē k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē tentes'am m…Ē.¬Ľ Awa, k…Ē Saray …Ēnt…Ēr…ôs Hakar haŇč k…Ē Hakar …õy…õks…ôr k…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…Ēl…õ.  
\v 7 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI m…ĒŇčk…Ē m…õb…ôp k…Ē nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ k…ôl…ômp k…ôl…Ēma k…ôs…ôk ta …Ēmb…Ēl…õ k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē \f + \fr 16:7 \ft  Tofo t…õnayi, nde domun d…Ēt…Ēt doncwur d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē. \f* nk…õ k…ôyi d…Ēp…Ē da Sur m…Ē.  
\v 8 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ meyif: ¬ęHakar, w…ôcar ka Saray, deke m…ôy…õf…õ-…õ? Deke m…ôŇčk…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Hakar oluks…õ mi moloku: ¬ęMariki mem Saray, iy…õks…ôr.¬Ľ  
\v 9 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI moloku, ¬ęM…ôluks…ôrn…õ ndena Mariki mam, m…ôk…Ē m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē d…ônt…Ēf.¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI moloku k…Ē: ¬ęIndes…ĒŇč…õ yuruya yam y…õla haŇč ta antam k…ôl…Ēm Ňča-…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 11 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI moloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ômb…õk…ôs tant…õ, wan w…ôrkun m…ôndekom, wan w…ôkak…Ē m…ôde m…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē tewe ta S…ômayila\f + \fr 16:11 \fq S…ômayila\ft  = c…ôHeb…ôre ¬ę∆źnc…ôŇčk…ôl¬Ľ \f*, bawo MARIKI ene k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ ka p…ôcuy pam.  
\v 12 Wan kam endeyi p…ôm…Ē s…Ēfale sa dop. Ende p…ôccaŇč afum f…ôp k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ, f…ôp f…ôcy…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn. Sona s'endend…õ p…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ afum alp…ôs aŇč…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē Hakar ewe MARIKI mm…õ m…õnalok-lok…ôr k…Ē m…Ē, ¬ęAta-∆źl-Roy,¬Ľ ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē: ¬ęIn…ôŇčk nn…Ē Kanu nk…õ k…ôn…ôŇčk im m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 14 Ti t'awen…õ k…ôl…ômp kaŇčk…Ē, k…ôl…ômp ka Lahay-Roy. K…ôl…ômp kaŇčk…Ē k…ôyi Kad…õs k…Ē Beredu dac…Ē.  
\v 15 K…Ē Hakar oŇčkom…õ Abram wan w…ôrkun, k…Ē Abram ewe wan w…ôkak…Ē Hakar …õnakom…õ k…Ē m…Ē tewe ta S…ômayila.  
\v 16 Abram …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 86 t…õm nt…õ Hakar onckom…õ k…Ē S…ômayila m…Ē. 
\c 17  
\s1 Kanu k…ôs…ôkp…ôr tewe ta Abram k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ¬ęAbraham¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ Abram …Ēs…Ēt…Ē meren 99 m…Ē, k…Ē MARIKI owur…ôr k…Ē, p…ôcloku k…Ē: ¬ęIn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Kanu nk…õ k…ôntam mes ma doru f…ôp m…Ē, m…ôk…Ēt f…Ēr yem kiriŇč, m…ôc…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč.  
\v 2 IndecaŇč…ôs danapa dosu, ina k…Ē m…ôna dac…Ē, is…ĒŇč …ôm yuruya y…õlar…ôm.¬Ľ  
\v 3 K…Ē Abram …õnc…ôp tobu d…ônt…Ēf k…Ē Kanu k…ôloku k…Ē nt…õ:  
\v 4 ¬ęTa ina, danapa dem d…õnd…õ k…Ē m…ôna dac…Ē: M…ôndey…Ēn…õ kas ka afum a t…Ēf y…õlar…ôm.  
\v 5 Af…Ēs…Ēw'am tewe ta Abram, mba Abraham,\f + \fr 17:5 \fq Abram\ft  = ¬ęPapa ka afum alar…ôm,¬Ľ \fq Abraham\ft  = ¬ępapa ka t…Ēf y…õlar…ôm.¬Ľ \f* bawo indes…ĒŇč'am k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka kas ka afum a t…Ēf y…õlar…ôm.  
\v 6 Indes…ĒŇč …ôm dokomb…ôra d…Ēp…ĒŇč, indes…ĒŇč'am k…ôkom ka afum alar…ôm, ab…õ yati Ňčandeyi Ňča dac…Ē.  
\v 7 Indep…õn…õ danapa, ina k…Ē m…ôna dac…Ē k…ôb…ôp ka yuruya yam k…Ē m…ôna m…ôfi-…õ, indec…ôm…õ danapa dad…Ēk…Ē dar…ôŇč k…Ē yuruya yam doru o doru. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē Kanu kam k'indey…Ēn…õ k…Ē ka yuruya yam k…Ē m…ôna m…ôndecep…ôr-…õ.  
\v 8 Indes…ĒŇč …ôm k…Ē yuruya yam at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč ŇčaŇč…õ m…ônt…õp k…ôcb…õr…õ m…Ē f…ôp, Ňčendey…Ēn…õ ŇčaŇčan doru o doru, iy…Ēn…õ Kanu k…ôŇčan.¬Ľ  
\v 9 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku Abraham: ¬ęM…ôna k…Ē yuruya yam, d…õt…õmp d…õt…õmp n…ôlel…ôs danapa nd…õ s…ôncaŇč…ôs m…Ē.  
\v 10 Nt…õ t…Ē n…ôndet…Ēmp…ôr…ôrn…õ danapa dem nd…õ incaŇč…ôs m…ôna k…Ē yuruya yam k…Ē m…ôndecep…ôr-…õ. Nw…õ o nw…õ …ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ w…ôrkun yuruya yam dac…Ē m…Ē, pak…ônc k…Ē.  
\v 11 K…ôk…ônc konu k…ôndement…ôr k…ôc…ôm…õ konu danapa dem dar…ôŇč.  
\v 12 K…ôy…õf…õ d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp awut anu arkun f…ôp pack…ônc Ňča tataka ta cam…ôt-maas, p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôkom w…ôka k…ôl…Ē kam, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ fum nw…õ as…Ēt…Ēn…õ p…ôsam nn…Ē w…ôcik…ôra eyi m…Ē, ta …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôka yuruya yam m…Ē.  
\v 13 P…ômar pade pack…ônc nw…õ andekom nde k…ôl…Ē kam k…Ē nw…õ andes…Ēt…Ēn…õ p…ôsam m…Ē, ti tendey…Ēn…õ k…ôfat ka danapa dem da doru o doru nde dis donu.  
\v 14 W…ôrkun nw…õ o nw…õ ant…Ēk…ônc m…Ē, aŇčwur…õ w…ôkayi afum …Ēn dac…Ē, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē danapa dem delip nn…Ē nk…Ēn eyi m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 15 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku s…Ē Abraham: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta w…ôran kam Saray m…Ē, ta m…ôwe k…Ē s…Ē Saray, k…ôy…õf…õ m…Ēk…Ē Sara s'ande pacwe k…Ē.  
\v 16 K…ôpoc…õ k…Ē k'inder, ipoc…õ s…Ē m…ôna wan nw…õ endekom'am m…Ē. Indepoc…õ k…Ē p…ôt…Ēt, nk…Ēn endey…Ēn…õ k…õr…õ ka t…Ēf y…õlar…ôm. Ab…õ a t…Ēf y…õlar…ôm Ňčandewur k…Ē d…ôris.¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē Abraham …õnc…ôp k…ôro d…ônt…Ēf k…ôsel, k'olokun…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc: ¬ęW…ôrkun w…ôka meren 100 …õntam k…ôkom ba? K…Ē Sara …Ēs…Ēt…Ē meren 90 endekom ba?¬Ľ  
\v 18 K…Ē Abraham oloku Kanu: ¬ęM…ôgb…ôtn…õ S…ômayila doru!¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku: ¬ęAla! W…ôran kam Sara endekom'am wan nw…õ m…ôndewe Siyaka \f + \fr 17:19 \fq Siyaka,\ft  it…Ē c…ôHeb…ôre = k…ôsel. \f* m…Ē. Indec…ôm…õ danapa dosu dar…ôŇč k…Ē nk…Ēn, iy…õf…õ s…Ē ic…ôm…õ di dar…ôŇč k…Ē yuruya y…Ēn k…Ē nk…Ēn encep…ôr-…õ danapa da doru o doru d…Ē.  
\v 20 Nt…õ tendeŇč…ôrn…õ ti m…Ē, ine w…ôran kam p…ôctolan…õ S…ômayila: Indepoc…õ k…Ē p…ôt…Ēt, indes…ĒŇč k…Ē dokomb…ôra d…Ēp…ĒŇč indes…ĒŇč…õ yuruya y…Ēn y…õla endey…Ēn…õ kas ka ab…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē w…ôtem ka afum alar…ôm.  
\v 21 Mba nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta danapa dem m…Ē, Sara oŇčkom'am t…õm tant…õ dok.¬Ľ  
\v 22 Nt…õ Kanu k…ôlip k…ôlok-lok…ôr Abraham m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ômp…õ darenc.  
\v 23 K'Abraham …õl…õk wan k…Ēn S…ômayila k…Ē afum aŇč…õ anakom k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ m…Ē f…ôp, k…ôb…ôp ka aŇč…õ …õnaway…õ p…ôsam p…Ēn m…Ē, ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē arkun a k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ f…ôp. K'…õŇčk…ônc Ňča d…Ēs…Ēk din dad…Ēk…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônaloku k…Ē ti m…Ē.  
\v 24 Abraham …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 99 a k'andek…ônc k…Ē.  
\v 25 Wan k…Ēn S…ômayila, …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco k…Ē maas a k'andek…ônc k…Ē.  
\v 26 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d'aŇčk…ônc Abraham k…Ē wan k…Ēn, S…ômayila.  
\v 27 K'aŇčk…ônc arkun aka k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ f…ôp, k…ôy…õf…õ acar aŇč…õ anakom di m…Ē haŇč ak…Ē …õnaway…õ p…ôsam p…Ēn nn…Ē acik…ôra Ňčayi m…Ē. K'aŇčk…ônc Ňča f…ôp k…Ē nk…Ēn Abraham. 
\c 18  
\s1 Kanu k…ônd…ôŇčk a Sara endes…Ēt…Ē wan w…ôrkun 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI owur…ôr Abraham nde tofo nt…õ Ňčkiri ya Mamre y…õnac…ôm…õ m…Ē, t…õt…ôŇčn…õ Abraham p…ônd…õ nde kusuŇčka ka abal Ňč…Ēn daŇč, t…õm nt…õ p…ôŇčwon…õ m…Ē.  
\v 2 K…Ē Abraham eyekti f…Ēr, k'…õn…ôŇčk arkun maas Ňčac…ôm…õ ta Ňčamb…Ēl…õ k…Ē-…õ. Nt…õ …õn…ôŇčk Ňča m…Ē, k'ewirn…õ k…ôk…Ēb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Ňča, k'ontontn…õn…õ Ňča haŇč d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 3 K…Ē Abraham oloku w…ôkin Ňča dac…Ē: ¬ęMariki, il…õts…õn'am intam k…ôs…Ēt…ôr …ôm k…ôwos…õn'em k…ôc…ôm…õ ka nn…Ēna wacar kam ba?  
\v 4 Pak…õr…õ nu oŇč domun depic n…ôbik…õn…õ w…õc…ôk, n…ôŇčes…ôm nn…Ē k…ôt…Ēk nk…õ d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 5 Indes…ĒŇč nu s…Ē peri, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôs…Ēt…Ē s…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr m…Ē, a n…ôdek…Ē t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē n…ôf…Ēdecep…ôr nn…Ē nderem kif…ôli, iyi kiyi konu.¬Ľ K'acik…ôra Ňčaloku: ¬ęTentes…õ! M…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ôloku m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē Abraham …ĒŇčk…Ē kat…ôna kat…ôna abal Ňč…Ēn disr…õ nde Sara eyi m…Ē, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôkuf…õ m…ôl…õk k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt tafala k…ômaas m…ôgb…õnt…õ akaŇč…õ c…ôcom.¬Ľ  
\v 7 K'…õy…õks…õ s…Ē k…ôk…Ē ka nde y…Ēc…Ēl yeyi m…Ē, k'osump…ôr tana p…Ēt…Ēt dis nde y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēn dac…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč pi w…ôcar k…Ēn w…ôt…õmp w…ôkin k…Ē w…ôkak…Ē olomp…ôs pi kat…ôna kat…ôna. 
\p  
\v 8 K…Ē Abraham …õl…õk fulaya k…Ē m…õs…õ ma wana k…Ē s…õm ya tana tat…Ēk…Ē analomp…ôs m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôc…ômb…ôr…ôr yi acik…ôra …Ēn. K…Ē nk…Ēn Abraham …õnc…ôm…õ Ňča k…ôs…ôk k…ôt…Ēk d…ônt…Ēf, k'acik…ôra Ňčacdi yeri.  
\v 9 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôdi yeri m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčayif Abraham: ¬ęDeke w…ôran kam Sara eyi-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Abraham oloku Ňča, ¬ęEyi nde abal disr…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē w…ôcik…ôra w…ôkin oloku: ¬ęInder nn…Ē ndaram dok t…õm tant…õ w…ôran kam Sara endekom wan w…ôrkun.¬Ľ Sara …õnac…ôm…õ d…ôkusuŇčka Abraham tadar…ôŇč p…ôcc…ôŇčk…ôl. 
\p  
\v 11 Abraham k…Ē Sara Ňčanasik…ôr, Ňčab…õk, Sara …õnawur…õn…õ f…õ s…Ē w…ôtam k…ôs…Ēt…Ē awut.  
\v 12 K…Ē Sara esel…ôrn…õ p…ôcloku: ¬ęNd…õk…ôl nt…õ isik…ôr oŇč m…Ē, p…ôbotu pendey'im s…Ē ba? Mariki wos im s…Ē, esik…ôr.¬Ľ  
\v 13 K…Ē MARIKI eyif Abraham ¬ęTa ake t…Ē Sara esel…õ-…õ a p…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻMba kance k…Ē, indetam k…ôs…Ēt…Ē wan nn…Ē isik…ôr m…Ē ba?‚Äļ  
\v 14 Tes teyi nt…õ t…õntamb…ôr MARIKI m…Ē ba? Dok t…õm tant…õ imbonc…ôr …ôm m…Ē, inder nn…Ē ndaram, Sara endes…Ēt…Ē wan w…ôrkun.¬Ľ  
\v 15 K…Ē Sara eyem…õ, k'ombup…ôr…õ ¬ęIsel f…õ,¬Ľ bawo …õnanes…õ. K…Ē MARIKI …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ: ¬ęAla, m…ôsel!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 16 K'afum aŇč…õ Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē, k…Ē Ňčam…Ēm…ôn k…ôca ka Sodom. K…Ē Abraham …õnc…ômb…ôr Ňča k…ôk…Ēlemb…ôrn…õ Ňča.  
\v 17 K…Ē MARIKI eyifn…õ: ¬ęIm…õŇčk…ôr Abraham nt…õ ifaŇč k…ôy…Ē m…Ē ba?  
\v 18 Abraham endey…Ēn…õ kas ka afum a at…Ēf Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč, Ňča f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr. Afum a doru f…ôp tet…Ēn t…Ē Ňčandes…Ēt…Ēn…õ k…ôpoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt.  
\v 19 Bawo inasom k…Ē p…ôloku awut …Ēn k…Ē afum …Ēn, a Ňčac…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē da ina MARIKI dar…ôŇč, Ňčac…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč k…Ē sariy…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ina Kanu ilas…õ Abraham dim nd…õ …õnas…ĒŇč tet…Ēn m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 20 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Abraham: ¬ęMes mm…õ ambonc…õ Sodom k…Ē Komora m…Ē, m…õmb…õk k…Ē kiciya ka mi k…ôy…Ē w…õyw…õy.  
\v 21 K…ôtor k'inder d…ônt…Ēf idem…Ēm…ôn k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a nt…õ aŇčloku taŇčan m…Ē kance k…Ē-…õ, k…Ē p…ônt…Ēy…Ēn…õ ti-…õ, ina s…Ē ic…ôr…õ ti.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 22 K…Ē acik…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčay…õf…õ tofo tat…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Ňčant…õf…ôrn…õ k…ôca ka Sodom. MARIKI p…ôs…Ēr…Ēyi k…Ē Abraham.  
\v 23 K…Ē Abraham …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k'eyif Kanu: ¬ęM…ôndek…Ēt…Ērs…õn…õ s…Ē fum w…ôlompu p…ôm…Ē w…ôl…õc ba?  
\v 24 T…Ēl…Ēma afum at…Ēt w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) Ňčayi afum aka dare dad…Ēk…Ē dac…Ē, m…ôndek…Ēl…ôs…ôr s…Ē dare dad…Ēk…Ē ba? M…ôf…Ētam k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ Ňča teta afum alompu akaŇč…õ w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) aŇč…õ Ňčayi Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 25 ¬ęT…Ēb…Ēl'am m…ôna k…ôy…Ē ka tant…õ! M…ôf…Ēdedif…õn…õ fum w…ôlompu k…Ē w…ôt…Ēlomp, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē w…ôt…Ēd…ôk…ôt p…ôs…Ēt…Ē p…ôcuy pin payi k…Ē w…ôd…ôk…ôt. T…Ēb…Ēl'am m…ôna nw…õ m…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôboc kiti ka doru f…ôp m…Ē, m…ôf…Ēdeyi ta m…ôlel…ôs sariy…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 26 K…Ē MARIKI oloku: ¬ęK'imb…ôp nde dare da Sodom disr…õ afum alompu w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt-…õ (50), iŇčaŇčn…õn…õ alp…ôs ak…Ē tetaŇčan.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 27 K…Ē Abraham …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ k'oloku: ¬ęN…ôm…Ēm…ôn nt…õ iyeŇčk ab…ôk…ôc k…ôlok-lok…ôr Mariki Kanu m…Ē, ina nw…õ iy…Ēn…õ k…ôbof ka d…ônt…Ēf k…Ē ka d…ôn…õnc d…ôm m…Ē.  
\v 28 T…Ēl…Ēma afum alompu akaŇč…õ w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) Ňčandek…Ēbut afum k…ôcam…ôt pal…ôs…ôr oŇč dare f…ôp ba?¬Ľ K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku: ¬ęIf…Ēl…ôs…ôr di k'imb…ôp di afum alompu w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt-…õ (45).¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 29 K…Ē Abraham …õnc…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč k…ôloku k…Ē toloku nt…õ: ¬ęT…Ēl…Ēma alompu w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) Ňč'andek…Ēb…ôp di?¬Ľ K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku: ¬ęIf…Ēl…ôs…ôr, k'imb…ôp di alompu w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ-…õ (40).¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 30 K…Ē Abraham oloku: ¬ęIl…Ēkt…ôrn'am, Mariki Kanu! Ta p…ôt…õl'am k'ilok-loku s…Ē-…õ! T…Ēl…Ēma alompu w…ôco maas (30) Ňč'andek…Ēb…ôp di?¬Ľ K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku Abraham: ¬ęIf…Ēl…ôs…ôr di k'imb…ôp d…Ēt…Ēf afum alompu w…ôco maas-…õ (30).¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 31 K…Ē Abraham oloku: ¬ęMariki Kanu, m…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ m…Ēc…Ēp mem. T…Ēl…Ēma alompu w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) Ňč'andek…Ēb…ôp di?¬Ľ K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku Abraham: ¬ęIf…Ēl…ôs…ôr di teta afum akak…Ē w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20).¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 32 K…Ē Abraham oloku: ¬ęIl…õts…õn'am, Mariki mem! Ta p…ôt…õl'am, t…õlp…ôs t'indelok-lok…ôr …ôm. T…Ēl…Ēma alompu w…ôco Ňčayi di.¬Ľ K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku s…Ē Abraham, ¬ęIf…Ēl…ôs…ôr di teta afum akak…Ē w…ôco.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 33 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôlok-loku m…Ē, k…Ē MARIKI …ĒŇčk…Ē, k…Ē Abraham olukus nde nd…Ēr…Ēn. 
\c 19  
\s1 L…Ēt k…ôyacn…õ k…Ēn k…ôl…ôs…ôr ka Sodom 
\p  
\v 1 Dec d…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ m…õr…ôŇč mender Sodom. L…Ēt p…ônd…õ d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da dare. Nt…õ …õn…ôŇčk mi m…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôk…Ēb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē mi, k'ontontn…õn…õ mi d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 2 K…Ē L…Ēt oloku Ňča: ¬ęIl…õts…õn…õ nu, n…ôna mariki mem, n…ôder nn…Ē k…ôl…Ē ka w…ôcar konu. N…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ d…õ pibi, n…ôbik…õn…õ w…õc…ôk, n…ôdena n…ôy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôtana suy, n…ôsump…ôr s…Ē d…Ēp…Ē donu, n…ôk…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ moloku k…Ē: ¬ęAla, nn…Ē tofo tant…õ t…Ē s…ôndecep…ôr…õn…õ pibi!¬Ľ  
\v 3 Mba k…Ē L…Ēt …õnc…ôm…õn…õ Ňča ti dar…ôŇč haŇč k…Ē Ňčade Ňčal…ôps…ôr k…ôk…Ē nde nd…Ēr…Ēn. K'olomps…õ Ňča yeri y…Ēt…Ēt, k'…õmp…õc…õ Ňča c…ôcom, k…Ē Ňčandi yeri. 
\p  
\v 4 Ta Ňčantaf…ônt…ôr…õ-…õ, k'afum a dare da Sodom ŇčaŇčk…õl k…ôl…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ awut haŇč abeki f…ôp faŇčan Ňčanayi di, ali fum anasak f…õ.  
\v 5 K…Ē Ňčawe L…Ēt k…Ē Ňčayif k…Ē: ¬ęDeke afum ak…Ē Ňčayi-…õ, aŇč…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ nn…Ē ndaram nn…Ē pibi pamp…õ m…Ē? M…ôwur…õn…õ Ňča nn…Ē s…ôyi m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôf…ônt…ôr…ôr Ňča m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē L…Ēt owur d…ôkusuŇčka nn…Ē Ňčayi m…Ē, k'…õŇčgb…ôt kumba tadar…ôŇč t…Ēn.  
\v 7 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęAla, Anapa, Il…õts…õn…õ nu ta n…ôy…Ē p…ôl…õc pamp…õ!  
\v 8 Il…õts…õn…õ nu! Iy…Ē ayec…ôra m…õr…ôŇč at…Ēc…ôr…õ arkun, il…õts…õn…õ nu ik…õr…õ nu Ňča nn…Ē dabaŇčka, n…ôy…Ē Ňča m…õfaŇč monu. Mba ta n…ôy…Ē acik…ôra em nt…õ o nt…õ, bawo k…ôyi kem k…Ē Ňčayin…õ d…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 9 K'afum a Sodom Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôb…Ēl…õ day! M…ôna w…ôcik…ôra m…ôfaŇč k…ôboc…ôr s…ôna d…Ēp…Ē nd…õ s…ôndek…Ēt m…Ē, k…Ē m…ônt…Ēwur…õn…õ Ňča-…õ, t…Ēk…Ē s…ôndedeŇč…ôr m…ôna m…Ē tendecep…ôr taŇčan!¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčaw…õn L…Ēt p…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ kumba k…ôk…Ēl…ôs…ôr ki.  
\v 10 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ m…õr…ôŇč mosump…ôr L…Ēt, k…Ē m…õmb…õrs…õ k…Ē, k…Ē m…õŇčgb…ôt kumba.  
\v 11 Afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi d…ôkusuŇčka m…Ē, k…Ē m…õl…õke m…Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča k…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk, k…ôy…õf…õ wanf…õt haŇč w…ôbeki, k…Ē t…õyams…õ Ňča k…ôn…ôŇčk s…Ē kumba. 
\p  
\v 12 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ Ňčayif L…Ēt: ¬ęAn'…Ē m…ôy…Ē s…Ē nn…Ē fum-…õ? Arkun aŇč…õ m…ôs…ĒŇč aran m…Ē, awut am arkun k…Ē aran, k…Ē afum am f…ôp, ak…Ē m…ôy…Ē dare dand…õ m…Ē f…ôp, m…ôwur…õn…õ Ňča nn…Ē dare dand…õ.  
\v 13 K…ôl…ôs…ôr k…Ē s…ônder tofo tant…õ, bawo MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, nt…õ aŇčlok…õ afum a dare dand…õ m…Ē, t…õmb…õk. MARIKI osom su k…ôdel…ôs…ôr dare dand…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 14 K…Ē L…Ēt …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…ôp arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanan…õnc…õ awut …Ēn m…Ē, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôkuf…õ n…ôy…õf…õ d…õ! Bawo MARIKI endeder k…ôl…ôs…ôr dare dand…õ.¬Ľ Mba, k…Ē arkun akaŇč…õ Ňčanc…õm-c…õmn…õ a k…ôwol…ôs k…Ē L…Ēt …õnd…õ. 
\p  
\v 15 P…ôndeyi d…Ēs…Ēka d…õl…ôp…ôs k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ Ňčaloku L…Ēt: ¬ęM…ôrokn…õ m…ôy…õf…õ d…õ, m…ôl…õk w…ôran kam, k…Ē awut am ayec…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčayi nn…Ē m…Ē, ta p…ôl…õc pedes…Ēt…Ē Ňča k…Ē dare dand…õ denciya m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 16 Mba L…Ēt p…ôcwon, k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ Ňčasump…ôr Ňča waca, nk…Ēn k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn k…Ē awut …Ēn ayec…ôra m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ Ňčawur…õn…õ Ňča dare disr…õ, bawo MARIKI …õnafaŇč k…ôyac k…Ē. 
\p  
\v 17 Nt…õ m…õl…õk…õ Ňčawur…õn…õ Ňča dare disr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ min moloku L…Ēt: ¬ęM…ôy…õks…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta m…ôfi m…Ē! Ta m…ôm…Ēm…ôn tadar…ôŇč, ta m…ôc…ômb…ôr…ôs tofo o tofo nn…Ē aranta ŇčaŇč…õ! M…ôk…Ē m…ônd…õ m…ôyacn…õ nde d…ôt…Ēr…Ē, ta m…ôdefi.¬Ľ  
\v 18 K…Ē L…Ēt oloku Ňča: ¬ęAla, mariki mem! T…Ēf…Ētam k…ôyi.  
\v 19 Il…õts…õn'am! W…ôcar kam …Ēs…Ēt…ôr …ôm k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ nt…õ m…ôlas layidi dam nn…Ē iyi m…Ē, nt…õ m…ôsak im k…ôyi doru m…Ē, mba if…Ētam k…ôy…õks…õ ib…ôp t…Ēr…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē a m…ôctor…õ p…ôl…õc, k…Ē p…ôyi f…õ ti-…õ ina s…Ē, iŇčfi.  
\v 20 Il…õts…õn'am m…ôŇčn…ôŇčk dare d…Ēk…Ē, d…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn'em k'iy…õks…õ ib…õr…õ di k…Ē d…õf…õt…õ s…Ē. M…ôc'em ik…Ē ind…õ iyacn…õ di, d…õf…õt…õ f…õ ba? Intam di k…ôb…õr…õ, t…Ēs…ĒŇč'em k…ôyi doru!¬Ľ  
\v 21 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ moloku k…Ē: ¬ęAwa, k…ôtola kam kaŇčk…õ disr…õ, if…Ēl…ôs…ôr dare dad…Ēk…Ē m…ôŇčle m…Ē.  
\v 22 Awa, m…ôrokn…õ m…ôk…Ē, bawo if…Ētam k…ôy…Ē t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm ta m…ôntab…õr…õ di-…õ.¬Ľ Ti t'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ awen…õ dare dad…Ēk…Ē Cohar \f + \fr 19:22 \fq Cohar\ft  = ¬ęp…ôf…õt¬Ľ \f* m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 23 Dec d…õncp…õ, a k…Ē L…Ēt …õmb…õr…õ Cohar.  
\v 24 K…Ē MARIKI …Ēntuf…ôr aka Sodom k…Ē Komora k…ôy…õf…õ darenc, p…ôrb…ôl…Ē k…Ē n…õnc, ny…õ MARIKI …õncsak m…Ē.  
\v 25 K…Ē Kanu k…ôl…ôs…ôr s…ôdare f…ôp, k…Ē aranta, k…Ē afum k…ôb…ôp ka yopoŇč d…ônt…Ēf f…ôp.  
\v 26 K…Ē w…ôran ka L…Ēt …Ēm…Ēm…ôn tadar…ôŇč, k'…õnt…ôŇčkl…õ k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ t…õr…ôŇčka ta m…õr. 
\p  
\v 27 K…Ē Abraham …õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē nde tofo t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanac…ôm…õ k…Ē MARIKI m…Ē.  
\v 28 K…Ē Abraham …Ēm…Ēm…ôn k…ôca ka Sodom k…Ē Komora, k'…Ēm…Ēm…ôn s…ôdare sa aranta f…ôp, k'…õn…ôŇčk kinim…õ k…ôcp…õ p…ôm…Ē nt…õ kinim…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ônde k…ôcp…õ daranta m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 29 Nt…õ Kanu k…ôncl…ôs…ôr s…ôdare sa aranta ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ Abraham, k…Ē k…ôyac L…Ēt p…ôl…õc nt…õ k…ôncl…ôs…ôr s…ôdare ns…õ L…Ēt …õnand…õ p…ôyacn…õ m…Ē. 
\s1 L…Ēt k…Ē awut …Ēn aran 
\p  
\v 30 K…Ē L…Ēt …õy…õf…õ Cohar k'awut …Ēn aran m…õr…ôŇč k…ôp…õ k…ôk…Ēnd…õ d…ôt…Ēr…Ē, bawo …õnanes…õ k…ônd…õ ka Cohar. K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôyi kumbuŇčkum \f + \fr 19:30 \ft  Abi nde t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčatam k…ôgb…Ēpn…õ m…Ē. \f* ka t…Ēr…Ē t…Ēl…Ēma disr…õ.  
\v 31 K…Ē wan w…ôran w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôka L…Ēt oloku w…ôlp…ôs: ¬ęPapa kosu …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôtem, fum eyi f…õ d…Ēt…Ēf nw…õ endeder su m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ mes mosu mokur moloku ti m…Ē.  
\v 32 M…ôder s…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ômun member nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôf…ônt…ôr…ôr su, t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôs…Ēt…Ēn…õ k…Ē yuruya m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 33 K…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč…õ kas k…ôŇčan k…ômun member pibi pap…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē wan k…Ēn w…ôran w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē kas. Mba L…Ēt …õnac…ôr…õn…õ f…õ k…ôb…õr…õ k…Ē k…ôwur ka wan k…Ēn.  
\v 34 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k'oloku w…ôf…õt…ôra k…Ēn: ¬ęIf…ônt…ôr…õna nn…Ē pibi k…Ē papa. Pas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē s…Ē k…ômun member nn…Ē pibi, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ m…ôna s…Ē n…ôk…Ē n…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn m…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ pas…Ēt…Ēn…õ k…Ē yuruya m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 35 P…ôndes…Ēbiy…õ k…Ē awut …Ēn aran Ňčas…ĒŇč k…Ē s…Ē member. Pibi pap…Ēk…Ē k…Ē wan k…Ēn w…ôran w…ôf…õt w…ôk…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…õr…ôr papa k…ôŇčan L…Ēt, k…Ē Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…õ. Kas k…ôŇčan …õnac…ôr…õn…õ f…õ k…ôb…õr…õ k…Ē k…ôwur ka w…ôkak…Ē s…Ē. 
\p  
\v 36 K…Ē awut aran a L…Ēt aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč f…ôp Ňčamb…õks…õ L…Ēt kas k…ôŇčan.  
\v 37 K…Ē wan w…ôran w…ôka L…Ēt w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē oŇčkom wan w…ôrkun, k'ewe k…Ē Mohab.\f + \fr 19:37 \fq Mohab\ft  = ¬ęw…ôka papa¬Ľ \f* Nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ papa ka aMohab, Ňčayi doru haŇč m…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 38 K…Ē wan ka L…Ēt w…ôran w…ôf…õt oŇčkom wan w…ôrkun, k'ewe k…Ē ¬ęBen Ami.¬Ľ\f + \fr 19:38 \fq Ben Ami\ft  = ¬ęwan ka afum em¬Ľ \f* Nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ papa ka aka Am…ĒŇč Ňčayi doru haŇč m…Ēk…Ē. 
\c 20  
\s1 Abraham k…Ē Abim…õl…õk 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Abraham …õy…õf…õ di k…ôk…Ē ka at…Ēf Ňča N…õk…õf. K'…õnd…õ Kad…õs k…Ē Sur dac…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ s…Ē k'encep…ôr…õn…õ t…õm Kerar.  
\v 2 Abraham oncloku afum aka di teta w…ôran k…Ēn Sara: ¬ęW…ôkir…õ kem …Ēf…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Abim…õl…õk, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Kerar, …õmbaŇč Sara.  
\v 3 Awa, k…Ē Kanu k…ônder Abim…õl…õk d…ômere ma pibi k…Ē k…ôloku k…Ē: ¬ęK…ôfi k…Ē m…ônder teta w…ôran w…ôk…Ē m…ôsump…ôr m…Ē, bawo w…ôran w…ôl…Ē …Ēf…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 4 Abim…õl…õk nw…õ …õnat…ĒgbuŇč…õn…õ w…ôran nw…õ m…Ē, k'eyif: ¬ęMariki mem, c…ôke c…Ē p…ôyi-…õ, k…ôdif k…Ē m…ônder at…Ēf Ňčin ali Ňčay…Ēn…õ afum alompu?  
\v 5 Nk…Ēn Abraham yati olok'im: ‚ÄĻW…ôkir…õ kem …Ēf…Ē,‚Äļ k…Ē w…ôran yati nk…Ēn s…Ē oloku: ‚ÄĻW…õnc im w…ôrkun …Ēf…Ē?‚Äļ Ab…ôk…ôc Ňčosoku Ňč'inay…Ē, ali p…ôl…õc iy…Ē f…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku k…Ē d…ômere: ¬ęInc…ôr…õ belbel ina s…Ē, a ab…ôk…ôc Ňčosoku Ňč…Ē m…ônay…Ē nt…õ m…ôcy…Ē tant…õ m…Ē. Ina yati in'…õyam…ôs am k…ôd…ôkt…ôr im, ti t'inat…Ēwos'am a m…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ k…Ē.  
\v 7 Nd…õk…ôl, m…ôluks…õ w…ôran w…ôkaw…õ wos. Bawo sayib…õ sa Kanu s'…Ēy…Ēn…õ, endetolan'am m…ôyi doru. K…Ē m…ônt…Ēluks…õ k…Ē-…õ, m…ôc…ôr…õ a k…ôfi k…Ē m…ônder k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē m…ôy…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 8 K…Ē Abim…õl…õk …õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy, k'ewe acar …Ēn f…ôp. K'…Ēl…Ēm…ôr Ňča mere mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp. K…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôsump…ôr afum akak…Ē.  
\v 9 K…Ē Abim…õl…õk ewe Abraham k'eyif k…Ē: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē m…ôy…Ē su tant…õ-…õ? K…Ē kiciya k…ôre k'inciy'am-…õ, nt…õ m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ su, ina k'at…Ēf Ňčem k…ôciya p…ôp…ĒŇč m…Ē? M…ôy'em m…Ēy…Ē mm…õ p…ônt…Ēmar m…ôy'em m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē Abim…õl…õk eyif Abraham: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē m…ônafaŇč nt…õ m…ôy…Ē tant…õ m…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 11 K…Ē Abraham oloku: ¬ęInac…õm-c…õmn…õ a k…ônes…õ Kanu k…ôyi f…õ nn…Ē, a andedif im teta w…ôran kem.  
\v 12 Nt…õ tendeŇč…ôrn…õ ti m…Ē, kance k…Ē, a w…ôkir…õ kem …Ēf…Ē. Kas kin k…Ē s…ômpaŇčn…õ, s…ôyer…õn…õ c…õr…õ. K'ender s…Ē k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôran kem.  
\v 13 Nt…õ Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč'em k…ôy…õf…õ k…ôl…Ē ka papa w…ôkem m…Ē, ti t'inaloku Sara: ‚ÄĻM…ôl…õk'em layidi k…ôca nk…õ o nk…õ s…ôŇčk…Ē m…Ē, m…ôdek…Ē m…ôcloku a w…õnc …ôm w…ôrkun iy…Ēn…õ.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 14 K…Ē Abim…õl…õk …õl…õk cir, Ňčkesiya, c…ôna k…Ē acar arkun k…Ē aran k'…Ēs…ĒŇč Abraham k'oluks…õ k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn Sara.  
\v 15 K…Ē Abim…õl…õk oloku: ¬ęAt…Ēf Ňčem Ňč…Ē ŇčaŇč…õ nn…Ē f…Ēr yam kiriŇč, m…ônd…õ nn…Ē p…ôndeb…Ēt …ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 16 K'oloku Sara: ¬ęIs…ĒŇč w…õnc …ôm w…ôrkun m…õnc…ômb…ôl ma gbeti wul win, b…Ēy…Ēn'am aca nn…Ē afum Ňčayi m…Ē, k…ôment…ôr a m…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm tes tant…õ disr…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē Abraham ontola Kanu, k…Ē Kanu k…ôntam…ôs Abim…õl…õk, w…ôran k…Ēn k…Ē acar …Ēn, k…Ē Ňčantam k…ôkom,  
\v 18 bawo MARIKI …õnasump…ôr aka k…ôl…Ē ka Abim…õl…õk f…ôp dokomb…ôra teta w…ôran ka Abraham, Sara. 
\c 21  
\s1 K…ôkom ka Siyaka 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI …õmbaŇč Sara p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnaloku ti m…Ē, k…Ē MARIKI …õlas…õ k…Ē dim d…Ēk…Ē …õnas…ĒŇč k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 2 K…Ē Sara …õmb…õk…ôs, k'oŇčkom…õ Abraham wan w…ôrkun detem d…Ēn disr…õ, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônabonc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 3 K…Ē Abraham ewe wan w…ôrkun nw…õ Sara oŇčkom…õ k…Ē m…Ē ¬ęSiyaka.¬Ľ  
\v 4 K…Ē Abraham …õŇčk…ônc Siyaka wan k…Ēn w…ôrkun nw…õ tataka ta cam…ôt-maas t…Ēn, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônasom k…Ē ti m…Ē.  
\v 5 Abraham …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren tasar tin (100), nt…õ anckom wan k…Ēn Siyaka m…Ē.  
\v 6 K…Ē Sara oloku: ¬ęKanu k…ôs…ĒŇč'em k…ôsels…ôr. Nw…õ o nw…õ ene k…ôkom kem Siyaka m…Ē, t…ĒŇčy…Ē k…Ē mesel.¬Ľ  
\v 7 K'endeŇč…ôr: ¬ęAn'…õnatam k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Abraham k…ôlaŇč a Sara endem…õs…ôr awut-…õ? Mba iŇčkom…õ k…Ē wan w…ôrkun detem d…Ēn disr…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 Abraham k…ôb…õl…ôs k…Ēn Hakar k…Ē S…ômayila 
\p  
\v 8 K…Ē wan …õmb…õk k'awur…õ k…Ē m…õs…õ. K…Ē Abraham omboc k…ôsata k…ôp…ĒŇč d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ awur…õ Siyaka m…õs…õ m…Ē.  
\v 9 K…Ē Sara …õn…ôŇčk wan w…ôrkun, nw…õ w…ôran w…ôMisira Hakar …õnakom…õ Abraham m…Ē, p…ôcsel.  
\v 10 K…Ē Sara oloku Abraham: ¬ęM…ôb…õl…ôs wan w…ôran w…ôcar nw…õ k…Ē wan k…Ēn w…ôrkun. Bawo wan ka w…ôcar w…ôkaw…õ Ňčaf…ĒdepaŇčn…õ k…õ k…Ē wan kem.¬Ľ  
\v 11 K…Ē toloku tat…Ēk…Ē t…õnt…õl…õ Abraham belbel teta wan k…Ēn.  
\v 12 Mba k…Ē Kanu k…ôloku Abraham: ¬ęTa t…õt…õl'am teta wan kam w…ôrkun k…Ē k…õr…õ, w…ôcar kam. M…ôwos…õn…õ Sara nt…õ o nt…õ …õŇčfaŇč…ôr …ôm m…Ē. Bawo nn…Ē Siyaka eyi m…Ē, m…ôndes…Ēt…Ē yuruya ny…õ yendet…Ēmp…ôr tewe tam m…Ē.  
\v 13 Indey…Ēn…õ s…Ē wan ka w…ôcar kam at…Ēf. Bawo nk…Ēn s…Ē yuruya yam y'…Ēy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 14 K…Ē Abraham …õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy, k'…õl…õk k…ôcom, k'…õlas apamp…õ domun k'…Ēs…ĒŇč Hakar, k'…õnd…ônd…ôs…ôr k…Ē wan, k'…õmb…õl…ôs Ňča. K…Ē Hakar …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôyi T…õgb…ôr…õ ta Bersaba.  
\v 15 Nt…õ apamp…õ Ňčelip domun m…Ē, k…Ē Hakar …õsak wan t…Ēt…Ēk d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 16 K'…õŇčkaf…ôl…ôr k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ k…ôs…ôk p…ôcc…Ēp…ôsn…õ: ¬ęIfaŇč f…õ k…ôgb…ôtn…õ wan kem p…ôcfi.¬Ľ K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ p…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ k…Ē dobolu da k…ôl…ôm ka amb…ônc…ôran katin p…ôt…õf…ôrn…õ k…Ē, p…ôcbok.  
\v 17 K…Ē Kanu k…ône wan dim, k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma Kanu mewe Hakar darenc k…Ē meyif k…Ē: ¬ęAke'nt…Ērs'…ôm-…õ Hakar? Ta m…ônes…õ! Bawo Kanu k…ône wan kam dim nde eyi m…Ē.  
\v 18 M…ôy…õf…õ m…ôl…õk wan, m…ôsump…ôr k…Ē waca m…õr…ôŇč, bawo afum alar…ôm Ňč'indes…ĒŇč k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē Kanu k…ômepi Hakar f…Ēr k'…õn…ôŇčk k…ôl…ômp. K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôlas apamp…õ domun, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč wan k'omun.  
\v 20 K…Ē Kanu k…ômbum wan nw…õ …õncb…õk, p…ôyi d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē, k'ende p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôp…õn…õ mb…ônc…ôran.  
\v 21 K…Ē S…ômayila …õmb…õk d…ôndo t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Paran, k…Ē k…õr…õ …õnt…õn…õ k…Ē w…ôran w…ôMisira. 
\s1 Abraham k…ôsek k…Ēn danapa k…Ē Abim…õl…õk 
\p  
\v 22 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, Abim…õl…õk Ňčasol k…Ē Pik…Ēl, w…ôb…õ w…ôka as…Ēdar …Ēn, k'ende p…ôloku Abraham: ¬ęKanu k…ôsol am mes mm…õ m…ôŇčy…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 23 M…ôd…õr…ôm'em oŇč ma nn…Ē, m…ôckorn…õ Kanu a m…ôf…ĒdetiŇčk…ôr im, awut em, k…Ē awut-s…Ē em, m…ôd…õr…ôm em s…Ē a m…ôndet…Ēmp…ôr em k…Ē at…Ēf nŇč…õ m…ôyi m…Ē ab…ôk…ôc Ňčosoku, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē iy…Ēn'am m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 24 K…Ē Abraham oloku: ¬ęInd…õr…ôm am ti.¬Ľ  
\v 25 Mba k…Ē Abraham …õnal Abim…õl…õk teta k…ôl…ômp nk…õ acar a Abim…õl…õk ŇčanabaŇč…õ f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr m…Ē.  
\v 26 K…Ē Abim…õl…õk oloku: ¬ęInc…ôr…õ f…õ nw…õ …õnay…Ē t…Ēy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē: M…ônas…ĒŇč…õ f'em ti k…ôc…ôr…õ, m…Ēk…Ē m…ôndes…ĒŇč'em oŇč ti k…ôc…ôr…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 27 K…Ē Abraham …õl…õk Ňčkesiya, cir k…Ē c…ôna, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč yi Abim…õl…õk. K…Ē Ňčaluks…ôrn…õ k…Ē Ňčasek danapa m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan.  
\v 28 K…Ē Abraham …õnc…ômb…ôr k…ôs…ôk cir c…ôyec…ôra cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ca y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēn.  
\v 29 K…Ē Abim…õl…õk eyif Abraham: ¬ęŇäkesiya y…õran cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ya ake y…Ē m…ônc…ômb…ôr k…ôs…ôk-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 30 K'Abraham oloku Abim…õl…õk: ¬ęM…ôwos…õ k…ôbaŇč Ňčkesiya y…õran cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč yay…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ kosu tes a in'…õnakay k…ôl…ômp kaŇčk…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 31 Ti t…Ē awen…õ tofo tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęBersaba¬Ľ, bawo d…ôndo k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē k…Ē Ňčanad…õrm…õn…õ.  
\v 32 K…Ē Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ k…ôsek danapa d…ôndo Bersaba. K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda, Abim…õl…õk k…Ē Pik…Ēl w…ôb…õ ka as…Ēdar …Ēn Ňčay…õf…õ, k…Ē Ňčalukus at…Ēf Ňča aFilisti.  
\v 33 K…Ē Abraham …Ēmb…Ēf abet \f + \fr 21:33 \ft  K…ôt…Ēk nk…õ k…ôwur…õn…õ ¬ętumbunyi¬Ľ m…Ē. \f* Bersaba, k'oŇčkorn…õ MARIKI nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēlip doru o doru m…Ē.  
\v 34 K'Abraham encep…ôr…õn…õ t…õm tobolu at…Ēf Ňča aFilisti. 
\c 22  
\s1 Abraham owos…õ k…ôloŇčn…õn…õ Kanu wan k…Ēn Siyaka 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ mes mm…õ mencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ômboc…ôr Abraham d…Ēp…Ē, k…Ē k…ôwe k…Ē: ¬ęAbraham!¬Ľ K'owos…õn…õ ki: ¬ęIn'…õw…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 2 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku: ¬ęM…ôl…õk oŇč wan kam sona Siyaka, w…ôkak…Ē m…ômb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē. M…ôk…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Moriya d…ôndo, m…ôk…Ē m…ôloŇčn…õn'em wan kam k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôc…Ēf nde t…Ēr…Ē mp…õ indek…Ēment…ôr …ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 3 K…Ē Abraham …õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy k'…õŇčgb…õk s…Ēfale s…Ēn k…ôb…ônda, k'…õl…õk…õn…õ acar …Ēn at…õmp m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē wan k…Ēn Siyaka. K…Ē Abraham …õŇčgb…õs t…Ēk ny…õ …õnak…Ēc…Ēf…õ Kanu poloŇčn…õ m…Ē, k'…õntas nde k…ôfo k…ôŇčk…Ē Kanu k…ônament…ôr k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 4 Tataka ta maas, k…Ē Abraham eyekti k…ôro k'…õn…ôŇčk k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē p…ôb…Ēl…õ.  
\v 5 K'oloku at…õmp …Ēn: ¬ęN…ôyi nn…Ē k…Ē s…Ēfale. Siyaka k'ina, k…ôp…õ k…Ē s…ônder nde k…ôroŇč k…ôk…Ētontn…õn…õ Kanu. K…Ē s…ôlip-…õ, s…ôndeb…ôp nu nn…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē Abraham …õl…õk t…Ēk ny…õ anak…Ēc…Ēf…õ Kanu poloŇčn…õ m…Ē, k'…õsars…ôr yi wan k…Ēn Siyaka, k…Ē nk…Ēn …õl…õk n…õnc k…Ē faka. K…Ē Ňčasol m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan k…ôk…Ē.  
\v 7 K…Ē Siyaka ewe kas Abraham k'eyif k…Ē: ¬ęPapa!¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē owos…õ: ¬ęIn'…õw…õ, wan kem!¬Ľ K…Ē Siyaka oloku: ¬ęN…õnc d…Ē dand…õ k…Ē t…Ēk, mba deke teŇčkesiya t…Ēk…Ē aŇčk…ĒloŇčn…õ Kanu pac…Ēf m…Ē peyi-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē Abraham oloku: ¬ęWan kem, Kanu ki s…ôrka k…ôŇčk…Ēs…Ēt…Ē teŇčkesiya nt…õ aŇčk…Ēc…Ēf…õ k…Ē poloŇčn…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p K…Ē Ňčasol m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan s…Ē k…ôk…Ē.  
\v 9 Nt…õ Ňčamb…ôp k…ôfo nk…õ Kanu k…ônament…ôr k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Abraham …õnc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu, k'omboc t…Ēk. K'oŇčkot wan k…Ēn Siyaka, k'edeŇč…ôr k…Ē t…Ēk ya k…ôloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč.  
\v 10 K…Ē Abraham …õnt…õnc k…ôca k'…õl…õk faka k…ôk…Ēfay wan k…Ēn amera.  
\v 11 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI mewe k…Ē darenc. K…Ē moloku: ¬ęAbraham! Abraham!¬Ľ K'owos…õ: ¬ęIn'…õw…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 12 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ moloku: ¬ęTa m…ôdeŇč…ôr wan kam k…ôca, ta m…ôy…Ē k…Ē tes o tes, bawo inc…ôr…õ oŇč nd…õk…ôl a m…ôŇčnes…õ Kanu, nt…õ m…ônt…Ēfat…õn'em wan kam m…Ē, wan kam sona.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē Abraham eyekti f…Ēr k'…õn…ôŇčkn…õ tadar…ôŇč aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun l…õn ya Ňči y…õp…ôts…ôrn…õ d…õr…ônt…ôm. K…Ē Abraham …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôl…õk aŇčkesiya nŇč…õ k'…õs…ôkp…ôr…õ Ňči wan k…Ēn, k'oloŇčn…õ Ňči Kanu k'…Ēnc…Ēf, k'…õsak wan k…Ēn.  
\v 14 K…Ē Abraham …Ēs…ĒŇč tofo tat…Ēk…Ē tewe ta ¬ęMARIKI …õŇčn…ôŇčk\f + \fr 22:14 \fq MARIKI …õŇčn…ôŇčk\ft  = ¬ęW…ôb…õ Kanu …Ēs…ĒŇč p…õmars…õn…õ.¬Ľ \f*.¬Ľ Ti t…Ē aŇčlok…õ m…Ēk…Ē: ¬ęNde t…Ēr…Ē ta MARIKI k…ôroŇč, andek…Ēn…ôŇčk k…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 15 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI m…ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôwe Abraham darenc,  
\v 16 k…Ē moloku: ¬ęToloku ta MARIKI ind…õr…ôm'am ti, ina s…ôrka! ‚ÄĻBawo m…ôy…Ē tant…õ, m…ôfat…õn…õ f'em wan kam sona Siyaka,  
\v 17 indelas …ôm k…ôpoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt, indes…ĒŇč…õ afum am Ňčala p…ôm…Ē c…Ēs ca darenc k…Ē as…ônc Ňča k…ôba k…ôs…ôk. Yuruya yam \f + \fr 22:17 \fq Yuruya yam\ft  = p…ôlay pa k…ôb…ônda ka dokom dam \f* yendetas…ôrn…õ ater…õn…õ aŇčan.  
\v 18 Afum a doru f…ôp Ňčandes…Ēt…Ē k…ôpoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt teta yuruya yam, bawo m…ônc…ôŇčk…ôl dim dem.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē Abraham oluks…ôrn…õ nde at…õmp …Ēn Ňčanckar k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…Ē Ňčasol f…ôp faŇčan k…ôk…Ē Berseba, bawo Abraham Berseba …õnand…õ. 
\p  
\v 20 Nt…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē mencep…ôr m…Ē, k'ande paloku Abraham nt…õ: Milka oŇčkom…õ s…Ē w…õnc Nahor awut arkun:  
\v 21 Huc wan k…Ēn w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, Bus w…õnc w…ôrkun, Kemuyel papa ka Aram,  
\v 22 Kesed, Haso, Pildas, Yidlaf k…Ē Betuh…õl.  
\v 23 K…Ē Betuh…õl oŇčkom Rebeka. Awut arkun akaŇč…õ cam…ôt-maas Ňč…Ē Milka …õnakom…õ Nahor, w…õnc ka Abraham.  
\v 24 K…Ē w…ôlak'…Ēn Rehuma, nk…Ēn s…Ē …õnakom…õ k…Ē awut: Tebah, Kaham, Tahas, k…Ē Mahaka. 
\c 23  
\s1 Abraham k…ôway…õ k…Ēn Sara kufu 
\p  
\v 1 K…ôwon ka Sara doru k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren tasar tin w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (127), meren mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē Sara …õnas…Ēt…Ē doru.  
\v 2 Sara …õnafi nde dare da Kiriyat-Arba, ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē Heb…ôr…ĒŇč at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč. K…Ē Abraham ender k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ k…ôwup ka Sara, p…ôbok k…Ē.  
\v 3 K…Ē Abraham …õy…õf…õ p…ôsak w…ôran k…Ēn w…ôfi, k'oloku aHewy moloku mm…õ:  
\v 4 ¬ęW…ôcik…ôra iy…Ēn…õ, w…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ t…õm nn…Ē ndoronu, n…ôpoc em tofo towup…õn…õ nn…Ē ndoronu, intam k…ôwup w…ôran kem, ib…Ēl…õn'em k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē aHewy Ňčaloku Abraham:  
\v 6 ¬ęM…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl su, mariki! Fum w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôka Kanu m…ôy…Ēn…õ su dac…Ē. M…ôm…Ēm…ôn k…ôfo nk…õ k…ômb…Ēt …ôm m…Ē, m…ôwup w…ôran kam d…ôk…ôwup…õn…õ dosu dac…Ē. Ali fum …Ēf…Ēdefat…õn…õ d…ôk…ôwup…õn…õ d…Ēn k…ôwup ka w…ôran kam.¬Ľ  
\v 7 K…Ē Abraham …õy…õf…õ k'ontontn…õn…õ afum a d…Ēt…Ēf, aHewy f…Ēr kiriŇč.  
\v 8 K…Ē Abraham oloku Ňča nt…õ: ¬ęK…Ē n…ôwos…õ a iwup w…ôran kem nn…Ē ib…Ēl…õn'em k…Ē-…õ, n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im, n…ôluks…õ t…õfaŇč tem H…õf…ôroŇč, wan ka Cohar.  
\v 9 A p…ôsak em kumbuŇčkum \f + \fr 23:9 \ft  Bi y…Ēk…Ē yeyi nde m…Ēr…Ē d…ônt…Ēf, nde Ňčancwup…õn…õ c…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē. \f* ka Makpela nk…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ k…Ēn m…Ē, nde dal…õ d…ôkusu. P…ôway…ôr im di gbeti mb…õ b…õntam k…ôs…Ēt…Ē di m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôy…Ēn…õ di d…ôk…ôwup…õn…õ dem n…ôna dac…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 10 H…õf…ôroŇč …õnand…õ aHewy dac…Ē. K…Ē H…õf…ôroŇč w…ôHewy oloku Abraham aHewy f…Ēr kiriŇč k…Ē aŇč…õ Ňčancb…õr…õ dare daŇčan d…ôkusuŇčka m…Ē:  
\v 11 ¬ęAla, mariki mem. M…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im! Is…ĒŇč …ôm dal…õ, k'is…ĒŇč …ôm s…Ē kumbuŇčkum k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôyi di m…Ē. Is…ĒŇč …ôm ki, f…Ēr ya awut a at…Ēf Ňčem kiriŇč. M…ôwup di w…ôran kam.¬Ľ  
\v 12 K…Ē Abraham ontontn…õn…õ afum aka d…Ēt…Ēf.  
\v 13 K'oloku nt…õ H…õf…ôroŇč, f…Ēr ya afum a d…Ēt…Ēf kiriŇč: ¬ęM…ôna s…Ē m…ôkaf…ôl…õ m…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im! IŇčs…ĒŇč k…ôway ka dal…õ! M…ôwos…õn'em ti, a idewup di w…ôran kem.¬Ľ  
\v 14 K…Ē H…õf…ôroŇč oloku Abraham:  
\v 15 ¬ęMariki mem, m…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im! Ant…Ēf Ňča gbeti m…õnc…ômb…ôl masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (400), ake bab…Ēk…Ē b…Ēy…Ēn…õ ina k…Ē m…ôna dac…Ē-…õ? M…ôwup di w…ôran kam!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 16 Nt…õ Abraham ene moloku ma H…õf…ôroŇč m…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē gbeti mb…õ …õnabonc m…Ē, gbeti m…õnc…ômb…ôl masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (400), f…Ēr ya aHewy kiriŇč. Gbeti m…õnc…ômb…ôl masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (400) bab…Ēk…Ē, b…õnay…Ēn…õ hak…õ Ňča k…ôway ka ant…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē nn…Ē acam…ôs Ňčayi m…Ē.  
\v 17 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ oŇč dal…õ da H…õf…ôroŇč nd…õ deyi Makpela, p…ôt…õf…ôr…õn…õ di k…Ē Mamre m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ dal…õ k…ôk…Ē kumbuŇčkum haŇč t…Ēk ny…õ y…õnac…ôm…õ d…ôk…ôl…ônc…ôr m…Ē f…ôp,  
\v 18 k…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ oŇč ya Abraham f…Ēr ya aHewy kiriŇč k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčancb…õr…õ dare dad…Ēk…Ē d…ôkusuŇčka m…Ē.  
\v 19 Nt…õ tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Abraham owup w…ôran k…Ēn Sara nde kumbuŇčkum ka dal…õ da Makpela, nde p…ônt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē Mamre m…Ē, ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē Heb…ôr…ĒŇč at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč.  
\v 20 Dal…õ k…Ē kumbuŇčkum nk…õ k…ônayi di m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ di oŇč d…ôk…ôwup…õn…õ da Abraham nd…õ …õnaway f…Ēr ya aHewy kiriŇč m…Ē. 
\c 24  
\s1 K…ôn…õnc…õn…õ ka Siyaka k…Ē Rebeka 
\p  
\v 1 Abraham …õnasik…ôr, meren m…Ēn m…õnab…Ēl…õ k…ôt…õnc, MARIKI …õnapoc…õ k…Ē p…ôt…Ēt f…ôp.  
\v 2 K…Ē Abraham oloku w…ôcar k…Ēn nw…õ …õnanaŇčkan…õ k…ôwon nn…Ē nd…Ēr…Ēn m…Ē, nw…õ onclomps…õ k…Ē ca y…Ēn m…Ē: ¬ęM…ôdeŇč k…ôca kam al…ôŇčk Ňčem tant…Ēf,  
\v 3 Indes…ĒŇč'am k…ôd…õr…ôm MARIKI, Kanu nk…õ k…ôyi darenc k…Ē d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē, ta m…ôl…õk…õ wan kem w…ôran w…ôKanaŇč, afum akaŇč…õ ind…õ dac…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 4 Mba m…ôde m…ôk…Ē at…Ēf Ňčem nde d…ôŇčkom dem, m…ôl…õk…õ di wan kem Siyaka w…ôran.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē w…ôcar k…Ēn oloku k…Ē: ¬ęT…Ēl…Ēma ta w…ôran …ĒŇčk…Ēwos…õ k…ôc…õps'em dar…ôŇč k…ôder ka nn…Ē-…õ, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē iluks…õ wan kam at…Ēf nŇč…õ m…ôy…õf…õ m…Ē ba?¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē Abraham oloku: ¬ęM…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ a m…ôluks…õ wan kem d…ôndo de!  
\v 7 MARIKI, Kanu nk…õ k…ôyi darenc m…Ē, nk…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč'em k…ôsak afum em k…Ē d…ôŇčkom dem m…Ē, nk…õ k…ôlok-lok…ôr im a k…ôd…õrm'em k…ôs…ĒŇč ka at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ yuruya yem m…Ē, nk…Ēn s…ôrka endesom m…õl…õk…õ m…õc…ôm'am f…Ēr kiriŇč, d…ôndo m…ôndek…Ēl…õk…õ wan kem w…ôran m…Ē.  
\v 8 K…Ē w…ôran …Ēnt…Ēk…Ēwos…õ k…ôc…ôm'am dar…ôŇč-…õ, iŇčaŇčn…õn'am k…ôd…õr…ôm nk…õ is…ĒŇč'am k…ôd…õr…ôm m…Ē. Mba ta m…ôluks…õ wan kem d…ôndo de!¬Ľ  
\v 9 K…Ē w…ôcar endeŇč k…ôca mariki m…Ēn Abraham al…ôŇčk tant…Ēf, k'…õnd…õrm…õ k…Ē teta moloku mam…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 10 K…Ē w…ôcar …õl…õk y…Ēk…Ēm…õ w…ôco y…Ēk…Ēm…õ ya mariki m…Ēn dac…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē. T…õnat…ôŇčn…õ p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr daka da w…ôb…õ k…Ēn d…Ēt…Ēt f…ôp.  
\v 11 Nt…õ …õmb…õr…õ Mesopotami nde dare da Nahor m…Ē, k'…õnc…ôp y…Ēk…Ēm…õ suwu dare k…ôs…ôk ta …Ēmb…Ēl…õ k…ôl…ômp ka domun-…õ, dec d…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy t…õm t…Ēk…Ē aran ŇčaŇčwur k…ôk…Ēk…õt domun m…Ē.  
\v 12 K'ontola: ¬ęM…ôna MARIKI, Kanu ka Abraham mariki mem, m…ômar im k…ôn…ôŇčk ka paka mp…õ int…õn m…Ē, il…õts…õn'am. K…Ē m…ôy…Ē ti-…õ, m…ôlas…õ mariki mem Abraham layidi d…Ēk…Ē m…ônas…ĒŇč k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 13 In'…õw…õ inc…ôm…õ nn…Ē k…ôl…ômp k…ôs…ôk m…Ē, k'ayec…ôra a afum a dare Ňčawur k…ôdek…õt domun-…õ.  
\v 14 P…ôy…Ēn…õ a w…ôyec…ôra nw…õ indeloku: ‚ÄĻIl…õts…õn'am m…ôti t…Ēb…Ēl tam imun,‚Äļ a w…ôkayi p…ôlok'im: ‚ÄĻM…ômun, is…ĒŇč s…Ē y…Ēk…Ēm…õ yam yomun,‚Äļ p…ôy…Ēn…õ a w…ôkak…Ē m…ômpoc…õ w…ôcar kam Siyaka! T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē indec…ôr…õ a m…ôlas…õ mariki mem Abraham layidi d…Ēk…Ē m…ônas…ĒŇč k…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 15 ∆źnalip f…õ moloku, k…Ē Rebeka wan ka Betuh…õl, wan s…Ē ka Milka k…Ē Nahor w…õnc ka Abraham oŇčwur p…ôgbaŇčn…õ t…Ēb…Ēl t…Ēn.  
\v 16 W…ôyec…ôra w…ôt…Ēt teyi …õnayi, ta …õntac…ôr…õ w…ôrkun-…õ, ali w…ôrkun w…ôkin …õnac…ôr…õ f…õ k…Ē d…õran. K'ontor d…ôk…ôl…ômp k'…õlas t…Ēb…Ēl t…Ēn k'…õmp…õ.  
\v 17 K…Ē w…ôcar …õy…õks…õ k…ôk…Ēfayn…õ k…Ē, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôpoc em domun depic da t…Ēb…Ēl tam, il…õts…õn'am.¬Ľ  
\v 18 K…Ē Rebeka oloku: ¬ęM…ômun, mariki mem!¬Ľ K'…õmb…õlk…ôr k…ôtin…õ k…Ē t…Ēb…Ēl t…Ēn, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē domun, k'omun.  
\v 19 Nt…õ elip k…ôs…ĒŇč w…ôcar ka Abraham k'omun m…Ē, k'oloku k…Ē s…Ē: ¬ęIndek…õt…õ y…Ēk…Ēm…õ yam domun yi s…Ē yomun haŇč p…ôt…ôŇčn…õ yi.¬Ľ  
\v 20 K'…õmb…õlk…ôr k…ôneŇčk…ôli domun d…õl…ôp…ôs d…ôk…ôsamp, k'…õy…õks…õ s…Ē k…ôk…Ēk…õt domun d…Ēl…Ēma d…ôk…ôl…ômp, k'…õŇčk…õt…õ y…Ēk…Ēm…õ f…ôp domun.  
\v 21 K…Ē w…ôcar ka Abraham eyifn…õ teta w…ôyec…ôra nw…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a MARIKI eyi k…ôlomps…õ k…Ē p…Ēk…Ēt p…Ēn-…õ. 
\p  
\v 22 Nt…õ y…Ēk…Ēm…õ yelip k…ômun m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ …õl…õk kurund…õ ka k…õma ka t…õnc…ômb…ôl dac…Ē,\f + \fr 24:22 \ft  Delel da kurund…õ ka k…õma kaŇčk…Ē d…õnay…Ēn…õ ¬ęgrammes¬Ľ cam…ôt-tin. \f* k…Ē c…ôsora ca d…ôk…ôca m…õr…ôŇč ca k…õma ka m…õnc…ômb…ôl w…ôco,\f + \fr 24:22 \ft  Delel da k…ôsora kin d…õnay…Ēn…õ ¬ęgrammes¬Ľ tasar tin k…Ē t…Ēl…Ēma. \f* k…ôsora kin o kin k'…Ēs…ĒŇč Rebeka.  
\v 23 K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ eyif Rebeka: ¬ęAn'okom …ôm-…õ w…ôyec…ôra? M…ôlok'im ti il…õts…õn'am. S…ôntam k…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…ôfo d…ôk…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ pibi, nde k…ôl…Ē ka papa kam?¬Ľ  
\v 24 K…Ē Rebeka oloku: ¬ęWan ka Betuh…õl iy…Ēn…õ, nw…õ Milka …õnakom…õ Nahor m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 25 K'endeŇč…ôr: ¬ęM…õmp…ôl…õ k…Ē yika y…õlar…ôm yeyi nn…Ē ndorosu k…Ē tofo tecep…ôr…õn…õ pibi teyi s…Ē di.¬Ľ  
\v 26 K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ ontontn…õn…õ MARIKI,  
\v 27 p…ôcloku: ¬ęIŇčkor-kor'…ôm m…ôna MARIKI, Kanu ka mariki mem Abraham. M…ôna nw…õ m…ônt…Ēsak k…ôlas layidi nd…õ m…ônas…ĒŇč k…Ē m…Ē, m…ôcy…Ēn…õ mariki mem m…õfaŇč m…Ēn f…ôp m…Ē! MARIKI m…ôsol'em k…Ē m…ôŇčk…õr'em haŇč nn…Ē k…ôl…Ē ka aw…õnc a mariki mem Abraham.¬Ľ  
\v 28 K…Ē w…ôyec…ôra …õy…õks…õ k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôl…Ēm…ôr mes mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp k…õr…õ nde nd…Ēr…Ēn.  
\v 29 Rebeka …õnay…Ē w…õnc w…ôrkun pacwe k…Ē LabaŇč. K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …õy…õks…õ k…ôk…Ēm…Ēm…ôn w…ôrkun nw…õ, nde d…ôk…ôl…ômp.  
\v 30 LabaŇč …õnan…ôŇčk…õ Rebeka kurund…õ k…Ē c…ôsora d…ôwaca, k'…õnanen…õ k…Ē p…ôcloku: ¬ęTi t…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē olok-lok…ôr …ôm.¬Ľ K…Ē w…õnc w…ôrkun w…ôka Rebeka ender nda w…ôrkun nw…õ, …õnayi k…ôl…ômp k…ôs…ôk k…Ē y…Ēk…Ēm…õ y…Ēn m…Ē.  
\v 31 K…Ē LabaŇč oloku: ¬ęM…ôder m…ôna nw…õ MARIKI ompoc…õ m…Ē! Ta ake t…Ē m…ôndeyin…õ dabaŇčka-…õ? If…õŇč dukul…Ē k'ilomps…õ y…Ēk…Ēm…õ yam tofo.¬Ľ  
\v 32 K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ …õmb…õr…õ d…ôk…ôl…Ē. K…Ē LabaŇč ontor…õ y…õsar…õ ya y…Ēk…Ēm…õ, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč yi yika k…Ē m…õmp…ôl…õ. K'…Ēs…ĒŇč w…ôrkun nw…õ k…Ē afum aŇč…õ …õnasol…õ m…Ē domun debik…õn…õ w…õc…ôk.  
\v 33 K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda k'anc…ômb…ôr…õ k…Ē yeri. Mba k'oloku: ¬ęIf…Ēdi k…ôr…õsna paka, m…õn…õ iloku toloku nt…õ inder k…ôloku m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē LabaŇč oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôloku!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 34 K'oloku: ¬ęAwa. W…ôcar ka Abraham iy…Ēn…õ.  
\v 35 Bel-bel b…Ē MARIKI ompoc…õ mariki mem p…ôt…Ēt nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ fum w…ôlel m…Ē. Kanu k…ômpoc…õ k…Ē c…ôna Ňčkesiya k…Ē cir, gbeti k…Ē k…õma, acar arkun k…Ē aran, y…Ēk…Ēm…õ k…Ē s…Ēfale.  
\v 36 Sara w…ôran ka mariki mem ende p…ôkom…õ k…Ē wan w…ôrkun detemb…ôra d…Ēn disr…õ. Wan w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē, nk…Ēn mariki mem …Ēs…ĒŇč daka d…Ēn f…ôp.  
\v 37 Mariki mem Abraham …Ēs…ĒŇč'em k…ôd…õr…ôm, k…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻM…ôf…Ēdet…õn…õ wan kem w…ôran ayec…ôra a KanaŇč dac…Ē at…Ēf nŇč…õ iyi m…Ē,  
\v 38 mba m…ôde m…ôk…Ē nde iy…õf…õ m…Ē, kor kosu disr…õ, m…ôt…õn…õ di wan kem w…ôran.‚Äļ  
\v 39 K'iloku Mariki mem: ‚ÄĻT…Ēl…Ēm ta w…ôran …ĒŇčk…Ēwos…õ k…ôc…õps'em dar…ôŇč k…ôder nn…Ē-…õ.‚Äļ  
\v 40 K'olok'im: ‚ÄĻMARIKI nw…õ iŇčk…Ēt f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē, endesom m…õl…õk…õ m…Ēn m…õbaŇč …ôm p…Ēk…Ēt pam. M…ôl…õk…õ wan kem w…ôran nde kusuŇčka kosu, p…ôy…Ēn…õ s…Ē w…ôka kor kosu.‚Äļ  
\v 41 K…Ē Abraham olok'im: ‚ÄĻIndewur'am k…ôd…õr…ôm kaŇčk…õ imb…õrs'am a m…ôd…õr…ôm m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a m…ôŇčk…Ē nde kor kosu a ta awos'am, k…ôs…ĒŇč ka wan w…ôran-…õ iŇčŇčaŇčn…õn'am k…ôd…õr…ôm kaŇčk…õ.‚Äļ  
\v 42 Nt…õ imb…ôpna m…Ēk…Ē nde d…ôk…ôl…ômp m…Ē, k'iloku: ‚ÄĻMARIKI, Kanu ka mariki mem Abraham, k…Ē m…ôŇčwos…õ k…ôlomp…ôs em p…Ēk…Ēt-…õ,  
\v 43 in'…Ēf…Ē nw…õ iyi k…ôl…ômp ka domun k…ôs…ôk m…Ē.‚Äļ W…ôyec…ôra nw…õ endewur k…ôdek…õt domun m…Ē, nw…õ indeloku: ‚ÄĻM…ôpoc em domun depic da t…Ēb…Ēl tam imun,‚Äļ  
\v 44 a w…ôkayi p…ôlok'im: ‚ÄĻM…ôbaŇč m…ômun m…ôna s…ôrka, indes…Ēk…õt…õ y…Ēk…Ēm…õ yam!‚Äļ W…ôyec…ôra w…ôkak…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ nw…õ MARIKI …õnc…ômb…ôr…õ wan ka mariki mem Abraham m…Ē!  
\v 45 Ilipna f…õ ti k…ôlokun…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc, k…Ē Rebeka oŇčwur p…ôgbaŇčn…õ t…Ēb…Ēl d…ôk…ôbanca. K'ontor d…ôk…ôl…ômp k'…õŇčk…õt domun. K'iloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻIl…õts…õn'am m…ôpoc'em imun.‚Äļ  
\v 46 K'…õmb…õlk…ôr k…ôtin'em t…Ēb…Ēl t…Ēn t…Ēk…Ē …õŇčgbaŇčn…õna m…Ē, k'olok'im: ‚ÄĻM…ômun, indepoc…õ s…Ē y…Ēk…Ēm…õ yam yomun.‚Äļ K'imun, k'ompoc…õ s…Ē y…Ēk…Ēm…õ yem k…Ē yomun.  
\v 47 K'iyif k…Ē: ‚ÄĻAn'okom …ôm-…õ w…ôyec…ôra?‚Äļ K'olok'im: ‚ÄĻWan ka Betuh…õl iy…Ēn…õ, wans…Ē ka Nahor k…Ē Milka.‚Äļ K'imb…õr k…Ē kurund…õ dolol…ôm k…Ē c…ôsora d…ôwaca.  
\v 48 K'intontn…õn…õ MARIKI, k'iyek-yek…ôs k…Ē, Kanu ka mariki mem Abraham, nk…õ k…ôsol'em k…ôdel…õk wan ka w…õnc ides…ĒŇč k…Ē Siyaka wan ka nk…Ēn Abraham m…Ē.  
\v 49 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a m…ôwos…õ k…ôlas…õ mariki mem Abraham p…ôsoku disr…õ, layidi nd…õ m…ônas…ĒŇč k…Ē m…Ē, m…ôs…ĒŇč'em ti k…ôc…ôr…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ik…Ē k…ôca k…ômeriya, k…Ē p…ôyi f…õ ti-…õ, k…ôt…Ēt.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 50 LabaŇč k…Ē Betuh…õl Ňčaloku: ¬ęTes tant…õ nda MARIKI t…õy…õf…õ, s…ôf…Ētam k…ôloku ti t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm.  
\v 51 Rebeka …Ēf…Ē w…ôkaw…õ f…Ēr yam kiriŇč, m…ôl…õk k…Ē n…ôk…Ē. P…ôk…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôran ka wan ka mariki mam p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI oloku ti m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 52 Nt…õ w…ôcar ka Abraham ene moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'ontontn…õn…õ MARIKI d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 53 K…Ē w…ôcar k'Abraham owur…õ yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya gbeti, ya k…õma, k…Ē yamos k'…Ēs…ĒŇč yi Rebeka, k'ompoc…õ s…Ē LabaŇč w…õnc w…ôrkun w…ôka Rebeka k…Ē k…õr…õ k…ôŇčan p…ôlar…ôm.  
\v 54 Nt…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē melip m…Ē, w…ôrkun nw…õ k'asol …Ēn, k…Ē Ňčandi yeri k…Ē Ňčamun, k…Ē Ňčancep…ôr…õn…õ pibi. Dec dendes…Ēk, nt…õ Ňčay…õf…õ m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôcar nw…õ oloku: ¬ęN…ôsak im iluks…ôrn…õ nda mariki mem.¬Ľ  
\v 55 K…Ē LabaŇč Ňčaloku k…Ē k…õr…õ: ¬ęWan w…ôran p…ôyi nn…Ē k…ôr…õsna mata w…ôco k…Ē s…ôna. K…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, m…ôntam k…ôk…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 56 K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ oloku Ňča: ¬ęTa n…ôs…ĒŇč'em k…ôwon ka nn…Ē, bawo MARIKI olomp…ôs em p…Ēk…Ēt. N…ôsak im ilukus ndena mariki mem.¬Ľ  
\v 57 K…Ē LabaŇč Ňčaloku k…Ē k…õr…õ: ¬ęS…ôwe wan w…ôran, s…ôyif k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õfaŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 58 K…Ē Ňčawe Rebeka k…Ē Ňčayif k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôfaŇč k…ôk…Ē k…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ ba?¬Ľ K…Ē Rebeka owos…õ: ¬ę∆źy.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 59 LabaŇč k…Ē k…õr…õ Ňčasak Rebeka k…Ē w…ôran nw…õ …õnabaŇč k…Ē m…Ē, w…ôcar ka Abraham k…Ē asol …Ēn k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē.  
\v 60 K…Ē Ňčantolan…õ Rebeka k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: 
\q1 ¬ęM…ôna w…ôkir…õ kosu, m…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôka afum alar…ôm! 
\q1 M…ôy…Ēn…õ fum nw…õ yuruya y…Ēn yendetam ater…õn…õ aŇčan m…Ē!¬Ľ 
\m  
\v 61 K…Ē Rebeka …õy…õf…õ k…Ē acar …Ēn ayec…ôra k'…õmp…õs…õ y…Ēk…Ēm…õ k…ôroŇč, k'…õnc…ôm…õ w…ôrkun nw…õ dar…ôŇč. K…Ē w…ôcar ka Abraham …õl…õk Rebeka k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē. 
\p  
\v 62 T…õt…ôŇčn…õ Siyaka p…ôlukus k…ôy…õf…õ ka k…ôl…ômp ka Lahay-Roy, p…ônd…õ nde at…Ēf Ňča N…õk…õf.  
\v 63 D…Ēf…Ēy d…Ēl…Ēma k…Ē Siyaka …ĒŇčk…Ē d…ôŇčk…Ēt…ôs d…ôkulum, endeyekti f…Ēr k'…õn…ôŇčk y…Ēk…Ēm…õ yecder.  
\v 64 Rebeka endeyekti s…Ē f…Ēr k'…õn…ôŇčk Siyaka, k'ontor y…Ēk…Ēm…õ k…ôroŇč.  
\v 65 K'eyif w…ôcar ka Abraham: ¬ęW…ôrkun w…ôre …Ēf…Ē w…ôkaw…õ nn…Ē d…ôkulum nw…õ ender k…ôfayn…õ su m…Ē?¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôcar oloku k…Ē: ¬ęMariki mem m…Ē.¬Ľ K'…õl…õk k…ôloto k…Ēn k'…õŇčgbal…ôrn…õ.  
\v 66 K…Ē w…ôcar ka Abraham …Ēl…Ēm…ôr Siyaka mes m…Ēk…Ē …õnacep…ôr…õn…õ m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 67 K…Ē Siyaka eŇčkek…ôr…õ Rebeka abal Ňča k…õr…õ Sara disr…õ. K'…õl…õk Rebeka k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôran k…Ēn, k'…Ēmb…Ēt…ôr k…Ē. Ti t'…õnas…ĒŇč…õ Siyaka p…ôwak k…ôp…ôl-p…ôl…ôs defi da k…õr…õ. 
\c 25  
\s1 Defi da Abraham: Mewe ma yuruya y…Ēn ny…õ w…ôran k…Ēn Ketura …õnakom…õ k…Ē m…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Abraham …õl…õk s…Ē w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma, pacwe k…Ē Ketura.  
\v 2 K…Ē Ketura oŇčkom…õ k…Ē awut arkun: SimraŇč, Y…ĒksaŇč, MedaŇč, MadiyaŇč, Yisbak, k…Ē Suwah.  
\v 3 K…Ē Y…ĒksaŇč oŇčkom Saba k…Ē DedaŇč. Awut arkun a DedaŇč Ňčanay…Ēn…õ afum a t…Ēf maas: Asuri, aLetusi k…Ē aLeyumi.  
\v 4 Awut a MadiyaŇč Ňčanay…Ēn…õ Hefah, Hefer, Henok, Abidah, k…Ē ∆źldaha. AkaŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ēn…õ awut a Ketura. 
\p  
\v 5 Abraham …õnas…ĒŇč daka d…Ēn f…ôp Siyaka.  
\v 6 Awut a alak'…Ēn, k'ompoc…õ Ňča, p…ôs…Ēr…Ēyi doru, k'eŇčkek…ôr…õ Ňča poŇč p…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ Ňča wan k…Ēn Siyaka, at…Ēf nŇč…õ Ňčeyi ntende k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.  
\v 7 K…ôwon ka Abraham doru k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren tasar tin w…ôco cam…ôt m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (175).  
\v 8 K…Ē Abraham ontor…õ kifir, k'efi nt…õ encep…ôr…õn…õ detem dobotu m…Ē, p…ôb…õk, p…ôn…õmb…ôr…õ mataka ma doru, k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl atem …Ēn aŇč…õ Ňčanafi m…Ē.  
\v 9 Siyaka k…Ē S…ômayila awut a Abraham, Ňčawup k…Ē nde d…ôk…ôwup…õn…õ da Makpela, nde dal…õ da H…õf…ôroŇč wan ka Cohar w…ôHewy, p…ôt…õf…ôr…õn…õ di k…Ē Mamre.  
\v 10 Dal…õ d…õnayi nd…õ Abraham …õnaway nn…Ē aHewy Ňčayi m…Ē. Dif…Ē anawup Abraham k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn Sara.  
\v 11 Nt…õ defi da Abraham dencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ômpoc…õ wan k…Ēn Siyaka nw…õ …õnand…õ nde k…ôl…ômp ka Lahay-Roy k…ôs…ôk m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 12 Awut a S…ômayila Ňč…Ē akaŇč…õ, S…ômayila wan k'Abraham, nw…õ wan w…ôran w…ôMisira Hakar w…ôcar ka Sara …õnakom…õ Abraham m…Ē.  
\v 13 Mewe ma awut a S…ômayila m…õm…õ, t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanab…õk…õn…õ m…Ē: Nebay…Ēt coco ca S…ômayila, Kedar, Adebel, Mib…ôsam,  
\v 14 Misma, Dumah, Masa,  
\v 15 Hadad, Tema, Yetur, Nafis, k…Ē Kedema. Awut a S…ômayila Ňč…Ē akak…Ē.  
\v 16 Mewe maŇčan m…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē t…õnd…õ taŇčan c…ôgbo c…ôgbo. Ab…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč Ňčanayi Ňča kiriŇč d…õlay daŇčan.  
\v 17 K…ôyi ka S…ômayila doru k…ônawon meren tasar tin w…ôco maas k…Ē cam…ôt m…õr…ôŇč (137). K'ontor…õ kifir, k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl atem …Ēn ak…Ē Ňčanafi m…Ē.  
\v 18 Afum a S…ômayila Ňčayi k…ôy…õf…õ ka Hawila haŇč Sur ns…õ s…ônt…õf…ôrn…õ Misira m…Ē, k…ôk…Ē ka k…ôca ka Asiri. Yuruya ya S…ômayila Ňčanand…õ Ňčat…õf…ôrn…õ aw…õnc aŇča f…ôp. 
\ms2 Tecep…ôr…õn…õ ta Yakuba 
\mr 25-36 
\s1 Esayu k…Ē Yakuba 
\p  
\v 19 Afum a Siyaka Ňč'aŇč…õ, wan ka Abraham. Abraham okom Siyaka.  
\v 20 Siyaka …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) a k'enden…õnc…õ Rebeka, wan w…ôran w…ôka Betuh…õl w…ôka Aram w…ôka PadaŇč-Aram, w…ôkir…õ ka LabaŇč w…ôka Aram.  
\v 21 K…Ē Siyaka ontola MARIKI teta w…ôran k…Ēn, bawo …õnakom f…õ wan. K…Ē MARIKI ene k…ôtola k…Ēn. K…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn Rebeka …õmb…õk…ôs.  
\v 22 K…Ē awut Ňčay…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē kor disr…õ, k…Ē Rebeka eyifn…õ: ¬ęAk'ender im tant…õ-…õ?¬Ľ K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôkorn…õ MARIKI.  
\v 23 K…Ē MARIKI oloku k…Ē: ¬ęAfum a t…Ēf m…õr…ôŇč Ňčay'…ôm d…ôkor, afum m…õr…ôŇč akak…Ē Ňčandegb…õy…õn…õ k…ôwur …ôm d…ôkor. Afum a w…ôkin nw…õ Ňčandetas…ôrn…õ aka w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč. W…ôbeki endeyi w…ôf…õt tant…Ēf.¬Ľ  
\v 24 D…ôŇčkom d…Ēn k'an…ôŇčk a c…ôberi c…ôyi k…Ē d…ôkor.  
\v 25 D…ôŇčkom daŇčan, k…Ē w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ender p…ôla c…ôfon c…ôyim d…ôris p…ôm…Ē w…õs…õm, k'awe k…Ē Esayu.  
\v 26 K…Ē tencep…ôr, k…Ē w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč ender p…ôsump…ôr atek Ňča w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē. K'awe w…ôkak…Ē Yakuba. Siyaka p…ôs…Ēt…Ē t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē oŇč meren w…ôco cam…ôt tin (60) a k'andekom…õ k…Ē awut akaŇč…õ.  
\v 27 K…Ē awut arkun aŇč…õ Ňčamb…õk. K…Ē Esayu ende p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôp…õn w…ôt…Ēt, w…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…ôy…õks…õ-y…õks…õ d…ôkulum k…ôt…õn ka s…õm y…õp…õn, k…Ē Yakuba nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôyi w…ôka dare, w…ôt…Ēsims…õ dis p…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…ônd…õ d'abal.  
\v 28 Siyaka …õnab…Ēt…ôr Esayu bawo …õnab…Ēt…ôr s…õm ny…õ Esayu …õncp…õn m…Ē. Rebeka nk…Ēn p…ôb…Ēt…ôr Yakuba.  
\v 29 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma k…Ē Yakuba oncoŇč…ôr m…õnc, k…Ē Esayu ender p…ôy…õf…õ d…ôkulum dis d…Ēl…Ēl k…Ē.  
\v 30 K…Ē Esayu oloku Yakuba: ¬ęM…ôpoc'em, il…õts…õn'am idi p…ôyim pam pap…Ēk…Ē bawo dis d…Ēl…Ēl im.¬Ľ Ti t…Ē as…ĒŇč…õ Esayu tewe ta ¬ęEd…Ēm\f + \fr 25:30 \fq Ed…Ēm\ft  ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęp…ôyim¬Ľ \f*¬Ľ.  
\v 31 K…Ē Yakuba oloku Esayu: ¬ęM…ôway…ôr im m…Ēk…Ē d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da debeki dam.¬Ľ  
\v 32 K…Ē Esayu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęIn'…õw…õ icfi, ake d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da debeki dad…Ēk…Ē dendey…Ē em-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 33 K…Ē Yakuba oloku: ¬ęM…ôd…õr…ôm'em k…ôr…õsna.¬Ľ K…Ē Esayu …õnd…õrm…õ Yakuba k'…õway…ôr k…Ē d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da debeki d…Ēn.  
\v 34 K…Ē Yakuba ompoc…õ Esayu k…ôcom, k…Ē m…õnc mam…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē Esayu endi yeri yay…Ēk…Ē, k'omun, k'…õy…õf…õ k'…ĒŇčk…Ē. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē Esayu …õnagbal d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da debeki d…Ēn. 
\c 26  
\s1 Siyaka k…Ē Abim…õl…õk 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē dor dende deyi d…Ēt…Ēf, nd…õ d…õnaciyan…õ k…Ē dor d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē d…Ēk…Ē d…õnayi di t…õm ta Abraham m…Ē. K…Ē Siyaka …ĒŇčk…Ē nda Abim…õl…õk, w…ôb…õ ka aFilisti nde Kerar.  
\v 2 K…Ē MARIKI owur…ôr Siyaka, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTa m…ôtor Misira, m…ôyi at…Ēf nŇč…õ indebonc…ôr …ôm m…Ē.  
\v 3 M…ônd…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ. Isol'am, indepoc'am p…ôt…Ēt, bawo m…ôna k…Ē yuruya yam \f + \fr 26:3 \ft  D…õlay dam \f* Ňč'indes…ĒŇč ant…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ f…ôp. Indelas t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē k…ôd…õr…ôm nk…õ inad…õrm…õ papa kam Abraham m…Ē.  
\v 4 Indey…Ē yuruya yam y…õla p…ôm…Ē c…Ēs ca darenc. Indes…ĒŇč yuruya yam t…Ēf yay…õ f…ôp. Afum a doru f…ôp Ňčande Ňčact…õn k…ôtola nn…Ē yuruya yam yeyi m…Ē.  
\v 5 Abraham …õnac…ôŇčk…ôl dim dem, p…ôc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē dem dar…ôŇč, p…ôsump…ôr moloku mem, p…ôlel…ôs m…õfaŇč mem k…Ē sariy…õ sem.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē Siyaka …õnd…õ Kerar.  
\v 7 Nt…õ afum a tofo tat…Ēk…Ē Ňčancyif…ôt teta w…ôran k…Ēn m…Ē, p…ôcloku Ňča: ¬ęW…ôkir…õ kem …Ēf…Ē.¬Ľ P…ôcnes…õ k…ôloku a w…ôran k…Ēn …Ēf…Ē, ta afum a tofo tat…Ēk…Ē Ňčadif k…Ē, bawo Rebeka …õnates…õ.  
\v 8 Nt…õ k…ôyi k…Ēn k…ôncwon di m…Ē, k…Ē tosur…õn…õ Abim…õl…õk w…ôb…õ ka aFilisti p…ôwur…õ k…ôro d…ôwund…õr p…ôcm…Ēm…ôn, k'…õn…ôŇčk Siyaka p…ôcc…õc…õn…õ k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn Rebeka.  
\v 9 K…Ē Abim…õl…õk ewe Siyaka k'eyif k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôran kam …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôran nw…õ ba! Ake's…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ m…ôloku su a w…ôkir…õ kam …Ēf…Ē m…Ē?¬Ľ K…Ē Siyaka oloku k…Ē: ¬ęIloku ti k…ônes…õ disr…õ ta idefin…õ tet…Ēn.¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē Abim…õl…õk oloku k…Ē: ¬ęC…ôke m…ôy…Ē su tant…õ? P…ôpic p…õc…ôm…õ w…ôl…Ēma su dac…Ē Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôran kam, k…Ē m…ôn'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôsar…õ kiciya.¬Ľ  
\v 11 K…Ē Abim…õl…õk …Ēs…ĒŇč dim dad…Ēk…Ē afum …Ēn f…ôp, nt…õ: ¬ęFum nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ w…ôrkun nw…õ k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn m…Ē, m…õn…õ padif w…ôkayi.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 12 K…Ē Siyaka …Ēmb…Ēf k…ôren kaŇčk…Ē d…Ēt…Ēf k'…õnt…õl tasar tin (100) ta t…Ēk…Ē …õnab…Ēf m…Ē, bawo MARIKI …õnapoc…õ k…Ē p…ôt…Ēt.  
\v 13 K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ …Ēs…Ēt…Ē daka, k'…õmb…õr…õn…õ k…ôs…Ēt…Ē daka haŇč k'…õnaŇčkan…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôka daka w…ôp…ĒŇč.  
\v 14 Siyaka …õnay…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…õlar…ôm: C…ôna, cir, Ňčkesiya, k…Ē acar alar…ôm, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ aFilisti Ňčay…Ēn…õ k…Ē k…ôraca. 
\s1 Siyaka k…ôsek k…Ēn danapa k…Ē Abim…õl…õk 
\p  
\v 15 C…ôl…ômp nc…õ acar a kas Abraham Ňčanakay kiyi k…Ēn doru m…Ē, k…Ē aFilisti Ňčam…ônt…ôn ci, k…Ē Ňčalas ci k…ôbof.  
\v 16 K…Ē Abim…õl…õk oloku Siyaka: ¬ęM…ôy…õf…õ ndorosu m…ôk…Ē bawo m…ômb…õk su f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr.¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē Siyaka …õy…õf…õ di, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôc…ômb…ôr saŇčka nde d…ôŇčgb…ôl da Kerar k…ôs…ôk.  
\v 18 K…Ē Siyaka …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôkay c…ôl…ômp nc…õ anakay t…õm ta kas Abraham, a k…Ē aFilisti Ňčam…ônt…ôn ci k…ôcep…ôr ka defi da Abraham m…Ē. K'ewe s…Ē ci mewe m…Ēk…Ē kas …õnawe ci m…Ē.  
\v 19 K…Ē acar a Siyaka ŇčaŇčkay s…Ē k…ôl…ômp k…ôl…Ēma, d…ôndo m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…ôp ki disr…õ domun d…Ēt…Ēt.  
\v 20 Ak…õk a y…Ēc…Ēl ya dare da Kerar ŇčancaŇč ak…õk a y…Ēc…Ēl ya Siyaka k…ôc…Ēp, Ňčacsims…õ k…ôl…ômp, k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęK…ôl…ômp kaŇčk…õ kosu k…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Siyaka ewe k…ôl…ômp kaŇčk…Ē Es…õk, bawo afum Ňčanagb…õk…ôl…õn…õ ta ki k…Ē nk…Ēn.  
\v 21 K…Ē acar a Siyaka Ňčaluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôkay k…ôl…ômp k…ôl…Ēma nk…õ anagb…õk…ôl…õn…õ s…Ē taka ki m…Ē, k'ewe ki Sitna.  
\v 22 K'eliŇč saŇčka s…Ēn d…ôndo, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôkay s…Ē k…ôl…ômp k…ôl…Ēma nk…õ anat…Ēgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ ta ki m…Ē, k'ewe ki Rehobot, bawo, oncloku: MARIKI p…ôyac su, p…ôsik…ôli su, k…ôdes…Ēt…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ.  
\v 23 K…Ē Siyaka …õmp…õrn…õ Bersaba.  
\v 24 K…Ē MARIKI owur…ôr k…Ē pibi pap…Ēk…Ē, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęIn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Kanu ka papa kam Abraham. Ta m…ônes…õ, bawo isol'am, indepoc'am p…ôt…Ēt, indey…Ē s…Ē yuruya yam Ňčala, teta w…ôcar kem Abraham.¬Ľ  
\v 25 K…Ē Siyaka …õnc…ômb…ôr di tetek toloŇčn…õ k'okorn…õ tewe ta MARIKI. K'…õnc…ômb…ôr s…Ē di abal, k…Ē acar …Ēn ŇčaŇčkay s…Ē di k…ôl…ômp. 
\p  
\v 26 K…Ē Abim…õl…õk …õy…õf…õ Kerar k…ôk…Ēn…ôŇčk nk…Ēn Siyaka Ňčasol k…Ē Ahusat wanapa k…Ēn, k…Ē Pik…Ēl w…ôb…õ w…ôka as…Ēdar …Ēn.  
\v 27 K…Ē Siyaka eyif Ňča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ônder…õn…õ nn…Ē nderem-…õ, bawo n…ônter im, k…Ē n…ômb…õl…ôs im nde ndoronu?¬Ľ  
\v 28 K…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęS…ôn…ôŇčk belbel a MARIKI osol'am. Ti t…Ē s…ôlok…õ: A pad…õrm…õn…õ, ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē m…ôna k…Ē s…ôna, pat…ôŇčn…õ pasek danapa.  
\v 29 Nt…õ tendes…ĒŇč…õ ta m…ôy…Ē su ali p…ôl…õc pin, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē s…ônat…Ēy…Ē …ôm p…ôl…õc, k…Ē s…ôy…Ē …ôm p…ôt…Ēt haŇč k…Ē s…ôsak …ôm k…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ē p…ôforu disr…õ m…Ē. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč MARIKI ompoc'am.¬Ľ  
\v 30 K…Ē Siyaka omboc…õ Ňča k…ôsata, k…Ē Ňčandi yeri k…Ē Ňčamun.  
\v 31 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy k…Ē Ňčand…õrm…õn…õ. K…Ē Siyaka …õsak Ňča k…Ē Ňčalukus k…Ē Ňčasak Siyaka p…ôforu disr…õ. 
\p  
\v 32 D…Ēs…Ēk din dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ē acar a Siyaka Ňčander Ňčaloku k…Ē teta k…ôl…ômp k…ôŇčk…Ē Ňčanakay m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęS…ôs…Ēt…Ē domun.¬Ľ  
\v 33 K…Ē Siyaka ewe k…ôl…ômp kaŇčk…Ē Sibeya. Ti t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ aŇčwen…õ dare dad…Ēk…Ē Bersaba haŇč m…Ēk…Ē m…Ē. 
\s1 Esayu k…ôn…õnc…õ k…Ēn 
\p  
\v 34 Esayu k…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…Ēn meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40), k'…õl…õk aran aHewy, pacwe Ňča Sudit wan ka Beri k…Ē Basmat wan ka El…Ēn.  
\v 35 K'aran aHitara akaŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč Ňčawon…ôs Siyaka k…Ē Rebeka dis. 
\c 27  
\s1 Yakuba k…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…Ēn k…ôpoc…õ nk…õ p…ônamar Esayu k…ôs…Ēt…Ē m…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 Siyaka …Ēncy…Ēn…õ w…ôtem, f…Ēr y…Ēcl…Ēl k…Ē haŇč k…Ē t…õl…ôps…ôr k…Ē k…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk. K'ewe wan k…Ēn w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Esayu, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęWan kem!¬Ľ K…Ē Esayu owos…õ: ¬ęIn'…õw…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 2 K…Ē Siyaka …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ: ¬ęIy…Ēn…õ w…ôtem, inc…ôr…õ f…õ d…Ēs…Ēk dem defi.  
\v 3 M…ôl…õk oŇč y…õp…õn…õ yam, c…ôb…ôlma cam k…Ē amb…ônc…ôran, m…ôk…Ē d…ôkulum m…ôk…Ē m…ôp…õn'em w…õs…õm.  
\v 4 M…ôlomp…ôs'em peri p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē imb…Ēt…ôr ti m…Ē. M…ôk…õr'em pi, idi, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ina yati itolan'am p…ôt…Ēt a icfi m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 5 Rebeka p…ôcc…ôŇčk…ôl t…Ēk…Ē Siyaka oncloku wan k…Ēn Esayu m…Ē. K…Ē Esayu …ĒŇčk…Ē d…ôkulum k…ôk…Ēp…õn w…õs…õm, p…ôk…õr…õ. 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē Rebeka oloku wan k…Ēn Yakuba: ¬ęNt…õ t'ine. Papa kam p…ôcloku w…õnc …ôm Esayu:  
\v 7 ‚ÄĻM…ôk…õr'em w…õs…õm. M…ôlomp…ôs'em peri mp…õ indedi, itolan'am p…ôt…Ēt nde MARIKI eyi m…Ē, a icfi.‚Äļ  
\v 8 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč wan kem m…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl dim dem, m…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē indelok'…ôm m…Ē.  
\v 9 M…ôk…Ē m…ôl…õk'em nde y…Ēc…Ēl dac…Ē, mbiyofo y…Ēt…Ēt m…õr…ôŇč. Ilomps…õ papa kam peri p…Ēt…Ēt p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …Ēmb…Ēt…ôr pi m…Ē.  
\v 10 M…ôndeken…õ papa kam peri pap…Ēk…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôtolan'am p…ôt…Ēt a p…ôcfi m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 11 K…Ē Yakuba oloku k…õr…õ Rebeka: ¬ę∆źy, mba w…õnc im Esayu …õla c…ôfon d…ôris, k'ina iy…Ē f…õ ci.  
\v 12 T…Ēl…Ēma papa w…ôkem p…ôk…Ēwak…ôs im dis, endec…ôr'em k…ôt…Ēlomp t…Ēs…ĒŇč'em k…ôs…Ēt…Ē p…ôl…õc ta is…Ēt…Ē p…ôt…Ēt-…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 13 K…Ē k…õr…õ oloku k…Ē: ¬ęT…Ēy…Ēn…õ a p…ôl…õc pap…Ēk…Ē peder im! M…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl gb…ôc…ôr…ôm dim dem. M…ôk…Ē m…ôk…õr'em mir.¬Ľ  
\v 14 K…Ē Yakuba …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôl…õk mir, k'…õŇčk…õr…õ iya k…Ēn. K…Ē iya k…Ēn olomp…ôs peri, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē papa k…Ēn …õnab…Ēt…ôr pi m…Ē.  
\v 15 K…Ē Rebeka …õl…õk yamos ya Esayu wan k…Ēn w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, yamos y…Ēt…Ēt y…Ēk…Ē …õnatam k…ôs…Ēt…Ē d…õk…õr m…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč yi wan k…Ēn w…ôlp…ôs Yakuba k'…õmb…õrn…õ.  
\v 16 K'oŇčkump Yakuba akata Ňča mbiyofo y…Ēk…Ē Ňčanadif m…Ē d…ôwaca k…Ē d…ôkilim, k…ôb…ôp ka mofo m…Ēk…Ē m…õnat…Ēy…Ē c…ôfon m…Ē.  
\v 17 K…Ē Rebeka …Ēs…ĒŇč wan k…Ēn Yakuba peri p…Ēk…Ē …õnalomp…ôs m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôcom.  
\v 18 K…Ē Yakuba …ĒŇčk…Ē nde papa k…Ēn eyi m…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęPapa w…ôkem!¬Ľ K…Ē Siyaka owos…õ: ¬ęIn'…õw…õ. M…ôn'an'…Ēf…Ē-…õ, Wan kem?¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē Yakuba oloku kas: ¬ęIn'…Ēf…Ē Esayu wan kam w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē. Iy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ôlokun'em m…Ē. M…ôy…õf…õ il…õts…õn'am, m…ônd…õ m…ôs…Ēm w…õs…õm wem, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ m…ôna yati m…ôtolan'em p…ôt…Ēt m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 20 K…Ē Siyaka oloku wan k…Ēn: ¬ęMba m…ôyeŇčk k…ôs…Ēt…Ē w…õs…õm wan kem!¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba oloku: ¬ęMARIKI Kanu kam k…ôk…õr'em wi f…Ēr yem kiriŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 21 K…Ē Siyaka oloku Yakuba: ¬ęM…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ oŇč wan kem, iwak…ôs …ôm, ic…ôr…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a wan kem Esayu …Ēf…Ē-…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē Yakuba …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ kas Siyaka, k'…õwak…ôs k…Ē k'oloku: ¬ęDim dand…õ da Yakuba d…Ē, mba waca waw…õ wa Esayu w…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 23 Siyaka …õnan…õp…ôl f…õ k…Ē. Bawo waca w…Ēn w…õnala c…ôfon p…ôm…Ē waca wa w…õnc Esayu, k'ontolan…õ k…Ē p…ôt…Ēt.  
\v 24 K'eyif: ¬ęM…ôn'…Ēf…Ē m…ôna wan kem Esayu?¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba owos…õn…õ k…Ē: ¬ę∆źy.¬Ľ  
\v 25 K…Ē Siyaka oloku: ¬ęM…ôb…õr'em is…Ēm w…õs…õm wa wan kem, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ, ina yati itolan'am p…ôt…Ēt m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba …õmb…õr…õ Siyaka yeri k'endi, k'…õŇčk…õr…õ k…Ē s…Ē member k'omun.  
\v 26 K…Ē kas Siyaka oloku s…Ē: ¬ęM…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ m…ôcup im wan kem.¬Ľ  
\v 27 K…Ē Yakuba …Ēnc…ĒŇčn…õ, k'oncup k…Ē. K…Ē Siyaka ene amb…Ēnc Ňča yamos ya Esayu. K'ontolan…õ k…Ē nt…õ: ¬ę∆źy, amb…Ēnc Ňča wan kem Ňčeyi p…ôm…Ē amb…Ēnc Ňča dal…õ nd…õ MARIKI ompoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt m…Ē.  
\v 28 Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm p…ôcaŇčki pa darenc 
\q1 k…Ē daka da d…ônt…Ēf: 
\q1 Mal…Ē k…Ē member p…ôlar…ôm! 
\p  
\v 29 MARIKI p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ, afum Ňčay'…ôm d…ônt…Ēf, 
\q1 Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ afum Ňčatontn…õn'am! 
\q1 Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ m…ôyi aw…õnc …ôm aŇča k…ôroŇč, 
\q1 Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ awut a iya kam Ňčatontn…õn'am d…ônt…Ēf! 
\q1 Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč p…ôl…õc, w…ôk…Ē …õŇčfaŇč'am p…ôl…õc m…Ē, 
\q1 Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč p…ôt…Ēt w…ôk…Ē …õŇčfaŇč'am p…ôt…Ēt m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 30 Siyaka …õnadelip k…ôtolan…õ Yakuba, Yakuba endey…õf…õ kas d…ônt…Ēf, k…Ē w…õnc Esayu …õmb…õr…õ p…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôp…õn.  
\v 31 K…Ē Esayu olomp…ôs s…Ē peri k'eŇčken…õ kas Siyaka. K'oloku kas: ¬ęPapa m…ôy…õf…õ m…ôs…Ēm w…õs…õm wa wan kam, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ m…ôtolan'em p…ôt…Ēt m…ôna yati m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 32 K…Ē kas Siyaka eyif k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôn'an'…Ēf…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Esayu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęIn'…Ēf…Ē wan kam w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Esayu.¬Ľ  
\v 33 K…Ē p…ôyi Siyaka yamayama, yamayama p…ôp…ĒŇč k'oloku: ¬ęAn'…Ēk…Ē p…ôp…õn w…õs…õm k'…õŇčk…õr'em-…õ? Is…Ēm yi a k…Ē m…ôndeder, intolan…õ k…Ē p…ôt…Ēt. K…ôtola p…ôt…Ēt k…ôlip k…ôsump…ôr k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 34 Nt…õ Esayu ene moloku ma kas m…Ē, k'…õmb…õr k…ôbebe, k'oŇčkul…õ-kul…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč, k'oloku kas: ¬ęIna s…Ē m…ôtolan'em p…ôt…Ēt Papa.¬Ľ  
\v 35 K…Ē Siyaka oloku k…Ē: ¬ęW…õnc …ôm ender…õn…õ c…ômp…ônp…ôn k'…õl…õk k…ôtolan…õ p…ôt…Ēt kam.¬Ľ  
\v 36 K…Ē Esayu oloku: ¬ęCep…Ē nt…õ as…ĒŇč k…Ē tewe ta Yakuba m…Ē, ti t'…õŇčn…õmps'em haŇč k…ôm…õr…ôŇč? ∆źnabaŇč…ôr im t…Ēk…Ē d…ôc…ôm…õ da debeki dem. K…Ē p…ôndes…Ēyi tant…õ k'…õŇčl…õk…ôr im s…Ē k…ôtolan…õ p…ôt…Ēt kem.¬Ľ K…Ē Esayu endeŇč…ôr: ¬ęPapa, m…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ f…õ s…Ē k…ôtolan…õ p…ôt…Ēt k…ôl…Ēma, m…ôs…ĒŇč im ki?¬Ľ  
\v 37 K…Ē Siyaka oloku Esayu: ¬ęIs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôyi kam k…ôroŇč, k'is…ĒŇč k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča f…ôp k…ôyi k…Ē d…ônt…Ēf, k'is…ĒŇč k…Ē b…ôle\f + \fr 27:37 \ft  C…ôTabo ¬ębleŐĀ¬Ľ \f* k…Ē w…õn. C…ôke c'indey…Ēn…õ m…ôna-…õ, wan kem?¬Ľ  
\v 38 K…Ē Esayu eyif kas: ¬ęK…ôtola p…ôt…Ēt kin kaŇčk…Ē gboŇč k…Ē m…ôy…Ē ba, Papa? Ina s…Ē m…ôtolan'em p…ôt…Ēt, Papa!¬Ľ K…Ē Esayu …õy…õf…õ k…ôbok.  
\v 39 K…Ē kas Siyaka oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôn…ôŇčk! 
\q1 D…ôk…ônd…õ dam d…Ēf…Ēdey…Ē daka da d…ônt…Ēf 
\q1 K…Ē p…ôcaŇčki mp…õ p…õŇčy…õf…õ darenc m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 40 Dakma dam dended…ôs …ôm doru, 
\q1 M…ôndeyi w…õnc …ôm d…ônt…Ēf. 
\q1 M…ôndeyi tam taciŇča 
\q1 F…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fam f…ôndes…ĒŇč…õ, m…ôccer k…Ē m…õfaŇč m…Ēn.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôk…Ē ka Yakuba nda nc…Ēk'…Ēn LabaŇč 
\p  
\v 41 K…Ē Esayu …õm…õŇčk…õ Yakuba m…õt…õl…õ, teta k…ôtolan…õ p…ôt…Ēt nk…õ kas …õnatolan…õ Yakuba m…Ē. Esayu p…ôcc…Ēp…ôsn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc, ¬ęMataka ma defi da papa w…ôkem m…Ēmb…Ēl…õ f…õ s…Ē. Indedif w…õnc im Yakuba.¬Ľ  
\v 42 K'aŇčk…Ē paloku Rebeka m…õc…õmc…õmn…õ m…õl…õc ma Esayu nn…Ē Yakuba eyi m…Ē. K…Ē Rebeka ewe wan k…Ēn Yakuba, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ône nt…õ w…õnc …ôm Esayu …õfaŇč k…ôluks'am ay…õk m…Ē, a p…ôdif …ôm.  
\v 43 Awa wan kem, m…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im! M…ôy…õf…õ, m…ôk…Ē m…ôgb…Ēpn…õ ndena w…õnc im w…ôrkun LabaŇč nde HaraŇč.  
\v 44 M…ôk…Ē m…ôyi di mataka, haŇč m…õt…õl…õ ma w…õnc …ôm melip.  
\v 45 K…Ē m…õt…õl…õ ma w…õnc …ôm mendelip-…õ, p…ôp…ôl…ôrn…õ p…ôcuy p…Ēk…Ē m…ôy…Ē k…Ē m…Ē, indew'am m…ôder. Ta ake t'indebut…õ nu m…õr…ôŇč monu d…Ēs…Ēk din-…õ?¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôy…õks…õ ka Yakuba P…ôk…Ē Mesopotami 
\p  
\v 46 K…Ē Rebeka oloku Siyaka: ¬ęDoru d…õŇčgb…ôf im teta awut aran aHewy. K…Ē Yakuba …õn…õnc…õ w…ôHewy, wan w…ôran w…ôka d…Ēt…Ēf p…ôm…Ē akaŇč…õ, ake indes…Ēy…Ē oŇč doru-…õ?¬Ľ 
\c 28  
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Siyaka ewe Yakuba, k'ontolan…õ k…Ē p…ôt…Ēt, k'osom k…Ē nt…õ: ¬ęTa m…ôn…õnc…õ w…ôran w…ôka KanaŇč.  
\v 2 M…ôy…õf…õ. M…ôk…Ē PadaŇč-Aram, ndena papa ka iya kam. M…ôl…õk di w…ôran awut aran a nc…Ēk'am LabaŇč dac…Ē.  
\v 3 Kanu k…õ k…ôntam mes f…ôp doru m…Ē k…ôpoc'am p…ôt…Ēt, k…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm dokomb…ôra, k…ôs…ĒŇč'am m…ôla nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ m…ôy…Ēn…õ afum alar…ôm m…Ē!  
\v 4 MARIKI p…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm p…ôt…Ēt pa Abraham k…Ē yuruya yam nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ m…ôyi decik…ôra m…Ē, Ňčey'…ôm d…ôwaca p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč Ňči Abraham m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē Siyaka …õsak Yakuba k'…ĒŇčk…Ē PadaŇč-Aram, ndena LabaŇč wan ka Betuh…õl, w…ôAram, w…õnc w…ôrkun w…ôka Rebeka, iya w…ôka Yakuba k…Ē Esayu.  
\v 6 K…Ē Esayu …õn…ôŇčk a Siyaka ontolan…õ Yakuba p…ôt…Ēt, k'oloku k…Ē k…ôk…Ē s…Ē PadaŇč-Aram p…ôk…Ēt…õn w…ôran, mba nt…õ Siyaka onctolan…õ k…Ē m…Ē, …õnasom k…Ē nt…õ: ¬ęTa m…ôn…õnc…õ w…ôran w…ôka KanaŇč de.¬Ľ  
\v 7 Yakuba …õnane moloku ma kas k…Ē k…õr…õ, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē PadaŇč-Aram.  
\v 8 K…Ē Esayu …õn…ôŇčk a mes ma awut aran aka KanaŇč m…õnab…Ēt f…õ papa k…Ēn Siyaka.  
\v 9 K…Ē Esayu …ĒŇčk…Ē ndena S…ômayila, k'…õl…õk di w…ôran pacwe k…Ē Mahalat, wan w…ôran w…ôka S…ômayila wan k'Abraham, w…ôkir…õ ka Nebay…Ēt, k…ôb…õr…õn…õ ka aran aHewy ak…Ē …õnay…Ē m…Ē. 
\s1 K…ôw…õr…ôp ka Yakuba 
\p  
\v 10 K…Ē Yakuba …õy…õf…õ Bersaba k'…ĒŇčk…Ē HaraŇč.  
\v 11 K'…õmb…ôp tofo t…Ēl…Ēma k'endir…õ di, bawo dec d…õnal…ôp…õ k…Ē. K…Ē Yakuba …õl…õk tasar tin ta k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē, k'…õfak…õn…õ pi, k'…õf…ônt…ôr…õ k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē.  
\v 12 K'…õw…õr…ôp, k'…õn…ôŇčk sam…õ s…ôc…ôm…õ d…ônt…Ēf domp da si docgbuŇč…õn…õ k…Ēm m…õl…õk…õ a Kanu m…õcf…ôr…ôŇčk si, m…õcp…õ, moctor.  
\v 13 K…Ē MARIKI …õnc…ôm…õ sam…õ sas…Ēk…Ē darenc. K'oloku: ¬ęIn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI, Kanu k'Abraham papa kam, k…Ē Kanu ka Siyaka. Ant…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ m…Ē, indes…ĒŇč …ôm Ňči m…ôna k…Ē yuruya yam.  
\v 14 Yuruya yam Ňčendela p…ôm…Ē k…ôbof ka d…ônt…Ēf. M…ôndew…Ēk…ôl…ôs d…ôk…ônd…õ dam k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…Ē k…ômeriya, nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē k…Ē nde d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē. Afum a doru f…ôp Ňčande Ňčact…õn…ôr …ôm k…ôtolan…õ p…ôt…Ēt k…Ē yuruya yam.  
\v 15 Ina yati in'osol'am, inde icbum …ôm k…ôca nk…õ o nk…õ m…ôŇčk…Ē m…Ē, indek…õr'am at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ, bawo if…Ēsak …ôm ta intalas tant…õ iŇčlok'…ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē Yakuba entim…õ d…ômere, k'oloku: ¬ęT…Ēl…Ēma MARIKI eyi nn…Ē tofo tant…õ, k'int…Ēnac…ôr…õ ti!¬Ľ  
\v 17 K'enes…õ k'oloku: ¬ęMba tofo t…Ēy…Ē w…õyw…õy! P…ônciyan…õ f…õ d…õ k…Ē k…ôl…Ē ka Kanu, kusuŇčka ka darenc k…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 18 K…Ē Yakuba …õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy, k'…õl…õk tasar t…Ēk…Ē …õnafak…õn…õ domp m…Ē, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr pi, k'oloŇč…ôr pi k…ôroŇč moro m…Ēb…Ēy teta k…ôpus…õ ka pi Kanu.  
\v 19 K…Ē Yakuba ewe tofo tat…Ēk…Ē Betel, mba dare dad…Ēk…Ē d…õnanuŇčk…õn…õ d…Ēy…Ē tewe ta Lus.  
\v 20 K…Ē Yakuba ontola p…ôcloku: ¬ęK…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a Kanu k…ôsol'em k…ôcbum im d…Ēp…Ē nd…õ iŇčk…Ēt m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a k…ôŇčs…ĒŇč im k…ôcom kem k…ôs…Ēm, k…ôs…ĒŇč im s…Ē yamos ib…õrn…õ,  
\v 21 k'ilukus p…ôforu disr…õ nde k…ôl…Ē ka papa w…ôkem-…õ, awa MARIKI endey…Ēn…õ Kanu kem.  
\v 22 Tasar tant…õ inc…ômb…ôr teta k…ôpus…õ ka pi Kanu m…Ē, pendey…Ēn…õ k…ôl…Ē ka Kanu. Indes…ĒŇč …ôm faril…õ fa mp…õ o mp…õ m…ôndek…Ēs…ĒŇč im m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\c 29  
\s1 Yakuba k…ôb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Ras…õl 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yakuba …õy…õf…õ k…ôk…Ēt k…ôk…Ē ka at…Ēf Ňča awut a nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.  
\v 2 K…Ē Yakuba …õn…ôŇčk k…ôl…ômp d…ôndo d…ôkulum, k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…õf…õt y…õf…õt yoloŇčkan…õ mofo maas y…õc…ôm…õ k…ôl…ômp kaŇčk…Ē k…ôs…ôk, bawo k…ôl…ômp kaŇčk…Ē k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yoncmun. Tasar mp…õ p…õnayi k…ôl…ômp d…ôkusu m…Ē p…õnab…õk.  
\v 3 Dif…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl f…ôp y…õncb…ôp…õn…õ. PabiŇčk…ôli tasar pap…Ēk…Ē anaboc k…ôl…ômp d…ôkusu m…Ē, cir k…Ē Ňčkesiya yomun. K…Ē yelip-…õ paluks…õ tasar pap…Ēk…Ē s…Ē k…ôl…ômp d…ôkusu.  
\v 4 K…Ē Yakuba eyif ak…õk y…Ēc…Ēl: ¬ęAw…õnc im aŇča, aka deke Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē akak…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęAka HaraŇč Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē Yakuba eyif Ňča: ¬ęN…ônc…ôr…õ LabaŇč, wan ka Nahor?¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčawos…õ: ¬ę∆źy, s…ônc…ôr…õ k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 6 K'eyif Ňča: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē p…ôyi k…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē akak…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęDaka o daka! Wan k…Ēn w…ôran Ras…õl ender w…ôk…Ē k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…õf…õt y…õf…õt.¬Ľ  
\v 7 K…Ē Yakuba oloku Ňča: ¬ęDec d…Ēs…Ēr…Ēb…õk k…ôr…õsna. T…õm toloŇčka y…Ēc…Ēl t…õntab…ôp f…õ. N…ôs…ĒŇč y…Ēc…Ēl domun, k…Ē n…ôlip-…õ n…ôkek…ôr…õ yi k…ôr…õsna y…Ēk…Ēs…Ēm…ôt.¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęS…ôf…Ētam ti k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl f…ôp y…Ēnt…ĒloŇčkan…õ-…õ, bawo ti t…Ē s…ômbiŇčk…ôli tasar nt…õ aŇčsunc…õ k…ôl…ômp m…Ē, a y…Ēc…Ēl y…õf…õt y…õf…õt yomun.¬Ľ  
\v 9 Yakuba eyi k…ôlok-lok…ôr ak…õk k…Ē Ras…õl …õmb…õr…õ k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…õf…õt y…õf…õt ya kas, bawo Ras…õl w…ôk…õk …õnayi.  
\v 10 Nt…õ Yakuba …õn…ôŇčk Ras…õl wan w…ôran w…ôka LabaŇč k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…õf…õt y…õf…õt ya LabaŇč m…Ē, k'…Ēnc…ĒŇčn…õ k'embiŇčk…ôli tasar tat…Ēk…Ē ancsunc…õ k…ôl…ômp m…Ē. K…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…õf…õt y…õf…õt ya LabaŇč yomun.  
\v 11 K…Ē Yakuba oncup Ras…õl, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôf…ôk, p…ôcbok.  
\v 12 K…Ē Yakuba oloku Ras…õl: ¬ęFum ka papa kam iy…Ēn…õ, wan ka Rebeka iy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ K…Ē Ras…õl …õy…õks…õ k…ôk…Ēloku ti kas LabaŇč.  
\v 13 Nt…õ LabaŇč ene k…ôder ka Yakuba wan ka w…ôkir…õ k…Ēn m…Ē, k'…õy…õks…õ k'ende p…ôsapn…õ Yakuba, k'…õmak…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē. K…Ē LabaŇč eŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē nde k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn, k…Ē Yakuba …Ēl…Ēm…ôr k…Ē mes m…Ēk…Ē m…õnas…Ēt…Ē k…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 14 K…Ē LabaŇč oloku k…Ē: ¬ęKance k…ôsoku p…õs k…Ē: Mecir min m…Ē s…ômpaŇčn…õ!¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba eyi ndena LabaŇč Ňčof Ňčin. 
\s1 K…ôn…õnc…õ ka Yakuba k…ôm…õr…ôŇč 
\p  
\v 15 K…Ē LabaŇč ende p…ôloku Yakuba: ¬ęBawo fum kem m…ôy…Ēn…õ, m…ôf…Ēdeb…ôc'em kif…ôli? M…ôbonc…ôr im daka nd…õ m…ôfaŇč da k…ôway kam m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 16 LabaŇč …õnay…Ē ayec…ôra m…õr…ôŇč: Tewe ta B…Ēmb…Ē b…Ēn t…õnay…Ēn…õ Leya, k…Ē Cayi c…Ēn Ras…õl.  
\v 17 Leya …õnates…õ f…Ēr d…ôk…ôro, mba Ras…õl …õnanaŇčkan…õ k…ôtes…õ.  
\v 18 Ras…õl …õnab…Ēt Yakuba mes. K…Ē Yakuba oloku LabaŇč: ¬ęIndeb…ôc'am meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, teta wan kam w…ôran Cayi: Ras…õl.¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē LabaŇč oloku k…Ē: ¬ęK…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm k…Ē k…ôncep…ôr im t…Ēk…Ē iŇčk…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôcuru m…Ē. M…ôyi nn…Ē nderem!¬Ľ  
\v 20 K…Ē Yakuba …õmb…ôc…õ LabaŇč meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč teta Ras…õl. K…Ē meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč mam…Ēk…Ē meyi, Yakuba d…ôf…Ēr p…ôm…Ē mataka, bawo Ras…õl …õnab…Ēt k…Ē mes.  
\v 21 K…Ē Yakuba ende p…ôloku LabaŇč: ¬ęM…ôs…ĒŇč im w…ôran w…ôkem bawo t…õm tem ta y…õb…ôc telip, ifaŇč k…ôn…õnc…õ k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē LabaŇč ewe aka tofo tat…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčamb…ôp…õn…õ k'omboc k…ôsata.  
\v 23 P…ôndeyi d…Ēf…Ēy, k'…õl…õk wan k…Ēn w…ôran Leya k'eŇčken…õ Yakuba, k…Ē Yakuba …õn…õnc…õ k…Ē.  
\v 24 K…Ē LabaŇč …Ēs…ĒŇč wan k…Ēn w…ôran Leya w…ôcar w…ôran nw…õ ancwe Silpa m…Ē.  
\v 25 Dec dendes…Ēk, k…Ē Yakuba …õn…ôŇčk a baf…Ē Leya as…ĒŇč k…Ē. K'oloku LabaŇč: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē m…ôy…Ē em nt…õ? Baf…Ē teta Ras…õl t'imb…ôc'am? Ta ake t…Ē m…ôntiŇčk…ôr'em-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 26 K…Ē LabaŇč oloku: ¬ęAf…Ēs…ĒŇč s…ôna ndorosu Cayi, ta antas…ĒŇč B…Ēmb…Ē-…õ.  
\v 27 M…ôl…ôp…ôs tataka toluks…ôr k…Ē B…Ēmb…Ē, a s…ôdes…ĒŇč …ôm s…Ē Cayi k…Ē m…ôndewos…õ s…Ē k…ôb…ôc'em tet…Ēn meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč-…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 28 K…Ē Yakuba …Ēy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē, k'…õl…ôp…ôs tataka toluks…ôr k…Ē Leya, k…Ē LabaŇč …Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē s…Ē wan k…Ēn w…ôran Ras…õl.  
\v 29 K…Ē LabaŇč …õl…õk w…ôcar k…Ēn Bilha k'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē Ras…õl.  
\v 30 Ka Yakuba …õn…õnc…õ s…Ē Ras…õl nw…õ …õnab…Ēt k…Ē mes, p…ôtas Leya m…Ē. K'…õmb…ôc…õ s…Ē LabaŇč meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. 
\s1 Awut a Yakuba 
\p  
\v 31 K…Ē MARIKI …õn…ôŇčk a amb…Ēt…ôr f…õ Leya p…ôm…Ē Ras…õl, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč Leya dokomb…ôra. K'osump…ôr Ras…õl dokomb…ôra.  
\v 32 K…Ē Leya …õmb…õk…ôs. K'oŇčkom wan w…ôrkun, k'ewe wan w…ôkak…Ē Ruben. Ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē nn…Ē eyi m…Ē, ¬ęMARIKI …õn…ôŇčk k…ôlap…ôs kem. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, wos im endeb…Ēt…ôr im.¬Ľ  
\v 33 K'…ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôb…õk…ôs, k'oŇčkom s…Ē wan w…ôrkun. K…Ē Leya oloku a: ¬ęMARIKI ene a amb…Ēt…ôr f'em, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč im s…Ē w…ôkaw…õ.¬Ľ K…Ē Leya …Ēs…ĒŇč w…ôkak…Ē tewe ta Simey…ĒŇč.  
\v 34 K…Ē Leya oluks…ôrn…õ k'…õmb…õk…ôs, k'oŇčkom wan w…ôrkun s…Ē. K'oloku: ¬ęTant…õ taŇč, wos im endegb…õk…ôr'em, bawo iŇčkom…õ k…Ē awut arkun maas. It'anas…ĒŇč…õ wan w…ôkak…Ē tewe ta Lewy.¬Ľ  
\v 35 K'…õmb…õk…ôs s…Ē k'oŇčkom wan w…ôrkun s…Ē. K'oloku: ¬ęTant…õ taŇč indekor-koru MARIKI.¬Ľ Ti t…õnawen…õ wan w…ôkak…Ē tewe ta Yuda. K…Ē Leya …õsak oŇč, k…ôkom. 
\c 30  
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ Ras…õl …õn…ôŇčk a eyi f…õ k…ôkom…õ Yakuba m…Ē, k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…õnc w…ôran Leya k…ôraca. K…Ē Ras…õl oloku Yakuba: ¬ęM…ôs…ĒŇč im awut k…Ē p…ôyi f…õ ti-…õ, iŇčfi!¬Ľ  
\v 2 K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Yakuba nn…Ē Ras…õl eyi m…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęInc…ôm…õ d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da Kanu, nk…õ k…ônt…Ēs…ĒŇč …ôm dokomb…ôra m…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 3 K…Ē Ras…õl oloku: ¬ęW…ôcar kem w…ôran Bilha …õw…õ, m…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôs…Ēt…Ē wan m…Ē. Nn…Ē suwu sem s'endekom wan w…ôkak…Ē, p…ôs…ĒŇč'em k…ôy…Ē wan.¬Ľ  
\v 4 K…Ē Ras…õl …Ēs…ĒŇč Yakuba w…ôcar k…Ēn w…ôran Bilha. K…Ē Yakuba …ĒŇčk…Ē k…Ē,  
\v 5 K…Ē Bilha …õmb…õk…ôs, k'oŇčkom…õ Yakuba wan w…ôrkun.  
\v 6 K…Ē Ras…õl oloku: ¬ęKanu k…ômboc'em kiti, k…Ē k…ône s…Ē dim dem, k…ômpoc'em wan w…ôrkun.¬Ľ Ti t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ wan w…ôkak…Ē tewe ta Dan.  
\v 7 K…Ē Bilha w…ôcar ka Ras…õl, …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôb…õk…ôs, k'oŇčkom…õ Yakuba wan w…ôrkun tam…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 8 K…Ē Ras…õl oloku: ¬ęKanu k…ômar im k…ôsim…ôs k…Ē w…õnc im w…ôran Leya, k'intam k…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Ras…õl …Ēs…ĒŇč wan w…ôkak…Ē tewe ta Naftali.  
\v 9 Nt…õ Leya …õn…ôŇčk a …õsak k…ôkom m…Ē, k'…õl…õk w…ôcar k…Ēn Silpa k'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē Yakuba p…ôn…õnc…õ.  
\v 10 K…Ē Silpa w…ôcar ka Leya oŇčkom…õ Yakuba wan w…ôrkun.  
\v 11 K…Ē Leya oloku a: ¬ęP…ôbotu pender!¬Ľ K…Ē Leya …Ēs…ĒŇč wan w…ôkak…Ē tewe ta Kadu.  
\v 12 Silpa w…ôcar ka Leya …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôkom…õ Yakuba wan w…ôrkun tam…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 13 K…Ē Leya oloku: ¬ęMba p…ômb…Ēt im! ∆źy, aran Ňčande Ňčackul'em oŇč a p…ômb…Ēt …ôm.¬Ľ K'…Ēs…ĒŇč wan kak…Ē tewe ta As…õr. 
\p  
\v 14 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma kat…õla k…ônayi, k…Ē Ruben …ĒŇčk…Ē dal…õ. K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôs…Ēt…Ē di yeri yokom y…Ēl…Ēma\f + \fr 30:14 \ft  Yokom ny…õ y…Ēy…Ēn…õ ac…Ēl Ňča dokomb…ôra m…Ē\f*, k'…õŇčk…õr…õ yi iya k…Ēn Leya. K…Ē Ras…õl oloku Leya: ¬ęIl…õts…õn'am, m…ôpoc'em yokom y…Ēl…Ēma ny…õ wan kam …õŇčk…õr'am m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 15 K…Ē Leya oloku Ras…õl: ¬ęP…ônt…ôŇčn…õ f'am nt…õ m…ômbaŇč…ôr im wos im m…Ē, m…õn…õ m…ôs…Ēt…Ē s…Ē yeri ya wan kem?¬Ľ K…Ē Ras…õl oloku Leya: ¬ęAwa! Ndaram ende m…Ēk…Ē f…ônt…ôr…õ, k…ôway ka yeri ya wan kam.¬Ľ  
\v 16 D…Ēf…Ēy dendeb…ôp, nt…õ Yakuba …õy…õf…õ dal…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Leya …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôfayn…õ k…Ē, k'oloku Yakuba: ¬ęNn…Ē nderem m…ônde m…Ēk…Ē f…ônt…ôr…õ, bawo k…ôs…Ēt…Ē kam pibi p…Ēm…Ēk…Ē, m…õn…õ nt…õ is…ôkp…ôr…õ pi yeri y…Ēl…Ēma ya dal…õ ny…õ wan kem …õŇčk…õr…õna m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…õ pibi pap…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Leya.  
\v 17 K…Ē Kanu k…ômbaŇč Leya, k'…õmb…õk…ôs. K'oŇčkom…õ Yakuba wan w…ôrkun w…ôka k…ôcam…ôt.  
\v 18 K…Ē Leya oloku: ¬ęKanu k…ôs…ĒŇč im k…ôway kem. Ina nw…õ il…õk w…ôcar kem w…ôran k'is…ĒŇč k…Ē wos im m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Leya ewe wan w…ôkak…Ē Isakar.  
\v 19 K…Ē Leya endes…Ē p…ôb…õk…ôs, k'oŇčkom…õ Yakuba s…Ē wan w…ôrkun w…ôka cam…ôt-tin.  
\v 20 K…Ē Leya oloku: ¬ęKanu ompoc'em! Tant…õ taŇč, wos im endeyi tofo tin k'ina, bawo iŇčkom…õ k…Ē awut arkun cam…ôt-tin.¬Ľ K…Ē Leya ewe wan w…ôkak…Ē Sabulon.  
\v 21 K…Ē Leya …õmb…õk…ôs, k'oŇčkom wan w…ôran nw…õ …õnas…ĒŇč tewe ta Dina m…Ē.  
\v 22 K…Ē Kanu k…ônde k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ Ras…õl, k…Ē k…ône k…ôtola k…Ēn, k…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē dokomb…ôra.  
\v 23 K…Ē Ras…õl ende p…ôb…õk…ôs, k'oŇčkom wan w…ôrkun. K'oloku: ¬ęKanu k…ôliŇč im malap.¬Ľ  
\v 24 K…Ē Ras…õl ewe wan k…Ēn w…ôkak…Ē Isifu, k'oloku: ¬ęMARIKI p…ôb…õr…õn'em s…Ē wan w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma!¬Ľ 
\s1 Yakuba k…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…Ēn daka 
\p  
\v 25 Nt…õ Ras…õl oŇčkom Isifu m…Ē, k…Ē Yakuba oloku LabaŇč: ¬ęM…ôsak im ilukus nn…Ē nderem, ik…Ē nde at…Ēf Ňčem.  
\v 26 M…ôs…ĒŇč im aran em k'awut em aŇč…õ imb…ôc'am tetaŇčan m…Ē, Ňča Ňč…Ē s…ôndek…Ē, bawo m…ôna yati m…ônc…ôr…õ y…õb…ôc ny…õ imb…ôc'am m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 27 K…Ē LabaŇč oloku Yakuba: ¬ęIfaŇč a m…ôbonc…ôr im k…ôway nk…õ indes…ĒŇč …ôm m…Ē. Canu cem c…ôs…ĒŇč'em k…ôc…ôr…õ a MARIKI ompoc'em p…ôt…Ēt tetam.  
\v 28 M…ôbonc…ôr im k…ôway kam iŇčs…ĒŇč …ôm ki.¬Ľ  
\v 29 K…Ē Yakuba oloku LabaŇč: ¬ęM…ôna yati, m…ônc…ôr…õ k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē imb…ôc'am m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē is…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yam yeyi m…Ē.  
\v 30 Bawo y…Ēc…Ēl yepic y…Ēk…Ē inab…ôp'am m…Ē, y…õla oŇč nd…õk…ôl. K…Ē MARIKI ompoc'am k…ôl…õk d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ imb…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē kam m…Ē, haŇč m…Ēk…Ē. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč ake t…õm t…Ē indeb…ôc…õ afum em-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 31 K…Ē LabaŇč eyif k…Ē: ¬ęAk'indes…ĒŇč …ôm-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba oloku: ¬ęM…ôf…Ēdes…ĒŇč im daka o daka. K…Ē m…ôwos…õ k…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē indelok'…ôm m…Ē, indes…Ēk…õk…ôs y…Ēc…Ēl yam y…õf…õt y…õf…õt, ibum'am s…Ē yi.  
\v 32 M…Ēk…Ē indecep…ôr y…Ēc…Ēl yam y…õf…õt y…õf…õt f…ôp dac…Ē, m…ôdek…Ēc…ômb…ôr Ňčkesiya y…õt…õms…ôr k…Ē y…õc…õmc…õm…ôr f…ôp k…ôs…ôk y…Ēy…Ēn…õ y…Ēp…ĒŇč, y…Ēy…Ēn…õ y…õf…õt, Ňčkesiya ny…õ y…Ēy…Ē lom y…õcaps…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē cir nc…õ c…ônc…õmc…õm…ôr, nc…õ c…ônt…õms…ôr m…Ē. Yay…Ēk…Ē yendey…Ēn…õ k…ôway kem.  
\v 33 Dolompu dem deŇčment…ôr …ôm ti alna, k…Ē m…ôndek…Ēm…Ēm…ôn k…ôway kem-…õ. Mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ē m…ôn…ôŇčk di alna cir dac…Ē ta p…õnt…õms…ôr, ta p…õnc…õmc…õm…ôr k…Ē Ňčkesiya dac…Ē ta p…õncaps…ôr alom m…Ē, m…ôc…ôr…õ a iŇčkiy…ôr …ôm pi.¬Ľ  
\v 34 K…Ē LabaŇč oloku Yakuba: ¬ęAwa! Iwos…õ toloku tam.¬Ľ  
\v 35 Awa, d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ē, LabaŇč …õnc…ômb…ôr mbiyofo ya c…ôgb…õr, y…õc…õmc…õm…ôr, cir c…ôt…õms…ôr k…Ē c…ôc…õmc…õm…ôr cir nc…õ c…ônay…Ē p…ôfer m…Ē f…ôp, Ňčkesiya y…Ēk…Ē y…õnay…Ē alom Ňč…õcaps…ôr m…Ē. K…Ē LabaŇč …õl…õk yi f…ôp, k'…õmb…õr awut …Ēn d…ôwaca.  
\v 36 K'awut …Ēn Ňčamb…Ēl…õn…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yay…Ēk…Ē, k…ôk…Ēt ka mata maas k…Ē Yakuba dac…Ē nw…õ …õnck…õk…ôs s…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl ya LabaŇč m…Ē.  
\v 37 K…Ē Yakuba …õl…õk wara w…õcaŇčk wa t…Ēk maas yeciyan…õ, k'…õnaci wi pol nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôfer pa k…ôt…Ēk powur m…Ē.  
\v 38 K…Ē Yakuba …Ēnd…Ēf…ôt wara waw…Ēk…Ē …õnanaci m…Ē nde y…Ēc…Ēl yoncmun m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ y…õcn…ôŇčk wara waw…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ yorkun y…õcc…õc y…õran k…Ē yender d…ôk…ômun-…õ.  
\v 39 K…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…õnc…õc…õn…õ wara waw…Ēk…Ē k…ôs…ôk, ti t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yockom…ôs mowut ma c…ôgb…õr, m…õt…õms…ôr k…Ē m…õc…õmc…õm…ôr.  
\v 40 Nt…õ Yakuba …õŇčgb…õy meŇčkesiya m…Ē, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr yi f…Ēr ya y…Ēc…Ēl ya LabaŇč kiriŇč ny…õ y…õnay…Ē c…ôgb…õr k…Ē alom Ňč…õcaps…ôr m…Ē, k'…Ēs…Ēt…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl ny…õ …õnac…ômb…ôr taciŇča ta owos…õ y…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl…õn…õ k…Ē ya LabaŇč m…Ē.  
\v 41 K…ôc…õc nk…õ o nk…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yetifi yorkun y…õcfaŇč k…ôc…õc y…õran m…Ē, Yakuba …õncl…õk wara w…Ēn w…õnaci p…ôc…ômb…ôr wi y…Ēc…Ēl f…Ēr kiriŇč d…ôndo yoncmun m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ y…õtam k…ôc…õc…õn…õ, y…õcn…ôŇčk wara waw…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 42 K…Ē Yakuba …õn…ôŇčk a, p…Ēc…Ēl peleŇčki p…õfaŇč k…ôc…õc-…õ, …Ēd…Ēf f…õ pi k…ôra k…Ēn k…ônaci. K…Ē tende t…õl…ôps…ôr oŇč Yakuba k…ôy…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yetifi k…Ē LabaŇč …Ēy…Ē yeleŇčki. 
\s1 Yakuba k…ôy…õks…õ p…ôk…Ē ndena LabaŇč 
\p  
\v 43 K…Ē Yakuba ende p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôka daka w…ôp…ĒŇč. K'…Ēy…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…õf…õt y…õf…õt y…õlar…ôm, acar arkun, acar aran, y…Ēk…Ēm…õ k…Ē s…Ēfale. 
\c 31  
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yakuba ene m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ ma awut a LabaŇč, Ňčacloku: ¬ęYakuba …õl…õk daka da papa kosu f…ôp, di d…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka w…ôka daka dand…õ f…ôp.¬Ľ  
\v 2 K…Ē Yakuba …õŇčgb…õk…ôr…õ a k…ôro ka LabaŇč k…ôyi f…õ s…Ē nn…Ē eyi m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē p…ônayi c…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 3 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Yakuba: ¬ęM…ôlukus at…Ēf Ňča awisi aŇča, d…ôŇčkom dam. Isol'am.¬Ľ  
\v 4 K…Ē Yakuba ewe Ras…õl k…Ē Leya aŇč…õ Ňčanayi dal…õ Ňčack…õk y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēn cir k…Ē Ňčkesiya m…Ē.  
\v 5 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęIŇčgb…õk…ôr…õ a, k…ôro ka papa konu k…ôyi f…õ s…Ē nn…Ē iyi m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē p…ônayi c…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē. Mba Kanu ka papa kem k…ôsol'em.  
\v 6 N…ônc…ôr…õ n…ôna yati a imb…ôc…õ papa konu k…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fem f…ôp.  
\v 7 Mba papa konu …õŇčkaf…ôli-kaf…ôli, k'encep…õ-cep…õ k…ôway kem haŇč w…ôco. Mba Kanu k…ôwos…õ f…õ k…Ē k…ôy'em p…ôl…õc.  
\v 8 P…ônaloku a y…õt…õms…ôr y…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôway kam-…õ, k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl f…ôp y…õnader yockom…ôs awut at…õms…ôr. P…ônaloku s…Ē a ya c…ôgb…õr y…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôway kam-…õ, y…Ēc…Ēl f…ôp k…Ē awut a c…ôgb…õr y…Ē y…õnader yockom…ôs.  
\v 9 Kanu k…ômbaŇč y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēn nn…Ē papa konu eyi m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč im.  
\v 10 T…õm nt…õ y…Ēc…Ēl y…õncfaŇč k…ôc…õc…õn…õ m…Ē, k'iyekti f…Ēr darenc, k'iw…õr…ôp a y…Ēc…Ēl yorkun ny…õ y…õncc…õc y…õran m…Ē, y…õnay…Ē c…ôgb…õr, y…õt…õms…ôr, y…õc…õmc…õm…ôr.  
\v 11 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma Kanu molok'im d…ômere: ‚ÄĻYakuba!‚Äļ K'iwos…õ: ‚ÄĻIn'…õw…õ!‚Äļ  
\v 12 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ molok'im: ‚ÄĻM…ôyekti f…Ēr m…ôm…Ēm…ôn. Y…Ēc…Ēl yorkun f…ôp ny…õ yeyi k…ôc…õc y…õran m…Ē, y…Ēy…Ē c…ôgb…õr k…Ē y…õnt…õms…ôr k…Ē y…õc…õmc…õm…ôr. Bawo in…ôŇčk m…Ēy…Ē m…Ēk…Ē LabaŇč …Ēy'…ôm m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 13 In'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Kanu ka Betel, nde m…ônac…ômb…ôr tasar, k…Ē m…ôb…Ēy pi moro teta k…ôpus m…Ē, nde m…ônad…õrm'im m…Ē. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, m…ôy…õf…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ, m…ôlukus d…ôŇčkom dam.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 14 Ras…õl k…Ē Leya Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęMba s…ôy…Ē s…Ē k…õ nn…Ē k…ôl…Ē ka papa kosu?  
\v 15 Mba …Ēl…Ēm f…õ su oŇč p…ôm…Ē acik…ôra ba, bawo …õncam…ôs su, k'endi p…ôsam posu.  
\v 16 Daka nd…õ Kanu k…ômbaŇč…ôr papa kosu m…Ē f…ôp, dendey…Ēn…õ oŇč dosu k'awut asu. M…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ôlok …ôm m…Ē f…ôp.¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē Yakuba …õy…õf…õ, k'…õnd…ôs awut …Ēn y…Ēk…Ēm…õ k…ôroŇč k…Ē aran …Ēn.  
\v 18 K…Ē Yakuba osol…õ y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēn k…ôk…õk, k…Ē daka d…Ēn f…ôp nd…õ …õnas…Ēt…Ē m…Ē, y…Ēc…Ēl ny…õ …õnas…Ēt…Ē PadaŇč-Aram m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē ndena papa k…Ēn Siyaka, at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč.  
\v 19 K…Ē LabaŇč ende p…ôk…Ē k…ôgb…õt-gb…õt Ňčkesiya y…Ēn. K…Ē Ras…õl eŇčkiy…õ m…õr…ôŇčka ma papa k…Ēn LabaŇč.  
\v 20 K…Ē Yakuba nk…Ēn entiŇčk…ôr LabaŇč w…ôAram nt…õ …Ēnck…Ē nd…Ēr…Ēn, ta elemb…ôrn…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 21 K…Ē Yakuba …õy…õks…õ k…Ē daka d…Ēk…Ē …õnay…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, k'…õy…õf…õ k'empimn…õ k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē, k'…õnt…õf…ôrn…õ m…Ēr…Ē ma Kaladu. 
\p  
\v 22 Tataka ta maas, k'aloku LabaŇč a Yakuba …õy…õks…õ.  
\v 23 K…Ē LabaŇč …õl…õk aw…õnc aŇča k…Ē Ňčanc…ôm…õ Yakuba dar…ôŇč k…ôk…Ēt ka mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē Ňčamb…ôp k…Ē nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Kaladu.  
\v 24 K…Ē Kanu k…ônder LabaŇč w…ôAram d…ômere ma pibi, k…Ē Kanu k…ôloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ k…ôlok-lok…ôr Yakuba.¬Ľ  
\v 25 K…Ē LabaŇč …õmb…ôp Yakuba p…ôc…ômb…ôr abal Ňč…Ēn t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč. K…Ē nk…Ēn s…Ē d…ômn…õ …õnc…ômb…ôr abal Ňč…Ēn k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča t…Ēr…Ē ta Kaladu k…ôroŇč.  
\v 26 K…Ē LabaŇč eyif Yakuba: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē m…ôy…Ē tant…õ-…õ? Ta ake t…Ē m…ôntiŇčk…ôr'em, m…ôckek…ôr…õ awut em aran p…ôm…Ē afum aŇč…õ asump…ôr d…ôk…ôwan m…Ē-…õ?  
\v 27 Ta ake t…Ē m…ôŇčgb…Ēpn…õn…õ k…Ē m…ôy…õks…õ-…õ? M…ôntiŇčk…ôr f'em ba, m…ôy…õks…ôr f'em ba? K'inasak …ôm m…ôk…Ē p…ôbotu disr…õ, pacleŇč…ôs, pacfula pacfer.  
\v 28 M…ôwos…õ f'em k…ôcup awut-s…Ē em arkun k…Ē awut em aran! Tant…õ taŇč m…ômbut amera.  
\v 29 Intam k…ôy…Ē …ôm p…ôl…õc, mba Kanu ka papa kam k…ôlokus'em nendisna: ‚ÄĻM…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ k…ôloku ka Yakuba p…ôl…õc!‚Äļ  
\v 30 Bawo p…ôŇčwon …ôm k…ôk…Ē ndena papa kam, ta ake t…Ē m…ôŇčkiy…õn…õ canu cem-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 31 K…Ē Yakuba oloku LabaŇč: ¬ęIndenanes…ôr-nes…ôr ti k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ a, m…ôndebaŇč…ôr im awut am aran.  
\v 32 Mba m…ôm…Ēm…ôn nw…õ o nw…õ m…ôŇčn…ôŇčk…õ canu cam afum em dac…Ē m…Ē, w…ôkak…Ē eŇčfi! Aw…õnc asu aŇča f…Ēr kiriŇč m…ôm…Ēm…ôn m…ôl…õk mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ēy…Ēn…õ pam m…Ē m…ôkek…ôr…õ.¬Ľ Mba Yakuba …õnac…ôr…õ f…õ a Ras…õl eŇčkiy…ôr LabaŇč canu ca kusuŇčka k…ôŇčan.  
\v 33 K…Ē LabaŇč …õmb…õr…õ abal Ňča Yakuba, k'owur k'…õmb…õr…õ Ňča Leya, k'owur k'…õmb…õr…õ abal Ňča acar aran aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč, …õn…ôŇčk f…õ daka o daka. K…Ē LabaŇč …õmb…õr…õ abal Ňča Ras…õl disr…õ.  
\v 34 Ras…õl p…ôl…õk m…õr…ôŇčka p…ôboc mi d…ônt…Ēf, k'…õl…õk d…Ēc…Ēm nd…õ aŇčn…Ēn…õ y…Ēk…Ēm…õ k…ôroŇč m…Ē k'endeŇč…ôr, k'…õy…õf…õ k'…õnd…õ di k…ôroŇč. K…Ē LabaŇč efen-feni abal disr…õ f…ôp …õn…ôŇčk f…õ m…õr…ôŇčka mm…õ.  
\v 35 K…Ē Ras…õl oloku papa k…Ēn: ¬ęMariki mem, ta p…ôt…õl'am, nt…õ int…Ēy…õf…õn'am m…Ē, t…õnt…ôŇčn…õ iy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē teŇčyi aran t…õm o t…õm m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē LabaŇč …õnt…õn m…õr…ôŇčka mm…õ haŇč, …õn…ôŇčk f…õ.  
\v 36 K…Ē ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õmp…õ Yakuba, k'…õncaŇč LabaŇč k…ôc…Ēp. K…Ē Yakuba …õl…õk moloku, k'oloku: ¬ęDeke il…ôs…ôr-…õ, deke inciya-…õ tant…õ m…ônc…ôm'em dar…ôŇč m…Ē?  
\v 37 Nt…õ m…ôfen-feni ca yem f…ôp m…Ē, ake m…ôn…ôŇčk-…õ ca yam ya dukul…Ē-…õ? M…ôment…ôr im yi f…Ēr ya aw…õnc im aŇča k…Ē aw…õnc …ôm aŇča Ňčab…õr…õ su dac…Ē ina k…Ē m…ôna.  
\v 38 Meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē iyi nn…Ē ndaram. Mba aŇčkesiya Ňčam Ňčin, wir wan win w…õl…õc…õ f…õ kor, is…Ēm…õ f'am aŇčkesiya y…Ēc…Ēl yam dac…Ē.  
\v 39 IŇčk…õr…õ f'am p…Ēc…Ēl pefi, in'…õnasar…õ teta yi. M…ôncwer im k…ôs…ĒŇč ka k…ôway k…Ē ny…õ anckiy…ôr im p…ôwaŇčk…ôra k…Ē pibi m…Ē.  
\v 40 Inayi nn…Ē nne y…Ēcc…Ēf im p…ôwaŇčk…ôra, k…ôfe k…ôcsut im pibi, mere m…Ēb…Ēl…õn'em.  
\v 41 T…Ēs…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč nt…õ iyi nn…Ē ndaram m…Ē. Icb…ôc'am teta awut am aran meren w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ, k…Ē meren mm…õ cam…ôt-tin, ta y…Ēc…Ēl yam y…õf…õt y…õf…õt. Mba m…ônacep…õ-cep…õ k…ôway kem haŇč w…ôco.  
\v 42 P…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ Kanu ka papa kem Abraham, Kanu K…ôw…õy-w…õy ka Siyaka k…ôsol'em-…õ, k…Ē tant…õ t…Ē m…ôsak im ilukus waca w…Ēs…Ēk…ôr. Kanu k…ôn…ôŇčk malap mem, k…Ē k…ôl…Ēl…ôs nk…õ inal…Ēl…ôs waca m…Ē, ti t…Ē k…ômboc…õsa su nendisna kiti.¬Ľ  
\v 43 K…Ē LabaŇč oloku Yakuba: ¬ęAwut arkun akaŇč…õ, awut aran akaŇč…õ k…ôb…ôp y…Ēc…Ēl yay…õ f…ôp yemi y…Ē. C…ôke c'intam m…Ēk…Ē k…ôy…Ēn…õ awut em aran k…Ē awut aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčkom m…Ē-…õ?  
\v 44 Nd…õk…ôl m…ôder s…ôsek danapa f…Ēr ya fum w…ôl…Ēma kiriŇč ina k…Ē m…ôna.¬Ľ  
\v 45 K…Ē Yakuba …õl…õk tasar tin, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr pi cos teta k…ôpus ka pi.  
\v 46 K…Ē Yakuba oloku aw…õnc aŇča: ¬ęN…ôw…õt…ôs masar!¬Ľ K'aw…õnc aŇča Ňčaw…õt…ôs masar k…Ē Ňčamboc t…õp…õsa. K…Ē Ňčand…õ t…õp…õsa pap…Ēk…Ē k…ôroŇč k…Ē Ňčandi yeri.  
\v 47 K…Ē LabaŇč ewe t…õp…õsa pap…Ēk…Ē ¬ęYekar Sahaduta,¬Ľ \f + \fr 31:47 \ft  It…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē c…ôAram c…Ē ¬ęT…õp…õsa pa sede¬Ľ\f* k…Ē Yakuba nk…Ēn ewe pi ¬ęKaled.¬Ľ\f + \fr 31:47 \fq Kaled\ft  = C…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęT…õp…õsa pa sede¬Ľ \f* 
\v 48 K…Ē LabaŇč oloku: ¬ęT…õp…õsa pamp…õ peyi su m…Ēk…Ē dac…Ē.¬Ľ Ti t…Ē as…ĒŇč…õ pi tewe ta Kaled.  
\v 49 T…õp…õsa pap…Ēk…Ē p'aŇčwe s…Ē Mispe, bawo LabaŇč …õnaloku: ¬ęMARIKI k…ôgb…õk…ôr…õ su ina k…Ē m…ôna k…Ē s…ôndes…Ēl…ôr…õn…õ.  
\v 50 K…Ē m…ônt…Ēr…ôs awut em aran-…õ, k…Ē m…ôl…õk s…Ē aran al…Ēma-…õ, m…ôc…ôr…õ a baf…Ē fum eyi su dac…Ē, mba Kanu yati.¬Ľ  
\v 51 K…Ē LabaŇč oloku: ¬ęT…õp…õsa p…õmp…õ, k…Ē tasar t…Ēk…Ē inc…ômb…ôr ina k…Ē m…ôna dac…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 52 T…õp…õsa pa masar pamp…õ k…Ē tasar p…õc…ômb…ôr cos pamp…õ peyi su dac…Ē k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ tes, a if…Ēs…Ēcep…ôr t…õp…õsa pamp…õ k…ôk…ĒcaŇč…ôrn'am k…ôy…Ē ka p…ôl…õc, m…ôna s…Ē ta m…ôcep…ôr t…õp…õsa pamp…õ k…Ē tasar pamp…õ k…ôk…ĒcaŇč…ôrn'em k…ôk…Ēy…Ē p…ôl…õc.¬Ľ  
\v 53 K…Ē LabaŇč oloku: ¬ęKanu ka Abraham k…Ē Nahor, k…Ē Kanu ka kas k…ôŇčan k…ôyi su dac…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba …õnd…õrm…õ Kanu K…ôw…õy-w…õy ka papa k…Ēn Siyaka.  
\v 54 K…Ē Yakuba oloŇčn…õ t…Ēr…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē k…ôroŇč, k'ewe aw…õnc aŇča k…ôdedi yeri yay…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē Ňčandi yeri yay…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Ňčandir…õ t…Ēr…Ē pap…Ēk…Ē k…ôroŇč. 
\c 32  
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē LabaŇč …õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy, k'oncup awut-s…Ē …Ēn arkun k'aran, k'ontolan…õ Ňča, k'osump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē k…ôlukus ka nde nd…Ēr…Ēn. 
\s1 Yakuba k…ôlomp…ôsn…õ k…Ēn k…ôb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Esayu 
\p  
\v 2 K…Ē Yakuba s…Ē …õnc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēn dar…ôŇč, k…Ē m…õl…õke a Kanu Ňčanc…õps…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč.  
\v 3 Yakuba enden…ôŇčk mi, k'oloku: ¬ęAfan Ňča Kanu Ňč…Ē!¬Ľ K'…Ēs…ĒŇč tofo tat…Ēk…Ē tewe ta Mahanayim\f + \fr 32:3 \fq Mahanayim\ft  = C…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęfan m…õr…ôŇč¬Ľ \f*. 
\p  
\v 4 Yakuba p…ôyi tadar…ôŇč k'osom nda w…õnc Esayu nw…õ …õnayi kulum ka Ed…Ēm m…Ē, at…Ēf Ňča Sehir.  
\v 5 K…Ē Yakuba osom Ňča nt…õ: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēloku mariki w…õnc im Esayu: ‚ÄĻA w…ôcar kam Yakuba-…õ, a iŇčk…Ē iwon nda LabaŇč haŇč.  
\v 6 Iy…Ē c…ôna, s…Ēfale, Ňčkesiya, cir, acar arkun k…Ē aran. Ti t'isom'am nn…Ē mariki w…õnc im eyi m…Ē, p…ôctam k…ôwos…õ ib…õr…õ.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 7 K'asom Ňčaluks…ôrn…õ nn…Ē Yakuba eyi m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęS…ôŇčk…Ē nda w…õnc …ôm Esayu, nk…Ēn s…Ē k…ôlomp…ôsn…õ k'…õnd…õ k…ôdeb…ôp …ôm, k…Ē afum 400.¬Ľ  
\v 8 K'ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…Ēnt…Ēf…ônt…ôr…õ Yakuba, k…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôsump…ôr k…Ē. K'eyer afum ak…Ē Ňčanasol m…Ē c…ôgba m…õr…ôŇč, k…ôb…ôp Ňčkesiya, cir, c…ôna haŇč y…Ēk…Ēm…õ.  
\v 9 K…Ē Yakuba oloku: ¬ęK…Ē Esayu …õntam afum a k…ôgba kin-…õ, a k…Ē ŇčaŇčy…õks…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 10 K…Ē Yakuba oloku: ¬ęKanu ka papa kem Abraham, Kanu ka papa kem Siyaka, MARIKI nw…õ olok'im: ‚ÄĻM…ôlukus at…Ēf Ňčam nde aŇčkom …ôm m…Ē, indey…Ēn'am p…ôt…Ēt!‚Äļ  
\v 11 If…õt…ôr layidi k…Ē p…ôt…Ēt mp…õ m…ôŇčk…õr'em m…Ē, ina w…ôcar kam. Bawo nt…õ inccep…ôr Yurd…õn yay…õ m…Ē, togbo tem gb…ôc…ôr…ôm t'inat…Ēmp…ôr, nd…õk…ôl oŇč iyer afum em c…ôgba m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 12 Il…õts…õn'am m…ôbaŇč im, w…õnc im Esayu d…ôwaca! Bawo iŇčnes…õ ta p…ôdesut im, k…Ē iya ka awut em.  
\v 13 K…Ē m…ôna Kanu m…ônalok'im: ‚ÄĻIndey'…ôm p…ôt…Ēt, indey…Ē yuruya yam Ňčala p…ôm…Ē as…ônc Ňča d…ôk…ôba, nŇč…õ ant…Ētam k…ôl…Ēm m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 14 Dif…Ē Yakuba …õnacep…ôr…õn…õ pibi. K'…õy…õk-y…õk daka d…Ēn d…Ēk…Ē …õnak…õr…õ m…Ē dac…Ē k…ôk…Ēpoc…õ w…õnc Esayu:  
\v 15 Cir masar m…õr…ôŇč (200), mbiyofo w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20), Ňčkesiya y…õran masar m…õr…ôŇč (200) k…Ē yorkun w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20),  
\v 16 k…Ē y…Ēk…Ēm…õ y…õran w…ôco maas (30) k…Ē awut ayi ak…Ē y…õncm…õs…ôr m…Ē, c…ôna c…ôran w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40), mura w…ôco (10), s…Ēfale s…ôran w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) k…Ē s…ôrkun w…ôco (10).  
\v 17 K…Ē Yakuba …Ēs…ĒŇč y…Ēc…Ēl yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp fa yi k…Ē dokom da yi acar …Ēn, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôy'im kiriŇč, n…ôsol…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yay…õ dokom dokom, n…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ yi k…Ē y…Ēk…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 18 K'osom w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē: ¬ęK…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē w…õnc im Esayu a p…ôyif …ôm: ‚ÄĻAn'…Ē m…ôy…Ēn…õ? Deke m…ôŇčk…Ē-…õ? An'…Ēy…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yay…õ m…ôsol…õ m…Ē-…õ?‚Äļ  
\v 19 M…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻYa w…ôcar kam Yakuba y…Ē, k…ôpoc…õ k…Ē nk…õ …Ēs…ĒŇč im a iken…õ mariki mem Esayu m…Ē. Mba nk…Ēn …Ēf…Ē w…ôk…Ē ender im tadar…ôŇč m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 20 K'osom s…Ē k…ôsom kin kaŇčk…Ē, asol…õ y…Ēc…Ēl ya m…õr…ôŇč, ya maas k…ôb…ôp ka alp…ôs ak…Ē Ňčanayi tadar…ôŇč Ňčasol…õ y…Ēc…Ēl m…Ē: ¬ęTat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēloku Esayu k…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēb…ôp…õn…õ-…õ.  
\v 21 N…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻW…ôcar kam Yakuba ender su w…ôk…Ē tadar…ôŇč.‚Äļ¬Ľ Bawo Yakuba …õnaloku: ¬ęK…ôpoc…õ kaŇčk…õ k…ôy'im kiriŇč m…Ē, ik'iŇčk…Ētor-tor…õn…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc, a s…ôden…ôŇčk…õn…õ f…Ēr disr…õ. T…Ēl…Ēma endek…Ēsel…õn'em belbel.¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē yopoc…õ yay…Ēk…Ē yeyi k…Ē kiriŇč, k'encep…ôr…õn…õ pibi pap…Ēk…Ē d…ôndo d…ôkulum. 
\s1 Yakuba k…ôsim…ôs k…Ēn k…Ē Kanu 
\p  
\v 23 K…Ē Yakuba …õy…õf…õ pibi pap…Ēk…Ē, k'…õl…õk aran …Ēn m…õr…ôŇč, amar…ôs aran …Ēn m…õr…ôŇč k'awut …Ēn w…ôco k…Ē pin, k'…õncal…õn…õ Ňča d…ôŇčgb…ôl da Yab…Ēk.  
\v 24 Nt…õ Yakuba …õl…õk aran …Ēn, k'…õncal…õn…õ Ňča d…ôŇčgb…ôl k…Ē daka d…Ēk…Ē …õnay…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 25 K…Ē Yakuba eyi di sona. P…ôndebiy…õ, k…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma …õy…õf…õ k…ôsim…ôs k…Ē Yakuba haŇč d…Ēs…Ēka.  
\v 26 Nt…õ w…ôsims…õn…õ k…Ēn …õn…ôŇčk, eyi f…õ k…ôtam k…Ē m…Ē, k'osut k…Ē nn…Ē d…ôt…Ēk…Ēc. K…Ē t…Ēk…Ēc ta Yakuba towur p…ôcsim…ôs k…Ē fum w…ôkak…Ē.  
\v 27 K…Ē fum w…ôkak…Ē oloku: ¬ęM…ôsak im ik…Ē, bawo p…ôyi k…ôy…Ē panpan.¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba oloku k…Ē: ¬ęIf…Ēsak …ôm m…ôk…Ē ta m…ôntolan'em-…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 28 K…Ē fum w…ôkak…Ē eyif Yakuba: ¬ęC…ôke c'aŇčw'am-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba oloku: ¬ęYakuba y'aŇčw'em.¬Ľ  
\v 29 K…Ē fum w…ôkak…Ē oloku k…Ē s…Ē: ¬ęYakuba y…Ēf…Ēs…Ēy…Ēn…õ tewe tam, Yisrayel\f + \fr 32:29 \fq Yisrayel\ft  = C…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęk…ôsim…ôs k…Ē Kanu¬Ľ \f* Ňč'ande pacw'am, bawo m…ôsim…ôs k…Ē Kanu k…Ē afum, k…Ē m…ôntam Ňča.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 30 K…Ē Yakuba eyif fum w…ôkak…Ē: ¬ęIl…õts…õn'am m…ôbonc…ôr im tewe tam.¬Ľ K…Ē fum nw…õ eyif k…Ē: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē m…ôfaŇč…õ k…ôc…ôr…õn…õ tewe tem-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē fum nw…õ ontolan…õ Yakuba d…ôndo.  
\v 31 K…Ē Yakuba …Ēs…ĒŇč tofo tat…Ēk…Ē tewe ta Peniy…õl\f + \fr 32:31 \fq Peniy…õl\ft  = C…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęk…ôro ka Kanu¬Ľ\f*, bawo nk…Ēn olokun…õ: ¬ęIn…ôŇčk Kanu s…ôgb…ôtn…õn…õ, k'int…Ēfi.¬Ľ  
\v 32 Dec d…õncp…õ a p…ôccep…ôr Peniy…õl. Yakuba p…ôctor…ôr t…Ēk…Ēc t…Ēn.  
\v 33 Ti t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ awut a Yisrayel Ňčant…Ēs…Ēm ab…ônta Ňča d…ôt…Ēk…Ēc m…Ē, bawo ab…ônta Ňča d…ôt…Ēk…Ēc Ňč…Ē Kanu k…ônasut Yakuba, nde k…ôb…õnt ka d…ôk…ôc…ôk k…Ē k…ôb…õnt ka d…ôkumunt y…õmb…ôp…õn…õ m…Ē. 
\c 33  
\s1 Yakuba k…ôb…ôp…õn…õ k…ôŇčan k…Ē Esayu 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yakuba eyekti k…ôro k'…õn…ôŇčk Esayu p…ôcder p…ôs…Ēl…õ afum tasar tin (100). K…Ē Yakuba eyer awut Leya, Ras…õl, k…Ē acar aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē.  
\v 2 K…Ē Yakuba …õnc…ômb…ôr aran …Ēn acar kiriŇč, k'awut aŇčan Ňčanc…Ēnc Ňča, k…Ē Leya …õnc…õk k'awut …Ēn Ňčayi k…Ē dar…ôŇč, k…Ē Ras…õl …õnc…ôm…õ k…Ē wan k…Ēn Isifu eyi k…Ē dar…ôŇč.  
\v 3 K…Ē nk…Ēn yati encep…ôr Ňča f…Ēr kiriŇč, k'ontontn…õn…õ Esayu d…ônt…Ēf cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, haŇč k'…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē.  
\v 4 K…Ē Esayu …õy…õks…õ k…ôk…Ēb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Yakuba w…õnc, k'…õsapn…õ k…Ē, k'…õn…õps…ôrn…õ k…Ē d…ôkilim, k'oncup k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ f…ôp faŇčan k…ôbok.  
\v 5 K…Ē Esayu eyekti k…ôro, k'…õn…ôŇčk aran k…Ē awut, k'eyif: ¬ęAre Ňč…Ē akaŇč…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba oloku k…Ē: ¬ęAwut akaŇč…õ Ňč…Ē Kanu k…ônamar im k…ôs…Ēt…Ē n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr d…Ēn disr…õ, ina w…ôcar kam.¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē aran …Ēn acar Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ Esayu, k…Ē awut aŇčan, k…Ē Ňčantontn…õn…õ k…Ē.  
\v 7 K…Ē Leya …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē s…Ē k…Ē awut …Ēn, k…Ē Ňča s…Ē Ňčantontn…õn…õ k…Ē, k…Ē Isifu k…Ē Ras…õl Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčantontn…õn…õ k…Ē.  
\v 8 K…Ē Esayu eyif k…Ē: ¬ęAke m…ôndey…Ēn…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yay…õ s…ôncep…ôr-cep…ôr m…Ē?¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba oloku k…Ē: ¬ęK…ôt…ôŇčn…õ ka m…ôna mariki mem k'inafaŇč. Ti t'inac…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm yi.¬Ľ  
\v 9 K…Ē Esayu oloku Yakuba: ¬ęY…õlar im ina w…õnc im, m…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ yay…õ y…Ēy…Ēn…õ yam.¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē Yakuba oloku Esayu: ¬ęAla. Il…õts…õn'am, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a is…Ēt…ôr …ôm k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ, m…ôwos…õ m…ôbaŇč k…ôpoc…õ kem. Ti t'im…Ēm…ôn…õ k…ôro kam p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē aŇčm…Ēm…ôn k…ôro ka Kanu m…Ē, k…Ē m…ôsel…õn'em belbel.  
\v 11 M…ôbaŇč k…ôpoc…õ kem nk…õ is…ĒŇč …ôm m…Ē, bawo Kanu k…ômar im k'is…Ēt…Ē daka d…Ēk…Ē ifaŇč m…Ē f…ôp.¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba …õnc…ôm…õn…õ ti Esayu dar…ôŇč haŇč k…Ē w…ôkak…Ē owos…õ k…ôbaŇč ka k…ôpoc…õ kaŇčk…Ē.  
\v 12 K…Ē Esayu oloku: ¬ęPaŇčk…Ēn, pasoln…õ d…Ēp…Ē, in'endey'…ôm kiriŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 13 K…Ē Yakuba oloku: ¬ęMariki mem, m…ônc…ôr…õ a awut Ňčancuca k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ, k'isol…õ s…Ē mir mowut k…Ē mana m…õm…õs…õ. K'ay…Ē yi y…Ēk…Ēt p…ôp…ĒŇč d…Ēs…Ēk din-…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yowut f…ôp yeŇčfi.  
\v 14 Mariki mem m…ôy'im kiriŇč, indey'…ôm tadar…ôŇč, p…ôpic-p…ôpic isur…õn…õ y…Ēc…Ēl k'awut p…Ēk…Ēt, haŇč ib…õr…õ ndena w…õnc im nde at…Ēf Ňča Sehir.¬Ľ  
\v 15 K…Ē Esayu oloku: ¬ęIsak…ôr'am afum em al…Ēma ak…Ē isol…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba eyif Esayu: ¬ęAk'indey…Ēn…õ Ňča-…õ? T…õfaŇč ta ina, is…Ēt…Ē k…ôŇčaŇčn…õ nn…Ē m…ôna mariki mem meyi m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 16 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ē Esayu …õl…õk d…Ēp…Ē k…ôlukus ka Sehir. 
\s1 Yakuba k…ônd…õ k…Ēn S…ôk…õm k…ôs…ôk 
\p  
\v 17 K…Ē Yakuba …ĒŇčk…Ē dare da Suk…Ēt. K'…Ēl…Ē k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn k'…Ēl…Ēn…õ y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēn Ňčgbancan. Ti t'as…ĒŇč…õ tofo tat…Ēk…Ē tewe ta ¬ęSuk…Ēt\f + \fr 33:17 \fq Suk…Ēt\ft  = C…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęŇčgbancan¬Ľ \f*¬Ľ.  
\v 18 K…Ē Yakuba …õmb…õr…õ k…ôtamn…õ disr…õ dare da S…ôk…õm, at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč. K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôc…ômb…ôr…ôs dare k…ôs…ôk k…ôb…õr…õ k…Ēn k…ôy…õf…õ ka PadaŇč-Aram.  
\v 19 K'…õway awut a Ham…Ēr arkun d…ôwaca, papa ka S…ôk…õm, tofok…ôl ta ant…Ēf nde …õnac…ômb…ôr abal m…Ē. ∆źnaway di m…õnc…ômb…ôl\f + \fr 33:19 \ft  C…ôHeb…ôre ¬ękesita¬Ľ = k…ôway ka teŇčkesiya k…ônayi t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē \f* tasar tin (100).  
\v 20 K…Ē Yakuba …õnc…ômb…ôr di tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu, k'ewe tofo tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęEl-Elohe-Yisrayel\f + \fr 33:20 \fq El-Elohe-Yisrayel\ft  = C…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęEl, Kanu ka Yisrayel¬Ľ \f*¬Ľ. 
\c 34  
\s1 Simey…ĒŇč k…Ē Lewy k…ôluks…õ ay…õk Ňča w…ôkir…õ k…ôŇčan Dina nw…õ analap…ôs m…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 Dina, wan w…ôran nw…õ Leya …õnakom…õ Yakuba m…Ē, …õy…õf…õ k…ôk…Ēn…ôŇčk awut aran a d…Ēt…Ēf.  
\v 2 S…ôk…õm, wan ka Ham…Ēr w…ôHewy w…ôb…õ w…ôka d…Ēt…Ēf, …õn…ôŇčk k…Ē, k'…õmbaŇč k…Ē, k'omboc…ôrn…õ k…Ē, k'…õlap…ôs k…Ē.  
\v 3 K…Ē S…ôk…õm esekt…ôrn…õ teta Dina wan w…ôran ka Yakuba, haŇč d…ômoloku m…Ēn k'…õs…õp k…ôs…Ēt…Ē ka k…ôb…Ēt…ôr ka Dina.  
\v 4 K…Ē S…ôk…õm oloku papa k…Ēn Ham…Ēr: ¬ęM…ôs…ĒŇč im w…ôyec…ôra w…ôkaw…õ p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôran kem w…ôn…õnc…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē Yakuba ende p…ôc…ôr…õ a S…ôk…õm …õnc…ôr…õ wan k…Ēn Dina d…õran. Mba nt…õ awut a Yakuba arkun Ňčanayi dal…õ k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē Yakuba …õncaŇčk…õ ti haŇč k…Ē Ňčander k…ôy…õf…õ dal…õ.  
\v 6 K…Ē Ham…Ēr papa ka S…ôk…õm …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôlok-lok…ôr Yakuba.  
\v 7 K…Ē awut a Yakuba Ňčander k…ôy…õf…õ dal…õ. Nt…õ Ňčane moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē mosump…ôr Ňča. K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Ňča, bawo S…ôk…õm …õnay…Ē t…Ēy…Ē nt…õ p…ônat…Ēmar paŇčaŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē Yisrayel m…Ē: K…ôkiy…õ k…ôc…ôr…õ Dina wan ka Yakuba d…õran, ta Ňčay…Ēn…õ akin ayi-…õ.  
\v 8 K…Ē Ham…Ēr oloku Ňča nt…õ: ¬ęWan kem S…ôk…õm …õfaŇč k…ôfaŇč d…ôm w…ôkir…õ konu Dina k…ôn…õnc…õ, n…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…Ē p…ôn…õnc…õ, il…õts…õn…õ nu.  
\v 9 Antam k…ôkot…ôr…õn…õ pacn…õnc…õn…õn…õ. N…ôde n…ôcs…ĒŇč su awut anu aran, n…ôcl…õk awut asu aran.  
\v 10 N…ôndend…õ k…Ē s…ôna, at…Ēf Ňčendeyi nu d…ôwaca p…ôm…Ē s…ôna, n…ôyi d…õ, n…ôccam…ôs, n…ôt…õn s…Ē d…õ nt…Ēf.¬Ľ  
\v 11 K…Ē S…ôk…õm oloku papa k…Ē aw…õnc a Dina: ¬ęK'is…Ēt…ôr nu k…ôwos…õ-…õ, iŇčs…ĒŇč nu mp…õ o mp…õ n…ôŇčwer im m…Ē.  
\v 12 N…ôwer im k…ôfac k…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē yopoc…õ y…õlar…ôm. IŇčs…ĒŇč nu yi. Mba n…ôs…ĒŇč w…ôyec…ôra w…ôkaw…õ S…ôk…õm p…ôn…õnc…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 13 K…Ē awut a Yakuba arkun ŇčantiŇčk…ôr S…ôk…õm k…Ē kas bawo S…ôk…õm …õnakiy…õ k…ôc…ôr…õ ka w…ôkir…õ k…ôŇčan d…õran.  
\v 14 K…Ē awut a Yakuba Ňčaloku S…ôk…õm k…Ē kas: ¬ęP…ôncuca su k…ôs…ĒŇč w…ôkir…õ kosu, fum nw…õ ant…Ēk…ônc m…Ē, bawo tendey…Ēn…õ k…ôlap…ôs kosu.  
\v 15 K…Ē s…ôndewos…õ t…õfaŇč tonu-…õ, m…õn…õ n…ôna s…Ē n…ôwos…õ k…ôyi p…ôm…Ē s…ôna, ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē arkun aŇč…õ Ňčayi nu dac…Ē m…Ē f…ôp pak…ônc Ňča.  
\v 16 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē s…ôŇčwos…õ k…ôcl…õk awut anu aran s…ôn…õnc…õ, n…ôna s…Ē d…ômn…õ n…ôcl…õk akosu n…ôcn…õnc…õ. S…ônd…õ nn…Ē k…Ē n…ôna pay…Ēn…õ s…Ē afum akin ayi.  
\v 17 Mba k…Ē n…ônt…Ētam k…ône t…Ēk…Ē s…ôloku a pak…ônc nu m…Ē, s…ôŇčl…õk wan kosu Dina, s…ôk…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 18 Ham…Ēr k…Ē wan k…Ēn S…ôk…õm Ňčawos…õ moloku mam…Ēk…Ē, k…ôwos…õ a pak…ônc Ňča.  
\v 19 K…Ē wan w…ôrkun nw…õ oncop t…Ēy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē, bawo …õnab…Ēt…ôr Dina haŇč p…ôcep…ôr…ôr. Nk…Ēn S…ôk…õm s…Ē, anab…Ēt…ôr k…Ē nde ndaraŇčan patas aka di f…ôp.  
\v 20 Ham…Ēr k…Ē S…ôk…õm ŇčaŇčk…Ē nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da dare daŇčan, k…Ē Ňčaloku afum a dare:  
\v 21 ¬ęAfum akaŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēk…õ su b…ôk…ôc. Ňäawos…õ k…ônd…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ Ňčaccam…ôs, at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ Ňč…Ēw…Ēk…ôl Ňča. Ande pacl…õk…ôr…õn…õ aran k…Ē Ňča.  
\v 22 Mba afum akaŇč…õ k…ôwos…õ k…ôŇčan k…ônd…õ k…Ē s…ôna, pay…Ēn…õ akin ayi, m…õn…õ pawos…õ arkun aŇč…õ Ňčayi su dac…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, pak…ônc Ňča p…ôm…Ē Ňča.  
\v 23 Y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan k…Ē ca yaŇčan f…ôp y…Ēf…Ēdey…Ēn…õ yosu ba? Pawos…õ t…õfaŇč taŇčan gb…ôc…ôr…ôm, Ňčayi su d…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 24 Ak…Ē Ňčanak…Ē d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da dare daŇčan m…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčanc…ôŇčk…ôl Ham…Ēr k…Ē wan k…Ēn S…ôk…õm. Arkun ak…Ē Ňčanader d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da dare daŇčan d…ôk…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl m…Ē f…ôp, k'aŇčk…ônc Ňča.  
\v 25 Tataka ta maas ta k…ôk…ônc k…ôŇčan, ak…ônc Ňčayi k…ôcun…õn…õ, k…Ē awut a Yakuba m…õr…ôŇč, Simey…ĒŇč k…Ē Lewy aw…õnc arkun a Dina, Ňčal…õk…ôs sakma s…ôŇčan k…Ē Ňčander Ňčacop d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da dare daŇčan, nde afum a di Ňčanac…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôyi p…ôforu disr…õ m…Ē. Simey…ĒŇč k…Ē Lewy Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ arkun a d…Ēt…Ēf k…ôdif…ôt haŇč k…Ē Ňčalip Ňča f…ôp.  
\v 26 K…Ē Ňčandif…õn…õ s…Ē Ham…Ēr k…Ē S…ôk…õm sakma s…ôŇčan, k…Ē Ňčal…õk w…ôkir…õ k…ôŇčan Dina ndena S…ôk…õm k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē.  
\v 27 K'awut a Yakuba Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ s…Ē afi, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkiy…ôr aka dare bawo m…õt…õl…õ m…õnayi Ňča k…ôlap…ôs ka w…ôkir…õ k…ôŇčan Dina.  
\v 28 K…Ē Ňčal…õk Ňčkesiya, cir, c…ôna, s…Ēfale, y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēk…Ē y…õnayi dare disr…õ k…Ē d…ôkulum m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 29 K…Ē awut a Yakuba Ňčaw…õt…ôs ca ya afi, awut aŇčan, aran aŇčan, k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē Ňčanab…ôp nda S…ôk…õm k…Ē Ham…Ēr m…Ē f…ôp k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ.  
\v 30 K…Ē Yakuba oloku Simey…ĒŇč k…Ē Lewy: ¬ęN…ôy…Ē em p…ôl…õc tetonu tendes…ĒŇč…õ aka KanaŇč k…Ē aka Perisi Ňčadeter im! N…ônc…ôr…õ a s…ômpic…õ, k…ôb…õr…õn…õ k…Ē Ňčander k…ôdesut…õn…õ k…Ē ina, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē Ňčandesut im Ňčal…ôs…ôr afum em.¬Ľ  
\v 31 K…Ē awut a Yakuba Ňčaloku kas k…ôŇčan: ¬ęS…ôndewos…õ S…ôk…õm p…ôy…Ē w…ôkir…õ kosu p…ôm…Ē w…ôran w…ôyi yamayama ba?¬Ľ 
\c 35  
\s1 Yakuba k…ôy…õf…õ S…ôk…õm p…ôk…Ē Betel 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku Yakuba: ¬ęM…ôy…õf…õ m…ôp…õ m…ôk…Ē m…ônd…õ Betel, m…ôlomp…ôs di tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu nk…õ k…ônawur…ôr …ôm, nt…õ m…ônay…õks…ôr w…õnc …ôm Esayu m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 2 K…Ē Yakuba oloku afum …Ēn, k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčanayi k…Ē nk…Ēn m…Ē: ¬ęN…ôwur…õ nu dac…Ē canu c…ôcik…ôra. N…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ, n…ôs…ôkp…ôr y…õb…õrn…õ.  
\v 3 K…ôy…õf…õ k'ander, pap…õrn…õ Betel. D…ôndo iŇčk…Ēc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu nk…õ k…ônalok-lok…ôr im d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ inayi p…ôcuca disr…õ, a k…Ē k…ôsol'em t…õm nt…õ inayi d…Ēp…Ē ick…Ē decik…ôra m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 4 K…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč Yakuba canu c…ôcik…ôra nc…õ c…ônayi Ňča d…ôwaca m…Ē f…ôp, k…ôb…ôp ya d…ôl…ôŇč…ôs yaŇčan. K…Ē Yakuba …õm…ôt yi nde k…ôt…Ēk k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôyi S…ôk…õm k…ôs…ôk m…Ē.  
\v 5 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē. K…Ē ayek-yek Ňča Kanu Ňč…õŇčgb…ôp…ôrn…õ aka s…ôdare s…ôk…ôs…ôk f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčant…Ētam k…ôc…ôm…õ awut a Yakuba dar…ôŇč. 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē Yakuba Ňčamb…õr…õ k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčanac…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč m…Ē f…ôp, k…ôk…Ē ka Lus, ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē dare da Betel, at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč.  
\v 7 K'…õnc…ômb…ôr di tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu, k'ewe tofo tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęEl-Betel¬Ľ, bawo dif…Ē Kanu k…ônawur…ôr k…Ē t…õm nt…õ …õnay…õks…ôr w…õnc m…Ē.  
\v 8 K…Ē Debora, w…ôran nw…õ …õnadusum Rebeka m…Ē, efi. K'awup k…Ē Betel tant…Ēf, nde aŇčkiri d…ônt…Ēf nŇč…õ awe tewe ta ¬ęK…ôt…Ēk ka M…õnc…ôr¬Ľ m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē Kanu k…ôwur…ôr s…Ē Yakuba, nt…õ …õmb…õr…õ PadaŇč-Aram m…Ē, k…Ē k…ômpoc…õ k…Ē p…ôt…Ēt.  
\v 10 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôn'aŇčwe Yakuba, mba af…Ēs…Ēw'am tewe ta Yakuba tat…Ēk…Ē. ‚ÄĻYisrayel‚Äļ Ňč'ande pacw'am oŇč.¬Ľ K…Ē Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē oŇč tewe ta Yisrayel.  
\v 11 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku k…Ē: ¬ęIn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Kanu nk…õ k…ôntam mes f…ôp m…Ē. M…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôkomb…ôra, m…ôla. Afum a t…Ēf y…õlar…ôm Ňč…Ē m…ôndekom, ab…õ Ňčandewur …ôm d…ôris.  
\v 12 At…Ēf nŇč…õ is…ĒŇč Abraham k…Ē Siyaka m…Ē, indes…ĒŇč …ôm Ňči k…Ē yuruya yam k…Ē m…ôndecep…ôr-…õ. Indes…ĒŇč Ňča at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 13 K…Ē Kanu k…ômb…Ēl…õ k…Ē day, nde k…ônalok-lok…ôr k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 14 K…Ē Yakuba …õnc…ômb…ôr tasar da k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē Kanu k…ônalok-lok…ôr k…Ē m…Ē. K'oloŇč…ôr pi member k…Ē moro m…Ēb…Ēy teta k…ôpus…õ ka pi Kanu.  
\v 15 K…Ē Yakuba …Ēs…ĒŇč tofo tat…Ēk…Ē tewe ta Betel\f + \fr 35:15 \fq Betel\ft  = C…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęK…ôl…Ē ka Kanu¬Ľ\f*, nde Kanu k…ônalok-lok…ôr k…Ē m…Ē. 
\s1 K…ôkom ka BeŇčyamin, defi da Ras…õl 
\p  
\v 16 Yakuba …õy…õf…õ Betel k…Ē afum …Ēn. Ňäanawak k…ôb…Ēl…õ s…Ē k…ôb…õr…õ ka Efrata, k…Ē Ras…õl oŇčkom, k…ôkom k…ôcuy.  
\v 17 Eyi p…ôcuy pa k…ôkom kaŇčk…Ē, k…Ē w…ôbaŇč k…Ēn wan oloku: ¬ęTa m…ônes…õ, bawo m…ôs…Ēt…Ē s…Ē wan w…ôrkun!¬Ľ  
\v 18 Nt…õ Ras…õl encfi m…Ē, k'ewe wan w…ôkak…Ē B…õn-Oni\f + \fr 35:18 \fq B…õn-Oni\ft  = C…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęwan w…ôka pucuy¬Ľ \f*. Mba k…Ē kas ewe k…Ē BeŇčyamin\f + \fr 35:18 \fq BeŇčyamin\ft  = C…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęWan w…ôka k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt¬Ľ \f*.  
\v 19 K…Ē Ras…õl efi. K'awup k…Ē nde d…Ēp…Ē da Efrata, nde Betl…õh…õm.  
\v 20 K…Ē Yakuba …õnc…ômb…ôr tasar nde kufu ka Ras…õl, tasar popus pap…Ēk…Ē …õnac…ômb…ôr kufu ka Ras…õl m…Ē, p…Ēs…Ēr…Ēyi di haŇč m…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 21 K…Ē Yakuba …ĒŇčk…Ē, p…ôc…ômb…ôr abal nde Mik…ôdal-Ed…õr tak…ôroŇč.  
\v 22 Nt…õ Yakuba eyi at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ruben …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôf…ônt…ôr…ôr Bilha w…ôlak…Ē ka papa k…Ēn, k…Ē Yakuba …õnc…ôr…õ ti. 
\p Yakuba …õnas…Ēt…Ē awut arkun w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč:  
\v 23 Awut a Leya: Ruben coco ca Yakuba, Simey…ĒŇč, Lewy, Yuda, Isakar, k…Ē Sabulon.  
\v 24 Awut a Ras…õl: Isifu k…Ē BeŇčyamin.  
\v 25 Awut a Bilha, w…ômar…ôs ka Ras…õl: Dan k…Ē Naftali.  
\v 26 Awut a Silpa, w…ômar…ôs ka Leya: Kadu k…Ē As…õr. Awut a Yakuba Ňčanayi akak…Ē, aŇč…õ …õnakom PadaŇč-Aram m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 27 K…Ē Yakuba ender kas Siyaka k…ôs…ôk, nde Mamre, nde Kiriyat Arba, nde p…ôy…Ēn…õ Heb…ôr…ĒŇč m…Ē, a k…Ē Abraham k…Ē Siyaka Ňčanayi decik…ôra m…Ē.  
\v 28 K…ôwon ka Siyaka doru k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren tasar tin k…Ē w…ôco cam…ôt maas (180).  
\v 29 K'eŇčgbiŇč kifir. K'efi, k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl atem …Ēn ak…Ē Ňčanafi m…Ē, Siyaka …õnasik…ôr, doru d…õt…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē. K'awut …Ēn Esayu k…Ē Yakuba Ňčawup k…Ē. 
\c 36  
\s1 Esayu k…ônd…õ k…Ēn nde at…Ēf Ňča Ed…Ēm 
\p  
\v 1 Dokomb…ôra da Esayu d…Ē dand…õ, nw…õ aŇčwe s…Ē Ed…Ēm m…Ē.  
\v 2 K…Ē Esayu …õl…õk aran …Ēn, aran a KanaŇč dac…Ē: Ada, wan w…ôran ka Elon w…ôHewy, Oholibama wan w…ôran ka Ana, wan w…ôran ka Cibeh…ĒŇč w…ôHewy,  
\v 3 Basmat wan w…ôran ka S…ômayila, w…ôkir…õ ka Nebay…Ēt.  
\v 4 K…Ē Ada oŇčkom…õ Esayu Elifas, k…Ē Basmat oŇčkom Rehuw…õl.  
\v 5 K…Ē Oholibama oŇčkom Yehus, Yahelam, k…Ē Korah. Awut a Esayu Ňč…Ē akak…Ē aŇč…õ anakom…õ k…Ē KanaŇč m…Ē.  
\v 6 K…Ē Esayu …õl…õk aran …Ēn, awut …Ēn arkun k…Ē aran, afum …Ēn aka k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn, y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēn k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē …õnas…Ēt…Ē at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē f…ôp, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē at…Ēf Ňč…Ēl…Ēma. K'…Ēmb…Ēl…õ w…õnc Yakuba,  
\v 7 bawo y…Ēc…Ēl y…õnalar Ňča, ta Ňčantam k…ôyi tofo tin-…õ. At…Ēf nŇč…õ Ňčanayi m…Ē Ňč…õnaf…õt…ôr Ňča teta y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan y…õlar…ôm.  
\v 8 K…Ē Esayu …õnd…õ nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Sehir. Esayu, nk…Ēn ancwe s…Ē Ed…Ēm. 
\s1 Yuruya ya Esayu 
\p  
\v 9 Dokomb…ôra da Esayu, d…Ē dand…õ w…ôtem ka yuruya ny…õ aŇčwe Ed…Ēm m…Ē, nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Sehir k…ôroŇč.  
\v 10 Mewe ma awut a Esayu m…Ē mam…õ: Elifas wan ka Ada w…ôran ka Esayu, Rehuw…õl wan ka Basmat w…ôran ka Esayu.  
\v 11 Awut a Elifas Ňčanay…Ēn…õ: Teman, Omar, Sefo, Kahetam, k…Ē Kenas.  
\v 12 Timna w…ôlak…Ē ka Elifas …õnayi wan ka Esayu. K'oŇčkom…õ Elifas Amal…õk. Awut a Ada Ňč…Ē akak…Ē w…ôran ka Esayu.  
\v 13 Mewe ma awut a Rehuw…õl m…Ē mam…õ: Nahat, Serah, Sama, k…Ē Misa. Awut a Basmat Ňč…Ē akak…Ē w…ôran ka Esayu.  
\v 14 Mewe ma awut a Oholibama wan w…ôran ka Ana, wans…Ē ka Cibeh…ĒŇč, w…ôran ka Esayu: K'oŇčkom…õ Esayu Yehus, Yahelam, k…Ē Korah.  
\v 15 Mewe ma ab…õ a yuruya ya Esayu m…õm…õ: Awut ab…õ a Elifas, coco ca Esayu: W…ôb…õ Teman, w…ôb…õ Omar, w…ôb…õ Sefo, w…ôb…õ Kenas,  
\v 16 w…ôb…õ Korah, w…ôb…õ Kahetam, k…Ē w…ôb…õ Amal…õk. Ab…õ a Elifas Ňč…Ē akak…Ē, at…Ēf Ňča Ed…Ēm. Awut a Ada Ňč…Ē akak…Ē.  
\v 17 Awut a Rehuw…õl, wan ka Esayu Ňč…Ē akaŇč…õ: W…ôb…õ Nahat, w…ôb…õ Serah, w…ôb…õ Sama, k…Ē w…ôb…õ Misa. Ab…õ a Rehuw…õl Ňč…Ē akak…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Ed…Ēm. Awut a Basmat Ňč…Ē akak…Ē, w…ôran ka Esayu.  
\v 18 Awut a Oholibama Ňč…Ē akaŇč…õ, w…ôran ka Esayu: W…ôb…õ Yehus, w…ôb…õ Yahelam, k…Ē w…ôb…õ Korah. Ab…õ a Oholibama Ňč…Ē akaŇč…õ wan w…ôran ka Ana, w…ôran ka Esayu.  
\v 19 Awut a Esayu Ňč…Ē akak…Ē, k…Ē ab…õ aŇčan. Esayu nw…õ ancwe s…Ē ¬ęEd…Ēm¬Ľ m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 20 Awut a Sehir w…ôHori Ňč…Ē akaŇč…õ: LotaŇč, Sobal, Cibeh…ĒŇč, Ana,  
\v 21 Dis…ĒŇč, Eser, k…Ē DisaŇč. Ab…õ aHori Ňč…Ē akak…Ē, awut a Sehir nde at…Ēf Ňča Ed…Ēm.  
\v 22 Awut a LotaŇč Ňčanay…Ēn…õ Hori k…Ē Hemam. W…ôkir…õ ka LotaŇč …õnay…Ēn…õ Timna.  
\v 23 Awut a Sobal Ňčanay…Ēn…õ AlwaŇč, Manahat, Ebal, Sefo, k…Ē Onam.  
\v 24 Awut a Cibeh…ĒŇč Ňčanay…Ēn…õ Aya k…Ē Ana. Ana w…ôkak…Ē …õnafir k…ôl…ômp nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, p…ôk…Ē d…ôŇčk…õk s…Ēfale sa papa k…Ēn Cibeh…ĒŇč.  
\v 25 Awut a Ana Ňčanay…Ēn…õ Dis…ĒŇč k…Ē Oholibama, wan ka Ana w…ôran.  
\v 26 Awut a DisaŇč Ňčanay…Ēn…õ: HemdaŇč, EsbaŇč, Yit…ôran, k…Ē Keran.  
\v 27 Awut a Eser Ňčanay…Ēn…õ: BilaŇč, SawaŇč, k…Ē AkaŇč.  
\v 28 Awut a DisaŇč Ňčanay…Ēn…õ Huc k…Ē AraŇč.  
\v 29 Ab…õ a Hori Ňč…Ē akaŇč…õ: W…ôb…õ LotaŇč, w…ôb…õ Sobal, w…ôb…õ Cibeh…ĒŇč, w…ôb…õ Ana,  
\v 30 w…ôb…õ Dis…ĒŇč, w…ôb…õ Eser, w…ôb…õ DisaŇč. Ab…õ a Hori Ňča akak…Ē, ab…õ aŇčan at…Ēf Ňča Sehir.  
\v 31 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē ab…õ Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr f…õ k…ôr…õsna d…õb…õ nde at…Ēf Ňča Yisrayel. Mewe ma ab…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanacep…ôr at…Ēf Ňča Ed…Ēm m…Ē, m…Ē mam…õ:  
\v 32 Bela, wan ka Behor, …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ Ed…Ēm, tewe ta dare d…Ēn t…õnay…Ēn…õ Dinaba.  
\v 33 K…Ē Bela efi. K…Ē Yobab wan ka Serah w…ôka B…Ēc…ôra …õl…õk d…õb…õ d…Ēn.  
\v 34 K…Ē Yobab efi. K…Ē Hucam w…ôka at…Ēf Ňča Temani …õl…õk d…õb…õ d…Ēn.  
\v 35 K…Ē Hucam efi. K…Ē Hadad wan ka Bedadu …õl…õk d…õb…õ d…Ēn. Nk…Ēn …õnac…ômb…ôr MadiyaŇč nde kulum ka Mohab. Tewe ta dare d…Ēn t…õnay…Ēn…õ Awit.  
\v 36 K…Ē Hadad efi. K…Ē Samla w…ôka Masreka …õl…õk d…õb…õ d…Ēn.  
\v 37 K…Ē Samla efi. K…Ē Sawul w…ôka dare da Rehobot D…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē …õl…õk d…õb…õ d…Ēn.  
\v 38 K…Ē Sawul efi. K…Ē Bal Hanan, wan ka Akb…Ēr, …õl…õk d…õb…õ d…Ēn.  
\v 39 K…Ē Bal Hanan wan ka Akb…Ēr efi. K…Ē Hadar …õl…õk d…õb…õ d…Ēn. Tewe ta dare d…Ēn t…õnay…Ēn…õ Pawu, k…Ē tewe ta w…ôran k…Ēn t…õnay…Ēn…õ Mehetab…õl, wan ka Mat…õrodu w…ôran, wan ka Mesahabu w…ôran.  
\v 40 Mewe ma ab…õ a Esayu m…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē, d…ôcor d…ôcor, d…ôt…Ēf t…Ēf. P…ôm…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē mewe maŇčan moloku ti m…Ē: W…ôb…õ Timna, w…ôb…õ Alwa, w…ôb…õ Yetet,  
\v 41 w…ôb…õ Oholibama, w…ôb…õ Ela, w…ôb…õ Pin…ĒŇč,  
\v 42 w…ôb…õ Kenas, w…ôb…õ Teman, w…ôb…õ Mib…ôcar,  
\v 43 w…ôb…õ Makdiy…õl, w…ôb…õ Iram. AkaŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ēn…õ ab…õ a Ed…Ēm, k…Ē d…ôk…ônd…õ daŇčan at…Ēf Ňč…Ēk…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ ab…õ m…Ē. Esayu …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôtem ka aka Ed…Ēm. 
\c 37  
\ms2 Tecep…ôr…õn…õ ta Isifu 
\mr 37-50 
\s1 Taruku ta Yakuba k'afum …Ēn 
\s2 M…õw…õr…ôp ma Isifu 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yakuba …õnd…õ at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč nde kas …õnand…õ m…Ē.  
\v 2 Dokomb…ôra da Yakuba d…õnd…õ: K…ôs…Ēt…Ē ka Isifu meren w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē Isifu …õy…õf…õ p…ôcc…õps…õ aw…õnc aŇča dar…ôŇč Ňčack…õk Ňčkesiya k…Ē cir. P…ôy…Ēn…õ wan w…ôf…õt, p…ôcc…ôm…õ awut arkun a Bilha k…Ē Silpa dar…ôŇč, aran a kas. Mba Isifu encder p…ôcs…ĒŇč…õ papa k…ôŇčan k…ôc…ôr…õ m…õc…õmc…õmn…õ m…õl…õc m…Ēk…Ē menccep…ôr di m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 3 Yakuba\f + \fr 37:3 \ft  C…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęYisrayel¬Ľ = tewe tant…õ t…Ē Kanu ki s…ôrka k…ônas…ĒŇč Yakuba. M…ôm…Ēm…ôn \f* …õnab…Ēt…ôr Isifu p…ôtas awut …Ēn alp…ôs aŇč…õ f…ôp, bawo detem disr…õ d'…õnas…Ēt…Ē k…Ē. K…Ē Yakuba …Ēs…Ēt burumus b…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôs…ôl lom k'…Ēs…ĒŇč bi Isifu.  
\v 4 K…Ē aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčande Ňčan…ôŇčk, a kas k…ôŇčan …Ēmb…Ēt…ôr Isifu p…ôtas Ňča f…ôp. K…Ē Ňčam…õŇčk…õ Isifu m…õt…õl…õ mam…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē Ňčayi ta ŇčaŇčlok-lok…ôr Isifu belbel-…õ.  
\v 5 K…Ē Isifu …õw…õr…ôp, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôloku mere mam…Ēk…Ē aw…õnc aŇča, k…Ē akak…Ē ŇčanaŇčkan…õ s…Ē k…ôter k…Ē.  
\v 6 K…Ē Isifu oloku Ňča: ¬ęAw…õnc im aŇča, n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl mere mm…õ iw…õr…ôpna m…Ē!  
\v 7 D…ôkulum ayina pacsek m…õmp…ôl…õ. P…ôwon f…õ k…Ē kilim kem ka m…õmp…ôl…õ k…ôy…õf…õ k…Ē k…ônc…ôm…õ sot! K…Ē cilim ca m…õmp…ôl…õ ma n…ôna c…ônder c…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr kem, k…Ē c…ôntontn…õn…õ ki.¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē aw…õnc aŇča Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęMba m…ôna m…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka w…ôb…õ ka s…ôna ba? M…ôyi su k…ôroŇč?¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õn…õ s…Ē k…ôter k…Ē teta moloku m…Ēn mam…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 9 K…Ē Isifu endes…Ē p…ôw…õr…ôp, k'oloku s…Ē ti aw…õnc aŇča. K'oloku: ¬ęIw…õr…ôpna s…Ē: Dec, Ňčof k…Ē c…Ēs w…ôco k…Ē pin yontontn…õn'em.¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē Isifu oloku mere mam…Ēk…Ē papa k…Ēn k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča. K…Ē papa k…Ēn oŇčkul-kul…ôr k…Ē, k'eyif k…Ē: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē mere mam…õ m…ôw…õr…ôp m…Ē moloku-…õ? M…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ a s…ôndeder, iya kam, aw…õnc …ôm aŇča, k…Ē ina s…ôdetontn…õn'am d…ônt…Ēf?¬Ľ  
\v 11 K…Ē aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčay…Ēn…õ k…Ē k…ôraca. Mba k…Ē kas k…ôŇčan …õm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ k…ôw…õr…ôp kaŇčk…Ē. 
\s1 Aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčancam…ôs k…Ē 
\p  
\v 12 K…Ē aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčande Ňčawur, k…ôk…Ēk…õk Ňčkesiya k…Ē cir ya kas k…ôŇčan nde S…ôk…õm.  
\v 13 K…Ē Yakuba oloku Isifu: ¬ęAw…õnc …ôm aŇča Ňčayi S…ôk…õm Ňčawur…õn…õ y…Ēc…Ēl k…ôk…Ēs…Ēm…ôt. M…ôder, ifaŇč k…ôsom …ôm nde Ňčayi m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Isifu owos…õ: ¬ęIn'…õw…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 14 K…Ē Yakuba oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē m…ôm…Ēm…ôn em k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a daka o daka d…Ēy…Ē f…õ aw…õnc …ôm aŇča k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…õf…õt y…õf…õt-…õ. M…ôder m…ôlok'im ti.¬Ľ K'osom k…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ ka aranta Ňča Heb…ôr…ĒŇč, k…Ē Isifu …ĒŇčk…Ē S…ôk…õm.  
\v 15 K…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…ôp k…Ē p…ôckaf…ôl…õ-kaf…ôl…õ d…ôkulum. K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ eyif k…Ē: ¬ęAke m…ônt…õn-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē Isifu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęAw…õnc im aŇča Ňč'int…õn, il…õts…õn'am m…ôment…ôr im nde Ňčayi k…ôk…õk y…Ēc…Ēl m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ oloku k…Ē: ¬ęŇäay…õf…õ d…õ, inen…õna Ňča Ňčacloku: ‚ÄĻPaŇčk…Ēn k…ôca ka DotaŇč.‚Äļ¬Ľ K…Ē Isifu …õnc…ôm…õ ni yaŇčan dar…ôŇč k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl haŇč k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…ôp Ňča DotaŇč. 
\p  
\v 18 K'aw…õnc aŇča Ňčan…ôŇčk k…Ē p…ôb…Ēl…õ, ta …õntab…ôp Ňča-…õ, k…Ē Ňčasek…õ k…Ē k…ôdif.  
\v 19 K…Ē Ňčalok…õn…õ: ¬ęW…ôb…õ ka k…ôw…õr…ôp ender w…ôk…Ē.  
\v 20 N…ôder oŇč padif k…Ē, pagbal k…Ē nde d…ôk…ôl…ômp. Pak…Ē paloku a w…õs…õm w…Ēs…Ēm k…Ē. Pam…Ēm…ôn oŇč daka nd…õ k…ôw…õr…ôp k…Ēn k…ôndey…Ēn…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 21 K…Ē Ruben ene ti, k'…õmbaŇč k…Ē akak…Ē d…ôwaca. K'oloku: ¬ęTa pas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôfi.¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē Ruben oloku s…Ē: ¬ęTa n…ôwur…õ mecir! N…ôgbal k…Ē k…ôl…ômp kaŇčk…õ k…ôyi nn…Ē d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē. Ta n…ôdeŇč…ôr k…Ē k…ôca!¬Ľ ∆źnaloku Ňča moloku mam…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôtam k…ôyac Isifu defi, p…ôken…õ k…Ē kas m…Ē.  
\v 23 Nt…õ Isifu …õmb…ôp aw…õnc aŇča m…Ē, k…Ē akak…Ē Ňčawur…õ k…Ē burumus b…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôs…ôl lom b…Ēk…Ē …õnab…õrn…õ m…Ē.  
\v 24 K…Ē Ňčasump…ôr k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčantor…õ k…Ē d…ôk…ôl…ômp. K…ôl…ômp kaŇčk…Ē k…ônawos…ôr, ali domun k…ônay…Ē f…õ.  
\v 25 K…Ē Ňčand…õ Ňčacdi yeri, Ňčandeyekti f…Ēr, k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk afum a S…ômayila Ňčay…õf…õ at…Ēf Ňča Kaladu. Y…Ēk…Ēm…õ yaŇčan y…õsar…õ suray, c…Ēl k…Ē labund…õ ny…õ Ňčanckek…ôr…õ Misira m…Ē.  
\v 26 K…Ē Yuda eyif aw…õnc aŇča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē andedif…õ w…õnc kosu pam…õŇčk mecir m…Ēn-…õ?  
\v 27 N…ôder pacams…ôr k…Ē afum a S…ômayila. Ta padeŇč…ôr k…Ē k…ôca. Bawo w…õnc kosu …Ēf…Ē, mecir min mayi m…Ē ampaŇčn…õ.¬Ľ K'aw…õnc aŇča Ňčanen…õ k…Ē moloku mam…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 28 K…Ē acam…ôs aMadiyaŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanccep…ôr m…Ē, Ňčamp…õn…õ Isifu d…ôk…ôl…ômp. K…Ē aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčancams…ôr k…Ē aMadiyaŇč gbeti nc…ômb…ôl w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč, k'aMadiyaŇč ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ Isifu Misira.  
\v 29 Nt…õ Ruben oluks…ôrn…õ k…ôdem…Ēm…ôn k…ôl…ômp disr…õ m…Ē, …õmb…ôp f…õ s…Ē Isifu k…ôl…ômp disr…õ. K'…õwal-wali y…õb…õrn…õ y…Ēn.  
\v 30 K'…õŇčkaf…ôl…õ nn…Ē aw…õnc aŇča Ňčayi m…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęWan nw…õ eyi f…õ s…Ē nn…Ē d…ôk…ôl…ômp! C…ôke indey…Ē oŇč-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 31 K…Ē Ňčal…õk burumus ba Isifu, k…Ē Ňčafay ambiyofo amera, k…Ē Ňčasop…ôt burumus bab…Ēk…Ē mecir.  
\v 32 K…Ē ŇčaŇčken…õ kas k…ôŇčan burumus b…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôs…ôl lom ba Isifu bab…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčacloku kas k…ôŇčan: ¬ęYamos yay…õ y…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē s…ôn…ôŇčk. M…ôna s…Ē m…ôm…Ēm…ôn ma k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a burumus ba wan kam b…Ē-…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 33 K…Ē Yakuba …õn…õp…ôl bi, k'oloku: ¬ęBurumus ba wan kem b…Ē! W…õs…õm w…õl…õc w…Ēl…Ēma w…Ēs…Ēm k…Ē! W…õs…õm w…õwat…ôri-wat…ôri k…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 34 K…Ē Yakuba …õwal-wali yamos y…Ēn, k'esek…ôn…õ k…ôloto k'ab…õk defi. K'ombok wan k…Ēn Isifu mataka m…õlar…ôm.  
\v 35 K…Ē awut …Ēn arkun k…Ē aran f…ôp Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôtor…õ-tor…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc. Mba k'ombup…ôr…õ k…ôl…õts…õn…õ f…ôp. K'oloku: ¬ęIndebok wan kem haŇč d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ indek…Ēb…ôp k…Ē dabiya m…Ē!¬Ľ K'…õnc…ôm…õ k…ôbok ka wan k…Ēn dar…ôŇč. 
\p  
\v 36 K…Ē aMadiyaŇč Ňčancam…ôs Isifu Misira. K…Ē Potifar w…ôtup…õ ka Firawona yeri nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka abum a d…ôsaŇčka sa Firawona m…Ē, …õway k…Ē. 
\c 38  
\s1 Yuda k…Ē Tamar 
\p  
\v 1 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, Yuda p…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ aw…õnc aŇča, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôyi k…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ ancwe Hira m…Ē, w…ôka Adulam …õnayi.  
\v 2 D…ôndo, k…Ē Yuda …õn…ôŇčk w…ôyec…ôra w…ôKanaŇč w…ôl…Ēma pacwe k…Ē Suwa. K'…õl…õk k…Ē k'…õn…õnc…õ k'omboc…ôrn…õ k…Ē.  
\v 3 K…Ē Suwa …õmb…õk…ôs, k'oŇčkom…õ Yuda wan w…ôrkun k'ewe k…Ē Er.  
\v 4 K'…õmb…õk…ôs s…Ē k'oŇčkom wan w…ôrkun k'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē tewe ta OnaŇč.  
\v 5 K'…ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôkom wan w…ôrkun nw…õ …õnawe S…õlah m…Ē. Dare da Kisibu Yuda …õnayi t…õm nt…õ Suwa onckom S…õlah m…Ē.  
\v 6 K…Ē Yuda …õfac…õ coco c…Ēn w…ôyec…ôra nw…õ ancwe Tamar m…Ē.  
\v 7 Mba Er, nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ coco ca Yuda m…Ē, …õnates…õ f…õ f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč. K…Ē MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôfi.  
\v 8 K…Ē Yuda oloku t…ĒŇč…Ē t…Ēn OnaŇč: ¬ęM…ôboc…ôrn…õ w…ôran ka w…ôbek'am. M…ôs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôran k…Ēn p…ôs…Ēt…Ēn…õ k…Ē yuruya.¬Ľ  
\v 9 Nt…õ OnaŇč …õnac…ôr…õ a awut aŇč…õ endes…ĒŇč w…ôran ka w…ôbek'…Ēn, Ňčaf…Ēdey…Ēn…õ ak…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē OnaŇč Ňčanck…Ēnaf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôran ka w…õnc-…õ, p…ôcloŇč domun d…Ēn d‚Äôarkun d…ônt…Ēf, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ w…õnc k…ôs…Ēt…Ē yuruya m…Ē.  
\v 10 M…Ēy…Ē m…Ēn mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ēncb…Ēt f…õ MARIKI, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ s…Ē nk…Ēn OnaŇč k…ôfi.  
\v 11 K…Ē Yuda oloku Tamar w…ôran ka wan k…Ēn: ¬ęM…ônd…õ k…ôbal ka wos …ôm ndena papa kam haŇč wan kem w…ôrkun S…õlah p…ôcb…õk.¬Ľ Bawo Yuda onclokun…õ: ¬ęW…ôkaw…õ s…Ē k…ôfi k'ender p…ôm…Ē abek'…Ēn.¬Ľ K…Ē Tamar …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôyi nde k…ôl…Ē ka papa k…Ēn. 
\p  
\v 12 K…Ē mataka m…õlar…ôm mencep…ôr, k…Ē wan w…ôran ka Suwa, w…ôran ka Yuda, efi. Nt…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õnator Yuda m…Ē, k'…õmp…õrn…õ k…ôca ka Timna k…Ē wanapa k…Ēn Hira w…ôka Adulam, nde ak…Ē Ňčancfon Ňčkesiya y…Ēn Ňčanayi m…Ē.  
\v 13 K'aŇčk…Ē paloku Tamar: Konci kam …õntas Timna k…ôk…Ēfon Ňčkesiya y…Ēn y…õf…õt.  
\v 14 K…Ē Tamar owur…õ yamos y…Ēn ya c…ôbok…ôra, k'…õŇčgbal…ôrn…õ k…ôloto, k'…õn…õps…ôrn…õ ki, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da Enayim nde d…Ēp…Ē da Timna. Bawo …õnan…ôŇčk a S…õlah …õmb…õk, k'ant…Ēl…õk k…Ē pas…ĒŇč S…õlah p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôran k…Ēn.  
\v 15 K…Ē Yuda …õn…ôŇčk Tamar, k…Ē p…ôyi k…Ē p…ôm…Ē w…ôran w…ôyamayama, bawo …õnakump…ôn…õ k…ôro.  
\v 16 K…Ē Yuda …õncaŇč Tamar moloku d…Ēp…Ē: ¬ęTaŇčk…Ēn, s…ôk…Ē s…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ.¬Ľ Bawo Yuda …õnac…ôr…õ f…õ a w…ôran ka wan k…Ēn w…ôrkun …Ēf…Ē. K…Ē Tamar eyif k…Ē: ¬ęAke m…ôndek…Ēs…ĒŇč im, k…Ē m…ômboc…ôrn'em-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 17 K'oloku: ¬ęIŇčk…Ēk…õr'am wir wowut y…Ēc…Ēl yem dac…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Tamar oloku: ¬ęM…õn…õ m…ôs…ĒŇč im paka p…Ēl…Ēm it…Ēmp…ôr haŇč m…ôck…õr…õ wir wowut waw…Ēk…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 18 K…Ē Yuda eyif k…Ē: ¬ęAke indes…ĒŇč …ôm haŇč ick…õr…õ wir wowut nw…õ-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Tamar oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôs…ĒŇč im tamp tam, k…ôb…ônda k…Ē k…ôgbo kaŇčk…Ē m…ônt…Ēmp…ôr m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Yuda …Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē yi. K…Ē Yuda …õf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē Tamar, k…Ē Tamar …õmb…õks…õ Yuda.  
\v 19 K…Ē Tamar …õy…õf…õ k'…ĒŇčk…Ē, k'owur…õ k…ôloto kaŇčk…Ē …õnagbal…ôrn…õ m…Ē, k'…õmb…õrn…õ s…Ē yamos y…Ēn ya k…ôbal. 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē Yuda osom wanapa k…Ēn w…ôAdulam, a p…ôken…õ Tamar wir wowut, p…ôk…õr…õn…õ ca y…Ēk…Ē …õnac…ômb…ôr di s…õk…õ m…Ē. Mba …õnan…ôŇčk f…õ k…Ē.  
\v 21 K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôcyif…ôt afum ak…Ē …õnab…ôp di m…Ē: ¬ęDeke w…ôran w…ôt…õn arkun, nw…õ …õnc…ôm…õna nn…Ē d…Ēp…Ē da Enayim m…Ē, eyi-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē akak…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôran w…ôt…õn arkun …Ēf…Ēc…ôm…õ nn…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ olukus k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôcloku Yuda: ¬ęIn…ôŇčk f…õ k…Ē. Ali afum a tofo tat…Ēk…Ē Ňčaloku: ‚ÄĻA w…ôran w…ôt…õn arkun eyi f…õ nn…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 23 K…Ē Yuda oloku: ¬ęP…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ ca yem y…Ēk…Ē …Ēnt…Ēmp…ôr m…Ē! Ta pat…õn…ôrn…õ malap. Bawo isom paken…õ k…Ē wir wowut k…Ē m…ônt…Ēn…ôŇčk k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 24 Nt…õ yof maas yencep…ôr m…Ē, k'ande paloku Yuda: ¬ęW…ôran ka wan kam …ĒŇčk…Ēt yamayama, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôb…õk…ôs.¬Ľ K…Ē Yuda oloku: ¬ęN…ôwur…õn…õ k…Ē. Pac…Ēf k…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 25 Nt…õ asol…õ k…Ē k…ôwur…õn…õ doru m…Ē, k'osom nda konci k…Ēn: ¬ęW…ôb…õk…ôs…ôs kem …Ēy…Ē ca ny…õ. M…ôs…õp m…ôc…ôr…õ nw…õ …Ēy…Ē tamp pamp…õ, k…ôb…ônda kaŇčk…õ, k…Ē k…ôgbo kaŇčk…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 26 K…Ē Yuda …õn…õp…ôl yi. K'oloku: ¬ęTamar olomp p…ôtas im, bawo iwos…õ f…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē wan kem S…õlah.¬Ľ Dif…Ē t…õnalip …õnc…ôr…õ f…õ k…Ē s…Ē d…õran. 
\p  
\v 27 Nt…õ Tamar …õy…õf…õ k…ôkom m…Ē, k'an…ôŇčk a c…ôberi c…ôyi k…Ē d…ôkor.  
\v 28 Tamar eyi k…ôkom. K…Ē wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē owur…õ k…ôca. K…Ē w…ôran w…ôbaŇč wan osump…ôr k…ônaka nk…õ k…ôca k'oŇčkot k…Ē debeŇča deyim d…ôk…ôca, p…ôcloku: ¬ęW…ôkaw…õ andenuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôkom.¬Ľ  
\v 29 Mba k…Ē k…ônaka nk…õ k…ôliŇč k…ôca, k…Ē w…õnc onuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôwur. K…Ē w…ôbaŇč wan eyifn…õ: ¬ęK…ôp…ôc k…ôre k…Ē m…ôwur…õ kaŇčk…õ-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Tamar ewe wan w…ôkak…Ē P…õr…õc. \f + \fr 38:29 \fq P…õr…õc\ft  = ¬ęk…ôp…ôc¬Ľ \f* 
\v 30 K…Ē wan w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč owur, nw…õ anakot debeŇča d…ôk…ôca m…Ē, k…Ē Tamar ewe w…ôkak…Ē tewe ta Serah. \f + \fr 38:30 \fq Serah\ft  = ¬ęK…ôp…õ ka dec¬Ľ \f* 
\c 39  
\s1 Isifu kiyi k…Ēn Misira ndena Potifar 
\p  
\v 1 K'aŇčkek…ôr…õ Isifu Misira. K…Ē Potifar w…ôMisira, w…ôb…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôka firawona, nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôkiriŇč ka abum …Ēn m…Ē, …õway k…Ē afum a S…ômayila d…ôwaca ak…Ē Ňčanak…õr…õ k…Ē Misira m…Ē.  
\v 2 MARIKI …õnasol…õ Isifu, p…ôcuca f…ôp p…Ē MARIKI …õncbaŇč k…Ē. K…ôl…Ē ka Mariki m…Ēn w…ôMisira k'…õnayi.  
\v 3 K…Ē Mariki m…Ēn …õn…ôŇčk a MARIKI osol…õ Isifu. Mosump…ôr m…Ēn f…ôp, MARIKI …õncmar k…Ē mectes…õ k…Ē d…ôwaca.  
\v 4 K…Ē Isifu ende p…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…ôlaŇč ka w…ôb…õ k…Ēn nw…õ …õncb…ôc…õ m…Ē. K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …õl…õk k…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē d…õb…õ da k…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr mes ma k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ. K'…õl…õk daka d…Ēn f…ôp, k'…õmb…õr di Isifu d…ôwaca p…ôclomps…õ-lomps…õ k…Ē di k…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr.  
\v 5 Nt…õ Potifar …õlaŇč Isifu, a k'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr ka mes ma k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ f…ôp m…Ē, k…Ē MARIKI ompoc…õ k…ôl…Ē ka w…ôMisira nw…õ, teta Isifu. K…Ē k…ôpoc…õ ka MARIKI k…ôsump…ôr daka da Potifar f…ôp, k…ôy…õf…õ d…õk…õr haŇč nde dal…õ.  
\v 6 K'…õsak…ôr…õ teta daka d…Ēn f…ôp Isifu, nk…Ēn …õnasump…ôr f…õ s…Ē nt…õ o nt…õ m…õn…õ yeri ny…õ encdi m…Ē. 
\s1 Isifu k…Ē w…ôran ka Potifar 
\p Mba Isifu fum w…ôt…Ēt teyi …õnayi.  
\v 7 Nt…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē mencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôran ka mariki m…Ēn ende p…ôcenc…ôr Isifu f…Ēr, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē ina!¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē Isifu …õfati. K'oloku w…ôran ka mariki m…Ēn: ¬ęM…ôn…ôŇčk nt…õ mariki mem …õl…õk mes m…Ēn f…ôp k'…õmb…õr im d…ôwaca m…Ē, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ …Ēf…Ēs…Ēy…Ē nt…õ o nt…õ d…õk…õr k'…õl…õk s…Ē daka d…Ēn f…ôp k'…Ēs…ĒŇč im k…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr.  
\v 9 Fum nw…õ o nw…õ eyi f…õ nn…Ē k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…õ nw…õ elel…õ p…ôcep…ôr im m…Ē. ∆Üm…Ēn…õn…õ f'em nt…õ o nt…õ ta k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…õ m…õn…õ m…ôna, bawo w…ôran k…Ēn m…ôy…Ēn…õ. Ak'endes…ĒŇč'em oŇč k…ôy…Ē p…ôl…õc p…Ēp…ĒŇč, iciyan…õ s…Ē Kanu-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ …õnc…ôm…õn…õ Isifu moloku mam…Ēk…Ē dar…ôŇč haŇč mataka m…õlar…ôm. Mba Isifu …õnawos…õ f…õ m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ m…Ēn, k…ôc…ôr…õ a Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn.  
\v 11 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma, k…Ē Isifu …õmb…õr…õ dukul…Ē d…ôk…ôlomp…ôs y…õb…ôc y…Ēn. Mba d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē afum a k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē ali w…ôkin …õnayi f…õ d…õk…õr.  
\v 12 K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ osump…ôr p…õb…õrn…õ pa Isifu k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē ina!¬Ľ K…Ē Isifu …õsak…ôr…õ k…Ē p…õb…õrn…õ p…Ēn, k'…õy…õks…õ k'owur doru.  
\v 13 Nt…õ w…ôran nw…õ …õn…ôŇčk a Isifu …õsak…ôr…õ k…Ē p…õb…õrn…õ p…Ēn d…ôwaca, k'…õy…õks…õ k'owur doru m…Ē.  
\v 14 K'ewe afum a k…ôl…Ē k…ôŇčan k'oloku Ňča nt…õ: ¬ęN…ôn…ôŇčk, w…ôHeb…ôre nw…õ wos im\f + \fr 39:14 \ft  Potifar \f* …õŇčk…õr…õ p…ôdefani su m…Ē. Isifu ender im a p…ôdef…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē ina. Ti t…Ē iŇčkul-kul…õn…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč.  
\v 15 Nt…õ endec…ôr…õ a k…ôp…õn…õ k'ind…õ dim m…Ē, k'…õy…õks…õ. K'…õsak…ôr'em p…õb…õrn…õ p…Ēn k…Ē nk…Ēn owur nde doru.¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ omboc…ôrn…õ p…õb…õrn…õ pa Isifu k…ôs…ôk, haŇč mariki ma Isifu p…ôcb…õr…õ d…õk…õr.  
\v 17 K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ oloku wos tin tayi, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôcar w…ôHeb…ôre nw…õ m…ôŇčk…õr…õ su m…Ē, ender im a p…ôdefan'im.  
\v 18 Mba nt…õ iŇčkul…õ-kul…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč m…Ē, k'…õsak p…õb…õrn…õ p…Ēn nn…Ē iyi m…Ē. K…Ē nk…Ēn …õy…õks…õ k'owur nde doru.¬Ľ  
\v 19 Nt…õ mariki ma Isifu ene moloku ma w…ôran k…Ēn, nw…õ oncloku k…Ē: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē w…ôcar kam …Ēy'em!¬Ľ  
\v 20 K…Ē m…õt…õl…õ m…Ēp…ĒŇč mosump…ôr mariki ma Isifu. K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …õmb…õr Isifu d…ôbili k…ôca nk…õ w…ôb…õ …õncb…õr afum d…ôbili m…Ē. K…Ē Isifu eyi d…ôndo d…ôbili. 
\s1 K…ôyi ka Isifu d…ôbili 
\p  
\v 21 K…Ē MARIKI osol…õ Isifu, k'…õlas layidi da amera Ňčobotu Ňč…Ēk…Ē …õnas…ĒŇč k…Ē m…Ē. K'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka d…ôbili k…ômar k…Ē.  
\v 22 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka d…ôbili …õl…õk aka d…ôbili f…ôp k'…õmb…õr Ňča Isifu d…ôwaca, nt…õ o nt…õ tenccep…ôr oŇč di m…Ē, Isifu tencep…ôr d…ôwaca k…ôr…õsna.  
\v 23 W…ôb…õ w…ôka d…ôbili …Ēncm…Ēm…ôn f…õ s…Ē nt…õ o nt…õ Isifu …õnat…Ēmp…ôr d…ôwaca, bawo MARIKI …õnasol…õ k…Ē, p…ôclomps…õ k…Ē mosump…ôr m…Ēn f…ôp. 
\c 40  
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē mencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē amar…ôs m…õr…ôŇč a Firawona, w…ôb…õ ka Misira, w…ôtup…õ k…Ē w…ôc…Ēf…õ k…Ēn c…ôcom, Ňčande Ňčaciyan…õ mariki maŇčan.  
\v 2 K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Firawona nn…Ē amar…ôs …Ēn m…õr…ôŇč Ňčayi m…Ē.  
\v 3 K…Ē Firawona osom k'asump…ôr Ňča, k'aŇčk…Ē pacaŇč…ôr Ňča nde bili b…Ēk…Ē anacaŇč…ôr Isifu m…Ē.  
\v 4 K…Ē w…ôb…õ ka aka d…ôbili oloku Isifu k…ôgb…õk…ôr…õ Ňča p…ôm…Ē nt…õ …õnayi Ňča k…ôs…ôk m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčayi d…ôbili t…õm t…õlar…ôm. 
\s1 Isifu k…ôloku tedisr…õ ta mere ma amar…ôs a Firawona, aŇč…õ …õnacaŇč…ôs d…ôbili m…Ē 
\p  
\v 5 Pibi pin disr…õ, k…Ē amar…ôs a Firawona aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč Ňčaw…õr…ôp. Nw…õ o nw…õ, t…õw…õr…ôp t…Ēn taciŇča teciyan…õ k…Ē ta w…ôk…Ē.  
\v 6 Dec dendes…Ēk, k…Ē Isifu …õn…ôŇčk Ňča Ňčam…Ēncn…õ.  
\v 7 K…Ē Isifu eyif amar…ôs a Firawona aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanayi d…ôbili k…Ē nk…Ēn m…Ē, k'eyif Ňča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ôŇč…õy…õ c…ôro m…Ēk…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē Ňčaloku Isifu: ¬ęS…ôw…õr…ôpna nn…Ē pibi, mba fum eyi f…õ nn…Ē nw…õ endetam k…ôloku su tedisr…õ ta mere mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Isifu eyif Ňča: ¬ęBaf…Ē Kanu k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôc…ôr…õ ka tedisr…õ ta mes ba? N…ôlok'im ma mere monu.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē w…ôtup…õ ka Firawona yomun…ôs …Ēl…Ēm…ôr Isifu mere mam…Ēk…Ē …õnaw…õr…ôp m…Ē. K'oloku: ¬ęMere mm…õ iw…õr…ôpna m…Ē: AŇčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē Ňča w…õn Ňčeyin'em f…Ēr kiriŇč.  
\v 10 Ňä…Ēy…Ē wara maas. Nt…õ aŇčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē nŇč…õ ŇčoŇčgbuc m…Ē k…Ē c…õk ya yokom y…õmb…õk, k…Ē yokom yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ēl…Ēl.  
\v 11 T…õt…ôŇčn…õ it…Ēmp…ôr ap…Ēt nŇč…õ inctup…õ w…ôb…õ kem Firawona m…Ē. K'il…õk yokom y…Ēl…Ēma k'if…Ēc…ôs yi nn…Ē ap…Ēt nŇč…õ inctup…õ Firawona m…Ē disr…õ, k'is…ĒŇč Firawona m…ônc…Ēnc…Ē ma pokom pap…Ēk…Ē inaf…Ēcs…õ k…Ē d…Ēp…Ēt m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 12 K…Ē Isifu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTedisr…õ tayi t…õnt…õ: Wara waw…Ēk…Ē maas, mata maas m…Ē.  
\v 13 K…Ē mata maas mencep…ôr-…õ, Firawona endes…Ēlukus k…ôyekt'…ôm domp, p…ôluks'am y…õb…ôc yam. M…ôndes…Ē m…ôctup…õ k…Ē yomun…ôs p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ôncb…ôc ti m…Ē, m…ôcb…õr k…Ē yeri y…Ēk…Ē m…ônde k…ôctup…õ k…Ē m…Ē d…ôk…ôca.  
\v 14 K'andesak …ôm-…õ, ta m…ôdek…Ēp…ôl…ôrn'em, il…õts…õn'am m…ôl…õk'em layidi a m…ôndek…Ēmar im nn…Ē w…ôb…õ eyi m…Ē. Nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôwur…õn'em nn…Ē k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…õ disr…õ m…Ē.  
\v 15 Bawo at…Ēf Ňča Heb…ôre Ňčal…õk im k'aŇčk…õr…õ Misira. K…Ē nn…Ē, ali tes iy…Ē f…õ nt…õ andeb…õr'em d…ôbili m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 16 Nt…õ w…ôc…Ēf…õ ka Firawona c…ôcom …õn…ôŇčk a moloku mm…õ Isifu oloku ma mere m…Ē, m…Ēmb…Ēt k…ône, k'oloku Isifu: ¬ęIna mere mem, mafala maas ma k…ôcom k…ôgb…õnt m'isar…õna.  
\v 17 K…ôfala kaŇčk…Ē k…ôŇč…õcna ci dac…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, yeri y…Ēk…Ē w…ôc…Ēf c…ôcom ontup a p…ôcs…ĒŇč yi Firawona m…Ē f…ôp yeyina d…ônda. B…õmp y…Ēcs…Ēm yeri yay…Ēk…Ē isar…õna k…ôfala disr…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 18 K…Ē Isifu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTedisr…õ tayi t…õnt…õ: C…ôfala cac…Ēk…Ē maas, mata maas m…Ē.  
\v 19 K…Ē mata maas mencep…ôr-…õ, Firawona endep…õn'am darenc, p…ôb…õr …ôm k…ôb…ônda d…ôkilim p…ôgb…õk …ôm, b…õmp y…Ēs…Ēm …ôm.¬Ľ  
\v 20 Tataka ta maas, d…Ēs…Ēk doluks…ôr da k…ôkom ka Firawona. K'omboc…õ amar…ôs …Ēn k…ôsata k…ôp…ĒŇč. K'…Ēs…ĒŇč w…ôc…Ēf…õ k…Ēn c…ôcom d…õb…õ d…Ēp…ĒŇč, amar…ôs …Ēn f…ôp f…Ēr kiriŇč.  
\v 21 K'oluks…õ s…Ē w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč w…ôk…Ē y…õb…ôc y…Ēk…Ē …õnayi c…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē: K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē oncop s…Ē k…ôctup p…ôb…õr Firawona ap…Ēt d…ôk…ôca.  
\v 22 K…Ē Firawona osump…ôr w…ôc…Ēf c…ôcom w…ôp…ĒŇč p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Isifu …õnaloku ti m…Ē.  
\v 23 W…ôtup…õ ka Firawona yomun…ôs …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ f…õ s…Ē Isifu, k'…õmp…ôl…ôrn…õ k…Ē. 
\c 41  
\s1 K…ôw…õr…ôp ka Firawona 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē teren tin tencep…ôr, teren ta m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē Firawona …õw…õr…ôp: P…ôc…ôm…õ k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē nk…õ aŇčwe Nil m…Ē k…ôs…ôk.  
\v 2 K…Ē c…ôna c…ôran c…ôtifi cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč c…ôncaf…õ d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē c…ôy…õf…õ k…ôs…Ēm…ôt dal…õ.  
\v 3 K…Ē c…ôna c…ôran cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč c…ôl…Ēma c…ôleŇčki c…ôncaf…õ s…Ē c…ôk…Ē tadar…ôŇč d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē ci c…ôŇčk…Ē s…Ē c…ôc…ôm…õ c…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…ôs…ôk d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 4 K…Ē c…ôna c…ôleŇčki nc…õ c…ôy…õf…õ k…ôs…Ēm c…ôna c…ôtifi c…ôk…Ē. K…Ē Firawona …õnt…ôm…õ.  
\v 5 K…Ē Firawona …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôdir…õ, k'…õw…õr…ôp s…Ē tam…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 6 S…ôbomp sa mal…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč s…ôp…ĒŇč s…ôwur…ôs atoka Ňčin Ňč…Ēt…Ēt. K…Ē s…ôbomp sa mal…Ē s…ôf…õt s…ôwur…ôs s…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē tant…Ēf.  
\v 7 K…Ē s…ôbomp sa mal…Ē s…ôf…õt ns…õ s…ôndi s…ôbomp sa mal…Ē s…ôp…ĒŇč s…ôlar…õ s…ôk…Ē. K…Ē Firawona …õnt…ôm…õ s…Ē. Mere mayi m…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē. 
\p  
\v 8 Dec dendes…Ēk, k…Ē amera Ňč…õl…õc…õ-l…õc…õ Firawona. K'ewe ac…ôr…õ mes k'abeki a Misira f…ôp. K…Ē Firawona …Ēl…Ēm…ôr Ňča mere m…Ēn. Mba ali fum …õnayi f…õ nw…õ …õnctam k…ôloku k…Ē tedisr…õ ta mere m…Ēn m…Ē.  
\v 9 K…Ē w…ôtup…õ k…Ēn yomun…ôs …õl…õk moloku, k'oloku Firawona: ¬ęInc…õm-c…õmn…õ m…Ēk…Ē t…õp…ôl…ôrn…õ tem.  
\v 10 P…ônat…õl…õ Firawona nn…Ē amar…ôs …Ēn Ňčayi m…Ē, k'osom k'asump…ôr im k…Ē w…ôc…Ēf…õ k…Ēn c…ôcom, k'…õmb…õr su d…ôbili nde k…ôl…Ē ka w…ôb…õ ka abum …Ēn.  
\v 11 K…Ē s…ôw…õr…ôp ina k…Ē w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč kem pibi pin. Nw…õ o nw…õ mere m…Ēn taciŇča mm…õ antam k…ôloku tedisr…õ ta mi m…Ē.  
\v 12 T…õt…ôŇčn…õ s…ôyi bili bin k…Ē w…ôt…õmp w…ôcar w…ôHeb…ôre w…ôka w…ôb…õ ka abum a Firawona w…ôl…Ēma. K…Ē s…ôloku k…Ē nw…õ o nw…õ mere m…Ēn k'oloku su tedisr…õ ta mi.  
\v 13 K…Ē tosur…õn…õ k…Ē teyi p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnaloku nw…õ o nw…õ m…Ē. K…Ē Firawona oluks'em y…õb…ôc yem y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē. K'…õŇčgb…õk w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč kem.¬Ľ 
\s1 Isifu oloku tedisr…õ ta mere ma Firawona 
\p  
\v 14 K…Ē Firawona osom a pawen…õ k…Ē Isifu. K'awur…õn…õ k…Ē kat…ôna kat…ôna d…ôbili. K'ofonn…õ, k'…õs…ôkp…ôr yamos, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē nde Firawona …õnawe k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 15 K…Ē Firawona oloku Isifu: ¬ęIw…õr…ôp, mba ali fum is…Ēt…Ē f…õ nw…õ oŇčlok'im tedisr…õ ta mere mem m…Ē. Mba alok'im a m…ôntam k…ôloku tedisr…õ ta mere mm…õ aŇčlok'…ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē Isifu oloku Firawona: ¬ęBaf…Ē in'…Ēf…Ē! Kanu k…ôndeloku Firawona tedisr…õ ta mere m…Ēn.¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē Firawona oloku Isifu: ¬ęMere mem-…õ, k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē k…ôs…ôk inc…ôm…õna.  
\v 18 K…Ē c…ôna cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč c…ôt…Ēt c…ôtifi c…ôncaf…õ d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē c…ôy…õf…õ k…ôs…Ēm…ôt dal…õ.  
\v 19 K…Ē c…ôna cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč c…ôl…Ēma c…ôleŇčki c…ôl…õc, ci c…ôncaf…õ s…Ē c…ôk…Ē tadar…ôŇč d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē. Mba intan…ôŇčk f…õ Misira c…ôna c…ôl…õc…õ p…ôm…Ē cac…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 20 K…Ē c…ôna c…ôl…õc c…ôleŇčki nc…õ c…ôy…õf…õ k…ôs…Ēm c…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč c…ôtifi c…ôt…Ēt c…ôk…Ē.  
\v 21 C…ôna c…ôtifi nc…õ c…ôcb…õr…õ c…ôleŇčki d…ôputuk, ta anc…ôr…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ yati c…ômb…õr…õ ci d…ôputuk-…õ. K…Ē c…ôna c…ôl…õc nc…õ c…ônaŇčkan…õ s…Ē k…ôl…õc…õ, p…ôtas t…Ēk…Ē c…ônal…õc…õ m…Ē. K'int…ôm…õ.  
\v 22 K'iw…õr…ôp s…Ē nt…õ: S…ôbomp cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč sa mal…Ē s…ôt…Ēt s…ôlar…õ s…ôwur…ôs atoka Ňčin Ňčayi.  
\v 23 K…Ē s…ôbomp cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč sa mal…Ē s…ôl…Ēma s…ôf…õt s…ôwur…ôs s…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē s…ôk…Ē tant…Ēf.  
\v 24 K…Ē s…ôbomp sa mal…Ē s…ôf…õt ns…õ s…ôndi s…ôbomp sa mal…Ē s…ôp…ĒŇč s…ôk…Ē. Iloku mere mam…õ ac…ôr…õ mes. Mba ali fum is…Ēt…Ē f…õ nw…õ oŇčlok'im tedisr…õ ta mi m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 25 K…Ē Isifu oloku Firawona: ¬ęMere ma Firawona f…ôp, toloku tin t…Ē moloku. Kanu k…ôyi k…ôment…ôr Firawona nt…õ k…ôndey…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 26 C…ôna c…ôt…Ēt nc…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē. K…Ē s…ôbomp sa mal…Ē s…ôt…Ēt ns…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē, mere min m…Ē.  
\v 27 C…ôna c…ôl…õc c…ôleŇčki nc…õ c…ômp…õna c…ôk…Ē tadar…ôŇč m…Ē, meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôbomp sa mal…Ē s…ôf…õt ns…õ, dor da meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč d…Ē.  
\v 28 P…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē int…õp ti k…ôcloku Firawona m…Ē, Kanu k…ôment…ôr Firawona t…Ēk…Ē k…ôndey…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 29 Meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ma k…ôn…õmb…ôr…õ mender mam…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp.  
\v 30 K…Ē meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ma k…ôn…õmb…ôr…õ mencep…ôr-…õ meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ma dor mendec…ôm…õ mi dar…ôŇč: Dor dad…Ēk…Ē dendeluks…õ Misira dar…ôŇč.  
\v 31 K…Ē dor dad…Ēk…Ē dencep…ôr-…õ, af…Ēdetam k…ôc…ôr…õ yati k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a k…ôn…õmb…ôr…õ k…ônayi d…õ t…Ēl…Ēma-…õ. Debeki da dor dad…Ēk…Ē dendes…ĒŇč…õ ti.  
\v 32 K…Ē m…ôn…ôŇčk Firawona p…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ k…ôw…õr…ôp mere min mam…Ēk…Ē k…ôm…õr…ôŇč-…õ, Kanu k…ôyi k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôc…ôr…õ: A mes melip nn…Ē k…ôyi m…Ē, k…ôb…õlk…ôr k…Ē k…ônder oŇč k…ôb…ôc y…õb…ôc ya ki.  
\v 33 Nt…õ Firawona …õnc…ôr…õ oŇč a Isifu …Ēy…Ē amera, k'…õnc…ôr…õ s…Ē mes m…Ē, k…Ē Firawona …Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē d…õb…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira disr…õ.  
\v 34 Firawona p…ôy…õf…õ oŇč, p…ôbonc…ôs ak…Ē Ňčandey…Ēn…õ ab…õ aŇč…õ Ňčandek…Ēt…õn…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ŇčabaŇč…ôs katin ka k…ôcam…ôt ka k…ôs…Ēt…Ē y…õt…õl yaŇčan, at…Ēf Ňča Misira meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ma k…ôm…õmb…ôr…õ mm…õ disr…õ m…Ē.  
\v 35 ŇäaloŇčka yeri ya meren mobotu mm…õ mender m…Ē, Ňčay…Ē ti dim da Firawona d…ônt…Ēf. Firawona p…ôsom pam…õŇčk yeri s…ôdare f…ôp.  
\v 36 Yeri yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē andem…õŇčk…õ at…Ēf, k…ôd…õm ka meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ma dor mm…õ Isifu oloku k…ôdeyi m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta dor dad…Ēk…Ē dedetam at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Isifu …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ômar…ôs w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôka Firawona 
\p  
\v 37 K…Ē moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ēmb…Ēt Firawona k…Ē amar…ôs …Ēn.  
\v 38 K…Ē Firawona eyif Ňča: ¬ęAndetam k…ôs…Ēt…Ē fum p…ôm…Ē Isifu ba, p…ôy…Ē amera Ňča Kanu?¬Ľ  
\v 39 K…Ē Firawona oloku Isifu: ¬ęNt…õ Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm k…ôc…ôr…õ ka mes mam…õ f…ôp m…Ē, fum o fum eyi f…õ nw…õ …Ēs…Ēk domp, p…ôc…ôr…õ mes p…ôm…Ē m…ôna m…Ē.  
\v 40 M…ôna Isifu, m…ôn'endey…Ēn…õ w…ôkiriŇč ka k…ôl…Ē kem, afum a at…Ēf Ňčem f…ôp. M…ôn'…Ē Ňčandeyi dar…ôŇč, d…õb…õ da ina Firawona gb…ôc…ôr…ôm dendecep…ôr dam.¬Ľ  
\v 41 K…Ē Firawona oloku Isifu: ¬ęMisira m…Ē mam…õ is…ĒŇč …ôm d…õb…õ da at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ f…ôp.¬Ľ  
\v 42 K…Ē Firawona owur…õ kurund…õ k…Ēn d…ôk…ôca, k'…õmb…õr ki Isifu d…ôk…ôca. K'…õmb…õr Isifu yamos y…Ēt…Ēt ya k…ôloto ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler. K'…õŇčgb…õk k…Ē k…õma d…ôkilim.  
\v 43 K…Ē Firawona …õmb…õk Isifu abil Ňča d…ôk…ôwan Ňč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnac…Ēnc Ňč…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčanc…õk k…ôk…Ē. K…Ē afum Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôkul-kul…õn…õ Ňča: ¬ęAb…ôrek!¬Ľ \f + \fr 41:43 \fq Ab…ôrek\ft  = ¬ęN…ôtontn…õ!¬Ľ \f* Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē Firawona …õnas…ĒŇč Isifu d…õb…õ, at…Ēf Ňča Misira.  
\v 44 K…Ē Firawona oloku s…Ē Isifu: ¬ęIn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Firawona! K…Ē m…ônt…Ēwos…õ-…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira, ali fum …Ēf…Ēyekti d…õ k…ôca, k'…ĒŇčk…Ēyekti k…ôc…ôk k…Ēn at…Ēf Ňča Misira.¬Ľ  
\v 45 K…Ē Firawona ewe Isifu tewe ta Misira ¬ęCaf…ônat Paheneyah.¬Ľ K'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē w…ôran pacwe k…Ē Asnat, wan w…ôran ka Potifera, w…ôloŇčn…õ ka dare da Hon. K…Ē Isifu owur k…ôk…Ēc…ôr…õ Misira mm…õ …õnas…Ēt…Ē k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ d…õb…õ ta …õnc…ôr…õ mi m…Ē.  
\v 46 Isifu …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco maas (30) a Firawona p…ôdec…ôr…õ k…Ē. Nt…õ anc…ômb…ôr k…Ē d…õb…õ m…Ē, f…Ēr ya Firawona kiriŇč y…Ē Isifu …õnawur k…ôk…Ēc…ôr…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp.  
\v 47 Meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ma k…ôn…õmb…ôr…õ mam…Ēk…Ē disr…õ, k…Ē afum a Misira Ňčamb…õr…õn…õ k…ôb…ôc.  
\v 48 K…Ē Isifu oloŇčka yeri yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp Misira meren mm…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. K'oloŇčka yeri ya s…ôdare s…ôf…õt s…ôk…Ē s…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr s…ôdare s…ôp…ĒŇč m…Ē.  
\v 49 Isifu …õnaloŇčka kur ka yeri p…ôm…Ē k…ôs…ônc ka d…ôk…ôba, kur k…ônab…õk haŇč pacc…õm-c…õmn…õ a dor d…Ēf…Ēs…Ētam k…ôsump…ôr aka Misira.  
\v 50 Teren t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ta dor, k…Ē Isifu oŇčkom awut arkun m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ Asnat wan w…ôran ka Potifera w…ôloŇčn…õ ka dare da Hon …õnakom…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 51 K…Ē Isifu ewe coco c…Ēn Manase, ti tat…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôp…ôl…ôr ka p…ôcuy f…ôp k…Ē k…ôsak…õn…õ k…Ē aka k…ôl…Ē ka kas.  
\v 52 K'ewe wan k…Ēn t…ĒŇč…Ē ∆źfrayim, ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē dokomb…ôra at…Ēf nŇč…õ analap…ôs k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 53 K…Ē meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ma k…ôn…õmb…ôr…õ melip.  
\v 54 K…Ē meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ma dor moncop p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Isifu …õnaloku ti m…Ē. Dor d…õnayi t…Ēf ya Misira f…ôp. Mba yeri y…õm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ y…õnayi s…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp.  
\v 55 Nt…õ dor dosump…ôr aka Misira m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčambok…ôr Firawona k…ôs…Ēt…Ē ka c…ôcom. K…Ē Firawona oloku aka Misira: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē n…ôn…ôŇčk Isifu, nt…õ oŇčloku nu m…Ē, n…ôy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 56 Nt…õ dor d…õmb…õk Misira m…Ē, k…Ē Isifu oncop k…ôcams…ôr aka Misira mal…Ē. Mba dor d…õncb…õk k…ôb…õk d…ôm at…Ēf Ňča Misira.  
\v 57 Afum Ňčacy…õf…õ mofo f…ôp ma Misira k…ôdeway mal…Ē nn…Ē Isifu eyi m…Ē, bawo dor d…õnanaŇčkan…õ k…ôb…õk Misira. 
\c 42  
\s1 Yakuba k…ôsom k…Ēn awut …Ēn Misira 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yakuba ene a m…õŇčgb…õn \f + \fr 42:1 \ft  M…õŇčgb…õn mm…õ anc…Ē pas…Ēt…Ē farin m…Ē\f* meyi Misira. K…Ē Yakuba oloku awut …Ēn: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ôndeyin…õ nn…Ē n…ôcm…Ēm…ôn…õn…õ f…Ēr disr…õ-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 2 K…Ē Yakuba oloku: ¬ęIne a mal…Ē meyi Misira. N…ôtor n…ôk…Ē n…ôway…õ su d…ôndo mal…Ē, ta padefin…õ dor.¬Ľ  
\v 3 K…Ē aw…õnc a Isifu w…ôco Ňčantor k…ôk…Ēway mal…Ē Misira.  
\v 4 Mba Yakuba …õnasak f…õ BeŇčyamin w…ôk…Ē …õnapaŇčn…õ k…õr…õ k…Ē Isifu m…Ē p…ôc…õps…õ aw…õnc aŇča dar…ôŇč, bawo Yakuba …õnaloku: ¬ęBeŇčyamin …Ēf…Ēk…Ē ta tes t…õl…õc t…Ēl…Ēma t…Ēk…Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē awut a Yakuba ŇčaŇčk…Ē Misira k…ôk…Ēway mal…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē afum alar…ôm Ňčanck…Ē Misira d…ôk…ôway mal…Ē m…Ē, bawo dor d…õnayi at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč f…ôp. 
\s1 Isifu eyeŇčk…ôs ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…Ēn nn…Ē aw…õnc Ňčayi m…Ē 
\p  
\v 6 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē Isifu p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka s…ôdare sa Misira. Nk…Ēn …õncway…ôr afum a Misira f…ôp mal…Ē. K…Ē aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčander Ňčatontn…õn…õ Isifu f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč, Ňčac…ôp mobu d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 7 K…Ē Isifu …õn…ôŇčk aw…õnc aŇča. K'…õn…õp…ôl Ňča. Mba owur…ôr f…õ Ňča k…ôc…ôr…õn…õ. K'olok-lok…ôr…õ Ňča dim deyeŇčki, k'eyif Ňča: ¬ęDeke n…ôy…õf…õ-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē aw…õnc aŇča Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęAt…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč Ňč…Ē s…ôy…õf…õ, k…Ē s…ônder k…ôway nn…Ē yeri.¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē Isifu …õn…õp…ôl aw…õnc aŇča. Mba aw…õnc aŇča Ňčanan…õp…ôl f…õ k…Ē.  
\v 9 K…Ē Isifu …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ mere m…Ēk…Ē …õnaw…õr…ôp tetaŇčan m…Ē. K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęAt…õn mes Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ! Mes ma at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ m…Ē n…ônder k…ôt…õn, n…ôk…Ē n…ôloku mi aka at…Ēf Ňčonu.¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē Ňčaloku Isifu: ¬ęAla, mariki mem, d…ôk…ôway yeri gb…ôc…ôr…ôm s…ônder.  
\v 11 D…õw…õnca d…Ē s…ôy…Ē f…ôp fosu, w…ôrkun w…ôkin okom su. S…ôs…Ēk…õn…õ b…ôk…ôc! S…ôclok'…ôm a d…ôk…ôt…õn yeri gb…ôc…ôr…ôm s…ônder.¬Ľ  
\v 12 K…Ē Isifu oloku Ňča: ¬ęK…ôbup…ôr…õ ti k…Ē n…ônd…õ, m…õtamb…ôr ma at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ m…Ē n…ônder k…ôt…õn n…ôk…Ēloku mi ndoronu.¬Ľ  
\v 13 K…Ē aw…õnc aŇča Ňčaloku Isifu: ¬ęW…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč w…Ē s…ônayi kas kosu k…ôkom nde KanaŇč. Mba w…ôk…Ē …õf…õt…õ su dac…Ē m…Ē eyi m…Ēk…Ē d…õk…õr k…Ē papa kosu, k…Ē w…ôkin …õnafi.¬Ľ  
\v 14 K…Ē Isifu oloku Ňča: ¬ęT…Ēk…Ē iloku nu m…Ē, ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ kance: At…õn mes Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ!  
\v 15 Awa, y…õb…ôc ny…õ y'indec…ômb…ôr nu: Ind…õrm…õ nu tewe ta Firawona, n…ôf…Ēwur nn…Ē ta w…ôf…õt konu w…ôlp…ôs w…ôkak…Ē n…ôsak d…õk…õr m…Ē ender-…õ.  
\v 16 N…ôsom w…õnc konu w…ôkin p…ôk…Ēk…õr…õ w…õnc konu w…ôkak…Ē n…ôsak d…õk…õr m…Ē. K…Ē n…ôna aŇč…õ endesak nn…Ē m…Ē, d…ôbili andeb…õr nu. Andem…Ēm…ôn moloku monu, pac…ôr…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ kance k…Ē n…ôloku-…õ. K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ind…õrm…õ nu tewe ta Firawona at…õn mes Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 17 K…Ē Isifu …õmb…õr Ňča d…ôbili mata maas.  
\v 18 Tataka ta maas, k…Ē Isifu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôy…Ē nt…õ, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôyi doru. IŇčnes…õ Kanu!  
\v 19 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a n…ôs…Ēk…õn…õ b…ôk…ôc-…õ, n…ôsak w…õnc konu w…ôkin d…ôbili. N…ôna alp…ôs aŇč…õ n…ôken…õ afum anu yeri k…ôr…õs bawo dor deyi.  
\v 20 N…ôk…õr…õn'em w…ôf…õt konu w…ôk…Ē n…ôsak d…ôndo m…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pam…Ēm…ôn moloku monu k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a kance k…Ē-…õ, ta n…ôdefi.¬Ľ  
\v 21 Ti t…Ē Ňčanay…Ē, Ňčaclok…õn…õ: ¬ę∆źy. S…ôn'…õnay…Ē ti w…õnc kosu. Bawo an…ôŇčk ay…õk Ňč…Ēn, t…õm nt…õ oncloku su a paŇčaŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē m…Ē, ta anc…ôŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē-…õ. Ti t…Ē ay…õk Ňč…Ēn Ňčeyi k…ôsut…õ su tant…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē Ruben …õl…õk moloku, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęInaloku f…õ nu ti ba, ta n…ôy…Ē wan nw…õ p…ôl…õc? Mba n…ônac…ôŇčk…ôl f'em. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč awer su mecir m…Ēn.¬Ľ  
\v 23 Aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčanac…ôr…õ f…õ a Isifu eŇčne kusu k…ôŇčan bawo w…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ moloku …õnayi k…Ē dac…Ē k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča.  
\v 24 K…Ē Isifu …Ēmb…Ēl…õ aw…õnc aŇča, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôbok. 
\s1 Awut a Yakuba k…ôlukus k…ôŇčan KanaŇč 
\p Nt…õ elip m…Ē, k'oluks…ôrn…õ k…ôdelok-lok…ôr Ňča. K'…õl…õk Simey…ĒŇč aw…õnc aŇča dac…Ē, k'…õmb…õr k…Ē d…ôbili f…Ēr ya aw…õnc aŇča kiriŇč.  
\v 25 K…Ē Isifu osom a palas…õ Ňča yeri d…ôl…Ēba, paluks…õ nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôsam p…Ēn nde al…Ēba Ňč…Ēn, pasars…ôr Ňča yeri yay…Ēk…Ē. Ti t…Ē anay…Ēn…õ Ňča.  
\v 26 K…Ē aw…õnc …Ēn Ňčasars…ôr s…Ēfale s…ôŇčan yeri. K…Ē Ňčasump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē.  
\v 27 K…Ē w…õnc ka Isifu w…ôkin ende p…ôsik…ôli al…Ēba Ňč…Ēn nde d…ôkarwaŇčse p…ôfaŇč k…ôwur…õ s…Ēfale s…Ēn yika y…Ēs…Ēm, k…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …õn…ôŇčk p…ôsam p…Ēn al…Ēba Ňč…Ēn disr…õ.  
\v 28 K'oloku aw…õnc aŇča: ¬ęAluks'em p…ôsam pem. Ip…õmp…õ nn…Ē al…Ēba Ňčem.¬Ľ K…Ē mera yeyi Ňča yamayama k…ôc…ôr…õ a ŇčaŇčk…Ē d…ôk…ôway paluks…õ Ňča s…Ē p…ôsam paŇčan. K…Ē Ňčayifn…õ: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē Kanu k…ôy…Ē su tant…õ-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 29 K…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ ndena papa k…ôŇčan Yakuba nde at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč. K…Ē Ňčal…Ēm…ôr kas k…ôŇčan mes m…Ēk…Ē m…õnas…Ēt…Ē Ňča m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 30 K…Ē Ňčaloku kas k…ôŇčan: ¬ęFum w…ôk…Ē …Ēy…Ēn…õ mariki ma at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē, olok-lok…ôr…õ su dim deyeŇčki, k'endeŇč…õ su k…ôy…Ēn…õ at…õn mes ma Misira mm…õ s…ôndeloku aka nn…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 31 K…Ē s…ôloku k…Ē a s…ôs…Ēk…õn…õ b…ôk…ôc, baf…Ē at…õn mes Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ.  
\v 32 K…Ē S…ôloku k…Ē s…Ē a w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč w…Ē s…ônayi kas kosu k…ôkom, mba w…ôf…õt kosu eyi d…õk…õr nde KanaŇč, k…Ē w…ôkin …õnafi su dac…Ē.  
\v 33 K…Ē mariki ma Misira moloku su: ‚ÄĻNt…õ t…Ē n…ôndey…Ē a itam k…ôc…ôr…õ a n…ôs…Ēk…õn…õ b…ôk…ôc. N…ôsak w…õnc konu w…ôkin nn…Ē, n…ôken…õ afum anu yeri k…ôr…õsna bawo dor deyi.  
\v 34 N…ôk…Ē, n…ôk…õr'em w…ôf…õt konu. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, indec…ôr…õ a baf…Ē at…õn mes Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ, k…Ē n…ôs…Ēk…õn…õ b…ôk…ôc. Indeluks…õ nu w…õnc konu, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē n…ôc…ôm…õ s…Ē k…ôcam…ôs konu dar…ôŇč d…Ēt…Ēf.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 35 Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ ndaraŇčan ak…Ē Ňčayuk mal…Ē m…Ēk…Ē Ňčanak…õr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē f…ôp faŇčan Ňčan…ôŇčk…ôs-n…ôŇčk…ôs p…ôsam paŇčan nde l…Ēba yaŇčan disr…õ. Ňäa k…Ē kas k…ôŇčan nt…õ Ňčan…ôŇčk…ôs p…ôsam nde l…Ēba yaŇčan disr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ônder Ňča.  
\v 36 K…Ē kas k…ôŇčan Yakuba oloku Ňča: ¬ęAwut em Ňč…Ē n…ôfaŇč k…ôbaŇčs…ôr im! Isifu eyi f…õ s…Ē doru, Simey…ĒŇč eyi f…õ s…Ē doru, k…Ē n…ôfaŇč s…Ē k…ôl…õk…ôr im BeŇčyamin-…õ! In'…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp mendet…Ēr…ôs.¬Ľ  
\v 37 K…Ē Ruben oloku papa k…Ēn: ¬ęM…ôde m…ôy…Ē padif awut em m…õr…ôŇč k'int…Ēk…õr'am B…õŇčyamin. M…ôb…õr im k…Ē d…ôwaca, indek…õr'am k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 38 K…Ē Yakuba oloku: ¬ęWan kem …Ēf…Ētor k…Ē n…ôna, bawo w…ôbek'…Ēn Isifu efi. Sona s'eyi oŇč. K…Ē t…õl…õc t…Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…Ē d…Ēp…Ē-…õ, c…ôke c…Ē n…ôndey…Ē-…õ, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē n…ôŇčs…ĒŇč'em k…ôtor…õ c…ôfon cem c…ôfer dabiya k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc Ňčocuy nde afi Ňčayi m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\c 43  
\s1 Yakuba k…ôwos…õ k…Ēn BeŇčyamin k…ôk…Ē k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča 
\p  
\v 1 Dor d…õncb…õk k…ôb…õk d…ôm d…Ēt…Ēf.  
\v 2 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôdi mal…Ē m…Ēk…Ē Ňčanak…õr…õ k…ôy…õf…õ Misira m…Ē, k…Ē Yakuba oloku awut …Ēn: ¬ęN…ôluks…ôrn…õ, n…ôk…Ē n…ôway…õ su yeri yepic.¬Ľ  
\v 3 K…Ē Yuda oloku k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôb…õ ka Misira …õnabeŇčn…õ su: ‚ÄĻTa in…ôŇčk nu s…Ē c…ôro, k…Ē n…ônt…Ēk…õr'em w…õnc konu w…ôlp…ôs-…õ.‚Äļ  
\v 4 K…Ē m…ôŇčwos…õ k…ôsak w…ôf…õt kosu s…ôk…Ē-…õ, s…ôntor Misira k…ôk…Ēway'am yeri.  
\v 5 K…Ē m…ônt…Ēwos…õ k…ôsak k…Ē s…ôk…Ē-…õ, s…ôf…Ētam k…ôtor Misira k…ôk…Ēway'am yeri, bawo w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē …õnaloku: ‚ÄĻTa in…ôŇčk nu s…Ē c…ôro k…Ē n…ônt…Ēk…õr'em w…ôf…õt konu-…õ.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē Yakuba oloku: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ônay…Ēn'em p…ôl…õc tant…õ, k…ôcloku w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē a n…ôy…Ē w…ôf…õt-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 7 K…Ē awut …Ēn Ňčaloku: ¬ęW…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē …õnayif…ôt su p…ôlar…ôm tetosu k…Ē tokom…õn…õ tosu, p…ôcyif su: ‚ÄĻPapa konu …Ēs…Ēr…Ēyi doru? N…ôy…Ē w…õnc w…ôl…Ēma s…Ē?‚Äļ K…Ē s…ôluks…õ k…Ē moloku mam…Ēk…Ē. S…ônatam k…ôc…ôr…õ, a endeloku su: ‚ÄĻN…ôk…Ē n…ôk…õr'em w…ôf…õt konu!‚Äļ?¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē Yuda oloku papa k…ôŇčan Yakuba: ¬ęM…ôsak w…ôf…õt s…ôk…Ē k…Ē ina. S…ôndey…õf…õ s…ôk…Ē, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôdeyi doru ta s…ôfi-…õ, m…ôna papa, awut asu k…Ē s…ôna.  
\v 9 In'…Ēs…ĒŇč …ôm temer, teta w…ôf…õt: In'…Ē m…ôndewer k…Ē, k…Ē int…Ēk…õr'am k…Ē-…õ, ta iluks…õ k…Ē ider ib…õr …ôm k…Ē d…ôwaca-…õ, in'endesar…õ t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē kiciya doru o doru nn…Ē m…ôyi m…Ē.  
\v 10 Pat…Ēb…Ēls…õn…õ moloku-…õ, k…Ē s…ôntam nt…õ k…ôk…Ē k…ôm…õr…ôŇč s…ôlukus.¬Ľ  
\v 11 K…Ē papa k…ôŇčan Yakuba oloku Ňča: ¬ęBawo teyi tant…õ, n…ôk…Ē n…ôy…Ē nt…õ: N…ôl…õk yopoc…õ, ca ya at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ y…Ēl…Ēma n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr…õn…õ w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē: D…Ēni, m…õs…õ ma c…ôme mepic, cigbili, yamaku, m…õŇčgb…õn ma yalak…õ k…Ē c…Ēla.\f + \fr 43:11 \ft  Ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē m…õŇčgb…õn m…õy…õŇčk k…ôway.\f* 
\v 12 N…ôl…õk p…ôsam p…Ēk…Ē n…ônakek…ôr…õ t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē k…ôm…õr…ôŇč. N…ôluks…õ p…ôsam p…Ēk…Ē anab…õr…õ nu d…ôl…Ēba m…Ē, t…Ēl…Ēma Ňčanaciya k…ôciya d…ôm.  
\v 13 N…ôl…õk w…ôf…õt konu n…ôk…Ē ndena w…ôrkun w…ôkaw…õ.  
\v 14 Intola MARIKI nw…õ …õntam mes ma doru f…ôp m…Ē, p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē p…ôk…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ nu n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr p…ôsak w…õnc konu w…ôk…Ē osump…ôr m…Ē n…ôder, n…ôk…õr…õn…õ s…Ē BeŇčyamin! K…Ē ina k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a awut em Ňčandewur im d…ôwaca-…õ, awa Ňčawur im d…ôwaca!¬Ľ 
\s1 Isifu Ňčandi yeri k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča 
\p  
\v 15 K…Ē awut a Yakuba Ňčal…õk yopoc…õ yay…Ēk…Ē k…Ē p…ôsam p…Ēk…Ē Ňčanakek…ôr…õ t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē k…ôm…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē BeŇčyamin. K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ, k…Ē Ňčantor Misira. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčament…ôrn…õ Isifu.  
\v 16 Nt…õ Isifu …õn…ôŇčk BeŇčyamin k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča m…Ē, k'oloku w…ôcams…õ k…Ēn: ¬ęM…ôb…õrs…õ afum akaŇč…õ d…õk…õr, m…ôdif p…Ēc…Ēl, m…ôcoŇč, bawo afum akaŇč…õ Ňč…Ē s…ôndenadi m…Ēk…Ē yeri tofo tin daŇčana.¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē fum w…ôkak…Ē …Ēy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Isifu …õnaloku k…Ē m…Ē, k'…õmb…õrs…õ afum aŇč…õ d…õk…õr ndena Isifu.  
\v 18 K…Ē aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčanes…õ nt…õ anab…õrs…õ Ňča ndena Isifu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęTeta p…ôsam p…Ēk…Ē anasak l…Ēba yosu disr…õ m…Ē ti t'aŇčk…õr…õ su nn…Ē. AŇčk…õr…õ su nn…Ē, Ňčadew…õk…ôrn…õ su Ňčac…ômb…ôr su dacar k…Ē s…Ēfale sosu.¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ w…ôcams…õ ka Isifu, k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē moloku mm…õ d…ôkusuŇčka:  
\v 20 ¬ęN…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ su, mariki mem! S…ônader t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…ôdeway yeri.  
\v 21 Nt…õ s…ônclukus m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ēsik…ôli l…Ēba yosu karwaŇčse, k…Ē s…ôn…ôŇčk nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôsam p…Ēn nde al…Ēba Ňč…Ēn. Mba s…ôŇčk…õr…õn…õ s…Ē pi.  
\v 22 S…ôŇčk…õr…õn…õ s…Ē p…ôsam p…Ēl…Ēma k…ôdeway yeri. S…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ nw…õ …õnab…õr p…ôsam pap…Ēk…Ē nde l…Ēba yosu disr…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 23 K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ oloku Ňča: ¬ęTa n…ônes…õ b…ôk…ôc y…Ēf…Ēr nu! Kanu konu k…Ē, Kanu ka papa konu k…ônas…ĒŇč nu p…ôsam nde l…Ēba yonu. P…ôsam ponu p…õnader im.¬Ľ 
\p K…Ē w…ôcams…õ ka Isifu owur…õn…õ Simey…ĒŇč nn…Ē aw…õnc aŇča Ňčayi m…Ē.  
\v 24 K…Ē fum w…ôkaw…õ …õmb…õrs…õ Ňča nde k…ôl…Ē ka Isifu disr…õ. K'…Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča domun, k…Ē Ňčambik…õn…õ w…õc…ôk. K'…Ēs…ĒŇč s…Ē s…Ēfale s…ôŇčan yika.  
\v 25 K…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs k…ôpoc…õ k…ôŇčan, Ňčackar k…ôder ka Isifu daŇč, bawo Ňčananen…õ Isifu p…ôcloku: ¬ęS…ôn'endedi yeri daŇč d…Ēm…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Ňča.¬Ľ  
\v 26 Nt…õ Isifu ender d…õk…õr daŇč m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč Isifu yopoc…õ yaŇčan ny…õ Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčantontn…õn…õ k…Ē d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 27 K…Ē Isifu eyif…ôt Ňča teta dis daŇčan, k'eyif Ňča: ¬ęPapa konu w…ôtem w…ôk…Ē n…ôŇčle m…Ē, …õntamn…õ? ∆Üs…Ēr…Ēyi doru?¬Ľ  
\v 28 K…Ē aw…õnc aŇča Ňčaloku: ¬ęW…ôcar kam, papa kosu …õntamn…õ, …Ēs…Ēr…Ēyi doru.¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčantontn…õn…õ Isifu.  
\v 29 K…Ē Isifu eyekti f…Ēr. Nt…õ …õn…ôŇčk BeŇčyamin w…ôpaŇčn…õ k…Ēn k…õr…õ m…Ē, k'eyif Ňča: ¬ęW…ôkaw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôf…õt konu w…ôlp…ôs, w…ôk…Ē n…ônalok'im tet…Ēn m…Ē?¬Ľ K'…Ēn…Ēc…ôr: ¬ęKanu k…ômar …ôm wan kem!¬Ľ  
\v 30 K…Ē Isifu oncop…ôr moloku, bawo …õnct…õy…õ-t…õy…õ p…ôbotu pa k…ôn…ôŇčk ka w…õnc, …õnafaŇč k…ôbok. K…Ē Isifu …õmb…õr…õ dukul…Ē d…Ēn, k'ombok di haŇč.  
\v 31 K…Ē Isifu …õsak k…ôbok, k'ombuf…ôrn…õ k…ôro, k'owur. K'…õs…õp k…ôt…Ēbok s…Ē f…Ēr ya aw…õnc aŇča kiriŇč. K'oloku: ¬ęN…ôwur…õn…õ su yeri.¬Ľ  
\v 32 K'amb…õr…õ Isifu yeri taciŇča, aw…õnc aŇča taciŇča, k…Ē aMisira Ňča Ňčayi s…Ē taciŇča. Bawo aMisira Ňčancwos…õ f…õ k…ôpaŇčn…õ dap da yeri k…Ē aHeb…ôre.  
\v 33 K…Ē aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčand…õ f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč. K…ôy…õf…õ ka coco ca papa k…ôŇčan haŇč w…ôf…õt k…ôŇčan nw…õ o nw…õ k…Ē d…ôk…ônd…õ d…Ēn. K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôlok…õn…õ k…ôciyan…õ nk…õ k…ôyi Ňča nt…õ Isifu osump…ôr Ňča m…Ē.  
\v 34 K…Ē Isifu …õmb…õr…õn…õ Ňča yeri y…Ēn ny…õ nk…Ēn encdi m…Ē. Mba p…õb…õr…õn…õ mp…õ …õnas…ĒŇč BeŇčyamin m…Ē p…õnala k…ôcam…ôt, p…õtas pa ak…Ē. K…Ē Ňčamun haŇč k…Ē p…ônt…ôŇčn…õ Ňča k…Ē nk…Ēn Isifu. 
\c 44  
\s1 Isifu …Ēnt…Ēr…ôs aw…õnc …Ēn nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôtam k…ôc…ôr…õ b…ôk…ôc yaŇčan m…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Isifu oloku w…ôcams…õ k…Ēn: ¬ęM…ôlas…õ afum akaŇč…õ mal…Ē d…ôl…Ēba p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē l…Ēba yaŇčan y…õntam k…ôl…õk mal…Ē m…Ē. M…ôb…õr p…ôsam paŇčan nde l…Ēba yaŇčan disr…õ.  
\v 2 M…ôb…õr s…Ē ap…Ēt Ňčem Ňčomun…õ Ňča gbeti Ňč…Ēk…Ē, nde al…Ēba Ňča w…ôf…õt w…ôk…Ē k…Ē p…ôsam p…Ēk…Ē …õŇčk…õr…õ k…ôdeway…õ mal…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôcams…õ ka Isifu …Ēy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Isifu …õnaloku k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 3 Dec dendes…Ēk, k'asak afum aŇč…õ k…ôlukus nde ndaraŇčan k…Ē s…Ēfale s…ôŇčan.  
\v 4 Ňäawur dare disr…õ ta Ňčantab…Ēl…õ-…õ, k…Ē Isifu oloku w…ôcams…õ k…Ēn: ¬ęM…ôy…õf…õ m…ôc…ôm…õ afum aŇč…õ dar…ôŇč haŇč m…ôb…ôp Ňča. M…ôyif Ňča: ‚ÄĻTa ake t…Ē n…ôs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôt…Ēt k…ôway p…ôl…õc-…õ?  
\v 5 Baf…Ē ap…Ēt ŇčaŇč…õ Ňč…Ē mariki mem oŇčmun…õ, Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôc…ôr…õ t…Ēk…Ē tender m…Ē ba? N…ônciya k…ôy…Ē tant…õ n…ôy…Ē m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē w…ôcams…õ ka Isifu …õmb…õl…ôr Ňča k'…õmb…ôp Ňča. K'…ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õn…õ Ňča moloku m…Ēk…Ē Isifu …õnasom k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 7 K…Ē Ňčaloku w…ôcams…õ ka Isifu: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē mariki oŇčlok-lok…ôr…õ su tant…õ-…õ? S…ôna amar…ôs am s…ôf…Ētam k…ôy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 8 S…ônuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôr…õsna k…Ē s…ôŇčk…õr…õ nu p…ôsam p…Ēk…Ē s…ônan…ôŇčk nde l…Ēba yosu m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ KanaŇč. Ta ake t…Ē s…ôndekiy…õn…õ p…ôsam k…Ē p…ôyi f…õ ti k…õma nde k…ôl…Ē ka mariki mam-…õ?  
\v 9 Nw…õ o nw…õ aŇčn…ôŇčk…õ ca yay…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, padif k…Ē, k…Ē s…ôna f…ôp s…ôy…Ēn…õ acar a mariki mem!¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē w…ôcams…õ ka Isifu oloku Ňča: ¬ęAwa. Ine nu sim! Nw…õ o nw…õ aŇčn…ôŇčk…õ paka m…Ē, …ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ w…ôcar kem. N…ôna alp…ôs aŇč…õ n…ôŇčk…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 11 K…Ē Ňčamb…õlk…ôr-b…õlk…ôr k…ôtor…õ-tor…õ l…Ēba yaŇčan d…ônt…Ēf k…Ē Ňčasik…ôli-sik…ôli yi.  
\v 12 K…Ē w…ôcams…õ ka Isifu oncop k…ôfen-feni k…ôy…õf…õ al…Ēba Ňča w…ôbeki, k'…õl…ôps…ôr al…Ēba Ňča w…ôf…õt. K…Ē w…ôcams…õ ka Isifu …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôn…ôŇčk ap…Ēt nŇč…õ nde al…Ēba Ňča BeŇčyamin.  
\v 13 K…Ē aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčawal-wali yamos yaŇčan, k…Ē Ňčand…ônd…ôs…ôr s…Ē s…Ēfale s…ôŇčan l…Ēba yaŇčan. K…Ē Ňčaluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē dare disr…õ. 
\s1 Yuda k…ôc…Ēp…õ BeŇčyamin 
\p  
\v 14 Yuda k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča Ňčander s…Ē nda Isifu w…ôk…Ē …õnas…Ēr…Ēyi k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē Ňčanasak k…Ē m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčant…õmp…õn…õ d…ônt…Ēf Isifu f…Ēr kiriŇč.  
\v 15 K…Ē Isifu eyif Ňča: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē n…ôy…Ē tant…õ-…õ? N…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ a intam k…ôc…ôr…õ t…Ēk…Ē t…ĒŇčgb…Ēpn…õ m…Ē, t…Ēk…Ē tender m…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē Yuda oloku: ¬ęC…ôke c'indeloku mariki mem-…õ? C…ôke c'indeloku m…ôtam k…ôlaŇč su-…õ? Kanu k…ômb…ôp amar…ôs am Ňčaciya. S…ôy…Ēn…õ oŇč acar a mariki mosu, k…ôy…õf…õ s…ôna haŇč w…ôk…Ē an…ôŇčk ap…Ēt al…Ēba Ňč…Ēn disr…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē Isifu oloku: ¬ęIf…Ēdeb…ôc ti tat…Ēk…Ē! Fum nw…õ an…ôŇčk…õ ap…Ēt m…Ē, endey…Ēn…õ w…ôcar kem. K…Ē n…ôna, n…ôp…õrn…õ n…ôk…Ē ndena papa konu b…ôk…ôc yoforu disr…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 18 K…Ē Yuda …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Isifu k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęIl…Ēkt…ôrn'am mariki, m…ôwos…õ w…ômar…ôs kam p…ôlok-lok…ôr …ôm ta ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õp'am nn…Ē eyi m…Ē! Bawo m…ôyi p…ôm…Ē Firawona.  
\v 19 T…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Mariki …õnayif…ôt amar…ôs …Ēn p…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻN…ôy…Ē kas k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ w…ôf…õt ba?‚Äļ  
\v 20 K…Ē s…ôwos…õn…õ k…Ē: ‚ÄĻS…ôy…Ē kas k…ôtem, k…Ē w…ôf…õt wan nw…õ oŇčkom detem d…Ēn disr…õ m…Ē. W…ôpaŇčn…õ k…Ēn k…õr…õ …õnafi. K…õr…õ k…Ēn k…ôkom, sona s'eyi oŇč, k…Ē kas …Ēmb…Ēt…ôr k…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 21 K…Ē m…ôloku amar…ôs am: ‚ÄĻN…ôk…Ē n…ôk…õr…õ w…ôf…õt konu in…ôŇčk k…Ē f…Ēr yem.‚Äļ  
\v 22 K…Ē s…ôloku mariki mem: ‚ÄĻW…ôf…õt kosu …Ēf…Ētam k…ôy…õf…õ papa kosu k…ôs…ôk. K'…õy…õf…õ k…Ē k…ôs…ôk-…õ, papa kosu eŇčfi.‚Äļ  
\v 23 K…Ē m…ôloku amar…ôs am: ‚ÄĻK…Ē n…ônt…Ēk…õr…õ w…ôf…õt konu-…õ, ta in…ôŇčk nu s…Ē d…õ.‚Äļ  
\v 24 Nt…õ s…ôluks…ôrn…õ ndena papa kosu w…ômar…ôs kam m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôluks…õ k…Ē moloku ma m…ôna mariki mem.  
\v 25 K…Ē papa kosu oloku: ‚ÄĻN…ôk…Ē s…Ē n…ôway…õ su yeri yepic.‚Äļ  
\v 26 K…Ē s…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻS…ôf…Ētam k…ôk…Ē. Mba k…Ē s…ôŇčsol…õ w…ôf…õt kosu-…õ, s…ôŇčk…Ē, bawo w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē …Ēf…Ēwos…õ k…ôn…ôŇčk su c…ôro ta s…ôŇčken…õ k…Ē w…ôf…õt kosu p…ôn…ôŇčk-…õ.‚Äļ  
\v 27 K…Ē papa kosu w…ômar…ôs kam oloku su: ‚ÄĻN…ônc…ôr…õ a w…ôran kem awut m…õr…ôŇč Ňč'…õnakom'em.  
\v 28 K…Ē w…ôkin ende p…ôsak im. IlaŇč ti a w…ôkak…Ē, anawat…ôri-wat…ôri k…Ē, bawo intan…ôŇčk f…õ k…Ē haŇč m…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 29 K…Ē n…ômbaŇč…ôr im s…Ē nd…õk…ôl w…ôkaw…õ-…õ, tes tedek…Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…Ē-…õ, p…ôcuy disr…õ p…Ē n…ôndes…ĒŇč'em k…ôtor…õ c…ôfon cem c…ôfer dabiya nde afi Ňčayi m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 30 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč k'ilukus nde w…ômar…ôs kam, papa kem eyi m…Ē, ta iŇčken…õ k…Ē w…ôf…õt kosu nw…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…Ēn Ňčosump…ôr m…Ē,  
\v 31 eŇčfi katina k…Ē …Ēnt…Ēn…ôŇčk…õ su w…ôf…õt kosu-…õ. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē amar…ôs am Ňčandes…ĒŇč…õ w…ômar…ôs kam papa kosu k…ôtor…õn…õ c…ôfon c…Ēn c…ôfer dabiya p…ôcuy disr…õ.  
\v 32 Bawo ina w…ômar…ôs kam is…ĒŇč k…Ē temer k…ôluks…õ k…Ē s…Ē wan k…Ēn, icloku papa kosu: ‚ÄĻK'int…Ēluks'am w…ôf…õt kosu-…õ, in'endesar…õ kiciya doru o doru nn…Ē papa kem eyi m…Ē!‚Äļ  
\v 33 Nd…õk…ôl il…õts…õn'am: Ina w…ômar…ôs kam iyi nn…Ē. Iy…Ēn…õ w…ôcar ka m…ôna mariki mem. W…ôf…õt kosu p…ôlukus k…Ē aw…õnc im aŇča nde papa kosu eyi m…Ē.  
\v 34 C…ôke c'intam k…ôlukus, ta iluks…õ w…ôf…õt kosu nn…Ē papa kosu eyi m…Ē-…õ? Ha! Intola f…õ k…ôn…ôŇčk p…ôl…õc p…Ēk…Ē pendek…Ēs…Ēt…Ē papa kosu m…Ē, k'int…Ēluks…õ k…Ē w…ôf…õt kosu-…õ!¬Ľ 
\c 45  
\s1 Isifu …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ aw…õnc aŇča k…ôn…õp…ôl k…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 Isifu …õnatam f…õ s…Ē k…ôm…õŇčk m…õnc…ôr nn…Ē afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi k…Ē k…ôs…ôk m…Ē dac…Ē, k'oŇčkul…õ: ¬ęN…ôwur…õn…õ afum f…ôp!¬Ľ Ali w…ôkin …õnayi f…õ s…Ē Isifu k…ôs…ôk nt…õ encment…ôrn…õ aw…õnc aŇča m…Ē.  
\v 2 K'…õy…õf…õ k…ôbok, aMisira k…Ē aka k…ôl…Ē ka Firawona Ňčane k…Ē dim k…ôbok.  
\v 3 K…Ē Isifu oloku aw…õnc aŇča: ¬ęIn'…Ēf…Ē Isifu! papa kem …Ēs…Ēr…Ēyi doru ba?¬Ľ Mba aw…õnc aŇča Ňčanatam f…õ k…ôluks…õ k…Ē moloku nt…õ p…ônciyan…õ Ňča k…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ē s…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 4 K…Ē Isifu oloku aw…õnc aŇča: ¬ęIl…õts…õn…õ nu, n…ôl…Ēt…ôrn'em.¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē. K'oloku Ňča s…Ē: ¬ęIn'…Ēf…Ē Isifu w…õnc konu nw…õ n…ônacam…ôs a k…Ē aŇčk…õr…õ k…Ē Misira m…Ē.  
\v 5 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, ta n…ôwak…ôsn…õ. Ta p…ôt…õl…õ nu k…ôcam…ôs kem pak…õr'em nn…Ē, bawo k…ôbum konu, n…ôyi doru k…Ē Kanu k…ônab…õlk…ôr'em k…ôk…õr…õ nn…Ē, iyi nu kiriŇč.  
\v 6 Teren ta m…õr…ôŇč ta dor t…Ē tant…õ d…Ēt…Ēf. P…ônc…ôm…õ meren k…ôcam…ôt af…Ēde pacbifti, af…Ēde pact…õl.  
\v 7 Kanu k…ôk…õr'em iyi nu kiriŇč, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôs…Ēt…Ē ka nn…Ē at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ yuruya m…Ē, imar nu ta n…ôfi, icbum nu p…ôyeŇčki pamp…õ ayi k…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ m…Ē.  
\v 8 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, baf…Ē n…ôn'…õk…õr'em nn…Ē, mba Kanu k…Ē. Kanu k…ônc…ômb…ôr im iy…Ēn…õ papa ka Firawona, mariki ma k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ, w…ôkiriŇč ka s…ôdare sa Misira f…ôp.  
\v 9 N…ôrokn…õ n…ôp…õ nde papa kem eyi m…Ē. N…ôk…Ē n…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻNt…õ t…Ē wan kam Isifu …õnaloku su: Kanu k…ônc…ômb…ôr im mariki ma at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp. Ta m…ôwon k…ôder nn…Ē iyi m…Ē!  
\v 10 Nde at…Ēf Ňča Kos…õŇč Ňč…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēyi, m…ôf…Ēdeb…Ēl'em, k…ôy…õf…õ m…ôna papa k…ôb…ôp awut am, awut-s…Ē am, y…Ēc…Ēl yam y…Ēp…ĒŇč k…Ē y…õf…õt haŇč ca ny…õ m…ôy…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 11 Nn…Ē taŇč indetam k…ôcs…ĒŇč …ôm ca f…ôp bawo p…ôs…Ēr…Ēc…ôm…õ meren k…ôcam…ôt a dor declip. Ti disr…õ dor d…Ēf…Ēdesump…ôr y…Ēk…Ē m…ôy…Ē m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 12 ¬ęF…Ēt…Ē n…ôŇčgb…ôtn…õ ti f…Ēr yonu, k…Ē w…ôf…õt kem BeŇčyamin …õŇčgb…ôt…ôn'em f…Ēr y…Ēn yati a in'oŇčlok-lok…ôr nu.  
\v 13 N…ôk…Ē n…ôloku papa kem k…Ē p…ôlel mp…õ is…Ēt…Ē Misira m…Ē f…ôp. N…ôl…Ēm…ôr k…Ē nt…õ n…ôn…ôŇčk d…õ m…Ē f…ôp. N…ôrokn…õ n…ôtor…õn…õ papa kem nn…Ē iyi m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 14 K…Ē Isifu …õnaps…ôrn…õ s…Ē w…ôf…õt k…Ēn BeŇčyamin d…ôkilim, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôbok.  
\v 15 K…Ē Isifu oncup…ôs aw…õnc aŇča f…ôp. K…Ē Ňčandel…ôps…ôr k…ônd…õ tofo tin k…Ē Ňčalok-loku. 
\s1 Firawona k…ôwe ka Yakuba Misira 
\p  
\v 16 K…Ē moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…õsam k…ôl…Ē ka Firawona f…ôp disr…õ, a aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčanderna m…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē toloku tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēmb…Ēt Firawona k…Ē amar…ôs …Ēn.  
\v 17 K…Ē Firawona oloku Isifu: ¬ęM…ôloku aw…õnc …ôm aŇča: ‚ÄĻN…ôy…Ē nt…õ: N…ôl…õk y…Ēc…Ēl yonu, n…ôk…Ē at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč.  
\v 18 N…ôl…õk papa konu k…Ē afum …Ēn, n…ôder nn…Ē iyi m…Ē. Indey…Ēn…õ nu nt…õ o nt…õ tentes…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē. N…ônde n…ôcdi yeri yoboŇču ya Misira.‚Äļ  
\v 19 Iwos'am k…ôloku aw…õnc …ôm aŇča: ‚ÄĻN…ôy…Ē nt…õ: N…ôl…õk cibil at…Ēf Ňča Misira, n…ôk…Ē n…ôl…õk awut k…Ē aran anu k…Ē papa konu n…ôder.‚Äļ  
\v 20 Ta n…ôŇčaŇčn…õ m…õl…ôr teta ca yonu y…Ēk…Ē n…ôndek…Ēsak di m…Ē, bawo mp…õ o mp…õ peyi at…Ēf Ňča Misira p…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…Ēt…Ēt m…Ē, pendey…Ēn…õ ponu.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 21 K…Ē awut a Yakuba Ňčay…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē Isifu …Ēs…ĒŇč aw…õnc aŇča cibil p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Firawona …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē. K'…Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča s…Ē yeri y…Ēk…Ē Ňčanak…Ē k…ôcdi d…Ēp…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 22 K…Ē Isifu ompoc…õ aw…õnc aŇča f…ôp yamos y…õs…ôkp…ôr…õ k'…Ēs…ĒŇč BeŇčyamin gbeti m…õnc…ômb…ôl masar maas (300) k…Ē yamos k…ôcam…ôt y…õs…ôkp…ôr…õ.  
\v 23 Ca ny…õ y…Ē Isifu …õnas…ĒŇč paken…õ kas k…ôŇčan: S…Ēfale surkun w…ôco s…ôsar…õ ca y…Ēt…Ēt ya Misira, k…Ē s…Ēfale s…ôran w…ôco s…ôsar…õ mal…Ē, c…ôcom k…Ē yeri ta nt…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēsump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē k…ôder Misira m…Ē.  
\v 24 K…Ē Isifu …õsak aw…õnc aŇča k…Ē Ňčalukus. K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęTa n…ôk…Ēc…Ēp d…Ēp…Ē de!¬Ľ  
\v 25 K…Ē aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčay…õf…õ Misira k…Ē Ňčamp…õ KanaŇč ndena papa k…ôŇčan Yakuba.  
\v 26 K…Ē aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčaloku kas k…ôŇčan teta Isifu kiyi k…Ēn doru s…Ē. K…Ē Ňčaloku kas k…ôŇčan a Isifu …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp. Mba ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õnap…õ f…õ Yakuba bawo …õnalaŇč f…õ Ňča.  
\v 27 K…Ē Ňčal…Ēm…ôr k…Ē moloku m…Ēk…Ē Isifu …õnasom Ňča m…Ē f…ôp. Nt…õ Yakuba …õnan…ôŇčk cibil c…ôk…Ē Isifu …õnasak k…ôdel…õk k…Ē m…Ē, ti t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē oŇč ab…ôk…ôc k…ôp…õ.  
\v 28 K…Ē Yakuba oloku: ¬ęIlaŇč ti oŇč! Wan kem Isifu …Ēs…Ēr…Ēyi doru! Indek…Ēn…ôŇčk k…Ē a icfi.¬Ľ 
\c 46  
\s1 Yakuba k…ôk…Ē k…Ēn Misira 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yakuba …ĒŇčk…Ē k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē …õnay…Ē m…Ē. Nt…õ …õmb…õr…õ Bersaba m…Ē, k'oloŇčn…õ di Kanu ka papa k…Ēn Siyaka.  
\v 2 K…Ē Kanu k…ôlok-lok…ôr Yakuba k…ôn…ôŇčk ka pibi disr…õ. K…Ē Kanu k…ôwe k…Ē: ¬ęYakuba! Yakuba!¬Ľ K'owos…õ: ¬ęIn'…õw…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 3 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku k…Ē: ¬ęIn'…Ēf…Ē ina Kanu, Kanu ka papa kam. Ta m…ônes…õ k…ôtor ka Misira. Bawo dif…Ē iŇčk…Ēs…ĒŇč'am k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka kas ka afum alar…ôm.  
\v 4 S…ôn'endesol k…ôtor ka Misira. In'endes…ĒŇč'am s…Ē k…ôp…õ. Isifu yati endem…õp'…ôm f…Ēr waca w…Ēn.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē Yakuba …õy…õf…õ Bersaba. K…Ē awut a Yakuba ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ kas k…ôŇčan, aran aŇčan, k…Ē awut aŇčan cibil ca d…ônt…Ēf disr…õ nc…õ Firawona …õnas…ĒŇč pak…Ē k…õr…õ Ňča m…Ē.  
\v 6 K…Ē Ňčal…õk s…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē. K…Ē Yakuba …ĒŇčk…Ē Misira k…Ē afum …Ēn f…ôp.  
\v 7 K'eŇčken…õn…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira yuruya y…Ēn f…ôp, awut …Ēn arkun k…Ē awut-s…Ē …Ēn arkun, awut …Ēn aran k…Ē awut-s…Ē …Ēn aran. 
\s1 D…õlay da afum a Yakuba 
\p  
\v 8 Mewe ma awut a Yakuba m…Ē mm…õ, aŇč…õ Ňčanak…Ē Misira m…Ē. Yakuba k…Ē awut …Ēn: 
\p Coco ca Yakuba, Ruben.  
\v 9 Awut a Ruben: Henok, Palu, Hec…ôr…ĒŇč, k…Ē Karmi. 
\m  
\v 10 Awut a Simey…ĒŇč: Yemuy…õl, Yamin, Ohad, Yakin, k…Ē Cohar, k…Ē Sawul wan w…ôrkun w…ôka w…ôKanaŇčara. 
\m  
\v 11 Awut a Lewy: Kerson, Kehat, k…Ē Merari. 
\m  
\v 12 Awut a Yuda: H…õr, Onan, S…õlah, Per…õc, k…Ē Serah, mba H…õr k…Ē Onan Ňčanafi nde at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč. Awut a Per…õc Ňčanay…Ēn…õ Hec…ôr…ĒŇč k…Ē Hamul. 
\m  
\v 13 Awut a Isakar: Tola, Puwa, Y…Ēb, k…Ē Simr…ĒŇč. 
\m  
\v 14 Awut a Sebul…ĒŇč: Sered, ∆źl…ĒŇč, k…Ē Yahal…õl. 
\m  
\v 15 Awut akaŇč…õ Ňč…Ē Leya …õnakom…õ Yakuba nde PadaŇč-Aram, mba wan k…Ēn w…ôran Dina eyi f…õ ti. K…ôl…õk awut …Ēn aran haŇč arkun, Ňčanak…Ē afum w…ôco maas (33). 
\p  
\v 16 Awut a Kadu: Cify…Ēn, Haki, Suni, Ec…ôb…ĒŇč, Eri, Arodi, k…Ē Areli. 
\m  
\v 17 Awut a As…õr: Yima, Yisuwa, Yisuwi, k…Ē Beriya, k…Ē Sera w…ôkir…õ k…ôŇčan. Wan ka Beriya: Heb…õr k…Ē Malkiy…õl. 
\m  
\v 18 Awut a Silpa w…ômar…ôs nw…õ LabaŇč …õnas…ĒŇč wan k…Ēn w…ôran Leya m…Ē, Ňč…Ē akak…Ē aŇč…õ …õnakom…õ Yakuba m…Ē. Ňäanayi afum w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-tin (16). 
\p  
\v 19 Awut a Ras…õl, w…ôran ka Yakuba: Isifu k…Ē BeŇčyamin.  
\v 20 K…Ē Isifu nk…Ēn oŇčkom Misira awut m…õr…ôŇč: Manase k…Ē ∆źfrayim, aŇč…õ Asnat wan w…ôran ka Potifera w…ôloŇčn…õ ka dare da Hon, …õnakom…õ Isifu m…Ē. 
\m  
\v 21 Awut a BeŇčyamin: Bela, Bek…õr, Asub…õl, Kera, Naman, Ehi, R…Ēs, Mupim, Hupim, k…Ē Ardu. 
\m  
\v 22 Yuruya yay…õ y…Ē Ras…õl …õnas…Ēt…Ēn…õ nk…Ēn Yakuba, Ňčanayi afum w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ (14). 
\p  
\v 23 Wan ka Dan: Husim. 
\m  
\v 24 Mewe ma awut a Naftali m…õm…õ: Yacel, Kumi, Yecer, k…Ē Silem. 
\m  
\v 25 Awut a Bilha Ňč…Ē akak…Ē, Bilha nw…õ LabaŇč …õnas…ĒŇč wan k…Ēn w…ôran Ras…õl m…Ē p…ôy…Ē k…Ē w…ôcar, k'oŇčkom…õ Ňča Yakuba. Ňäanayi afum cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. 
\p  
\v 26 Afum aŇč…õ Ňčanac…õps…õ Yakuba k…ôk…Ē ka Misira m…Ē, Ňčanayi afum w…ôco cam…ôt tin k…Ē cam…ôt tin (66) aŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ēn…õ akom …Ēn m…Ē, al…Ēm f…õ aran a awut …Ēn arkun de.  
\v 27 Awut a Isifu aŇč…õ …õnakom Misira m…Ē: Ňäanayi awut m…õr…ôŇč. Afum a Yakuba aŇč…õ Ňčanac…ôps…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč k…ôk…Ē ka Misira m…Ē, Ňčanayi f…ôp faŇčan afum w…ôco cam…ôt m…õr…ôŇč (70). 
\s1 Yakuba k…ônd…õ k…Ēn nde Misira 
\p  
\v 28 K…Ē Yakuba osom Yuda p…ôyi k…Ē kiriŇč k…ôk…Ē ka Kos…õŇč ndena Isifu. K…Ē Yuda …õmb…õr…õ at…Ēf Ňča Kos…õŇč.  
\v 29 K…Ē Isifu …õl…õk abil Ňč…Ēn k'…õmp…õ Kos…õŇč k…ôk…Ēb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē papa k…Ēn Yakuba. Isifu ŇčaŇčk…Ēwur…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē papa k…Ēn, k'…õnaps…ôrn…õ k…Ē d…ôkilim k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôbok. K'ombok haŇč.  
\v 30 K…Ē Yakuba oloku Isifu: ¬ęIntam oŇč k…ôfi bawo in…ôŇčk …ôm k…ôro, k'inc…ôr…õ oŇč a m…ôyi doru!¬Ľ  
\v 31 K…Ē Isifu oloku aw…õnc aŇča k…Ē afum a papa k…Ēn: ¬ęIlukus ik…Ē iluks…õ Firawona k…ôb…õr…õ konu. Ik…Ē iloku k…Ē a: ‚ÄĻAw…õnc im aŇča k…Ē afum a papa kem aŇč…õ Ňčanayi at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē, Ňčander nn…Ē iyi m…Ē.  
\v 32 Afum ak…õk a Ňčkesiya, cir, k…Ē c…ôna Ňč…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ, bawo ak…õk a ac…Ēl Ňč…Ē. ŇäaŇčk…õr…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan f…ôp k…Ē ca yaŇčan.‚Äļ  
\v 33 K…Ē t…õm tendeb…ôp nt…õ Firawona endewe nu p…ôcyif nu: ‚ÄĻAke'y…Ēn…õ y…õb…ôc yonu-…õ?‚Äļ  
\v 34 N…ôcloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻS…ôn'acar am, ak…õk Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ, k…ôy…õf…õ d…õt…õmp dosu haŇč m…Ēk…Ē, y…õb…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē s…ômb…ôp…õ akomb…ôra asu.‚Äļ Ti disr…õ, n…ôyi Kos…õŇč, bawo p…ôcyik-yik aMisira k…ônd…õ k…Ē ak…õk a Ňčkesiya k…Ē cir.¬Ľ 
\c 47  
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Isifu …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôluks…õ ti Firawona. K'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęAw…õnc im aŇča k…Ē papa kem Ňčander k…ôy…õf…õ ka at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan Ňčkesiya, cir k…Ē c…ôna k…ôb…ôp ka ca yaŇčan f…ôp. Ňäayi tant…õ at…Ēf Ňča Kos…õŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 2 K…Ē Isifu …õl…õk aw…õnc aŇča k…ôcam…ôt k'ement…ôr Ňča Firawona.  
\v 3 K…Ē Firawona eyif aw…õnc a Isifu: ¬ęAke'y…Ēn…õ y…õb…ôc yonu-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčaloku Firawona: ¬ęS…ôn'acar am, ak…õk a Ňčkesiya, cir k…Ē c…ôna Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ p…ôm…Ē papa kosu aŇča.¬Ľ  
\v 4 K…Ē Ňčaloku s…Ē Firawona: ¬ęS…ônder k…ôdend…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ, bawo d…ôk…ôc…Ēl deyi f…õ s…Ē nde acar am Ňčay…õf…õ m…Ē, k…Ē dor d…õmb…õk k…ôb…õk d…ôm at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč. M…ôwos…õ oŇč acar am k…ônd…õ at…Ēf Ňča Kos…õŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē Firawona oloku Isifu: ¬ęPapa kam k…Ē aw…õnc …ôm aŇča Ňčander nn…Ē m…ôyi m…Ē.  
\v 6 At…Ēf Ňča Misira Ňčey'…ôm d…ôwaca, m…ôd…ôs papa kam k…Ē aw…õnc …ôm aŇča nn…Ē p…ôntes…õ Ňča Kos…õŇč m…Ē, k…Ē m…ônc…ôr…õ s…Ē aw…õnc …ôm aŇča dac…Ē afum alompu-…õ, m…ôc…ômb…ôr Ňča Ňčack…õks'em y…Ēc…Ēl.¬Ľ  
\v 7 K…Ē Isifu …õŇčk…õr…õ papa k…Ēn Yakuba k…ôdement…ôr k…Ē Firawona. K…Ē Yakuba ontolan…õ Firawona.  
\v 8 K…Ē Firawona eyif Yakuba: ¬ęMeren c…ôke m…Ē m…ôyi doru-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 9 K…Ē Yakuba oloku k…Ē: ¬ęMeren mm…õ is…Ēt…Ē k…ôcep…õ-cep…õ disr…õ m…Ē, m…õmb…ôp meren tasar tin k…Ē w…ôco maas (130), kiyi kem doru k…ôncep…ôr kat…ôna kat…ôna. Incep…ôr…õn…õ meren meyeŇčki kiyi kem doru. Intas…Ēt…Ē f…õ meren mm…õ akomb…ôra em Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē m…Ē, mba tecep…ôr…õn…õ doru tin tayi t…Ē s…ôncep…ôr…õn…õ doru.¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē Yakuba ontolan…õ s…Ē Firawona. K'…õy…õf…õ, k'…õsak k…Ē. 
\p  
\v 11 K…Ē Isifu …õnd…ôs papa k…Ēn k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča at…Ēf Ňča Misira. K'…Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča ant…Ēf Misira, nde at…Ēf Ňča Rams…õs, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Firawona …õnaloku k…Ē ti m…Ē.  
\v 12 K…Ē Isifu …õntam oŇč k…ôgb…õk…ôr…õ papa k…Ēn, aw…õnc aŇča, k…Ē aka k…ôl…Ē ka papa k…Ēn f…ôp p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanalan…õn…õ m…Ē. 
\s1 Isifu k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ mes ma Misira 
\p  
\v 13 Yeri y…õnayi f…õ s…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp, bawo dor d…õnas…Ēt…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr. At…Ēf Ňča Misira k…Ē at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč dor d…õncl…õŇčk…ôs oŇč k…ôl…õŇčk…ôs d…ôm afum a t…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 14 K…Ē Isifu …õw…õt…ôs gbeti f…ôp mb…õ b…õnayi at…Ēf Ňča Misira k…Ē at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē. P…ôcs…ôkp…ôr…õ gbeti bab…Ēk…Ē mal…Ē, k…Ē Isifu …õmb…õrs…õ gbeti bab…Ēk…Ē nde k…ôl…Ē ka Firawona.  
\v 15 Nt…õ gbeti ba Misira k…Ē KanaŇč belip m…Ē, k…Ē aMisira f…ôp Ňčander nn…Ē Isifu eyi m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęM…ôs…ĒŇč su yeri! Cep…Ē s…ôndefi f…Ēr yam kiriŇč bawo gbeti beyi f…õ s…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē Isifu oloku: ¬ęN…ôs…ĒŇč y…Ēc…Ēl yonu. IŇčs…ĒŇč nu k…ôcom k…ôs…ôkp…õ ka y…Ēc…Ēl yonu, bawo gbeti beyi f…õ s…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ Isifu y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan. K…Ē Isifu …ĒŇčs…ĒŇč Ňča yeri k…ôs…ôkp…õ ka y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan: F…ôl…õs, y…Ēc…Ēl y…õf…õt k…Ē y…Ēp…ĒŇč, s…Ēfale. K…Ē Isifu …Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča yeri ya teren tat…Ēk…Ē k…ôs…ôkp…õ ka y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan f…ôp.  
\v 18 Nt…õ teren tat…Ēk…Ē tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē aka Misira Ňčander s…Ē nn…Ē Isifu eyi m…Ē teren t…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk. K…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęS…ôf…Ētam k…ôm…õŇčk…ôr mariki mem a gbeti bosu belip, k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yosu yelip. Daka o daka d…õnc…ôm…õ f…õ su s…Ē, m…õn…õ dis dosu k…Ē nt…Ēf yosu.  
\v 19 S…ôndefi oŇč f…Ēr yam kiriŇč ba, k…Ē nt…Ēf yosu? M…ôway su k…Ē nt…Ēf yosu k…ôs…ôkp…õ ka yeri. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ acar a Firawona, s…ôna k…Ē nt…Ēf yosu. M…ôs…ĒŇč su defet s…ôb…ôc ta s…ôdefi, nt…Ēf yosu yedef…ônt…ôr…õ gb…ôlm…ôs.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē Isifu …õway…õ Firawona nt…Ēf ya Misira f…ôp, aka Misira f…ôp Ňčanacam…ôs nt…Ēf yaŇčan, bawo dor d…õnab…õk…ôr Ňča. K…Ē at…Ēf Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ oŇč Ňča Firawona.  
\v 21 K…Ē Firawona …õl…õk afum aŇč…õ Ňčanayi d…ôc…ôl…ônc…ôr ca Misira m…Ē, k'…õŇčk…õr…õ Ňča s…ôdare s…ôp…ĒŇč.  
\v 22 Mba Isifu …õnaway f…õ nt…Ēf ya aloŇčn…õ, bawo Firawona …õnam…Ēn…õ k…ôway ka nt…Ēf yaŇčan. AloŇčn…õ Ňčayi k…ôk…õk…ôs ka Firawona disr…õ, ti t…Ē aloŇčn…õ Ňčanat…Ēcams…õ nt…Ēf yaŇčan. 
\p  
\v 23 K…Ē Isifu oloku afum a Misira: ¬ęIway nu m…Ēk…Ē k…Ē nt…Ēf yonu, n…ôy…Ēn…õ m…Ēk…Ē aka Firawona. Defet d…õnd…õ: N…ôntam k…ôb…Ēf d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 24 K…Ē n…ônde n…ôct…õl-…õ, n…ôde n…ôcs…ĒŇč faril…õ poboc pin pa y…õt…õl yonu Firawona. N…ôna n…ôl…õk yoboc maŇčk…ôl…õ ny…õ, yendey…Ēn…õ nu yeri ya d…õk…õr k…Ē awut, y…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu s…Ē defet da teren t…Ēc…Ēnc m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 25 K…Ē Ňčaloku Firawona: ¬ęM…ôluks…õ su k…ôyi doru! S…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ ka mariki mosu, s…ôndey…Ēn…õ acar a Firawona.¬Ľ  
\v 26 K…Ē Isifu …õnc…ômb…ôr ti k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ m…Ēk…Ē t…Ēy…Ē ta Misira: Poboc pa k…ôcam…ôt f…ôp pa Firawona p…Ē. M…õn…õ nt…Ēf ya aloŇčn…õ gb…ôc…ôr…ôm y…Ēt…Ēy…Ēn…õ ya Firawona. 
\s1 M…õfaŇč ma Yakuba m…õlp…ôs 
\p  
\v 27 K…Ē Yakuba …õnd…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira, at…Ēf Ňča Kos…õŇč. K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ di ndaraŇčan k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ kas ka afum alar…ôm.  
\v 28 K…Ē Yakuba eyi doru meren w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (17) at…Ēf Ňča Misira. K…ôwon ka Yakuba doru f…ôp k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren tasar tin w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē cam…ôt m…õr…ôŇč (147).  
\v 29 Mataka ma Yakuba k…ôl…Ēt…ôs k…ôlip, k'ewe wan k…Ēn Isifu k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęK…Ē m…ôfaŇč k…ômar im-…õ, m…ôboc k…ôca kam al…ôŇčk Ňčem tant…Ēf, m…ôl…õk'em layidi p…ôsoku disr…õ nd…õ m…ôndet…Ēmp…ôr'em m…Ē: Il…õts…õn'am ta m…ôwup im Misira!  
\v 30 K'indef…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē papa kem aŇča-…õ, m…ôwur…õn'em Misira. M…ôk…Ē m…ôwup im nde kufu k…ôŇčan k…ôyi m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Isifu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęIndey…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ôlok'im m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 31 K…Ē Yakuba oloku: ¬ęM…ôd…õr…ôm'em ti.¬Ľ K…Ē Isifu …õnd…õrm…õ k…Ē ti. K…Ē Yakuba ontontn…õ nde k…ôf…ônc k…Ēn d…ôromp. 
\c 48  
\s1 Yakuba k…ôtolan…õ k…Ēn awut arkun a Isifu 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē mencep…ôr m…Ē, k'aŇčk…Ē paloku Isifu a Papa k…Ēn …õntamn…õ f…õ. K…Ē Isifu …õl…õk…õn…õ awut …Ēn m…õr…ôŇč Manase k…Ē ∆źfrayim.  
\v 2 K'as…ĒŇč…õ ti Yakuba k…ôc…ôr…õ, k'aloku k…Ē: ¬ęWan kam Isifu eyi k…ôder nn…Ē m…ôyi m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba oloŇčka f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…Ēn k'…õy…õf…õ, k'…õnd…õ k…ôf…ônc k…Ēn k…ôroŇč.  
\v 3 K…Ē Yakuba oloku Isifu: ¬ęMARIKI nw…õ …õntam mes f…ôp ma doru m…Ē …õnawur…ôr im dare da Lus nde at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč k'…Ēs…ĒŇč im temer k…ôdepoc'em p…ôt…Ēt.\x - \xo 48:3 \xt 28.13\x* 
\v 4 K'olok'im: ‚ÄĻIndes…ĒŇč …ôm dokomb…ôra, indes…ĒŇč'am k…ôla, indes…ĒŇč'am k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôtem ka afum alar…ôm. Indes…ĒŇč at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ yuruya yam k…Ē m…ôncep…ôr-…õ, at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ Ňčendey…Ēn…õ ŇčaŇčan doru o doru.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 5 ¬ęNd…õk…ôl oŇč, awut m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ m…ôŇčkom at…Ēf Ňča Misira a k'indeder nn…Ē m…ôyi m…Ē, Ňčandey…Ēn…õ akemi. ∆źfrayim k…Ē Manase Ňčay…Ēn…õ akemi, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē iy…Ē Ruben k…Ē Simey…ĒŇč m…Ē.  
\v 6 Mba awut aŇč…õ m…ôndekom oŇč aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč tadar…ôŇč m…Ē, akam Ňčandeyi akak…Ē, aw…õnc aŇča Ňč…Ē Ňčandes…Ēt…ôr k…õ.  
\v 7 K…ôder kem PadaŇč, k…Ē Ras…õl efir im d…Ēp…Ē da KanaŇč, ta p…ômb…Ēl…õ su k…ôb…õr…õ Efrata-…õ. Dif…Ē inawup k…Ē katina d…ôndo d…Ēp…Ē da Efrata, nde p…ôy…Ēn…õ Betl…õh…õm m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē Yakuba …Ēm…Ēm…ôn awut a Isifu k'eyif: ¬ęAre Ňč…Ē akaŇč…õ-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 9 K…Ē Isifu oloku papa k…Ēn: ¬ęAwut em Ňč…Ē, aŇč…õ Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč im nn…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Yakuba oloku: ¬ęIl…õts…õn'am m…ôy…Ē Ňča Ňčac…ĒŇčn…õ nn…Ē itolan…õ Ňča.¬Ľ  
\v 10 Detem d…õnal…Ēl…ôs Yakuba f…Ēr. ∆źnctam f…õ s…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk. K…Ē Isifu …Ēnc…ĒŇč awut …Ēn nde Yakuba eyi m…Ē, k…Ē Yakuba oncup Ňča, k'…õmak…ôrn…õ Ňča.  
\v 11 K…Ē Yakuba oloku Isifu: ¬ęInac…õm-c…õm…ôn…õ f…õ s…Ē k…ôden…ôŇčk …ôm. Mba Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč'em k'in…ôŇčk …ôm haŇč awut am!¬Ľ  
\v 12 K…Ē Isifu eliŇč awut kas d…ôl…ôŇčk, k'…õnc…ôp k…ôro d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 13 K…Ē Isifu osump…ôr m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan f…ôp waca, p…ôsump…ôr…õ ∆źfrayim k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt mba p…ôyi k…ôca k…ômeriya ka Yakuba, k'osump…ôr…õ Manase k…ôca k…ômeriya mba p…ôyi Yakuba k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, k'…Ēnc…ĒŇč…õn…õ Ňča s…Ē nde w…ôtem k…ôŇčan eyi m…Ē.  
\v 14 K…Ē Yakuba …õnt…õnc k…ôca k…Ēn k…ôt…Ēt, k'endeŇč ki ∆źfrayim d…ôromp nw…õ …õnaf…õt…õ m…Ē, k'endeŇč…ôr Manase k…ôca k…Ēn k…ômeriya d…ôromp. ∆źnac…ôr…õ belbel t…Ēk…Ē …Ēncy…Ē waca w…Ēn m…Ē, ali nt…õ Manase …õnay…Ēn…õ wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 15 Motolan…õ mm…õ m…Ē Yakuba …õnatolan…õ Isifu: 
\q1 ¬ęKanu nk…õ k…ôn…ôŇčk papa kem aŇča Abraham k…Ē Siyaka tecep…ôr…õn…õ taŇčan m…Ē, 
\q1 Kanu nk…õ k…ôŇčk…õks'im k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ iyi doru haŇč m…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, 
\q1  
\v 16 M…õl…õk…õ mm…õ m…õncyac im p…ôl…õc m…Ē, m…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ awut aŇč…õ! 
\q1 Pawe Ňča tewe tem 
\q1 k…Ē mewe ma papa kem aŇča, Abraham k…Ē Siyaka. 
\q1 Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôkom p…ôlar…ôm nde at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē dac…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 17 Nt…õ Isifu …õn…ôŇčk kas p…ôcdeŇč…ôr ∆źfrayim k…ôca k…Ēn k…ôt…Ēt m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēnt…Ēb…Ēt k…Ē. K…Ē Isifu osump…ôr k…ôca ka kas, k'…Ēnc…ĒŇč ntende domp da Manase ta p…ôdeŇč…ôr ki ∆źfrayim.  
\v 18 K…Ē Isifu oloku papa k…Ēn: ¬ęTa m…ôy…Ē tant…õ, f…Ēt…Ē Manase …õb…õk. Nk…Ēn p…ômar m…ôdeŇč…ôr k…ôca kam k…ôt…Ēt.¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē papa k…Ēn …õfati, k'oloku: ¬ęInc…ôr…õ ti, wan kem. Inc…ôr…õ ti! Nk…Ēn s…Ē endey…Ēn…õ w…ôtem ka afum alar…ôm, endeb…õk. Mba w…õnc T…ĒŇč…Ē endeb…õk k…Ē, yuruya y…Ēn yendelas t…Ēf f…ôp.¬Ľ  
\v 20 K…Ē Yakuba ontolan…õ Ňča d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęM…ôn'endes…ĒŇč…õ Yakuba p…ôctolan…õ a p…ôckul…õ a: ‚ÄĻKanu k…ôs…ĒŇč'am k…ôyi p…ôm…Ē ∆źfrayim, p…ôm…Ē Manase!‚Äļ¬Ľ Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē Yakuba …õnac…ômb…ôr Efrayim Manase kiriŇč.  
\v 21 K…Ē Yakuba oloku Isifu: ¬ęK…ôfi k'inder! Mba Kanu k…ôndesol…õ nu. K…ôndeluks…õ nu at…Ēf Ňča atem anu.  
\v 22 Imb…õr…õn'am p…Ēk…Ē aw…õnc …ôm aŇča Ňčant…Ēdes…Ēt…Ē m…Ē\f + \fr 48:22 \ft  Paka pap…Ēk…Ē p…Ēy…Ēn…õ dare da S…ôk…õm.\f*, ip'…Ēy…Ēn…õ mp…õ inabaŇč…ôr…õ aka Am…Ēr dakma dem k…Ē amb…ônc…ôran Ňčem m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\c 49  
\s1 K…ôtolan…õ ka Yakuba awut …Ēn w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yakuba ewe awut …Ēn, k'oloku: 
\q1 ¬ęN…ôloŇčkan…õ iloku nu t…Ēk…Ē tendeder nu kiriŇč m…Ē. 
\q1  
\v 2 N…ôloŇčkan…õ, n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im awut a Yakuba! 
\q1 N…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl Yisrayel\f + \fr 49:2 \ft  M…ôm…Ēm…ôn 32.29, 35.10\f* papa konu! 
\q1  
\v 3 Ruben, m…ôna coco cem, 
\q1 m…ôna nw…õ inakom 
\q1 t…õm nt…õ inay…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr m…Ē: 
\q1 M…ôncep…ôr aw…õnc …ôm aŇča 
\q1 tokom, k…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr. 
\q1  
\v 4 M…ôyeŇčk p…ôm…Ē domun nd…õ d…õŇčy…õks…õ d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, 
\q1 mba m…ôf…Ēdes…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôkiriŇč, 
\q1 Bawo m…ônap…õs…õ d…ôk…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ da papa kam, 
\q1 M…ônayik-yik…ôs k…ôf…ônc kem k…ôp…õs…õ ka ki, k…Ē w…ôran kem w…ôkin.\x - \xo 49:4 \xt 35.22\x* 
\b  
\q1  
\v 5 Simey…ĒŇč k…Ē Lewy d…õw…õnca d…Ē Ňčay…Ē: 
\q1 Ňäa Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ, Ňčasek k…ôk…Ēy…Ē p…ôl…õc. 
\q1  
\v 6 Ala, ifaŇč f…õ k…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôl t…õŇčk…ônd…ôm taŇčan! 
\q1 Ta m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ mem m…õt…ôŇčn…õ nde Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ k…ôb…ôp…õn…õ m…Ē! 
\q1 Bawo m…õt…õl…õ maŇčan disr…õ, Ňčandif fum. 
\q1 K…ôwos…õ k…ôŇčan disr…õ, k…Ē Ňčancopu-copu mura b…ônta.\x - \xo 49:6 \xt 34.25\x* 
\q1  
\v 7 Intolan…õ m…õt…õl…õ maŇčan p…ôl…õc, bawo m…õmb…õk p…õl…ôs…ôr. 
\q1 Intolan…õ p…ôl…õc deyeŇčki b…ôk…ôc daŇčan, bawo d…Ēf…Ēy…Ēn…õ n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr. 
\q1 Indeyer…ôs Ňča at…Ēf Ňča Yakuba, 
\q1 Indesams…ôr Ňča at…Ēf Ňča Yisrayel. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Yuda, m…ôna, aw…õnc …ôm aŇča Ňčandeyek-yek…ôs …ôm. 
\q1 M…ôndesump…ôr ater…õn…õ am c…ôr…Ēb…Ē. 
\q1 K…Ē aw…õnc …ôm aŇča Ňčandec…ôp am s…ôbomp f…Ēr yam kiriŇč. 
\q1  
\v 9 Yuda, kusunuŇčku k…ôwut k…Ē m…ôy…Ēn…õ. 
\q1 D…ôk…ôwat…ôri-wat…ôri w…õs…õm wam m…ôy…õf…õ, wan kem! 
\q1 Nk…Ēn oŇčnut w…õc…ôk, p…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ p…ôm…Ē kusunuŇčku. 
\q1 P…ôm…Ē kusunuŇčku k…ôran: An'…õntam ki k…ôyekti ta k…ôfaŇč-…õ? 
\q1  
\v 10 K…ôgbo ka d…õb…õ k…ôf…Ēde k…ôcb…Ēl…õ Yuda, 
\q1 k…ôgbo ka d…õb…õ k…ôndeyi yuruya y…Ēn d…ôwaca, 
\q1 haŇč t…õm nt…õ w…ôka k…ôgbo kaŇčk…Ē yati endeder m…Ē, 
\q1 w…ôk…Ē afum f…ôp Ňčandeyi d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē. 
\q1  
\v 11 Nk…Ēn (Yuda) ende p…ôckot s…Ēfale s…Ēn d…ôŇčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn, 
\q1 p…ôkot wan ka si nde k…ôt…Ēk ka w…õn, 
\q1 Ende p…ôcyak yamos y…Ēn d…ôw…õn, 
\q1 k…Ē burumus b…Ēn, d…ôm…ônc…Ēnc…Ē ma yokom ya w…õn. 
\q1  
\v 12 Member mendes…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē f…Ēr k…ôyimb…ôr…õ, 
\q1 M…õs…õ ma wana mendefert…ôr …ôm sek. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 K…Ē m…ôna Sabulon, k…ôba k…ôs…ôk m…ôndend…õ, 
\q1 nde cibil c…ôndey…Ē k…ôt…ônta m…Ē. 
\q1 C…ôl…ônc…ôr ca at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē c…ôndew…Ēk…ôl haŇč SidoŇč. 
\q1  
\v 14 Isakar, m…ôna s…Ēfale s…ôp…ĒŇč s…Ē m…ôy…Ēn…õ, 
\q1 ns…õ s…ôŇčf…ônt…ôr…õ gb…Ēr…õ m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē m…Ē. 
\q1  
\v 15 P…ôn…ôŇčk a k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē eyi k…ôŇčes…ôm m…Ē k…ôntes…õ, 
\q1 k'at…Ēf Ňč…Ēmb…Ēt. 
\q1 P…ôtirmi kumunt pad…ônd…ôs…ôr k…Ē p…õsar…õ, 
\q1 Y…õb…ôc ya dacar y'endeyi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 16 Dan, endey…Ēn…õ afum …Ēn w…ôb…õ. 
\q1 P…ôm…Ē kusuŇčka k…ôl…Ēma cusuŇčka c…ôlp…ôs ca Yisrayel c…ôk…Ē. 
\q1  
\v 17 Dan, endeyi p…ôm…Ē abok nŇč…õ Ňčeyi d…Ēp…Ē m…Ē, 
\q1 aŇčkisin nŇč…õ Ňčeyi d…Ēp…Ē k…ôs…ôk m…Ē. 
\q1 Abok nŇč…õ Ňč…õŇčaŇč b…ônta ya af…ôl…õs, 
\q1 a t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôy…õks…õn…õ ka Ňči k…ôt…õmp…õn…õ m…Ē. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 IŇčgb…õk…ôr …ôm amera MARIKI, a m…ôndeyac im! 
\b  
\q1  
\v 19 Kadu, k…ônay\f + \fr 49:19 \ft  K…ônare\f* k…ôndepaŇčn…õ k…Ē 
\q1 p…ôy…õf…õ p…ôc…ôm…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč k…ôb…õl…ôs. 
\q1  
\v 20 Ndena As…õr, yeri yoboŇču yendela di. 
\q1 Ant…Ēf Ňčam Ňčende Ňč…Ēcs…ĒŇč yeri ny…õ p…ômar y…Ēy…Ēn…õ yeri y'ab…õ m…Ē. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 21 Naftali, were w'…Ēy…Ēn…õ nw…õ weyi kiyi ka wi, ta tes o tes toŇčkot…ôrn…õ wi m…Ē. 
\q1 Ende p…ôckom…ôs awut at…Ēt\f + \fr 49:21 \ft  P…ôcloku moloku m…Ēt…Ēt\f*. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 22 Isifu, popoŇč pa k…ôt…Ēk k…ôkom p…Ēy…Ēn…õ, 
\q1 PopoŇč pa k…ôt…Ēk k…ôkom nk…õ k…ôc…ôm…õ k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē k…ôs…ôk m…Ē, 
\q1 wara wa ki wetils…ôrn…õ damba. 
\q1  
\v 23 Ňäand…ôkt…ôr k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamp…õn. 
\q1 Ap…õn…õ mb…ônc…ôran Ňčanay…Ēn…õ ay…õf…ôr…õn…õ am. 
\q1  
\v 24 Mba amb…ônc…ôran Ňč…Ēn Ňčende Ňč…õt…ôŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn s…ôrka. 
\q1 AnacaŇč…ôs waca w…Ēn 
\q1 k…ôtam ka Kanu k…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa Yakuba d…ônt…Ēf. 
\q1 ∆Üy…Ēn…õ w…ôk…õk…ôs k…Ē togbu pa aka Yisrayel\f + \fr 49:24 \ft  C…ôHeb…ôre = ¬ętasar pa aka Yisrayel¬Ľ \f*. 
\q1  
\v 25 Tewe ta Kanu ka papa kam, nk…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ômar kam m…Ē, 
\q1 tewe ta Kanu nk…õ k…ôntam mes f…ôp ma doru m…Ē, nk…õ k…ôndepoc'am m…Ē: 
\q1 K…ôpoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt nk…õ k…ôndey…õf…õ darenc m…Ē, 
\q1 k…ôpoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt nk…õ k…ôŇčy…õf…õ d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē, 
\q1 k…ôpoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt ka awut alar…ôm k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…õlar…ôm. 
\q1  
\v 26 K…ôtolan…õ nk…õ papa kam ontolan'am m…Ē, 
\q1 k…ôncep…ôr k…ôtolan…õ p…ôt…Ēt ka aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčkom im m…Ē, 
\q1 haŇč d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da m…Ēr…Ē ma doru o doru. 
\q1 K…ôtolan…õ p…ôt…Ēt kaŇčk…Ē k…ôyi Isifu d…ôromp, 
\q1 d…ôndo domp dac…Ē da Isifu 
\q1 nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka aw…õnc aŇča m…Ē! 
\b  
\q1  
\v 27 BeŇčyamin, kalma k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ nk…õ k…ôŇčwat…ôri-wat…ôri m…Ē. 
\q1 B…ôtb…ôt k…ôwat…ôri-wat…ôri w…õs…ôm wa ki, 
\q1 d…Ēf…Ēy, p…ôyer…ôs y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē ya ki.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 28 Awut akaŇč…õ Ňčay…Ēn…õ cusuŇčka w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč ca Yisrayel. Moloku mam…õ m…Ē kas k…ôŇčan …õnaloku Ňča, nt…õ onctolan…õ Ňča m…Ē. Yakuba …õnatolan…õ Ňča nw…õ o nw…õ k…Ē k…ôtolan…õ k…Ēn taciŇča. 
\s1 Defi da Yakuba 
\p  
\v 29 Nt…õ Yakuba elip k…ôtolan…õ awut …Ēn m…Ē, k'osom Ňča: ¬ęIntas k…ôb…ôp atem em aŇč…õ Ňčafi m…Ē. N…ôwup im k…Ē papa kem aŇča, nde kufu k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôyi nde dal…õ da H…õf…ôroŇč w…ôHewy m…Ē,  
\v 30 nde kufu nk…õ k…ôyi dal…õ da Makpela, Mamre k…ôs…ôk, nde at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč. Dal…õ dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ē Abraham …õnaway nn…Ē H…õf…ôroŇč eyi m…Ē, p…ôy…Ēn…õ di d…ôk…ôwup…õn…õ da afum …Ēn.  
\v 31 Dif…Ē anawup Abraham k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn Sara, dif…Ē anawup Siyaka k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn Rebeka, dif…Ē inawup s…Ē Leya w…ôran kem.  
\v 32 Dal…õ k…Ē kufu nk…õ k…ôyi di m…Ē, Abraham …õnaway di aHewy d…ôwaca.¬Ľ  
\v 33 Nt…õ Yakuba elip k…ôsom awut …Ēn m…Ē, k'…õf…ônt…ôr…õ d…ôk…ôf…ônc. K'eŇčgbiŇč kifir k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl…õn…õ atem …Ēn aŇč…õ Ňčanafi m…Ē. 
\c 50  
\s1 K…ôbal ka Yakuba 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Isifu …õnt…õmp…õn…õ papa k…Ēn k…ôroŇč, k'ombok k…Ē k…ôroŇč, k'oncup k…Ē.  
\v 2 K…Ē Isifu osom acar …Ēn ak…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ at…õn c…Ēl m…Ē, a Ňčasop kas ac…Ēl nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ ta w…ôfi ente kat…ôna m…Ē. K…Ē at…õn c…Ēl Ňčasop Yakuba ac…Ēl ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 3 K…Ē t…ĒŇčk…Ē mata w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40). T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē mataka mam…Ēk…Ē m'ancsop afi ac…Ēl Ňča k…ôt…Ēte ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē aMisira Ňčambok k…Ē mata w…ôco cam…ôt m…õr…ôŇč (70). 
\p  
\v 4 Nt…õ mataka ma k…ôbal k…Ēn mencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Isifu oloku afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi nde saŇčka sa Firawona m…Ē, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęK'intam k…ôs…Ēt…ôr nu layidi-…õ, n…ôloku nt…õ Firawona il…õts…õn…õ nu:  
\v 5 Papa kem …õnas…ĒŇč'em k…ôd…õr…ôm, p…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻK…ôfi k'inder! M…ôk…Ē m…ôwup im nde kufu k…ôŇčk…Ē iŇčkay nde at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē.‚Äļ Dif…Ē ifaŇč k…ôp…õ ik…Ēwup papa kem. K'ilip-…õ, inder.¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē Firawona oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôp…õ m…ôk…Ē m…ôwup papa kam p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …Ēs…ĒŇč'am k…ôd…õr…ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 7 K…Ē Isifu …õmp…õ k…ôk…Ēwup papa k…Ēn. K…Ē Ňčamp…õ k…Ē abeki aka saŇčka sa Firawona f…ôp k…ôb…ôp abeki a at…Ēf Ňča Misira.  
\v 8 K…Ē afum a Isifu f…ôp, k…ôl…õk aw…õnc aŇča k…ôb…ôp ka afum a papa k…Ēn, m…õn…õ awut af…õt, y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan y…Ēp…ĒŇč k…Ē y…õf…õt Ňč'anasak at…Ēf Ňča Kos…õŇč.  
\v 9 Isifu k…Ē cibil ca d…ônt…Ēf k'ay…õks…õn…õ f…ôl…õs Ňčamp…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ ak…Ē a KanaŇč k…ôla.  
\v 10 Ňäandeb…ôp p…ôferere pa Atad, nŇč…õ Ňčeyi Yurd…õn tak…ôroŇč m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčawup Yakuba d…ôndo k…ôyek-yek…ôs disr…õ. K…Ē Isifu ombok kas mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 11 K…Ē and…õ a at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, aka KanaŇč, Ňčayi k…ôbal ka Yakuba d…ôndo p…ôferere pa Atad. K…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęDefi d…Ēp…ĒŇč d…Ē dand…õ aMisira dac…Ē!¬Ľ Ti t'as…ĒŇč…õ tofo tat…Ēk…Ē tewe ta ¬ęAb…õl Misira¬Ľ nde Yurd…õn tak…ôroŇč.  
\v 12 K…Ē awut a Yakuba Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē papa k…ôŇčan …õnaloku Ňča m…Ē.  
\v 13 K…Ē awut …Ēn ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč. K…Ē Ňčawup k…Ē nde kufu ka dal…õ da Makpela, dal…õ nd…õ Abraham …õnaway H…õf…ôroŇč w…ôHiti d…ôwaca m…Ē, p…ôy…Ē di d…ôk…ôwup…õn…õ da afum …Ēn, nde Mamre k…ôs…ôk.  
\v 14 Nt…õ Isifu elip k…ôwup papa k…Ēn m…Ē, k'oluks…ôrn…õ Misira k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčanac…ômb…ôr k…Ē, k…ôk…Ēwup papa k…Ēn m…Ē. 
\s1 Mes mam…Ēk…Ē m…õnacep…ôr nt…õ defi da Yakuba delip m…Ē 
\p  
\v 15 Nt…õ aw…õnc a Isifu Ňčan…ôŇčk a papa k…ôŇčan efi m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęK…Ē Isifu …õŇčkaf…ôl…õ p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôter…õn…õ kosu, k…ôluks…õ ka ay…õk Ňča p…ôl…õc mp…õ s…ônay…Ē k…Ē m…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē Ňčasom a paloku Isifu: ¬ęPapa kam …õnasom nt…õ a p…ôcfi:  
\v 17 ‚ÄĻNt…õ t…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēloku Isifu: O! Il…õts…õn'am m…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ aw…õnc …ôm aŇča p…ôl…õc k…Ē kiciya k…ôŇčan, bawo Ňčanay…Ē …ôm p…ôl…õc! Il…õts…õn'am m…ôŇčaŇčn…õ oŇč kiciya ka acar a Kanu ka papa kam!‚Äļ¬Ľ K…Ē Isifu ombok nt…õ analoku k…Ē moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 18 K…Ē aw…õnc aŇča Ňčander Ňča s…ôrka Ňčat…õmp…õn…õ Isifu d…ônt…Ēf k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęS…ôn'…Ēf…Ē akaŇč…õ acar am.¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē Isifu oloku Ňča: ¬ęTa n…ônes…õ. Cep…Ē Kanu k'iy…Ēn…õ?  
\v 20 N…ônasek'em k…ôy…Ē ka p…ôl…õc. Mba Kanu k…ônakaf…ôli ti p…ôt…Ēt, k…ôlomps…õ ka nt…õ teyi m…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôyac ka defi da afum alar…ôm.  
\v 21 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, ta n…ônes…õ! Indetam…õ nu m…õfaŇč monu f…ôp k…Ē ma awut anu.¬Ľ K…Ē Isifu ontor…õ-tor…õ Ňča b…ôk…ôc, k'olok-lok…ôr…õ Ňča dim d'ant…Ēf. 
\p  
\v 22 K…Ē Isifu …õnd…õ Misira nk…Ēn k…Ē afum …Ēn. K'eyi doru meren tasar tin k…Ē w…ôco (110).  
\v 23 K…Ē Isifu …õn…ôŇčk awut a ∆źfrayim haŇč d…õt…õmp maas. K…Ē Makir, wan ka Manase, oŇčkom awut …Ēn l…ôŇčk ya Isifu k…ôroŇč.  
\v 24 K…Ē Isifu oloku aw…õnc aŇča: ¬ęK…ôfi k'inder. Mba Kanu k…ôndemar nu ilaŇč ti. Kanu k…ôndep…õn…õ nu nde at…Ēf Ňč…Ēk…Ē k…ônal…õk…õ Abraham, Siyaka k…Ē Yakuba layidi k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 25 K…Ē Isifu …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ awut a Yakuba k…ôd…õr…ôm, p…ôcloku: ¬ęKanu k…ôndemar nu ilaŇč ti. N…ôde n…ôp…õn…õ b…õnt yem, n…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ yi nn…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 26 K…Ē Isifu efi p…ôs…Ēt…Ē meren tasar tin k…Ē w…ôco (110). K'asop k…Ē ac…Ēl nŇč…õ Ňč…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôfi k…ôt…Ēte kat…ôna m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčamb…õr k…Ē kaŇčk…ôra ka tasar p…õpat d…ôndo at…Ēf Ňča Misira.